Je\u253?hun-bahry, de\u328?zi-Hazar arasy,\par
\u199?\u246?l \u252?st\u252?nden \u246?ser \u253?eli t\u252?rkmeni\u328?.\par
G\u252?l-gun\u231?asy \u8213? gara g\u246?z\u252?m garasy,\par
Gara dagdan iner sili t\u252?rkmeni\u328?.\par
\par
Hak sylamy\u351? bardyr onu\u328? sa\u253?asy,\par
\u199?yrpyn\u351?ar \u231?\u246?l\u252?nde neri-ma\u253?asy,\par
Re\u328?be-re\u328? g\u252?l a\u231?ar \u253?a\u351?yl \u253?a\u253?lasy,\par
Gark bolmu\u351? re\u253?hana \u231?\u246?li t\u252?rkmeni\u328?.\par
\par
Al-\u253?a\u351?yly b\u252?r\u228?p \u231?ykar perisi,\par
K\u252?kre\u253?ip bark urar anbary\u328? ysy,\par
Beg, t\u246?re, aksakal \u8213? \u253?urdu\u328? e\u253?esi,\par
K\u252?ren tutar g\u246?zel ili t\u252?rkmeni\u328?.\par
\par
Ol merdi\u328? ogludyr, mertdir pederi,\par
G\u246?rogly garda\u351?y, serho\u351?dyr seri,\par
Dagda-d\u252?zde kowsa, sa\u253?\u253?atlar, diri -\par
Ala bilmez, \u253?olbars ogly, t\u252?rkmeni\u328?.\par
\par
G\u246?w\u252?nler, \u253?\u252?rekler bir bolup ba\u351?lar,\par
Tartsa \u253?ygyn, er\u228?r topraklar-da\u351?lar,\par
Bir suprada ta\u253?\u253?ar kylynsa a\u351?lar,\par
G\u246?teriler ol ykbaly t\u252?rkmeni\u328?.\par
\par
G\u246?w\u252?n howalanar ata \u231?ykanda,\par
Daglar lagla d\u246?ner gy\u253?a bakanda,\par
Bal getirer, jo\u351?up der\u253?a akanda,\par
Bent tutdurmaz, gelse sili t\u252?rkmeni\u328?.\par
\par
Gapyl galmaz, d\u246?w\u252?\u351? g\u252?ni har bolmaz,\par
Gargy\u351?a, ne zora giriftar bolmaz,\par
Bilbilden a\u253?rylyp, solup, zar galmaz,\par
Da\u253?ym anbar sa\u231?ar g\u252?li t\u252?rkmeni\u328?.\par
\par
Tireler garda\u351?dyr, urug \u253?arydyr,\par
Ykballar ters gelmez, Haky\u328? nurudyr,\par
Mertler ata \u231?yksa, s\u246?we\u351? sarydyr,\par
Alamana \u253?\u246?r\u228?r \u253?oly t\u252?rkmeni\u328?.\par
\par
Serho\u351? bolup \u231?ykar, jiger daglanmaz,\par
Da\u351?lary syndyrar, \u253?oly baglanmaz,\par
G\u246?z\u252?m ga\u253?ra d\u252?\u351?mez, g\u246?w\u252?n eglenmez,\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?zl\u228?r \u231?aly t\u252?rkmeni\u328?.\par
\par
T\u220?RKMEN BINASY\par
Gurdugym aslynda bilgil, bu zemini\u328? myhydyr,\par
Erer ol erkan mydam, budur ki t\u252?rkmen binasy.\par
\par
Terki-d\u252?n\u253?\u228? e\u253?le\u253?ir ol, gelse rakyp ga\u351?yna,\par
Bil, polatdan bina bolan, budur t\u252?rkmen galasy.\par
\par
S\u252?le\u253?man, R\u252?stem-u Zal, Jem\u351?it o\u328?a bolmu\u351? geda,\par
G\u252?nde \u253?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? salsa le\u351?ger, degmez \u351?any\u328? belasy.\par
\par
Daglar ondan alar t\u228?lim, le\u351?geri sap-sap durar,\par
Her salanda Z\u252?lp\u252?karyn, artar \u253?igidi\u328? h\u246?wesi.\par
\par
Teke, \u253?omut, \u253?azyr, g\u246?kle\u328?, Ahal ili bir bolup,\par
Kylsa bir ja\u253?a \u253?\u246?ri\u351?, a\u231?ylar g\u252?l l\u228?lesi.\par
\par
K\u252?lli gyzylba\u351? baryny, atdy dag arkasyna,\par
Gije-saba \u253?atma\u253?ar, geler olary\u328? nalasy.\par
\par
Ger gadam ursa sa\u253?\u253?at, bolma\u253?ar ol du\u351?yg\u228?r,\par
Bendi kylyp ala bilmez, d\u252?\u351?mez t\u252?rkmen balasy.\par
\par
Aryplary dem-dem geler, to\u253?y bardyr her zaman,\par
Merdi-merdan s\u246?zl\u252?dir ol, \u253?okdur g\u246?w\u252?n hilesi.\par
\par
A\u253?dadyr Magtymguly, bolmaz g\u246?w\u252?nde bir gara,\par
Hak syla\u253?yp, kylmy\u351? nazar, bardyr onu\u328? sa\u253?asy.\par
\par
\u171?TURGUL\u187? DI\u221?DILER\par
Bir gije \u253?atyrdym t\u252?n\u252?\u328? \u253?arynda,\par
Bir d\u246?rt atly gelip: \u171?Turgul\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\u171?Habarmyz bar sa\u328?a pursat ja\u253?ynda,\par
\u350?ol \u253?erde \u228?rler bar, g\u246?rg\u252?l\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Nazarym \u253?eti\u351?ge\u231? \u351?ol d\u246?rt merdana,\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?m jo\u351?a geldi, ba\u351?ym gerdana,\par
\u350?ol wagtda bar idi iki diwana:\par
\u171?Durma, oglan, onda bargyl!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
\u350?ol iki diwana tutdy golumdan,\par
Alyban gitdiler duran \u253?erimden,\par
Bir y\u351?arat boldy \u351?ol wagt \u253?anymdan:\par
\u171?Sa\u253?ramda boluban durgul!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Oturypdyk, geldi iki pirzada,\par
G\u246?z\u252?nden \u253?a\u351? akar, dili dogada,\par
\u171?H\u252?w, Hak!\u187? di\u253?ip \u231?ykdy alty py\u253?ada,\par
\u171?Adam indi geler, g\u246?rg\u252?l!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Bir d\u246?rt atly geldi, bary sebzebaz,\par
Hasalary \u253?a\u351?yl, aty teblebaz,\par
\u171?Mejlis halkasyny gurma\u328? be\u253?le az,\par
Adam k\u246?pd\u252?r, ulug gurgul!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Da\u351?dan \u231?ykdy altmy\u351? atly, g\u246?rd\u252?ler,\par
\u171?Muhammet!\u187? di\u253?p, bary gar\u351?y bardylar,\par
Saglyk-salamatlyk bir-bir sordular,\par
\u171?Durma\u328?, ulug ja\u253?a \u253?\u246?rg\u252?l!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Bir aty\u328? ardyna bizi berdiler,\par
Sa\u253?ramda - \u351?ol ja\u253?a baryp durdular,\par
Tamam oturdylar, mejlis gurdular,\par
\u171?Oglan \u8722? ma\u328?a \u8722? ara girgil!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
\u171?Alydyr\u187? di\u253?diler, tutdy destimden,\par
Bor\u253?a d\u252?\u351?egimi aldy astymdan,\par
Men bilmedim, bir zat gu\u253?dy \u252?st\u252?mden,\par
\u171?\u221?olugan d\u246?wrandyr, s\u252?rg\u252?l!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Ha\u253?dardan soradym bar\u231?a atba-at:\par
\u171?Hezreti pygamber \u8722? oldur, bolma \u253?at,\par
Ol \u8722? Eslim hojadyr, ol \u8722? Baba z\u252?r\u253?at,\par
Ol - We\u253?sil-Karandyr, bilgil!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
\u171?Ol \u8722? Bahaweddindir, ol hem bir \u228?rdir,\par
Biri Ze\u328?\u328?i Baba ol-da namdardyr,\par
Ol s\u246?\u253?en\u351?ip duran d\u246?rt \u199?ary\u253?ardyr,\par
Maksady\u328? ne bolsa a\u253?gyl!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
\u350?ol wagtda duran birki \u351?yhy-\u351?ap,\par
\u171?Bu oglana pata beri\u328? - di\u253?di - sap -\par
\u221?\u252?z \u253?igrimi d\u246?rt m\u252?\u328? enbi\u253?a, eshap,\par
Barysy \u351?olardyr, bilgil!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Resulalla a\u253?dy: \u171?\u221?a, \u350?ahymerdan,\par
E\u253?-\u228?, Eslim hoja, \u253?a, Baba Selman,\par
Abu Bekr Syddyk, \u253?a, Omar, Osman,\par
Bu gulu\u328? maksadyn bergil!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Eslim, Baba Selman bu\u253?urdy merde,\par
Py\u253?alany tutup, saldylar derde,\par
Gitdi akyl-hu\u351?um, \u253?atdym \u351?ol \u253?erde,\par
\u171?Ar\u351?da-fer\u351?de ne bar, g\u246?rg\u252?l!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
\u221?el boldum, \u253?\u252?g\u252?rdim \u253?eri\u328? damarna,\par
Nazarym tokundy Ar\u351?y\u328? kemerne,\par
\u171?Jebrut \u228?leminde Jelil syryna -\par
Gelip, \u246?z\u252?\u328? garap g\u246?rg\u252?l!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
N\u228?ge hy\u253?al etsem, ele getirdim,\par
Ka\u253?da baksam, o\u328?a nazar \u253?etirdim,\par
Bu hal ile men parahat \u253?atyrdym,\par
\u221?\u252?z\u252?me t\u252?\u253?k\u252?rip: \u171?Tur, gul!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Resulalla a\u253?dy: \u171?Eshaplar, \u253?\u246?r\u252?\u328?,\par
Oglany uzady\u328?, bir pata beri\u328?\u187?,\par
Bu\u253?urdy d\u246?rt atla: \u171?Eltip tab\u351?yry\u328?,\par
Getiren ja\u253?y\u328?da go\u253?gul!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Turup Magtymguly g\u246?z\u252?n a\u231?ypdyr,\par
Serine ne k\u246?\u253?ler gelip ge\u231?ipdir,\par
Esrek ner dek ak k\u246?p\u252?kler sa\u231?ypdyr,\par
\u171?Oglan, Alla \u253?ary\u328?, bargyl!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
\u196?LEME BELGILIDIR\par
Dostlar-a, dostum meni\u328? jandan \u351?irin s\u246?\u253?g\u252?lidir,\par
Jan kibi pynhan jahanda \u228?leme belgilidir.\par
\par
Ba\u351? bile barsam o\u328?a, handan olursa g\u252?zeri,\par
Tutsam ol \u253?erde watan, ol \u253?er ki onu\u328? \u253?oludyr,\par
\par
Di\u253?erdi \u253?ar: Men a\u351?ygym \u246?z elim-le katl edem,\par
Ondan owwal gam meni pa\u253?mal edip almalydyr.\par
\par
\u214?zge a\u351?yklary\u328? olsa pa\u253?y bent z\u252?lp-taryna,\par
Men garyby\u328? bent o\u328?a hem a\u253?agy, hem elidir,\par
\par
Ga\u253?ry-le bezm e\u253?le\u253?ip, e\u253?lese ho\u351? k\u246?\u328?l\u252?ni \u253?ar\par
Mejlis i\u231?re \u253?at edip di\u253?: \u171?Ol garyp ga\u253?gylydyr\u187?.\par
\par
\u221?az geler, wagt-da gider, gaflata batmy\u351? g\u246?zlerim,\par
A\u231?a\u253?yn di\u253?sem a\u231?ylmaz, ne agyr u\u253?kulydyr.\par
\par
Bilme\u253?en soranlara a\u253?dy\u328? bu garyp adymyz,\par
Asly gerkez, \u253?urdy Etrek, ady Magtymgulydyr.\par
\par
G\u214?KLE\u327?\par
\u199?\u246?le \u231?ykar bolsa, me\u328?z\u228?r,\par
Ke\u253?ige, gulana g\u246?kle\u328?.\par
T\u228?sip edip, s\u246?we\u351? etse,\par
D\u246?ner a\u231? arslana g\u246?kle\u328?.\par
\par
Ili\u328? \u253?urduny byrakmaz,\par
Bela bakmaz, \u253?owuz \u253?okmaz,\par
Alladan emirdir, \u231?ykmaz -\par
Bu s\u246?z\u252?m \u253?alana, g\u246?kle\u328?.\par
\par
Ylham etdi M\u246?wlam ma\u328?a,\par
Nazar d\u252?\u351?di senden \u253?a\u328?a,\par
\u221?ok bolar kast eden sa\u328?a,\par
Ga\u253?dyp dol G\u252?rgene, g\u246?kle\u328?.\par
\par
S\u246?zi agzyma Hak salar,\par
Bir nepes a\u253?dylan bolar,\par
\u221?amanlyk e\u253?le\u253?en geler,\par
\u171?Nurbat!\u187? di\u253?p, amana, g\u246?kle\u328?.\par
\par
Hyru\u231? e\u253?l\u228?p tursa mawyr,\par
Permana geler Ny\u351?apur,\par
\u214?wr\u252?ler bu d\u246?wran-d\u246?w\u252?r\par
\u196?hli-musulmana, g\u246?kle\u328?.\par
\par
Haraba d\u246?ner Horasan -\par
At a\u253?agna galar \u253?egsan,\par
Yrak gitse Mazanderan,\par
Gelerler permana, g\u246?kle\u328?.\par
\par
Dini\u328? durar Hak nury dek,\par
G\u252?\u253?j\u252?n artar Rum zory dek,\par
Asly\u351?ar sen a\u231? b\u246?ri dek,\par
Ma\u351?k edip me\u253?dana, g\u246?kle\u328?!\par
\par
Zor bi\u253?r sypahy\u328? s\u246?we\u351?e,\par
D\u246?wleti\u328? \u246?\u328?k\u252?den da\u351?a,\par
Gyly\u231? urup gyzylba\u351?a, -\par
Dolar sen E\u253?rana, g\u246?kle\u328?!\par
\par
Be\u253?ik dergaha \u253?\u252?z s\u252?rt\u252?p,\par
Isl\u228?rin - d\u246?wleti\u328? artyp,\par
Pyragy di\u253?r, do\u351?un tartyp,\par
Barar sen T\u228?hrana, g\u246?kle\u328?!\par
\par
\u214?\u327?I-ARDY BILINMEZ\par
G\u246?kle\u328?, \u253?omut t\u228?sip edip \u246?z\u252?nden,\par
\u199?ekdi go\u351?un, \u246?\u328?i-ardy bilinmez.\par
Sygma\u253? \u231?ykdy De\u351?ti-Dahan d\u252?z\u252?nden,\par
\u221?\u246?r\u228?n \u253?oly, gonan \u253?urdy bilinmez.\par
\par
Garga salsa, tugun bile depi\u351?er,\par
Ha\u253?batyndan daglar-da\u351?lar gapy\u351?ar,\par
\u214?li turup, dirilere \u253?apy\u351?ar,\par
Arslany, tilkisi, gurdy bilinmez.\par
\par
\u220?\u231? m\u252?\u328? na\u253?zabazy bardyr n\u246?kerden,\par
D\u246?rt m\u252?\u328? pildary bar gala \u253?ykardan,\par
Teke, salyr \u253?\u246?ri\u351? etse \u253?okardan,\par
Du\u351?many\u328? namardy, merdi bilinmez.\par
\par
\u196?hli s\u252?nni namys edip gelerler,\par
Gala \u253?ykyp, bagyn berbat kylarlar,\par
D\u246?w \u231?ekip, Yspyhan \u351?\u228?hrin alarlar,\par
Bu kentleri\u328? \u252?\u231?i-d\u246?rdi bilinmez.\par
\par
Magtymguly, Alyny\u328?dyr bu me\u253?dan,\par
Ne i\u351? tutar, g\u246?r\u252?\u328?, bu Omar, Osman,\par
At deminden doldy zemin-u asman,\par
Horasany\u328? h\u228?ki-gerdi bilinmez.\par
\par
D\u214?KER BOLDUK \u221?A\u350?YMYZ\par
Ist\u228?r - elden \u231?yka d\u246?wlet huma\u253?ym,\par
Doga kylyp, d\u246?ker bolduk \u253?a\u351?ymyz.\par
Dilegim du\u351? e\u253?le, g\u246?zel Allahym,\par
Ersgin boldy gitdi gyzylba\u351?ymyz.\par
\par
Hydyr gezen \u231?\u246?lde iller \u253?a\u253?ylsyn,\par
\u221?urt binamyz ga\u253?ym bolsun, go\u253?ulsyn,\par
\u199?ille mest nerlermiz bar\u231?a a\u253?ylsyn,\par
Bir suprada eda bolsun a\u351?ymyz.\par
\par
Derw\u252?\u351?ler k\u246?\u328?li jem dursun namaza,\par
\u221?igitler \u253?ygylsyn s\u246?hbete-saza,\par
Ilimiz ula\u351?syn sowulmaz \u253?aza,\par
Togsan dolup, tamam bolsun gy\u351?ymyz.\par
\par
T\u252?rkmenler baglasa bir \u253?ere bili,\par
Gurudar Gulzumy, der\u253?a\u253?y-Nili,\par
Teke, g\u246?kle\u328?, \u253?omut, \u253?azyr, alili,\par
Bir paty\u351?a gulluk etsek b\u228?\u351?imiz.\par
\par
Magtymguly, du\u253?dy, jany\u328? dirligne,\par
Musulmany go\u253?ma, kapyr horlugna,\par
Rowa\u231? bergil \u253?omut, g\u246?kle\u328? birligne,\par
Ol Kemal han owgan bolsun ba\u351?ymyz.\par
\par
\u199?OWDUR HAN \u220?\u199?IN\par
Ahmet paty\u351?adan habar tutmaga,\par
Umyt etdi iller \u199?owdur han \u252?\u231?in.\par
Sag baryp, salamat ga\u253?dyp gelm\u228?ge,\par
O\u328?mady ykballar \u199?owdur han \u252?\u231?in.\par
\par
Baglar do\u328?up galdy, \u253?agy\u351?lar gezm\u228?n,\par
Bulut b\u246?klek saldy, bu derde d\u246?zm\u228?n,\par
Zemin za\u253?a boldy, pelekler lerzan,\par
Jennet boldy \u231?\u246?ller \u199?owdur han \u252?\u231?in.\par
\par
Kaza gahra m\u252?ndi - perin syndyrsa,\par
Pelek hy\u253?al etdi - m\u228?hrin indirse,\par
Der\u253?a jo\u351?a geldi - suwdan gandyrsa,\par
Mu\u351?tak boldy k\u246?ller \u199?owdur han \u252?\u231?in.\par
\par
Yzy\u328?da galdylar il intizary\u328?,\par
Umyt bilen gezdi Annahal \u253?ary\u328?,\par
Atanazar boldy \u231?ekere zary\u328?,\par
G\u246?zle\u253?-g\u246?zle\u253? \u253?ollar \u199?owdur han \u252?\u231?in.\par
\par
Barsa, pa\u253?y belli soltanda-handa,\par
Iller bilme\u253? galdy - armany janda,\par
Kazadyr, kysmatdyr \u221?ezdde, Kermanda,\par
Meger tartdy ganlar \u199?owdur han \u252?\u231?in.\par
\par
Gurralar g\u252?\u328? boldy, pallar \u351?um boldy,\par
Baranlar bent boldy, \u253?ollar bim boldy,\par
\u199?e\u351?meler h\u246?\u351?k boldy, da\u351?lar mum boldy,\par
Gu\u253?a boldy diller \u199?owdur han \u252?\u231?in.\par
\par
S\u246?\u253?le, Magtymguly, \u228?lem bilsinler,\par
Ja\u253?y jennetdedir, g\u252?w\u228? bolsunlar,\par
\u171?Hak rehmet etsin!\u187? di\u253?p, doga kylsynlar,\par
Tamam ulus-iller \u199?owdur han \u252?\u231?in.\par
\par
\u199?OWDUR HAN\par
G\u246?kle\u328?, \u253?omut, \u253?ola \u231?ykyp, baky\u351?yp,\par
Umyt etdi, geler aman, \u199?owdur han.\par
Molla, m\u252?fti Haka doga oky\u351?yp,\par
Gutardylar kitap \u8722? Gurhan, \u199?owdur han.\par
\par
Gu\u351?-gumursy id\u228?p dagdan ge\u231?diler,\par
Balyklar \u253?ol di\u253?ip suwun i\u231?diler,\par
Gelin-gyzlar gyrmyz donlar bi\u231?diler,\par
Kamysdan lybaslar hem don, \u199?owdur han.\par
\par
Daglar ba\u351?yn egdi, duman b\u252?rendi,\par
\u221?eller galabilm\u228?n, \u253?erde s\u252?\u253?rendi,\par
A\u253?-G\u252?n batyp, g\u246?kde Myrryh g\u246?r\u252?ndi,\par
Bulutlar boldular baran, \u199?owdur han.\par
\par
Malyn ta\u351?lap geldi \u231?opan-\u231?oluklar,\par
Kenara \u231?ykdylar suwdan balyklar,\par
\u214?z\u252?n tuta bilm\u228?n \u253?erde halklar,\par
Tartdylar barysy efgan, \u199?owdur han.\par
\par
Bezirgenler yrak \u253?olun unutdy,\par
S\u246?wdag\u228?rler malyn yza uzatdy,\par
A\u253?lar-g\u252?nler batdy, zarlap da\u328? atdy,\par
Yns-jyns tartyp arman, \u199?owdur han.\par
\par
Dolandylar Hindistana baranlar,\par
E\u328?re\u351?diler merdan ady\u328? soranlar,\par
Kelamylla a\u231?yp, ykbal garanlar,\par
Tapmady derdi\u328?e derman, \u199?owdur han.\par
\par
Tartan oky hi\u231? \u231?ykmady sa\u253?\u253?ady\u328?,\par
Titretdi \u228?lemi \u199?owdur han ady\u328?,\par
Sany, hesibi \u253?ok gel\u253?\u228?n per\u253?ady\u328?,\par
Dyza \u231?\u246?k\u252?p \u253?yglar Turan, \u199?owdur han.\par
\par
Magtymguly, u\u231?dy ol algyr gu\u351?um,\par
Arkadagym, eziz syrda\u351?, garda\u351?ym,\par
Many sa\u231?a bilmez \u231?alaran ba\u351?ym,\par
B\u252?r\u228?p aldy ony duman, \u199?owdur han.\par
\par
ZARLAR I\u199?INDE\par
\u199?owdur han, g\u246?rejim, g\u246?w\u252?n diregim,\par
Sen wepat bolup sen zarlar i\u231?inde.\par
G\u246?kle\u328?de p\u228?lwanym, ile geregim,\par
Halky go\u253?up gitdi\u328? narlar i\u231?inde.\par
\par
Gelebilmez idi bady\u328?dan du\u351?man,\par
Gelen tapdy gitdi zoru\u328?dan pu\u351?man,\par
Goja dagdan b\u228?ri \u8722? g\u246?kle\u328?e a\u351?man,\par
Bizi go\u253?up gitdi\u328? marlar i\u231?inde.\par
\par
Pelek seni\u328? g\u252?l \u246?mr\u252?\u328?i soldurdy,\par
Hazan degdi, now gun\u231?a\u328?y \u253?oldurdy,\par
Gara daglar d\u246?zme\u253?, serin galdyrdy,\par
\u199?e\u351?min \u253?a\u351?lar duman-garlar i\u231?inde.\par
\par
Kime nesip etdi yspyhan \u253?a\u253?y\u328?,\par
S\u246?z\u252?m galat d\u228?ldir, behi\u351?tdir ja\u253?y\u328?,\par
G\u246?kle\u328?, \u253?omut \u8213? we\u253?ran boldy sara\u253?y\u328?,\par
Pelek we\u253?ran etdi harlar i\u231?inde.\par
\par
Magtymguly, hemdem, akyl-syrda\u351?y\u328?,\par
Tutabilmez \u246?z\u252?n, d\u246?k\u252?p g\u246?z\u253?a\u351?yn,\par
Duman aldy daglar kemerin, ba\u351?yn,\par
A\u253?-g\u252?nler batdylar zarlar i\u231?inde.\par
\par
D\u214?WLETALYNY\u327?\par
S\u252?nn\u252?\u253?e s\u252?t\u252?ndir, kapyra setdir,\par
\u199?alsa tygy-tizi D\u246?wletalyny\u328?.\par
\u196?lemde dessandyr, illerde hatdyr,\par
S\u246?hbet i\u231?re s\u246?zi D\u246?wletalyny\u328?.\par
\par
S\u246?zleri pent bolup galdy dillerde,\par
Pakyrlar penahy \u253?aman g\u252?nlerde,\par
Yrak \u252?lkelerde, \u253?akyn illerde,\par
Dost-du\u351?many razy D\u246?wletalyny\u328?.\par
\par
\u199?oh jahangir etdi \u246?mri bolyn\u231?a,\par
\u221?aradan \u253?ok edip, \u253?ere salyn\u231?a,\par
\u221?alan\u231?yda \u253?a\u253?nap, t\u228?ki \u246?lin\u231?\u228?,\par
Sowulmady \u253?azy D\u246?wletalyny\u328?.\par
\par
Har ge\u231?mez her kimi mydam islese,\par
Takdyrdan da\u351? \u231?ykmaz ge\u328?e\u351? taslasa,\par
B\u252?rg\u252?di alardy la\u231?yn beslese,\par
\u350?ir alardy bazy D\u246?wletalyny\u328?.\par
\par
Agyr uruglydyr hem be\u253?ik illi,\par
K\u246?p \u253?ygylsa me\u351?hur, \u228?lemde belli,\par
Me\u253?danda - gyly\u231?ly, diwanda - dilli,\par
\u221?\u252?ze ta\u253?dyr \u246?zi D\u246?wletalyny\u328?.\par
\par
Dileg etse, do\u328? da\u351?lary erider,\par
Gazap etse, h\u246?kmi daglar \u253?\u246?r\u252?der,\par
G\u252?ne\u351?den g\u246?wherdir, A\u253?dan d\u252?r\u252?dir,\par
Pelekde \u253?yldyzy D\u246?wletalyny\u328?.\par
\par
Sansyz ile serkerdedir, soltandyr,\par
Je\u328? \u253?erinde jellat, belki, arslandyr,\par
Menzili \u8722? metjitdir, \u246?\u253?i \u8722? diwandyr,\par
Gijesi-g\u252?ndizi D\u246?wletalyny\u328?.\par
\par
Temennasy \u253?erden asmana de\u328?dir,\par
Bi\u351?ede babyrdyr, dagda pele\u328?dir,\par
G\u228?mige labyrdyr, der\u253?a n\u228?he\u328?dir,\par
Her \u253?an barsa \u246?zi D\u246?wletalyny\u328?.\par
\par
Na\u231?arlary\u328? e\u328?re\u351?erler sag-solda,\par
Hi\u231? biri bolmady derdi\u328?e dalda,\par
Bedew bagda galdy, \u253?olda\u351?y \u253?olda,\par
Di\u253?inmez habary D\u246?wletalyny\u328?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ge\u231?di d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de de\u328?siz,\par
T\u246?relikde \u8722? ta\u253?syz, \u228?rlikde \u8722? e\u328?siz,\par
Pygamber \u8722? pe\u253?sizdir, S\u252?le\u253?man \u8722? so\u328?suz,\par
\u350?o\u328?a me\u328?z\u228?r yzy D\u246?wletalyny\u328?.\par
\par
GE\u199?DI DI\u221?DILER\par
E\u253? \u253?aranlar, \u253?owuz dessan bitildi,\par
Bir go\u231?ak panydan ge\u231?di di\u253?diler.\par
Ahyrzaman boldy, aftap tutuldy,\par
A\u253?-G\u252?n\u252?\u328? \u351?uglasy \u253?a\u351?dy di\u253?diler.\par
\par
N\u228?gehan ugrady a\u253?ralyk dagy,\par
Se\u253?dim Tarhan \u231?eker derdi-pyragy,\par
\u214?mr\u252?ni\u328? hasyly \u8722? \u253?al\u328?yz \u231?yragy,\par
Bady-hazan urup, \u246?\u231?di di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Gitdi \u214?wezgeldi, \u253?ene \u231?oh zatlar,\par
Bozuldy s\u246?hbetler, gam boldy \u351?atlar,\par
Garda\u351?lar, syrda\u351?lar, \u253?akyn-u \u253?atlar,\par
Gara ge\u253?ip, gan \u253?ygla\u351?dy di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Bedew atly, bek kemerli, \u253?aragly\par
D\u246?wlete, zynata, malyna bagly,\par
Myhmanly bir \u228?rdir, zatly, otagly,\par
Bir belent ordasy \u231?a\u351?dy di\u253?diler.\par
\par
\u221?ekelik hesreti ba\u351?dan \u246?termi\u351?,\par
Ogulsyzlyk bar\u231?a i\u351?den betermi\u351?,\par
Z\u252?r\u253?atsyz \u253?igidi\u328? orny \u253?itermi\u351?,\par
\u221?urdy \u253?ok, kerweni g\u246?\u231?di di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Magtymguly, T\u252?rk\u252?stany\u328? t\u246?resi,\par
Bir go\u231?akdyr - S\u246?\u253?\u252?nhany\u328? seresi,\par
\u221?ygyn g\u246?rki, \u253?ow g\u252?n\u252?ni\u328? \u246?resi,\par
U\u351?bu gara \u253?eri gu\u231?dy di\u253?diler.\par
\par
SEN SOLTANY, ABDYLLA\par
Mazanderan seni\u328? mekany\u328?, \u253?urdu\u328?,\par
\u350?ul mekany\u328? sen soltany, Abdylla.\par
Ta\u328?rym, nesibedir bir ro\u253?un g\u246?rd\u252?m,\par
Ol baglary\u328? sen re\u253?hany, Abdylla.\par
\par
Gulluga m\u228?t\u228?\u231?dir Bagdad-u Turan,\par
Ga\u253?rasy Arka\u231?dyr, ilersi E\u253?ran,\par
Pere\u328?de, Rumda \u231?oh ady\u328? soran,\par
Bulgary\u328? g\u246?wheri, k\u228?ni, Abdylla.\par
\par
Bulgar \u351?asy sa\u328?a iberdi haty,\par
Ta\u328?rym bag\u351? e\u253?lemi\u351? size rehmeti,\par
Pata berer Muhammedi\u328? ymmaty,\par
Dirilik \u231?e\u351?m\u228?ni\u328? jany, Abdylla.\par
\par
Sa\u328?a zardyr Arabystan, Hindistan,\par
Nagra\u328?dan titir\u228?r oldy T\u252?rk\u252?stan,\par
\u221?ollady k\u246?p sowgat dagly G\u252?rj\u252?stan,\par
Owgan halypany\u328? rany, Abdylla.\par
\par
Sypaty\u328? og\u351?a\u253?yr R\u252?stem-u Zala,\par
Ba\u351? go\u351?du\u328?yz Hatyja de\u253? z\u252?lala,\par
Altmy\u351? oglan sunup berer py\u253?ala,\par
Bu jahany\u328? sen p\u228?lwany, Abdylla.\par
\par
H\u246?k\u252?mi\u328?den titr\u228?r T\u252?rk\u252?stan \u351?asy,\par
Sa\u328?a m\u228?t\u228?\u231? hany-begi, gedasy,\par
Bir s\u246?z\u252?\u328?ni\u328? bardyr m\u252?\u328?l\u228?p dogasy,\par
D\u252?zerem men bu dessany, Abdylla.\par
\par
Pyragy Ta\u328?ryny\u328? \u253?azykly guly,\par
Hi\u231? kimse bilme\u253?\u228?r nedir ykbaly,\par
\u199?ohdan gu\u231?sa\u328? \u253?ene h\u252?\u253?r gyz jemaly,\par
Degr\u228?\u328?de \u253?igitler hany, Abdylla.\par
\par
ALY SIZI\u327?DIR\par
S\u252?r, Fath serdar ogly, geldi wagt,\par
\u221?ene bu d\u246?wrany-aly sizi\u328?dir.\par
K\u246?ne agyr d\u246?wlet t\u228?ze eder bagt,\par
Be\u253?iklik, serdarlyk \u253?oly sizi\u328?dir.\par
\par
Yl\u253?as kimin ebr \u231?\u246?ken suwlarda,\par
Kowus kimin duman d\u252?\u351?en daglarda,\par
Gen\u231?li \u351?\u228?her, Hydyr gezen \u231?\u246?llerde,\par
Kadyr beren d\u252?n\u253?\u228? maly sizi\u328?dir.\par
\par
Bag\u351?a\u351?y\u328? bent eder biler-bilmezi,\par
Ykbaly\u328? nist eder dogry gelmezi,\par
D\u252?kan k\u228?ni \u8722? Jahangiri\u328? almazy,\par
Badah\u351?an magdany - lagly sizi\u328?dir.\par
\par
Gahry\u328?yza du\u351?an - guma bula\u351?ar,\par
Kerem\u328?ize du\u351?an - ar\u351?a ula\u351?ar,\par
Be\u253?iklik besaty size \u253?ara\u351?ar,\par
Feriduny\u328? fert ykbaly sizi\u328?dir.\par
\par
Samarkant tagtynda gurlan \u253?a\u253?lara,\par
M\u228?ti dek hylap siz sebze pa\u253?lara,\par
S\u252?le\u253?man dek s\u246?z\u252?\u328? \u253?\u246?rir suwlara,\par
Isgender dek der\u253?a saly sizi\u328?dir.\par
\par
Ma\u351?ryga \u253?\u252?z urup \u231?yksa\u328? Horasan,\par
Owwal k\u252?rt sizi\u328?dir, so\u328?ra \u221?azyr han,\par
Zir pa\u253?y-esbi\u328?iz Yrak, Yspyhan,\par
Dagystan ha\u351?amy-ha\u253?ly sizi\u328?dir.\par
\par
S\u246?z\u252?m \u253?erde galmaz, di\u253?digim geler,\par
Nazarym kim\u253?adyr, mis altyn bolar,\par
Parsa \u231?\u246?ken d\u246?wlet size \u246?wr\u252?ler,\par
Indi bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? me\u253?li sizi\u328?dir.\par
\par
Erenler \u231?etr alyp, ba\u351?y\u328? daldarlar,\par
Hydyr, Yl\u253?as rekaby\u328?yz \u253?eld\u228?rler,\par
On bir ymam golu\u328?yzdan goldarlar,\par
Jylaw\u328?yzda ymam Aly sizi\u328?dir.\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, Rum dek o\u253?anmaz,\par
Isgender gorsudyr d\u246?w\u252?lmez, synmaz,\par
Dag kimin deprenmez, der\u253?a dek d\u246?nmez,\par
Bu, \u253?omut, g\u246?kle\u328?i\u328? ili sizi\u328?dir.\par
\par
AR\u350?Y-AGLA\u221?A\par
\u221?a Ahmet \u351?a, \u253?erde \u253?a\u253?ylyp \u231?awu\u328?,\par
Ady\u328? asman gider ar\u351?y-agla\u253?a.\par
Gelen n\u246?keri\u328?dir, gelme\u253?en awu\u328?,\par
Be\u253?iklik zinesin kyl pa\u253?a-pa\u253?a.\par
\par
E\u253?rana gyly\u231? ur, \u253?\u246?r\u252?t sypahy,\par
Ba\u351?y\u328?da berk olsun d\u246?wlet kulahy,\par
Huma\u253?un dagynda \u351?irleri\u328? \u351?ahy,\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? bir n\u228?he\u328? sen m\u246?wji-der\u253?a\u253?a.\par
\par
Bi\u351?eleri\u328? aw a\u328?ta\u253?an \u351?iri sen,\par
Rumustan be\u253?nisi, d\u246?w\u252?\u328? biri sen,\par
Zal ogluny\u328? almaz pe\u253?kan, tiri sen,\par
G\u252?\u351?tasp ogly dek belli bela\u253?a.\par
\par
Pi\u351?\u228?\u328? E\u253?ran bolsa, pu\u351?tu\u328? Turandyr,\par
Dost i\u351?i\u328?e ho\u351?wagt, du\u351?man ha\u253?randyr,\par
Ykbaly\u328? a\u231?ylar, i\u351?i\u328? d\u246?wrandyr,\par
Merhemet nazary\u328? salsa\u328? bir ja\u253?a.\par
\par
Pyragy di\u253?r, rowa\u231? berer sen dini,\par
\u350?alary\u328? \u351?alary, yslamy\u328? ze\u253?ni,\par
Emri\u328?e mutyg et E\u253?ran zemini,\par
Roz-u \u351?eb naly\u351?ym budur Huda\u253?a.\par
\par
FETDAH\par
E\u253?ran, Turan indi golu\u328? astynda,\par
\u171?S\u252?rg\u252?n\u187? indi bu d\u246?wrany sen, Fetdah.\par
K\u252?lli t\u252?rkmen o\u253?nar \u231?\u246?l\u252?\u328? \u252?st\u252?nde,\par
D\u246?kme, bilgin, nahak gany sen, Fetdah.\par
\par
Bu g\u252?n \u351?a sen, erte geda bolar sen,\par
Ilden-g\u252?nden, dinden jyda bolar sen,\par
Bir g\u252?n jany\u328? \u231?ykyp, pida bolar sen,\par
Gazanypsy\u328? \u231?oh g\u252?n\u228?ni sen, Fetdah.\par
\par
G\u246?z\u252?m \u253?et\u253?\u228?r, bilse\u328?, ba\u351?ym alar sen,\par
\u221?a k\u252?ndel\u228?p, meni \u231?a\u253?a salar sen,\par
Men hak di\u253?dim, sen \u231?oh g\u252?n\u228? galar sen,\par
Bu aly\u351?y\u328? bilen jany sen, Fetdah.\par
\par
Sen t\u252?rkmeni\u328? ilin-g\u252?n\u252?n soldurdy\u328?,\par
Ganlar d\u246?k\u252?p, g\u246?zel \u253?urdum doldurdy\u328?,\par
\u350?ehit bolanlary\u328? serin galdyrdy\u328?,\par
Unudar sen tagty-k\u228?ni sen, Fetdah.\par
\par
Halky\u328? \u246?ji \u231?ohdur, ykbaly\u328? \u253?aman,\par
\u221?a \u246?ler sen, \u253?a zyndandyr big\u252?man,\par
Tagty\u328? synyp, di\u253?me galar men aman,\par
\u199?\u252?nki z\u228?her kyldy\u328? nany sen, Fetdah.\par
\par
Permany\u328?dan tala\u328? d\u252?\u351?di illere,\par
Golu\u328? urdu\u328? n\u228?hak g\u246?zde sillere,\par
Kyrk gam\u231?ydan bu\u253?rdu\u328? n\u228?zik billere,\par
Der\u253?a etdi\u328? g\u246?zde huny sen, Fetdah.\par
\par
A\u253?yrdy\u328? atadan, ene, garda\u351?dan,\par
Gollardan, a\u253?akdan, sakaldan, sa\u231?dan,\par
Dendandan, zybandan, akyldan, hu\u351?dan,\par
Zyndan etdi\u328? bu jahany sen, Fetdah.\par
\par
A\u253?yrdy\u328?, agla\u253?yp galdy \u253?arlarmyz,\par
Pelege \u253?etendir tartan zarlarmyz,\par
Adamlar asylgy dur\u253?ar darlar\u328?yz,\par
\u221?\u252?zden tutdu\u328?, bil, gassaby sen, Fetdah.\par
\par
Pyragy, dert a\u253?dyp, derde \u253?anmaly,\par
Gan \u253?uwudyp, zalym Fetdah ganmaly,\par
Diri \u246?z\u252?m, l\u228?kin \u246?li sanmaly,\par
A\u328?sa \u246?ldir, bu dessany ol Fetdah.\par
\par
RE\u221?GAN E\u221?LEDI\par
Ga\u253?gy-gamda eziz \u246?mr\u252?m solduryp,\par
\u350?um pelek azabym re\u253?gan e\u253?ledi.\par
\u221?azan kitaplarym sile aldyryp,\par
G\u246?zlerim yzynda gir\u253?an e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
Gapyllykda du\u351?man aldy da\u351?ymyz,\par
Dargatdy her \u253?ana de\u328?i-du\u351?umyz,\par
B\u228?\u351? \u253?ylda bir kitap eden i\u351?imiz -\par
Gyzylba\u351?lar alyp, we\u253?ran e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
Bir ni\u231?\u228?miz goly bagly gul bolup,\par
Ni\u231?eler yzynda sargaryp, solup,\par
Kimi berip, onu\u328? bahasyn alyp,\par
Her kime bir belli baha e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
\u350?um pelek birehim, ma\u328?a bildirdi,\par
Aglamakdan g\u252?l \u253?\u252?zlerim soldurdy,\par
Gol\u253?azma kitabym sile aldyrdy,\par
Du\u351?manymy je\u253?hun der\u253?a e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
Ni\u231?eler d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de boldy bir ki\u351?i,\par
Ni\u231?\u228?ni\u328? agzyny doldurmaz a\u351?y,\par
Ni\u231?\u228?ni\u328? matamdan gutulmaz ba\u351?y,\par
Gije-g\u252?ndiz wawe\u253?leta e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
K\u246?\u253?d\u252?rer \u351?um pelek zulmy-jepasy,\par
\u221?alandyr, ynanma\u328?, \u228?hdi-wepasy,\par
Magtymguly, \u253?ok bu s\u246?z\u252?\u328? hatasy,\par
Pelek elip kaddym duta e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
G\u214?R\u220?LSIN INDI\par
Gorka-gorka \u252?flis \u253?agda\u253?a d\u252?\u351?d\u252?k,\par
Takdyr n\u228?me bolsa, g\u246?r\u252?lsin indi.\par
Pikir gazanynda ga\u253?nadyk, bi\u351?dik,\par
Degme, ol jo\u351? urup d\u246?k\u252?lsin indi.\par
\par
Ozal ba\u351?da Jepbar bar etdi \u253?okdan,\par
Ni\u231?\u228?ni nurundan, k\u246?pi toprakdan,\par
Habar geldi, dostlar, \u253?akyn-yrakdan,\par
Du\u351?mana gurt o\u253?ny gurulsyn indi.\par
\par
Oturmasyn kempir, \u253?a\u351?lar dul bolup,\par
Galma\u328?lar, t\u252?rkmenler, ile dil bolup,\par
Rakyp \u228?hli musulmana gul bolup,\par
Ilersi So\u328?udaga s\u252?r\u252?lsin indi.\par
\par
G\u246?z bilen g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?iz, k\u246?pler gedadyr,\par
Ni\u231?eler aza\u351?dy, ni\u231?e pidadyr,\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, kuwwat berjek Hudadyr,\par
Aly z\u252?lp\u252?kary syrylsyn indi.\par
\par
N\u228?hak d\u246?k\u252?lmesin gyzyl ganymyz,\par
Du\u351?mana galmasyn be\u253?tin, nanymyz,\par
\u221?ada saly\u328?, amanatdyr janymyz,\par
Ta\u328?ra zerur bolsa, alynsyn indi.\par
\par
\u220?st\u252?mizden du\u351?man h\u246?k\u252?m s\u252?rendir,\par
M\u246?min bary jebri-jepa g\u246?rendir,\par
Ogul-gyzy har \u246?\u328?\u252?ne berendir,\par
Hemmeler ol ja\u253?dan \u231?ykylsyn indi.\par
\par
Pyragy \u253?\u252?z tutar t\u252?rkmen iline,\par
Du\u351?man gol urmasyn gyzyl g\u252?l\u252?ne,\par
Dostlar, bizem ahyreti\u328? siline,\par
Gark etm\u228?nk\u228?, rakyp \u231?apylsyn indi.\par
\par
\u221?\u214?RMELI BOLDY\par
E\u253? \u253?aranlar, musulmanlar,\par
Jebirde \u253?\u246?rmeli boldy.\par
Nije z\u228?hmet \u231?eken janlar,\par
Jepany g\u246?rmeli boldy.\par
\par
Jahan gi\u328?dir, melamat k\u228?n,\par
Arada k\u246?\u253?di \u351?irin jan,\par
\u220?st\u252?mizde rehimsiz han,\par
Bil ahyr urmaly boldy.\par
\par
Azypdyr g\u246?kle\u328? hanlary,\par
K\u228?n g\u246?rer bize hallary,\par
Go\u253?man s\u252?rdi bar mallary,\par
G\u246?z dikip durmaly boldy.\par
\par
Magtymguly, a\u253?ama jan,\par
Bili\u328? gu\u351?a, ge\u253? gazap don,\par
Hetden a\u351?dy bu zalym han,\par
Ahyr tor gurmaly boldy.\par
\par
G\u214?ZL\u196?R MEN\par
\u221?urdum Etrek, ilim g\u246?kle\u328?,\par
Men bir s\u246?wer \u253?ar g\u246?zl\u228?r men.\par
Jan \u351?\u228?hrine d\u252?\u351?di tala\u328?,\par
Kuwwat beren pir g\u246?zl\u228?r men.\par
\par
A\u253?ryldym ene-atadan,\par
G\u246?z\u252?m guwanjy-watandan,\par
Jan bermek asan hijrandan,\par
Haryt k\u246?p, bazar g\u246?zl\u228?r men.\par
\par
M\u228?mmetsapadyr garda\u351?ym,\par
Molla Matam sapakda\u351?ym,\par
Abdylla gelse basda\u351?ym,\par
Pygamber nazar g\u246?zl\u228?r men.\par
\par
\u221?\u252?regimden en\u231?e pygan,\par
G\u246?zden akdy bulaklap gan,\par
Syrda\u351? imes pelek-d\u246?wran,\par
Ga\u231?sam di\u253?p, mazar g\u246?zl\u228?r men.\par
\par
So\u328?udag, guwanjym meni\u328?,\par
Gezip men seri\u328?de seni\u328?,\par
Sa\u253?\u253?at men awlap jereni\u328?,\par
Sy\u253?a \u253?yl\u231?yr mar g\u246?zl\u228?r men.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu ky\u253?amat,\par
Go\u253?dy ba\u351?yma \u231?oh apat,\par
T\u252?rkmen ilim, e\u253?, adamzat,\par
Azat sil, g\u252?zer g\u246?zl\u228?r men.\par
\par
MOLLA AZADYM\par
Girdim janym \u351?\u228?hrine, myhman eredir bir ny\u351?an,\par
\u221?a-ha hijran, \u253?a-da pyrkat galdy, molla Azadym.\par
\par
\u221?el \u246?\u328?\u252?nden ga\u231?dy geldi, istedi ol pyrkaty,\par
Dokuz \u253?yldyr \u253?albaryp, boldy byradar, Azadym.\par
\par
J\u246?wlan urup her zaman ol almy\u351? golumdan karar,\par
Bent kylypdyr bagyny, g\u252?l soldy, bil, Azadym.\par
\par
Bu ne hadys, bu ne jebir, \u253?ygla\u253?yr aby-ku\u253?a\u351?,\par
Sylma\u253?an g\u246?z\u253?a\u351?larym, boldy hyrydar, Azadym.\par
\par
Derdime derman di\u253?ip, gezdi Lukman illeri,\par
Owazy j\u252?mle jahana doldy, molla Azadym.\par
\par
G\u246?r, meni\u328? bu derdimi \u228?\u351?g\u228?r kylarlar illere,\par
Gorkaram \u231?arhy-pelekden, boldy bizar, Azadym.\par
\par
Pyragy di\u253?r, derdime e\u253?le sen, atam, nazar,\par
Erse gitdi ygty\u253?ar, aldy kararym, Azadym.\par
\par
OGLUM - AZADYM\par
Azady:\par
Pa\u351? e\u253?le syry\u328?y, saklama pynhan,\par
Emma ki, s\u246?z\u252?mden \u231?ykmagyl, oglum!\par
G\u252?nde \u253?\u252?z k\u246?\u253? geler-ge\u231?er bu ba\u351?a,\par
Agyrtma k\u246?\u328?l\u252?mi, \u253?ykmagyl, oglum!\par
\par
Magtymguly:\par
- Utanardym, syrym pa\u351? e\u253?lemezdim,\par
Pa\u351? ederin, habar alsa\u328?, Azadym!\par
\u221?\u252?z k\u246?\u253? geler-ge\u231?er her g\u252?n bu ba\u351?a,\par
Ist\u228?ri bar, sapar kylsak, Azadym!\par
\par
Jepa urma \u246?z\u252?\u328?, \u231?agyr M\u246?wlany,\par
Arzuwlama hany, begi, soltany,\par
Besdir bize owwal Ta\u328?ry bereni,\par
Aldyrma k\u246?\u328?l\u252?\u328?i, gitmegil, oglum!\par
\par
Gidenmiz \u253?ok alty bile, b\u228?\u351? bile,\par
Se\u253?ran etsek ni\u231?e de\u328?-u du\u351? bile,\par
Meger \u351?onda gamgyn k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m ho\u351? bola,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l galkar, karar etmez, Azadym!\par
\par
Werzi\u351?i\u328? \u253?ok, \u253?a\u351? sen, gide bilmer sen,\par
\u350?\u246?w\u252?r bar, \u351?owhun bar, \u231?yda bilmer sen,\par
Her i\u351?e ba\u351? go\u351?up, ede bilmer sen,\par
Gitmeklik \u253?agda\u253?yn etmegil, oglum!\par
\par
Ki\u351?i s\u246?zleme\u253?en, syry pa\u351? olmaz,\par
\u221?ag\u351?ydan-\u253?amandan a\u328?lan \u253?a\u351? olmaz,\par
\u350?u gez ibermese\u328?, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m ho\u351? olmaz.\par
Ra\u253?ymyz ga\u253?tarma, go\u253?ber, Azadym!\par
\par
- Bizi be\u253?le ni\u231?ik terk edesi\u328? bar?\par
Bu \u253?ol bihudadyr, bir gidesi\u328? bar.\par
Gel, gitmegil, oglum, \u231?oh terhosym bar,\par
Ga\u253?ga, harajata batmagyl, oglum!\par
\par
- Kalbyma giripdir yslam h\u246?wesi,\par
Te\u328?\u328?edir, dirhemdir halky\u328? tamasy,\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?m n\u228?row etme, kylma terhosy,\par
Bir sapar i\u351?idir, go\u253?ber, Azadym!\par
\par
- Gurhan okap gezgil, \u253?ag\u351?y kelamdyr,\par
Birehim owgandyr, dini yslamdyr,\par
Garak\u231?ydyr \u253?ollar, hyzdyr, haramdyr,\par
\u214?lermi\u328?, galarmy\u328?, gitmegil, oglum!\par
\par
Syna\u253?yn, g\u246?re\u253?in, bu g\u252?n ykbalym,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y g\u252?n, ho\u351? s\u228?het gelipmi salym,\par
Kast edip janyma, \u253?etse ajalym,\par
Bu \u253?erde hem bolsa, tapar, Azadym!\par
\par
- Bilge\u351?le\u253?in \u246?z\u252?\u328? nir\u228? atar sen?\par
Ni\u231?ik i\u351?dir, muny be\u253?le tutar sen?\par
Di\u253?gil ahyr, kimi\u328? bile gider sen?\par
Dem tartyp, her \u253?ana bakmagyl, oglum!\par
\par
Jylawdary bolam \u221?azyr han piri\u328?,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l gu\u351?y perwaz urar pakyry\u328?,\par
Bu g\u252?n \u253?edi g\u252?nd\u252?r, \u171?Alhamd\u187? okyryn,\par
\u350?at e\u253?le k\u246?\u328?l\u252?mi, go\u253?ber, Azadym!\par
\par
- Azady di\u253?r, bile sapa s\u252?reli,\par
E\u253?sem ibereli, synap g\u246?reli,\par
\u171?\u196?min!\u187? di\u253?, tur, oglum, pata bereli,\par
Bir Ta\u328?ry \u253?ar olsun sa\u328?a git, oglum!\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar: galmy\u351?am \u231?ohdan,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l gu\u351?y telwas urar yrakdan,\par
Her \u253?erde saglygym iste ol Hakdan,\par
Doga kylyp, Haka \u253?albar, Azadym!\par
\par
ATAMY\u327?\par
Altmy\u351? b\u228?\u351?de, nowruz g\u252?ni, luw \u253?yly,\par
Turdy ajal, \u253?olun tusdy atamy\u328?.\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? i\u351?i be\u253?lemi\u351?, beli,\par
\u214?mr\u252?ni\u328? tanapyn kesdi atamy\u328?.\par
\par
Agyr d\u246?wletlere k\u246?\u328?\u252?l go\u253?mady,\par
Bu jahany\u328? e\u351?retini s\u246?\u253?medi,\par
Eski \u351?aldan artyk pu\u351?e\u351? ge\u253?medi,\par
Ahret \u246?\u253?i boldy kasdy atamy\u328?.\par
\par
Di\u253?rdi: \u171?D\u252?n\u253?\u228? durmaz, \u246?mre baky \u253?ok\u187?,\par
G\u252?ndiz roza, gije bolsa uky \u253?ok,\par
M\u252?\u328?k\u252?r bilmez, muhlyslary\u328? \u351?eki \u253?ok,\par
Pygamber destidir desti atamy\u328?.\par
\par
G\u246?rmesem, s\u246?\u253?lemen o\u253? bile \u231?enden,\par
Maksadyna \u253?eter \u253?ykylan \u231?yndan,\par
\u221?arysy melekden, \u253?arysy jyndan,\par
M\u252?jew\u252?rsiz bolmaz \u252?sti atamy\u328?.\par
\par
Nukaba di\u253?rler, \u252?\u231? \u253?\u252?z eren ugra\u351?dy,\par
\u199?iltende atama nazarym d\u252?\u351?di,\par
Nujaba barsam, heftenlere gary\u351?dy,\par
Abdallardyr \u231?yn pe\u253?westi atamy\u328?.\par
\par
\u196?lem i\u231?re adam galmaz, at gezer,\par
Bu syrlardan jahan halky \u253?at gezer,\par
Ja\u253?y jennet i\u231?re, g\u246?kde \u351?at gezer,\par
\u221?erde ho\u351?wagt \u253?atar posty atamy\u328?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, gizli syry\u328? bar i\u231?de,\par
K\u228?mil tapsa\u328?, kyl gullugyn dyry\u351?da,\par
Mag\u351?ar g\u252?n ga\u253?gysyz girer behi\u351?te, -\par
Her kim \u231?yndan bolsa dosty atamy\u328?.\par
\par
AZADYM KANY?\par
Pelek, id\u228?r idim, sen du\u231?ar boldu\u328?,\par
G\u246?z\u252?mi\u328? nurany - Azadym kany?\par
\u221?\u252?regim soguryp, seglere berdi\u328?,\par
\u350?\u228?hrimi\u328? soltany - Azadym kany?\par
\par
Ymamsyz galandyr metjit-m\u228?hrabym,\par
Dogmady nur sa\u231?yp ol mahy-tabym,\par
\u221?owuz galdym, sil alypdyr etrabym,\par
G\u246?wn\u252?mi\u328? ummany - Azadym kany?\par
\par
\u350?ekerlikden z\u228?her boldy s\u246?zlerim,\par
Zagpyran dek sargarypdyr \u253?\u252?zlerim,\par
Kuwwat gitdi, gubarlandy g\u246?zlerim,\par
M\u252?nberim azany - Azadym kany?\par
\par
D\u246?rt paslym nar boldy, daglar eredi,\par
Diriler u\u231?dular, \u246?li \u253?\u246?redi,\par
Giden baryp Haka ma\u328?la\u253? diredi,\par
Ilimi\u328? zybany - Azadym kany?\par
\par
Topraklar sil boldy, siller gum boldy,\par
Humlar jam boldular, jamlar hum boldy,\par
H\u246?wesler \u253?as boldy, pi\u351?\u228?m gam boldy,\par
\u221?\u252?regim aramy - Azadym kany?\par
\par
\u214?l\u252?ler direlip, arza bardylar,\par
Hakdan bir kelamy \u253?\u246?rip sordular,\par
\u199?oh \u253?albaryp, \u171?Go\u253?ber\u187? di\u253?ip durdular,\par
\u214?li-diri d\u246?wrany - Azadym kany?\par
\par
Kapyrlar bolupdyr \u253?yglap musulman,\par
Haka \u253?albarypdyr Hydyr, S\u252?le\u253?man,\par
Bug bolup g\u246?terldi ar\u351?a, g\u246?r, umman,\par
G\u246?kle\u328?i\u328? p\u228?lwany - Azadym kany?\par
\par
Armanym \u253?ok, pelek, bir s\u246?we\u351? kylsam,\par
\u221?a \u253?yksa\u328?, basylsam, \u253?a seri\u328? alsam,\par
Seglere a\u351? e\u253?l\u228?p, bazara salsam,\par
Bagymy\u328? re\u253?hany - Azadym kany?\par
\par
G\u252?w\u351?ler e\u351?itgende bary ker boldy,\par
Daglar er\u228?p akdy, da\u351?lar \u253?er boldy,\par
Mollalar Gurhansyz, pirler k\u246?r boldy,\par
Sahyplar Gurhany - Azadym kany?\par
\par
Zemin \u253?\u252?z\u252?n sy\u253?a duman e\u253?ledi\u328?,\par
Di\u253?gil pelek kimi aman e\u253?ledi\u328?,\par
Pyragyny, bak, biiman e\u253?ledi\u328?,\par
Namysym imany - Azadym kany?\par
\par
TERK E\u221?LEME BU MEKANY\par
E\u253?, garda\u351?ym, sen Abdylla,\par
Terk e\u253?leme bu mekany.\par
Gurbat bersin sa\u328?a Alla,\par
Hijrana salmagyl jany.\par
\par
Gider bolsa\u328? bu watandan,\par
Ny\u351?an algyl \u351?irin jandan,\par
\u214?ter bolsa\u328? ol ummandan,\par
Meger, goldar Nuhy nebi.\par
\par
\u221?al\u328?yz munda men galaram,\par
Pisada hemra bolaram,\par
Her dem \u253?atlap, gan aglaram,\par
Kyblam-atam Azadyny.\par
\par
Boz dumanly be\u253?ik daglar,\par
\u214?ter boldy ajap \u231?aglar,\par
Bihasap miweli baglar,\par
Pynhan kylyp sen bagbany.\par
\par
Pelek ne i\u351? ba\u351?a saldy,\par
Jismimden janymy aldy,\par
Uly iller n\u228?ho\u351? boldy,\par
Hak, uzatgyl ol Lukmany.\par
\par
Be\u253?tinler zaryna d\u246?zm\u228?n,\par
Bu jahany \u253?el de\u253? gezm\u228?n,\par
Umman i\u231?re girip \u253?\u252?zm\u228?n,\par
Bikarar kyldym Je\u253?huny.\par
\par
Agam, inim, ol garda\u351?ym,\par
\u214?ter boldy \u253?al\u328?yz ba\u351?ym,\par
Gaflat bolandyr syrda\u351?ym,\par
Zyndan kyldy\u328? bu jahany.\par
\par
Hany hemra\u253?ym, \u253?aranlar.\par
Hindistan sary \u253?\u246?renler,\par
Ajap jemaly g\u246?renler,\par
G\u246?rd\u252?\u328?izmi Me\u328?li hany?\par
\par
Terhos e\u253?l\u228?p galar boldum,\par
Jana jepa salar boldum,\par
Tagna bilen k\u246?\u253?er boldum,\par
Soldum g\u246?\u253?\u228? \u253?yl hazany.\par
\par
\u221?yglap, d\u246?kd\u252?m hunum n\u228?hak,\par
A\u253?rylmady serden pyrak,\par
Bu s\u246?z\u252?me bir bawer \u253?ok,\par
\u221?at kyla\u253?yn ol Hudany.\par
\par
Ser ornuna bolupdyr pa\u253?,\par
Toprak \u8722? h\u228?ki \u246?wr\u252?lip ma\u253?,\par
Kime derdim \u228?\u351?g\u228?r kyla\u253??\par
Kime a\u253?dyp bu pynhany?\par
\par
G\u246?rmedim men mekan ary,\par
Kylmy\u351?am bihet nisary,\par
Hemra kyldym bazyg\u228?ri,\par
\u221?ortup gezip Hindistany.\par
\par
Ol lukmandan boldum hums,\par
Tilki-\u351?agal bolmu\u351? bars,\par
Molla \u228?hli d\u246?n\u252?p hyrs,\par
Unudypdyr ol Gurhany.\par
\par
S\u246?z di\u253?er men, kelam sorsa\u328?,\par
Odum \u253?andyr gola\u253? dursa\u328?,\par
Bir ak \u246?\u253?e barar bolsa\u328?,\par
Asla almaz ol myhmany.\par
\par
Umman i\u231?re \u253?\u252?zer har\u231?e\u328?,\par
\u221?ortgul bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni her \u231?en,\par
Dem gutarar, bilmez ha\u231?an,\par
T\u228? gelin\u231?\u228? Hak pe\u253?many.\par
\par
Kelam getirdim dilime,\par
Z\u252?nnar urmu\u351?am bilime,\par
Magtymguly di\u253?r, ilime.\par
Bag\u351? etmi\u351?em bar dessany.\par
\par
ABDYLLA\par
Sen gideli\u328? dokuz \u253?yldyr \u246?teni,\par
Ka\u253?da watan tutdu\u328?, garda\u351? Abdylla?\par
Dolanmazmy ynsan\u253?eti\u328? gideni,\par
Ka\u253?da watan tutdu\u328?, garda\u351? Abdylla?\par
\par
Daga arzym a\u253?dyp, tutdum habary\u328?,\par
Lal bolupdyr dili, di\u253?mez azary\u328?,\par
Ata-enesiz nedir seni\u328? karary\u328??\par
Ka\u253?da watan tutdu\u328?, garda\u351? Abdylla?\par
\par
Gorky pe\u253?dasy \u253?ok gidejek jana,\par
\u214?m\u252?r ahyr boldy, doldy pe\u253?mana,\par
\u221?a-da sen d\u252?\u351?d\u252?\u328?mi d\u252?\u253?ps\u252?z ummana?\par
Ka\u253?da watan tutdu\u328?, garda\u351? Abdylla?\par
\par
\u220?st\u252?mize hijran ody sepildi,\par
Kuwwatym gidipdir, dyzym epildi,\par
Gan \u253?yglap, atamy\u328? bili b\u252?k\u252?ldi,\par
Ka\u253?da watan tutdu\u328?, garda\u351? Abdylla?\par
\par
\u221?\u252?z\u252?m tutup \u231?ykdym jandar baryna,\par
\u214?z\u252?m rowa geldim hijran daryna,\par
D\u246?ze bilmen be\u253?tinleri\u328? zaryna,\par
Ka\u253?da watan tutdu\u328?, garda\u351? Abdylla?\par
\par
Ilde-g\u252?nde \u253?okdur meni\u328? kararym,\par
Dert \u252?st\u252?ne artdy ga\u253?ta azarym,\par
\u221?at boldy watany\u328?, \u246?\u253?\u252?\u328?-\u246?wzary\u328?,\par
Ka\u253?da watan tutdu\u328?, garda\u351? Abdylla?\par
\par
G\u252?w\u351? tutar men her di\u253?ilen s\u246?zlere,\par
Jepa berdi\u328? hijran bilen bizlere,\par
\u214?z\u252?m urar boldum oda-k\u246?zlere,\par
Ka\u253?da watan tutdu\u328?, garda\u351? Abdylla?\par
\par
G\u252?l\u252?p-o\u253?namadyk bile \u351?at bolup,\par
Ba\u351?dan gitdi\u328?, b\u252?tin bizden \u253?at bolup,\par
Magtymguly zar agla\u253?yr mat bolup,\par
Ka\u253?da watan tutdu\u328?, garda\u351? Abdylla?\par
\par
BULAR GELMEDI\par
G\u246?\u231?i-gony birle g\u246?\u231?di Abdylla,\par
Hemme giden geldi, bular gelmedi.\par
M\u228?mmetsapa gitdi k\u246?mek berm\u228?ge,\par
Uzadanlar geldi, bular gelmedi.\par
\par
Enesinden a\u253?ry \u253?atmaz oglanlar,\par
\u221?a, Rep, g\u246?ren barmy bulardan, iller,\par
A\u253?lany\u253?ar a\u253?lar, dolanyp \u253?yllar,\par
A\u253?lar-\u253?yllar geldi, bular gelmedi.\par
\par
Hassadan sagaldy z\u228?her dadanlar,\par
Algy alyp \u231?ykdy go\u253?un g\u252?\u253?denler,\par
Alty a\u253?lyk \u253?ola - K\u228?b\u228? gidenler,\par
Hajy bolup geldi, bular gelmedi.\par
\par
Yrakdan, \u253?akyndan baryp gelenler,\par
Barmydyr bulardan g\u246?r\u252?p, bilenler,\par
Hindistana bezirgenlik kylanlar,\par
Malyn satyp geldi, bular gelmedi.\par
\par
\u221?olukdy bir doly, degdi bir baran,\par
Birin \u253?urdy bile e\u253?ledi we\u253?ran,\par
Birisini\u328? \u253?ary yzynda ha\u253?ran,\par
G\u246?zleri \u253?oldadyr, bular gelmedi.\par
\par
\u221?ykylany\u328? bagry \u253?erden galmazmy,\par
Hi\u231? baran gelmezmi, aglan g\u252?lmezmi,\par
\u214?tenden-ge\u231?enden sorsa\u328? bilmezmi,\par
Bilinmezler geldi, bular gelmedi.\par
\par
Magtymguly, derdi go\u253?maz \u253?atmaga,\par
Ugrun bilmez sora\u253?-sora\u253? gitm\u228?ge,\par
\u221?erden jogap \u231?ykmaz habar tutmaga,\par
G\u246?ren-bilen barmy, bular gelmedi.\par
\par
U\u199? KYLDY\par
Abdylla gitdi di\u253?p umyt \u252?z\u252?pdim,\par
Bezirgenler gelip, ondan u\u231? kyldy.\par
Mejnun bolup, dagdan-daga gezipdim,\par
Galat boldy, gamly k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m \u246?\u231? kyldy.\par
\par
Gamdan dolup galdy bo\u351?an ba\u351?larym,\par
G\u246?z \u253?umuldy, \u231?ytyldylar ga\u351?larym,\par
Gurhan okap gezen de\u328?i-du\u351?larym,\par
Mal iste\u253?ip, \u231?ete baryp se\u231? kyldy.\par
\par
Elip kaddym bolup bardy, ne\u253?le\u253?, nun,\par
Kependir lybasym, i\u231?digimdir hun,\par
Ka\u253?sy, anyk bili\u328?, e\u253?ledi Mejnun,\par
Ilden-g\u252?nden ony a\u253?ra sa\u231? kyldy.\par
\par
Otly lybas pelek ma\u328?a ge\u253?dirip,\par
\u221?aksam di\u253?di g\u252?l \u253?\u252?z\u252?mi so\u253?duryp,\par
Bina kyldym golda barym k\u246?\u253?d\u252?rip,\par
\u350?e\u253?tan demin urdy, s\u246?wdam pu\u231? boldy.\par
\par
Kapas i\u231?re galmy\u351? gu\u351?lar gara\u351?yp,\par
Dura bilmez atlar b\u246?k\u252?p, dyza\u351?yp,\par
Y\u351?ky\u328? k\u246?\u231?esine d\u252?\u351?d\u252?m aza\u351?yp,\par
\u221?asawullar gelip, g\u246?wn\u252?m pa\u231? kyldy.\par
\par
Magtymguly, munda gelen g\u246?r\u252?\u351?ip,\par
\u214?td\u252?ler du\u351?umdan atyn s\u252?r\u252?\u351?ip,\par
De\u328?im-du\u351?um Medin\u228?ge \u253?\u246?r\u252?\u351?ip,\par
\u221?eke galdym, syrda\u351?larym haj kyldy.\par
\par
WE\u221?RANA GELDI\par
Ba\u253?ram gelin, Hanme\u328?li gyz, Janesen,\par
Bu dertleri\u328? ha\u253?sy birne \u253?ana sen,\par
\u199?arhy-pelek, her g\u252?n \u231?epe d\u246?ne sen,\par
Kalbymy\u328? d\u252?n\u253?\u228?si we\u253?rana geldi.\par
\par
\u220?\u231?\u252?\u328? ykbalyny batyrdy\u328? la\u253?a,\par
\u214?mr\u252?mi gam bilen \u246?t\u252?rdim za\u253?a,\par
\u350?am-u s\u228?her golum serdim Huda\u253?a,\par
Asman ahym g\u246?r\u252?p, gir\u253?ana geldi.\par
\par
Magtymguly, elip bilim buruldy,\par
Damarym dartyldy, ganym duruldy,\par
\u214?l\u252?m zarby \u252?\u231? tarapdan uruldy,\par
Akylym dagylyp, ha\u253?rana geldi.\par
\par
KA\u221?DA SEN?\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?in, tagty we\u253?ran S\u252?le\u253?manym, ka\u253?da sen?\par
Amanady berer boldum, bir imanym, ka\u253?da sen?\par
Tagty-t\u228?jim e\u253?esi, e\u253? soltanym, ka\u253?da sen?\par
Iki dide g\u246?rejim, sahypkyranym, ka\u253?da sen?\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
Bu pelegi\u328? zulmy bilen birje zaman g\u252?lmedi\u328?,\par
Wa\u253? purum di\u253?ip gala, men misgini almady\u328?,\par
To\u253?larymda \u351?at bolup sen, ajap nazar salmady\u328?,\par
Birje zaman eglenip sen ykbalymy bilmedi\u328?,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
Ser salyban bu zemine, arzymy men s\u246?zlesem,\par
Taparynmy, m\u228?hribanym, jemaly\u328?y g\u246?zlesem,\par
De\u351?te \u231?ykyp, zary-gir\u253?an, en\u231?e g\u252?nler bozlasam,\par
Bar\u231?a pi\u351?eden ge\u231?ip men bu jahany yzlasam,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
G\u252?l ro\u253?u\u328? g\u246?rmemi\u351?em, bu pelek gerdi\u351?iden,\par
Bihabar boldy nala\u253?yp, pelek tutan i\u351?iden,\par
Halas e\u253?l\u228?p \u246?ter boldy bu pany te\u351?w\u252?\u351?iden,\par
Indi men ge\u231?mi\u351?em, wa\u253?, bahar, nowruz, gy\u351?ydan,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
Ne hasraty \u246?t\u252?rip sen, k\u246?rd\u252?r g\u246?rmez g\u246?zlerim,\par
Uly jemagatlar i\u231?re boldy sy\u253?a \u253?\u252?zlerim,\par
Asal eripdi bu g\u252?n z\u228?her bolmu\u351? s\u246?zlerim,\par
Daglarym de\u351?te d\u246?n\u252?p, dag bolupdyr d\u252?zlerim,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
\u221?owuz galyp bu jahanda telmurar bu \u351?irin jan,\par
Sensiz indi men pakyram boldum, ne\u253?le\u253?, natuwan,\par
Gymmatyndan a\u253?rylypdyr, g\u246?z\u252?me zyndan jahan,\par
\u221?\u246?risem misli gu\u253?un dek, taparynmy bir ny\u351?an,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
Pederim, d\u246?zme\u253? bu derde huna bo\u253?\u253?almy\u351? Ku\u253?a\u351?,\par
Ol eziz jany\u328? bilen pelek, meger, kylmy\u351? tala\u351?,\par
Sil ornuna iki dide\u253?imden akmy\u351? ganly \u253?a\u351?,\par
Z\u228?hri-katyl \u253?uwudyp men, ge\u253?enim kepen pu\u351?e\u351?,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
Ger ki bir s\u246?we\u351? kylardym alnyda bolsam meger,\par
Bu hijrany\u328? \u231?arhy bilen ne\u253?le\u253? \u253?andy jany-jiger,\par
Hazan bady urdy g\u252?li, kyldy bagy serbeser,\par
K\u228?\u253?i\u351?imi Hak e\u351?itmez, \u253?anar boldy bu jiger,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
\u221?yglar boldy dagy-da\u351?lar ol rowany sil bilen,\par
Hak alnynda naly\u351? kylmy\u351? Je\u253?hun bahry, Nil bilen,\par
Bag i\u231?inde \u253?esir bolmu\u351? bilbil, baky\u328?, s\u252?nb\u252?l bilen,\par
Pederim Azady \u253?yglar \u253?omut, g\u246?kle\u328? il bilen,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
Pany jahandan gidipdir bakyga g\u246?zel a\u253?y\u328?,\par
Soltanyndan jyda d\u252?\u351?di, \u253?yglar boldy sara\u253?y\u328?,\par
\u220?z\u252?lipdir kir\u351?i onu\u328?, oksuz we\u253?randyr \u253?a\u253?y\u328?,\par
Di\u253?digim galat imesdir, meger, behi\u351?tdir ja\u253?y\u328?,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
A\u253?dadyr Magtymguly ki, bu dessany bagladym,\par
Men ki misgin perzendi\u328?em, daga \u231?ykyp agladym,\par
Sorag ja\u253?ynda \u351?ypa di\u253?p, \u221?aradany \u231?agladym,\par
Go\u253?ma\u253?an panyda bary bar\u231?any soragladym,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
\u350?\u196?HRI \u8722? IMANYM, KA\u221?DA SEN?\par
Wadaryg-a, ne\u253?lerem men, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
Iki d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u253?olda\u351?ym, \u351?\u228?hri-imanym, ka\u253?da sen?\par
G\u246?zlerimi\u328? r\u246?w\u351?eni, \u253?agty nuranym, ka\u253?da sen?\par
Ne\u253?lerem bag-u \u231?emeni, mahy-tabanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
\u350?um pelegi\u328? zulmudan \u231?ykmy\u351? jesetden jany, he\u253?,\par
Gitdi ol \u351?\u228?hri-behi\u351?te, a\u253?rylyp imany, he\u253?,\par
Sowuldy daglar ba\u351?ydan, \u253?agynly dumany, he\u253?,\par
Turdy naladan bu g\u252?n, ol guradyp ummany, he\u253?,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
G\u246?rmedim \u246?z rastyma, ol bakydan g\u252?l de\u253? \u253?\u252?z\u252?n,\par
Di\u253?di: \u171?G\u246?rmedim \u231?yragym\u187?, \u253?a\u351? edip iki g\u246?z\u252?n,\par
\u171?Pyragy! Pyragy!\u187? di\u253?p, unudyban ol s\u246?z\u252?n,\par
Berdi ol zemin i\u231?re biygty\u253?ar g\u246?rge \u246?z\u252?n,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
A\u253?ra d\u252?\u351?mez k\u228?kilik, \u231?\u246?lde go\u253?uban balasyn,\par
Agla\u253?yr bilbil mydam, \u228?leme \u253?a\u253?yp nalasyn,\par
Ak maraly\u328? owlagy \u231?yksa golundan, ne\u253?lesin,\par
\u350?um pelekde \u253?ok utan\u231?, saldy-la pyrkat hilesin,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
Il-g\u252?ni bolmasa \u351?alar tagtydan d\u252?\u351?er gider,\par
Salsa\u328? ol nara daragty, k\u252?l bolar, bi\u351?er gider,\par
Bozsa\u328? ki ary hinini, d\u246?wr e\u253?le\u253?ip, \u252?\u253?\u351?er gider,\par
\u214?lse g\u246?z astyda owlak, g\u228?besi \u231?i\u351?er gider,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
\u221?ygna\u253?yrlar mallary bir ki\u351?i e\u253?l\u228?p sarywan,\par
Ukuda \u253?atsa ki\u351?i, mallar ki \u231?a\u351?ar big\u252?man,\par
Du\u351?adyr b\u246?rige her dem, galma\u253?a biri aman.\par
D\u252?\u351?di ba\u351?ymga ki, dostlar, be\u253?le bir ahyrzaman,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
Il-uluslar zar edip, kyldy \u246?z\u252?ni har-u zar,\par
Gy\u351? paslyga \u246?wr\u252?lib\u228?n, gitdi ol pasly-bahar,\par
Gu\u253?dy bulutlar \u253?agmyryn, halyma e\u253?l\u228?p gahar,\par
Jo\u351?duryp d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u253?\u252?z\u252?n, umman de\u253?in siller akar,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
Girmi\u351?em baga rowan, solmu\u351? ki g\u246?rd\u252?m g\u252?llerim,\par
Tyg degme\u253?en, tamy \u246?s\u252?p \u246?lm\u252?\u351? ki ol bilbillerim,\par
\u199?ykdy der\u253?a kenaryndan, akdy d\u252?n\u253?\u228? sillerim,\par
Agla\u253?yr A\u253?ym-G\u252?n\u252?m, matam tutuban illerim,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
Go\u231? \u253?igitni\u328? goludan ga\u231?dy bu g\u252?n, g\u246?r, gylyjy,\par
Uzamaz, \u253?etmez, zeminde, \u253?okdur onu\u328? alajy,\par
D\u246?kdi \u253?apragyn birden, \u253?as tutup serwi agajy.\par
Da\u253?y, dogan-garda\u351?y zar e\u253?le\u253?ip hem-de bajy.\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
A\u253?ra d\u252?\u351?\u252?p k\u228?beden, go\u253?dum Pyragy adyma,\par
Il-ulus, hazynadan d\u252?\u351?mez bir zerre \u253?adyma,\par
G\u246?rdi garak\u231?y bu g\u252?n, gol urdy g\u246?wher zadyma,\par
Eredi daglary\u328? da\u351?y, \u231?ydamady oduma,\par
Walydam, Mekge-Medin\u228?m, m\u228?hribanym,\par
ka\u253?da sen?\par
\par
A\u221?RYLYP\par
Gitdi g\u246?zlerim r\u246?w\u351?eni, \u351?irin jandan a\u253?rylyp,\par
Tagty-bagtym boldy we\u253?ran, \u351?a-jahandan a\u253?rylyp.\par
Soldy bagym g\u252?lleri, anbar-re\u253?handan a\u253?rylyp,\par
Kyldy je\u328?\u328?i ol rakyplar, zor p\u228?lwandan a\u253?rylyp,\par
Gitdi sabrym-takatym m\u228?hribandan a\u253?rylyp.\par
\par
Dadyma hi\u231? kimse \u253?etmez, bir \u253?azykly gul menem,\par
Suw gadryn balyk biler, gadry bilinmez sil menem,\par
Z\u228?hri jandarlar i\u253?erler, z\u228?hri-katyl bal menem,\par
Andalybyn aldyran \u351?ol bagty gara g\u252?l menem,\par
Gitdi sabrym-takatym m\u228?hribandan a\u253?rylyp.\par
\par
\u196?hli be\u253?tin \u253?ygla\u351?ar, nalasy ar\u351?a \u253?etip,\par
Bendi kyldy men pakyry, g\u246?rg\u252?l ol pelek tutup,\par
Etdi illere wejera, kylyban o\u253?un edip,\par
\u221?ollady hijran \u351?\u228?hrine, ol ajal pe\u253?man satyp,\par
Gitdi sabrym-takatym, m\u228?hribandan a\u253?rylyp.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y di\u253?ip gol uranym, \u231?ykdy bagtyma \u253?aman,\par
Depmi\u351?em bedew di\u253?ip, g\u246?r, e\u351?ek olmu\u351?dyr\par
\u231?aman.\par
D\u246?kdi nurun ol pelek, z\u228?heri \u253?ere daman,\par
Bu halyma rehmi inip, aglady \u351?\u228?hri-\u221?emen,\par
Gitdi sabrym-takatym m\u228?hribandan a\u253?rylyp.\par
\par
G\u246?zlerimden u\u231?dy ruhy, g\u246?\u253?\u228?ki \u253?az \u253?agmyry,\par
Bakdym ykbalyma a\u231?yp, kylmadym men sabyry,\par
Toba kyldym gara bagtym, e\u253? Hak, algyl \u246?m\u252?ri,\par
G\u246?zleme\u253? ahyryn i\u351?i\u328?, nara saldym bagyry,\par
Gitdi sabrym-takatym, m\u228?hribandan a\u253?rylyp.\par
\par
Di\u328?lemez arzymy ol Hak, mende, dostum,\par
\u231?\u228?re \u253?ok,\par
Eredi janym-jigerim, g\u246?rg\u252?l, tende \u253?ara \u253?ok,\par
Berdi\u328? ynsana azary, ne pelekde para \u253?ok,\par
Di\u253?r Pyragy, ne de\u328?sizlik, bu hijranda gara \u253?ok,\par
Gitdi sabrym-takatym m\u228?hribandan a\u253?rylyp.\par
\par
BAGTYM GARADYR\par
Bu ne bela, bu ne hasrat, ne gowga,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
Naly\u351? etsem, arzym \u253?etmez ol Huda,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
Pelek dost bolupdyr alag\u246?z bile,\par
Derdimi di\u328?lemez, di\u253?sem s\u246?z bile,\par
Ilimi ugratdy dagy-d\u252?z bile,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
G\u246?rogly dek ga\u253?ratymdan a\u253?ryldym,\par
Gojalyp men, kuwwatymdan a\u253?ryldym,\par
Iki did\u228?m \u8722? z\u252?r\u253?adymdan a\u253?ryldym,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
\u350?am-u s\u228?her \u253?ata bilmen parahat,\par
\u221?\u252?regim telmurar g\u246?w\u252?n bitakat,\par
K\u228?b\u228?m, kyblam, garda\u351? boldular wepat,\par
Rehm eden bolmady bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
Pelege du\u351?an aw ga\u231?yp gutulmaz,\par
Tartan oky adam ogly, atylmaz,\par
\u221?eke \u228?ri\u328? \u246?m\u252?r ady tutulmaz,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
De\u328?im-du\u351?um her bir k\u228?re bula\u351?dy,\par
Dostlar yrak d\u252?\u351?di, hijran dola\u351?dy,\par
Yhlasym, myradym gama ula\u351?dy,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
Ba\u351?yma \u351?um pelek her g\u252?n s\u252?r\u252?ner,\par
\u221?owuz d\u252?\u351?en g\u246?wre kime direner,\par
\u221?amanlar g\u246?z\u252?me eziz g\u246?r\u252?ner,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
Sarwanym aza\u351?dy, dargady malym,\par
Ykbalym ke\u231? turdy, gitdi hy\u253?alym,\par
Altmy\u351?a azm urdy garta\u351?an salym,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
Gama erkim berdim, hu\u351?um dargatdym,\par
Sara\u253? we\u253?ran, kerwenimi ugratdym,\par
Me\u328?li hanym \u8722? y\u351?k s\u246?wdasyn unutdym,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u231?ohlara bipe\u253?an boldy,\par
Garyp golun serdi, gury san boldy,\par
Namartlar mert boldy, ile han boldy,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
Ah, ne\u253?le\u253?, \u246?t\u252?rd\u252?m \u253?igitlik \u231?agym,\par
Daragty gurady, bo\u351? galdy bagym,\par
Dumany sowuldy, eredi dagym,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?etmez \u253?yglap kararym,\par
Bo\u351? galdy d\u252?kanym, dargady barym,\par
Pa\u253? astyna d\u252?\u351?di namysym-arym,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
BAR MENI\u327?\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, ne\u253?le\u253?in men, k\u246?\u253?en janym\par
bar meni\u328?,\par
Bazary we\u253?ran bolupdyr, ol d\u252?kanym\par
bar meni\u328?.\par
Dowzah odundan beter ata\u351? suzanym\par
bar meni\u328?,\par
Y\u351?ka \u246?z\u252?n gurban kylan bir perwanym\par
bar meni\u328?,\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?in sepil gezip, Hindistanym bar meni\u328?.\par
\par
G\u252?l \u253?\u252?z\u252?ni kylsa pu\u351? ol, A\u253?-G\u252?n ondan u\u253?alar,\par
Bag i\u231?ine girse meger, \u351?uglasyndan g\u252?l solar,\par
Nazar salsa gazap bilen, bu jahan we\u253?ran bolar,\par
\u214?l\u252?ler jana girip, betbagtlar ykbal alar,\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?in ol arap zyban, asal zybanym\par
bar meni\u328?.\par
\par
Geldi ebir, kyldy s\u246?we\u351? su\u253?y-asman sa\u253?yda,\par
Behi\u351?t Erem hasyl olmu\u351? bu jahan sara\u253?yda,\par
Se\u253?il kylyp geler boldy Remezany\u328? a\u253?yda,\par
Dowzahlar behi\u351?t bolupdyr, toba e\u253?l\u228?p ja\u253?yda,\par
Bu zemini\u328? \u252?zresinde l\u228?mekanym bar meni\u328?.\par
\par
K\u252?lli \u228?lem y\u351?ky birlen ot alyp nara bi\u351?er,\par
Ro\u253?una mu\u351?tak bolupdyr, k\u246?wkepler \u253?ere d\u252?\u351?er,\par
Serwiler g\u252?l bitirip, etrapyna g\u246?zel \u252?\u253?\u351?er,\par
Jemal \u252?zre hindi hala ha\u253?randyr ha\u253?rul-be\u351?er,\par
K\u252?lli \u228?lem g\u246?zelinden zy\u253?at jenanym bar meni\u328?.\par
\par
Kapas i\u231?re telmuryp, y\u351?kyna perwana men,\par
Bilbil oldum, \u253?etmedim, ol g\u246?zel re\u253?hana men,\par
Ser salyp kyldym nazar, bu y\u351?ky-pynhana men,\par
Y\u351?ky bilen h\u228?kister bolan natuwana men,\par
Istemez men ol behi\u351?ti, behi\u351?t mekanym bar meni\u328?.\par
\par
G\u246?renleri\u328? g\u246?zi do\u253?maz, g\u246?rmegen arman \u231?eker,\par
Ro\u253?una ma\u253?yl bolup men, t\u252?t\u252?nim asman \u231?ykar,\par
Bagy i\u231?re bolsam hasyl, alnymdan re\u253?han \u231?ykar,\par
Z\u252?lpi-sy\u253?a k\u228?kilinden g\u246?zel zeref\u351?an \u231?ykar,\par
Zeref\u351?an dahyl emesdir, Nil - ummanym bar meni\u328?.\par
\par
De\u351?te sa\u253?\u253?at bolup girse, gutarmaz bir maraly,\par
Bent e\u253?lemi\u351? bir z\u252?lp\u252?ne Kadyr Suhan bu haly,\par
Bahyllar p\u228?lin unudyp, sadaka kylmy\u351? maly,\par
Bilmenem, janymdamy ol g\u246?zeli\u328? hy\u253?aly,\par
G\u252?l ro\u253?una g\u252?nde \u253?anyp, en\u231?e pyganym bar meni\u328?.\par
\par
Zaryma toba kylypdyr go\u328?\u351?y, garda\u351?, illerim,\par
Bilbile intizardyr bag i\u231?inde g\u252?llerim,\par
Zemin bilen s\u252?\u253?renipdir de\u328?zi Hazar \u253?ellerim,\par
A\u253?dadyr Magtymguly, asal ermi\u351?dir dillerim,\par
Ar\u351? i\u231?re mekan tutan ajap dessanym bar meni\u328?.\par
\par
MENI\par
\u221?a\u328?\u328?y halym tagna kylyp, bak, kibir etdi\u328? meni,\par
\u221?ow-le \u252?flaslara menzil-mekandar etdi\u328? meni.\par
Gurby giden dyzlarma bigadyr bar etdi\u328? meni,\par
Ku\u253?a\u351?ymy bent kylyp, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge zar etdi\u328? meni,\par
Biwatan namartlara bag\u351?y-di\u253?ar etdi\u328? meni.\par
\par
Hana i\u231?re bent e\u253?le\u253?ip, ryzkym Karuna berip,\par
\u199?yn-Ma\u231?yny, Rum, Horezmi \u253?\u246?rd\u252?m ykbal\par
agtaryp,\par
\u214?tdi \u253?azym, geldi gy\u351?ym, galdym indi sargaryp,\par
Be\u253?tullany\u328? ja\u253?y i\u231?re hasyl boldum k\u246?p \u253?\u246?rip,\par
Zaglar gonan g\u252?lleri\u328?de, ne\u253?le\u253?, anbar\par
etdi\u328? meni.\par
\par
Y\u351?k ata\u351?yn iste\u253?ip bir gir\u253?any perwana men,\par
G\u228?hi y\u351?ka bolsam du\u231?ar, k\u246?z\u252?ne bir\u253?ana men,\par
Mejnun kibi Le\u253?li \u253?ary\u328? ro\u253?una gir\u253?ana men,\par
Akly \u231?a\u351?an, bagty \u253?atan, bir misgin big\u228?ne men,\par
Daga urup darga\u253?an ummanda lemmer\par
etdi\u328? meni.\par
\par
Sara\u253?ymy bada berip girdim Je\u253?hun bahryna,\par
Lemmerleri azm urup atlandylar gahryna,\par
Guwwas kibi \u253?\u252?z\u252?p \u231?yksam, du\u351?dum a\u382?dar\par
z\u228?hrine,\par
Hazan uran kemine men, han kyldy\par
Lutu\u328? \u351?\u228?hrine,\par
Tagt ornuna nar \u252?st\u252?nde Ispendi\u253?ar etdi\u328? meni.\par
\par
Daga-da\u351?a takat berme\u253?, gezdim derman iste\u253?ip,\par
U\u231?dum su\u253?y-asman \u252?zre men S\u252?le\u253?man iste\u253?ip,\par
Hemra isl\u228?p d\u228?li-diwan men natuwan iste\u253?ip,\par
H\u246?km e\u253?ledi\u328? Ybra\u253?yma sen ki gurban iste\u253?ip,\par
\u350?ol Ybra\u253?ym goly i\u231?re, ne\u253?le\u253?, pur etdi\u328? meni.\par
\par
Tanybilmez boldy serim, altynmy sen, zermi sen?\par
\u221?a ki Karun merjeni sen, \u253?akutmy sen, d\u252?rmi sen?\par
G\u252?l-gun\u231?amy \u253?a ki baldak, \u253?a ki \u253?aprak, permi sen?\par
A\u382?darmy sen, jellatmy sen, \u253?a ki toprak, \u253?ermi sen?\par
Mert eripdim, kylyp namart, ile g\u252?ftar etdi\u328? meni.\par
\par
Dynma\u253?an men, \u246?t\u252?p \u246?mr\u252?m bu pelegi\u328? jebriden,\par
Saldy le\u351?ger jem kylypdyr, \u231?ykdym ga\u231?yp\par
\u351?\u228?hriden,\par
Lukman \u253?\u252?ze tartmy\u351? perde men pakyry\u328?\par
zarydan,\par
Magtymguly, men ge\u231?mi\u351?em d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u8722? her ne\par
barydan,\par
Ol Isaga bagy\u351? kylma\u253?, namarda har etdi\u328? meni.\par
\par
A\u221?T\par
Bady-saba, arzymy ol \u253?owuz dogana a\u253?t,\par
Elmydam zar e\u253?legen, g\u246?zleri hun-gana a\u253?t.\par
\u350?um pelegi\u328? golundan gitgen ol-janana a\u253?t,\par
A\u253?ra d\u252?\u351?\u252?p, gam \u231?eken, garabagt hana a\u253?t,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?den armanly bolgan ol pahyr perwana a\u253?t.\par
\par
Ne bolupdyr, ne seb\u228?pdir, g\u246?rmerem men \u253?\u252?z\u252?ni,\par
Gara ganlara bo\u253?ap oturmy\u351? ki g\u246?z\u252?ni,\par
Bizaram mal-u m\u252?lkden, ger e\u351?tmesem s\u246?z\u252?ni,\par
Nirde gapyl e\u253?le\u253?ip, bent kyldy\u328? sen \u246?z\u252?ni,\par
Derdimi\u328? yzharyny ol emin-Lukmana a\u253?t.\par
\par
Bizleriden \u253?at kylyp, bent e\u253?ledi\u328? ki dilini,\par
Ata-eneden a\u253?yryp, \u252?zd\u252?\u328?-e\u253?, sen bilini,\par
Hijrana rowa\u231? e\u253?le\u253?ip, \u253?atyryp sen \u253?elini,\par
Agtaram, \u231?a\u253? tapma\u253?an, iki g\u246?z\u252?m silini,\par
Jany-aramy\u328? takaty ol be\u253?ik ummana a\u253?t.\par
\par
Kyldylar k\u228?b\u228?mi we\u253?ran, \u253?okdur indi ga\u231?arym,\par
\u199?ykdy gitdi gollarymdan jan \u351?\u228?hrimi\u328? a\u231?arym,\par
\u220?zd\u252?ler bu ganatymy, \u253?okdur-e\u253? me\u253?l u\u231?arym,\par
D\u252?\u351?di tala\u328? hazynaga, gutardy mal sa\u231?arym,\par
Halymy\u328? bu te\u328?ligin egsilmez d\u252?kana a\u253?t.\par
\par
Haka arzym budur, e\u253?, dost, kylsyn azat garda\u351?y,\par
Akyban, der\u253?aga d\u246?ndi, m\u246?w\u231? urup g\u246?zler \u253?a\u351?y,\par
Go\u253?dy alnyma getirip, pelek a\u253?ralyk a\u351?y,\par
Di\u253?, ni\u231?ik zar kylmasyn Pyragy, \u253?okdur syrda\u351?y,\par
Iki d\u252?n\u253?\u228? geregim, arzuwly imana a\u253?t.\par
\par
\u350?IRGAZY\par
Mekan e\u253?l\u228?p, \u252?\u231? \u253?yl i\u253?dim duzu\u328?y,\par
Gider boldum, ho\u351? gal, g\u246?zel \u350?irgazy.\par
\u214?t\u252?rdim gy\u351?y\u328?y, nowruz-\u253?azy\u328?y,\par
Gider boldum, ho\u351? gal, g\u246?zel \u350?irgazy.\par
\par
Hakdan bize bu\u253?ruk, baglydyr bilim,\par
Sende taglym aldy, a\u231?yldy dilim,\par
Gelsin di\u253?ip garar ol gerkez ilim,\par
Gider boldum, ho\u351? gal, g\u246?zel \u350?irgazy.\par
\par
Seljerer men indi agy-garany,\par
Dost, rakyp, garda\u351?ym, Haky, \u253?arany,\par
Okadym, g\u246?terdim kitap, Gurhany,\par
Gider boldum, ho\u351? gal, g\u246?zel \u350?irgazy.\par
\par
Aklym gysga erdi, k\u228?s\u228?m ga\u253?nady,\par
Jiger telwas urdy, g\u246?w\u252?n o\u253?nady,\par
......................................................\par
Gider boldum, ho\u351? gal, g\u246?zel \u350?irgazy.\par
\par
Jo\u351?gun \u253?\u252?regimde m\u246?w\u231? urar, \u253?atmaz,\par
Ga\u253?nar, gazaplanar, hi\u231? la\u253?a batmaz,\par
Ylym-taglym alan seni unutmaz,\par
Gider boldum, ho\u351? gal, g\u246?zel \u350?irgazy.\par
\par
Pe\u253?man dolma\u253?, gelsek takat \u253?etme\u253?en,\par
Pynhan zahyr kylmaz akyl gitme\u253?en,\par
Bady-pa\u253? atlanyp, se\u253?ran etme\u253?en,\par
Gider boldum, ho\u351? gal, g\u246?zel \u350?irgazy.\par
\par
Rige girsem-de, guwwas \u253?\u252?zer men,\par
Bihasrat \u253?a\u253?na\u253?am, bigam gezer men,\par
Dahan i\u231?re asal-zyban ezer men,\par
Gider boldum, ho\u351? gal, g\u246?zel \u350?irgazy.\par
\par
K\u228?mil bolup, serenjam ki kylyp men,\par
Mu\u351?fykymdan - ol pederden galyp men,\par
K\u228?b\u228?mden a\u253?rylyp, jyda bolup men,\par
Gider boldum, ho\u351? gal, g\u246?zel \u350?irgazy.\par
\par
Kutbda sa\u253? g\u246?zl\u228?p, g\u252?mana du\u351?dum,\par
Ne\u253?san gu\u253?dy, umman \u8722? ga\u253?nadym-jo\u351?dum,\par
Ho\u351? gal, bu g\u252?n Je\u253?hun bahrydan a\u351?dym,\par
Gider boldum, ho\u351? gal, g\u246?zel \u350?irgazy.\par
\par
Magtymguly ta\u351?lap g\u246?w\u252?n hapasyn,\par
Sylady pirini, molla-sopusyn,\par
Da\u253?ym unutmaz men tylla gapysyn,\par
Gider boldum, ho\u351? gal, g\u246?zel \u350?irgazy.\par
\par
BADY-SABANY G\u214?RSEM\par
Dehistany\u328? ba\u253?rynda,\par
Bady-sabany g\u246?rsem.\par
Bahaweddin, Mirkulal,\par
Ze\u328?\u328?i Babany g\u246?rsem.\par
\par
Nagle\u253?ni ar\u351?a t\u228?\u231?dir,\par
Ady \u228?leme pa\u231?dyr,\par
Iki jahan m\u228?t\u228?\u231?dir,\par
Arap zybany g\u246?rsem.\par
\par
Gelen ge\u231?er \u231?\u228?\u351?t edip,\par
Eglenmez g\u252?ze\u351?t edip,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l a\u253?dar ke\u351?t edip,\par
Gezsem, jahany g\u246?rsem.\par
\par
Hydyr kimin \u231?\u246?llerde,\par
Yl\u253?as kimin suwlarda,\par
Kowus kimin daglarda,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?amany g\u246?rsem.\par
\par
\u221?okarda Hindistany,\par
Arkada T\u252?rk\u252?stany,\par
\u214?wl\u252?\u253?\u228?ler ummany\par
Ol Rumystany g\u246?rsem.\par
\par
Jan d\u228?li, jahan \u351?e\u253?da,\par
Munda ne bolmaz pe\u253?da,\par
\u221?edi dag, \u253?edi der\u253?a, -\par
D\u228?li d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni g\u246?rsem.\par
\par
Magtymguly ho\u351? bolsa,\par
Aksa did\u228?m, \u253?a\u351? bolsa,\par
Imanym \u253?olda\u351? bolsa,\par
Barsam, K\u228?b\u228?ni g\u246?rsem.\par
\par
DA\u350?LAR BILE\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l a\u253?dar: halkdan galyp,\par
Gezsem daglar-da\u351?lar bile.\par
\u221?azygymy \u253?ada salyp,\par
\u221?\u252?z\u252?m \u253?uwsam \u253?a\u351?lar bile.\par
\par
Her kim, g\u246?rsem, bir pi\u351?ede,\par
Meni\u328? k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m endi\u351?ede,\par
K\u246?\u253?i-ser i\u231?re k\u246?\u351?ede\par
Otursam aga\u231?lar bile.\par
\par
Garry d\u252?n\u253?\u228? al i\u231?inde,\par
Adamzat hy\u253?al i\u231?inde,\par
Jahan galmagal i\u231?inde,\par
Her kim \u253?\u252?z tala\u351?lar bile.\par
\par
Allany\u328? y\u351?kynda mestler,\par
Du\u351? geli\u351?mez zeberdestler,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l perwaz urar, dostlar,\par
Durmaz \u253?\u252?z ala\u231?lar bile.\par
\par
K\u246?p k\u252?\u253?ler bile oturdym,\par
Bilmedim, ne i\u351? bitirdim,\par
G\u252?mra bolup, \u253?ol \u253?itirdim,\par
Oturdym biwe\u231?ler bile.\par
\par
Bik\u228?r go\u253?ma \u246?m\u252?r tagty,\par
O\u253?andyrsak u\u253?mu\u351? bagty,\par
Doga kylyp, s\u228?her wagty,\par
Naly\u351? kylsam gu\u351?lar bile.\par
\par
Magtymguly, towpyk alsam,\par
Bir \u228?r tapsam, gulluk kylsam,\par
\u221?\u252?rek a\u253?dar: \u253?olda\u351? bolsam,\par
Dem \u231?eken derw\u252?\u351?ler bile.\par
\par
GE\u199?MI\u350?EM BEGLER\par
Belent dag ba\u351?ynda \u253?oldan\par
Da\u328?-s\u228?her ge\u231?mi\u351?em, begler.\par
Erenler \u253?\u246?regen silden\par
Ke\u351?t edip \u246?tm\u252?\u351?em, begler.\par
\par
K\u246?llerde gonup gazlary,\par
Di\u328?le\u253?ip ho\u351? owazlary,\par
Nowjuwan gelin-gyzlary\par
Ke\u253?p e\u253?l\u228?p gu\u231?mu\u351?am, begler.\par
\par
Gyr atlar s\u252?r\u252?p mekandan,\par
S\u228?her ys alyp re\u253?handan,\par
Zer, tylla-k\u252?m\u252?\u351? d\u252?kandan,\par
Misgine sa\u231?my\u351?am, begler.\par
\par
Gezip g\u246?zel, bak, ni\u253?etden,\par
D\u252?\u351?m\u228?n \u253?\u246?rd\u252?m d\u246?wlet atdan,\par
Aby-K\u246?wser al \u351?erapdan\par
Kyrk jamy i\u231?mi\u351?em, begler.\par
\par
Garyp bolup gezdim aglap,\par
Jigerim ata\u351?a daglap,\par
Men bu g\u252?n, bak, ganat baglap,\par
Asmana u\u231?mu\u351?am, begler.\par
\par
Bulanyp k\u246?wser la\u253?yna,\par
Ok bolup ga\u351?y\u328? \u253?a\u253?yna,\par
\u221?arymy\u328? jennet ja\u253?yna,\par
Nesipdir, d\u252?\u351?m\u252?\u351?em, begler.\par
\par
Habar alar munda gelen,\par
Gadrym biler t\u228?lim alan,\par
\u221?igrimi \u253?a\u351? y\u351?k bilen,\par
Men ga\u253?nap bi\u351?mi\u351?em, begler.\par
\par
Pyragy di\u253?r, men \u253?a\u253? kibi,\par
Bak d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de sara\u253? kibi,\par
G\u246?r\u252?\u328? \u351?u g\u252?n ol A\u253? kibi,\par
D\u246?w\u252?r edip \u253?a\u351?my\u351?am, begler.\par
\par
GOJALAN G\u220?NLER\par
Goja daglar, nazar kyly\u328?,\par
Siz kibi gojalan g\u252?nler.\par
G\u246?teri\u328?, ser\u328?ize aly\u328?,\par
Janymdan par\u231?alan g\u252?nler.\par
\par
Ata-enemden \u253?owuz men,\par
Suwun tartan bir howuz men.\par
H\u246?wessiz inen bir \u253?az men,\par
Yhlasym par\u231?alan g\u252?nler.\par
\par
Abdylla hem M\u228?mmetsapa,\par
A\u253?ra d\u252?\u351?di, \u231?ekdim jepa,\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? berme\u253?dir wepa,\par
N\u228?hak jan har\u231?lanan g\u252?nler.\par
\par
Guwanmadym ogul-gyza,\par
Goluma almadym jyza.\par
Hy\u253?al bar - gitsem T\u246?wrize,\par
Gadamym gargy\u351?lan g\u252?nler.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?ok ygty\u253?ar,\par
\u221?\u252?z tutar men, Perwerdig\u228?r,\par
G\u246?kle\u328? ilimdir bikarar,\par
\u221?agysyn gar\u351?ylan g\u252?nler.\par
\par
BIR I\u350?E ULA\u350?DY\par
De\u328?im-du\u351?um, go\u231? \u253?igitler,\par
Her kim bir i\u351?e ula\u351?dy.\par
Hak her kime bir \u253?ol berdi,\par
Her kim bir borja dala\u351?dy.\par
\par
Kimler girdi Hak \u253?oluna,\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylyk d\u252?\u351?di p\u228?line,\par
Kim gyly\u231? aldy eline,\par
\u199?aldy, yslam dinin a\u231?dy.\par
\par
Ner-bedewli begler, hanlar,\par
Atlansa, dolar me\u253?danlar,\par
S\u246?kdi zereh, d\u246?kdi ganlar,\par
Go\u231?aklar serinden ge\u231?di.\par
\par
Biz istedik uly \u253?aran,\par
Nesip bizi etdi ha\u253?ran,\par
Kimi gitdi E\u253?ran, Turan,\par
Kim Yspyhan, T\u246?wriz a\u351?dy.\par
\par
Haka a\u253?an boldy halym,\par
Halkda bilen bolmaz m\u228?lim,\par
Magtymguly, meni\u328? \u253?olum\par
Ol dostlardan a\u253?ra d\u252?\u351?di.\par
\par
\u221?YGLAP GE\u199?ER HALYMA\par
Gi\u328? g\u246?wr\u228?ni gam basypdyr \u246?z\u252?nden,\par
Ba\u351? hem gelse, \u253?yglap ge\u231?er halyma.\par
Bagyr \u253?a\u351?yn k\u246?\u328?\u252?l d\u246?ker g\u246?z\u252?nden,\par
Ga\u351? hem gelse, \u253?yglap ge\u231?er halyma.\par
\par
Garrylyga d\u246?nd\u228?r \u253?igit \u231?aglary,\par
Geda e\u253?l\u228?r t\u228?\u231? e\u253?esi begleri,\par
Gur\u351?un de\u253? erider Kap dek daglary,\par
Da\u351? hem gelse, \u253?yglap ge\u231?er halyma.\par
\par
\u196?lem i\u231?re bir ah ursam bir zarba,\par
Eda bolar ynsan, pil gelmez gurba,\par
Gapla\u328? g\u252?\u253?\u231?den galar, d\u246?ner gurt g\u252?rb\u228?,\par
Gu\u351? hem gelse, \u253?yglap ge\u231?er halyma.\par
\par
Pu\u351?manda men eden-etmi\u351? k\u228?rimden,\par
Biperwa\u253?am bolan-bolmu\u351? barymdan,\par
\u221?olda\u351? bolan \u253?ata bilmez zarymdan,\par
Da\u351? hem gelse, \u253?yglap ge\u231?er halyma.\par
\par
Hak y\u351?kydyr bizi go\u253?an k\u246?zlere,\par
Bu k\u246?zlerdir kysmat bolan bizlere,\par
Bilbil dilsiz galar, barsam \u253?azlara,\par
Gy\u351? hem gelse, \u253?yglap ge\u231?er halyma.\par
\par
A\u328?lama\u253?an y\u351?k derdini\u328? k\u228?ninden,\par
Bu s\u246?z ge\u231?mez \u253?akynyndan-\u253?anyndan,\par
Y\u351?ka d\u252?\u351?en umyt \u252?zer janyndan,\par
L\u228?\u351? hem gelse, \u253?yglap ge\u231?er halyma.\par
\par
P\u228?hm e\u253?le\u253?en Magtymguly s\u246?z\u252?ni,\par
Derde d\u252?\u351?\u252?p, \u253?a\u351?a doldyr g\u246?z\u252?ni,\par
\u350?at g\u252?lenler tuta bilmez \u246?z\u252?ni,\par
Ho\u351? hem gelse, \u253?yglap ge\u231?er halyma.\par
\par
\u221?ETI\u350?DI SALYM\par
Garrydyk\u231?a, goldan gitdi ynsabym,\par
E\u253?-\u228?, dostlar, ell\u228? \u253?eti\u351?di salym.\par
Kerim-\u228?, g\u252?n-g\u252?nden kemelip howpum,\par
Dembe-demden artdy bu \u253?aman p\u228?lim.\par
\par
Daryg-a, din \u252?\u231?in \u253?okdur bir i\u351?im,\par
\u214?mr\u252?m edalandy, agardy ri\u351?im,\par
Kuwwatym kemeldi, k\u252?teldi di\u351?im,\par
\u221?igitlik \u246?wj\u252?nde heniz hy\u253?alym.\par
\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l d\u252?n\u253?\u228? zerin yzlap durupdyr,\par
G\u246?z hem g\u246?zelleri g\u246?zl\u228?p durupdyr,\par
Dil hem gybat, \u253?alan s\u246?zl\u228?p durupdyr,\par
\u350?e\u253?tan bir kapyrdyr, nebis bir zalym.\par
\par
Senden medet \u253?eti\u351?mese, \u253?a Jepbar,\par
Bu beladan ba\u351? gutarmak ha\u231?an bar?\par
Howa\u253?y-h\u246?wese boldum giriftar,\par
Hak gullugna \u253?okdur zerre mejalym.\par
\par
Dostlar, ygtybarym \u253?okdur \u246?m\u252?re,\par
Bagtymy\u328? sy\u253?asy re\u328? bi\u253?r k\u246?m\u252?re,\par
Talygym g\u252?ne\u351?i galmy\u351? \u252?m\u252?re,\par
E\u253?\u228?m, Sen o\u253?andyr u\u253?my\u351? ykbalym.\par
\par
Hudawend-a, ger\u231?e nebsim \u253?amandyr,\par
Dilegim derg\u228?hden nury-imandyr,\par
\u350?er i\u351?im bihetdir, g\u252?n\u228?him k\u228?ndir,\par
Sen \u214?z\u252?\u328? ge\u231?irgil, \u253?a, Z\u252?ljelalym.\par
\par
Magtymguly, y\u351?k oduna bir\u253?anam,\par
Il malyna, men halyma gir\u253?anam,\par
Gorky, umyt ortasynda ha\u253?ranam,\par
Ta\u328?la-mag\u351?ar, \u253?a, Rep, ne ola halym?\par
\par
L\u196?\u350?LER AGLAR HALYMA\par
La\u231?ynsyz \u231?\u246?l \u253?erde galan maslyk men,\par
Meni g\u246?r\u252?p, l\u228?\u351?ler aglar halyma.\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? gadryn bilmez nadan mahluk men,\par
Akly gidip, ba\u351?lar aglar halyma.\par
\par
Sepil boldum, j\u252?mle jahany \u253?\u246?rip,\par
Gapyl galdym, gam \u246?\u253?\u252?nde sargaryp,\par
U\u231?a bilm\u228?n, \u253?a\u351?yn d\u246?k\u252?p telmuryp,\par
Sergerdana gu\u351?lar aglar halyma.\par
\par
Kuwwatsyz galyp men, ne\u231?\u252?n \u231?a\u351?maz men,\par
Ha\u253?rany men, bent astynda da\u351?maz men,\par
Nar \u252?st\u252?ne d\u252?\u351?d\u252?m, \u253?anyp-bi\u351?mez men,\par
Kebap bolup, \u231?i\u351?ler aglar halyma.\par
\par
Takatsyz \u253?\u252?regim lerzana d\u246?ndi,\par
Ah ursam, t\u252?t\u252?nim dumana d\u246?ndi,\par
G\u246?zden d\u246?ken \u253?a\u351?ym ummana d\u246?ndi,\par
D\u252?wme-d\u252?wme \u253?a\u351?lar aglar halyma.\par
\par
Nalamdan, g\u246?r, daglar lagly d\u246?redi,\par
Bulutlar dargady, baran \u253?\u246?redi,\par
Gara daglar suw-sil boldy, eredi,\par
Ol bi\u231?\u228?re da\u351?lar aglar halyma.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bentdir akyl gapysy,\par
Dert bolupdyr, ili\u328?-g\u252?n\u252?\u328? \u253?apysy,\par
Zeberdest pirleri, i\u351?an-sopusy,\par
Telpek ge\u253?mi\u351?, pe\u351?ler aglar halyma.\par
\par
BAGY\u350?LA BIZI\par
Resul damadydyr, \u214?z arslany\u328?dyr,\par
\u221?a ymam Aly\u253?a bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\u199?e\u351?mi-\u231?yragymdyr, nury-a\u253?nymdyr,\par
\u221?a ymam Hasana bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\par
\u221?alan d\u252?n\u253?\u228? kime berdi wepany,\par
Ahyrynda anlar s\u252?rer sapany,\par
\u350?ymr ile ol \u221?ezit berdi jepany,\par
\u221?a ymam H\u252?se\u253?ne bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\par
Nasry-Se\u253?\u253?ar, Merwan-Hekem d\u246?wr\u252?nde,\par
Ymamlar galdylar jepa-j\u246?wr\u252?nde,\par
\u199?a\u253?a atdyrdylar Dyma\u351?k \u351?\u228?hrinde,\par
Ze\u253?nelabydyna bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\par
Patma\u253?y-Z\u228?hradyr onu\u328? enesi,\par
Zatynda bir zerre \u253?okdur g\u252?n\u228?si,\par
Huma\u253?un dagydyr ahyr binasy,\par
Muhammet Bakyra bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\par
Kemaly pelekden, a\u351?ypdyr ar\u351?dan,\par
Ba\u351?a go\u253?dy jeddi ge\u253?digi t\u228?\u231?den,\par
\u220?\u231? keramat bile galdy Hajjajdan,\par
\u221?a ymam Jagfara bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\par
Kim biler i\u351?i\u328?de ni\u231?iksi syr bar,\par
Akl o\u328?a yeti\u351?mez gudratly Jepbar,\par
Du\u351?manyga dostu\u328? etdi\u328? giriftar,\par
\u221?a Musa K\u228?zime bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\par
De\u328?-du\u351?lar \u253?anynda bir bikemalam,\par
A\u351?ygam, mejnunam, \u351?ikeste halam,\par
Syna\u253?y-Horasan, zuwwary-\u228?lem,\par
\u221?a ymam Ryza\u253?a bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\par
Ymamlar y\u351?kynda ma\u328?a bergin jam,\par
A\u231?a\u253?yn zybany, oka\u253?yn Kelam,\par
Il\u228?hi behakky-Patma\u253?y-ky\u253?am,\par
Muhammet Taky\u253?a bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de \u231?ekdiler \u253?\u252?z derdi-dagy,\par
Mag\u351?ar g\u252?n m\u252?nerler sa\u253?lap Byragy,\par
Hakykat \u253?oluny\u328? \u351?emi-\u231?yragy,\par
Aly\u253?\u253?yn-Naky\u253?a bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\par
\u221?akyn k\u246?\u328?\u252?l birle mu\u351?tagam bende,\par
\u221?ady\u328?yz e\u253?l\u228?rem t\u228? bar men zinde,\par
Ady G\u252?nden me\u351?hur olmu\u351? \u228?lemde,\par
\u221?a ymam Esgere bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\par
Kap dagyndan \u253?ol a\u231?ylsa \u374?ajuja,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u253?\u252?zi dolar zulm ile g\u252?\u253?je,\par
Zaman ahyrynda geler hyruja,\par
\u221?a Sahypzamana bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, men h\u228?ki-pa\u253?am,\par
Ymamlar \u253?olunda hem jan pida\u253?am,\par
Kemine bende\u253?em, gelip-gide\u253?em,\par
\u221?a Apbas Aly\u253?a bagy\u351?la bizi.\par
\par
TAPAR BOLDUM\par
E\u253? \u253?aranlar, hala\u253?yklar,\par
Mert \u253?igidi tapar boldum.\par
Bagt synap, bu panyda,\par
Ykbalymy \u231?apar boldum.\par
\par
Gaflatda \u246?tm\u252?\u351?dir g\u252?n\u252?m,\par
Y\u351?k oduna \u253?anyp tenim,\par
Il g\u246?z\u252?nden jan-u tenim\par
Toprak bilen \u253?apar boldum.\par
\par
Syna\u253?yp men bu bagtymy,\par
We\u253?ran kylyp men tagtymy,\par
De\u351?t \u252?zre gyr atymy,\par
G\u246?rogly dek deper boldum.\par
\par
D\u252?\u351?m\u252?\u351?em d\u252?n\u253?\u228? k\u252?\u253?\u252?ne,\par
Gysdy ne\u253?l\u228?rem, \u246?\u253?\u252?ne,\par
Dostlar bu g\u252?n \u253?ar ro\u253?una\par
M\u252?\u351?ki-anbar seper boldum.\par
\par
Gezip jahany\u328? \u252?st\u252?nde,\par
Pelegi\u328? zalym kastynda,\par
Galyp men pa\u253?y\u328? astynda,\par
\u221?amanlara sapar boldum.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de Nemrut kibi,\par
Ol d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de Syrat kibi,\par
Ol Isgender, Jem\u351?it kibi,\par
G\u246?zde \u253?a\u351?ym d\u246?ker boldum.\par
\par
Jahanda bar ni\u231?e baplar,\par
Jemaly a\u253? dek sahyplar,\par
S\u246?we\u351? kylyp agyr t\u252?pler,\par
R\u252?stem, Zal dek bozar boldum.\par
\par
Bilbilem, galdym g\u252?l\u252?mden,\par
Sarwanam, d\u252?\u351?d\u252?m ilimden,\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?, indi bu dilimden\par
Agyr bela tapar boldum.\par
\par
Panyny men g\u246?ze alma\u253?,\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylara hemra bolma\u253?,\par
En\u231?e zaman \u246?z\u252?m bilme\u253?,\par
Her kanda bir \u253?\u246?rer boldum.\par
\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?in, ka\u253?dadyr \u253?arym,\par
Bagymda biten enarym,\par
G\u246?kle\u328?de ol Me\u328?li \u253?arym\par
Il-ulusdan sorar boldum.\par
\par
Ge\u231?ip men dowzah, Syratyn,\par
M\u252?n\u252?p men behi\u351?ti\u328? atyn,\par
Magtymguly, \u253?ar suratyn,\par
K\u228?tip e\u253?l\u228?p \u253?azar boldum.\par
\par
SOLUPDYR PYGAN BILEN\par
\u214?mr\u252?m, e\u253?, g\u252?l \u246?mr\u252?m, e\u253?,\par
Solupdyr pygan bilen.\par
Ata\u351? \u252?st\u252?ne d\u252?\u351?\u252?p,\par
K\u246?\u253?\u252?pdir ten jan bilen.\par
\par
\u214?mr\u252?m, e\u253?, gara g\u246?z\u252?m,\par
Kims\u228? derkardyr s\u246?z\u252?m,\par
G\u246?kle\u328? i\u231?re bir \u246?z\u252?m,\par
Galyp men arman bilen.\par
\par
\u214?mr\u252?m, g\u252?l\u351?en baharym,\par
D\u252?\u351?me\u253? ajap nazarym,\par
Magtymguly azarym,\par
Gitdi ten-u jan bilen.\par
\par
NE\u221?LE\u221?, INDI BI\u199?\u196?RE\u221?EM\par
Watanymda han idim,\par
Hanlara perman idim,\par
Dertlere derman idim,\par
Misgine d\u252?kan idim,\par
Jansyza men jan idim,\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?, indi bi\u231?\u228?re\u253?em.\par
\par
G\u246?zs\u252?zleri\u328? g\u246?zi idim,\par
Lallary\u328? men s\u246?zi idim,\par
Il-g\u252?n\u252?mi\u328? \u253?\u252?zi idim,\par
S\u246?wer mag\u351?uk n\u228?zi idim,\par
Hatam Ta\u253?y\u328? \u246?zi idim,\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?, indi pukara\u253?am.\par
\par
Erem i\u231?re re\u253?han idim,\par
Watanda zeref\u351?an idim,\par
Mert \u253?igitde \u231?aman idim,\par
Dag ba\u351?ynda duman idim,\par
Pyragy di\u253?r, aman idim,\par
Indi we\u253?ran bir sara\u253?am.\par
\par
AT GALMADY\par
Zalym pelegi\u328? golundan,\par
A\u351?yklarda at galmady;\par
Gara zemini\u328? p\u228?linden\par
Uzak \u246?m\u252?r, zat galmady.\par
\par
Pelek saldy bu te\u351?wi\u351?i,\par
Apatdyr her tutan i\u351?i,\par
Dargady \u228?rler ge\u328?e\u351?i,\par
Uly jemagat galmady.\par
\par
Pelek ne g\u252?n ba\u351?a saldy,\par
\u221?\u252?rek \u253?agym, nurum aldy,\par
Ilat \u228?hli \u171?alym\u187? boldy,\par
Bizde nesihat galmady.\par
\par
Pelek e\u253?leme bahana,\par
Zulm e\u253?ledi\u328? geda, hana,\par
A\u231?yk g\u246?w\u252?n \u253?ok myhmana,\par
Pirlere hormat galmady.\par
\par
Dagymda bent galdy siller,\par
Gitdi hu\u351?um, egri biller,\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, iller,\par
Yzymda z\u252?r\u253?at galmady.\par
\par
IL G\u214?ZL\u196?R\par
\u221?owuzlykda gam la\u253?yna gark bolan,\par
Ukuly g\u246?zlerim g\u246?zel il g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
En\u231?e ah-u zarly kapasda galan,\par
Azat bolan bilbil, gyzyl g\u252?l g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
G\u246?zel ilim, sen di\u253?p s\u246?kerem \u253?ollar,\par
G\u246?z\u252?m gubarlandy, zebundyr hallar,\par
Kenarda darga\u253?an e\u253?esiz sallar,\par
Deprenme\u253? \u253?a\u351? d\u246?k\u252?p, umman, sil g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
Otly lybas ge\u253?en g\u246?w\u252?n y\u351?klar,\par
\u350?asyz \u253?owuz d\u252?\u351?en tagty-k\u246?\u351?kler,\par
\u221?ar di\u253?ip sergezdan pakyr-a\u351?yklar,\par
Uzyn bo\u253?, gara g\u246?z, in\u231?e bil g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
Kararsyz g\u246?w\u252?nler, biala\u231? janlar,\par
N\u228?hak aksa, \u351?ehit - ynsandan ganlar,\par
Rebig g\u252?l \u252?st\u252?nde ol perwanalar,\par
Nowbahar paslynda saba \u253?el g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
Zybansyz dahanlar, g\u246?rks\u252?z \u253?\u252?zler,\par
Sy\u253?a ga\u351?, ok kirpik, ol gara g\u246?zler,\par
Hi\u231? \u253?ersiz g\u252?rr\u252?\u328?ler, manysyz s\u246?zler,\par
Hylwatdan da\u351? \u231?ykar, g\u252?\u328?-u lal g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
Akmak \u351?alar, erksiz wezir, ol gullar,\par
In\u231?e bil, serwi bo\u253?, ak, uzyn gollar,\par
G\u246?w\u252?n nag\u351?y, d\u252?\u253?\u351?de g\u246?rlen hy\u253?allar,\par
Tylla, g\u246?wher, gen\u231?-hazyna, mal g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
Magtymguly, biz de\u253? misgin hem ba\u253?lar,\par
Oksuz keman, kir\u351?siz gurulan \u253?a\u253?lar,\par
A\u253?lanan d\u246?w\u252?rler, g\u252?nler-u a\u253?lar,\par
\u199?oh gerdi\u351? \u246?wr\u252?ler, t\u228?ze \u253?yl g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
AJAP E\u221?\u221?AM GELMEDI\par
Nadan menem, d\u252?\u351?d\u252?m pelek toruna,\par
\u199?oh gara\u351?dym, ajap e\u253?\u253?am gelmedi.\par
\u199?ydamaz men indi hijran zoruna,\par
\u199?oh gara\u351?dym, ajap e\u253?\u253?am gelmedi.\par
\par
Kyrka gadam go\u253?dum, k\u228?s\u228?m dolmu\u351?dyr,\par
Ondan efgan dartyp, g\u246?wn\u252?m galmy\u351?dyr,\par
Ni\u253?et ma\u328?a \u253?aman hemra bolmu\u351?dyr,\par
\u199?oh gara\u351?dym, ajap e\u253?\u253?am gelmedi.\par
\par
Geldi gara bela, ili dolady,\par
Dahan a\u231?yp, dili bilen \u253?alady,\par
Seg bolupdyr, g\u246?ren ilin dalady,\par
\u199?oh gara\u351?dym, ajap e\u253?\u253?am gelmedi.\par
\par
Garypda san \u253?okdur, m\u228?reke g\u246?rmez,\par
Hak s\u246?\u253?se-de ykbalyna mal bermez,\par
At m\u252?n\u252?p depsede-de, du\u351?akly, \u253?\u246?rmez,\par
\u199?oh gara\u351?dym, ajap e\u253?\u253?am gelmedi.\par
\par
Ni\u253?eti \u253?amandyr, bahyl mal \u253?ygar,\par
I\u253?e bilmez, her dem rysgalyn bogar,\par
Maly haram bolar, ba\u351?yndan agar,\par
\u199?oh gara\u351?dym, ajap e\u253?\u253?am gelmedi.\par
\par
Hak s\u246?z\u252?me di\u253?er mollalar galat,\par
\u221?alan s\u246?ze \u253?apar boldular halat,\par
Kasam edip, eretdiler, g\u246?r, polat,\par
\u199?oh gara\u351?dym, ajap e\u253?\u253?am gelmedi.\par
\par
Pirler ro\u253?un a\u231?dy, juwans\u246?\u253?erdir,\par
Namyssyzy sopy alyp e\u253?erdir,\par
Galat a\u253?dyp: \u171?\u350?uny Alla di\u253?er\u187? di\u253?r\par
\u199?oh gara\u351?dym, ajap e\u253?\u253?am gelmedi.\par
\par
Magtymguly, dili otly, ot sa\u231?ar,\par
\u221?\u252?z g\u246?rmez, n\u228?kesi\u328? a\u253?byny a\u231?ar,\par
Alla ganat berse, Hindistan u\u231?ar,\par
\u199?oh gara\u351?dym, ajap e\u253?\u253?am gelmedi.\par
\par
HASAR DAGYNDADYR\par
Hasar dagy be\u253?ik bolar,\par
\u220?sti doly ke\u253?ik bolar,\par
Mergenlere se\u253?ik bolar,\par
Barsa\u328?, Hasar dagyndadyr.\par
\par
Hasary\u328? bardyr t\u246?resi,\par
G\u246?reni\u328? gider h\u246?wesi,\par
Gyz-gelinleri\u328? seresi\par
Syrsa\u328?, Hasar dagyndadyr.\par
\par
Kuh erer \u253?eri\u328? soltany,\par
G\u246?ws\u252?nde gurmu\u351? d\u252?kany,\par
\u220?\u231? \u253?\u252?z altmy\u351? pir mekany\par
G\u246?rse\u328?, Hasar dagyndadyr.\par
\par
Mesgen tutar \u231?arwadarlar,\par
\u221?al\u231?ysynda \u253?atar marlar,\par
Deresinde biter barlar,\par
Tirse\u328?, Hasar dagyndadyr.\par
\par
Pele\u328?ler \u231?yrpynyp \u231?ykan,\par
Boz marallar gy\u253?a bakan,\par
Serkemerdir - deri\u328? d\u246?ken,\par
\u221?\u246?rse\u328?, Hasar dagyndadyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly di\u253?r bu dagy,\par
\u221?akypdyr heseri\u328? dagy,\par
Y\u351?k edip sapaly \u231?agy\par
S\u252?rse\u328?, Hasar dagyndadyr.\par
\par
G\u220?RGENI\u327?\par
\u214?\u328?\u252?nde belent dag, serinde duman,\par
De\u328?izden \u246?w\u252?ser \u253?eli G\u252?rgeni\u328?.\par
Bulut o\u253?nap, baran dolsa \u231?a\u253?lara,\par
Akar boz bulanyp sili G\u252?rgeni\u328?.\par
\par
Toka\u253?lary bardyr gargy-gamy\u351?ly,\par
G\u246?zelleri bardyr altyn-k\u252?m\u252?\u351?li,\par
Boz g\u252?sbent, gyr \u253?ylky, gara g\u228?wmi\u351?li,\par
Argaly g\u228?w bolar maly G\u252?rgeni\u328?.\par
\par
Hatarlan\u351?yp duran iner, ma\u253?alar,\par
Agyr bezirgenli, t\u252?\u231?jar e\u253?eler,\par
Se\u328?rikl\u228?p, abanyp duran ga\u253?alar,\par
\u214?\u328?i-ardy, sagy-soly G\u252?rgeni\u328?.\par
\par
Begleri bar, tirme \u231?alar biline,\par
\u221?orga m\u252?n\u252?p, tarla\u328? gondyr eline,\par
Ak g\u246?ws\u252?n bi\u253?r jeren de\u328?iz \u253?eline,\par
M\u228?le\u253?ir maraly \u231?\u246?li G\u252?rgeni\u328?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ilden ile aralar,\par
Hijran tygy bilen bagryn paralar,\par
Golun sallap maral gabak periler,\par
Iner olumyndan d\u228?li G\u252?rgeni\u328?.\par
\par
SO\u327?UDAGY\par
Janym bizi\u328?, So\u328?udagy,\par
Dagdanlydyr bili\u328? seni\u328?.\par
Ganym g\u246?rse gar\u351?yla\u351?ar,\par
\u221?omut, g\u246?kle\u328? ili\u328? seni\u328?.\par
\par
\u214?\u253?l\u252?kde \u253?a\u253?lany gursak,\par
At \u231?apdyryp, ba\u253?rak bersek,\par
Temetede orak orsak,\par
A\u351? d\u246?kmek hy\u253?aly\u328? seni\u328?.\par
\par
Kesgi\u231?-kesgi\u231? ba\u253?yr ge\u231?er,\par
Gyzylba\u253?yr g\u246?w\u252?n a\u231?ar,\par
Sowuk \u231?e\u351?me suwun i\u231?er,\par
\u350?onda d\u252?rli maly\u328? seni\u328?.\par
\par
D\u252?rli-d\u252?men otu\u328? biter,\par
Her der\u228?\u328? bir ile \u253?eter,\par
Hatarlan\u351?yp kerwen \u246?ter.\par
Na\u253?bada\u253?dyr 6 \u253?olu\u328? seni\u328?.\par
\par
Magtymguly d\u252?r se\u231?ende,\par
Bu d\u246?wran senden ge\u231?ende,\par
\u220?st\u252?\u328?den ili\u328? g\u246?\u231?ende,\par
Ni\u231?ik ge\u231?er haly\u328? seni\u328??\par
\par
UTUP DURUPDYR\par
Bir \u231?\u252?\u253?r\u252?k hoz bilen jahan j\u246?wherin,\par
Ol ne humarbazdyr, utup durupdyr.\par
\u199?\u252?\u253?r\u252?k saman etmi\u351? mata bazaryn,\par
G\u246?where barabar satyp durupdyr.\par
\par
Ne d\u252?\u351?ekdir, o\u328?a basan \u253?arymaz,\par
Ne ki\u351?tidir, der\u253?a batar, \u253?\u246?rimez,\par
Ne enedir, \u246?lmez, \u253?itmez, garrymaz,\par
\u214?z balasyn \u246?zi \u253?uwtup durupdyr.\par
\par
Ne \u231?yragdyr, g\u252?ns\u252?z \u253?eri \u253?arydyr,\par
Ne g\u246?zg\u252?dir, bu a\u253?nadan arydyr,\par
Ne sakydyr, py\u253?alasyn \u253?\u246?reder,\par
Bir eli bogzundan tutup durupdyr.\par
\par
Dostlar, bir mysaldyr dilime gelen,\par
Zehin go\u253?sa, biler akyly bolan.\par
Jahany ger tutmu\u351? bir gudrat \u253?ylan,\par
Gu\u253?rugy ba\u351?yndan artyp durupdyr.\par
\par
Ba\u351?y baryp \u231?ykmy\u351? Ar\u351?y\u328? \u252?st\u252?ne,\par
A\u253?agy inmi\u351?dir \u253?eri\u328? astyna,\par
Janly, jansyz, her ne gelse destine,\par
Dannama\u253?, agzynja atyp durupdyr.\par
\par
Ne mahlukdyr, ne erkekdir, ne di\u351?i,\par
Bir g\u246?zi dym-akdyr, bir g\u246?zi \u231?a\u351?y,\par
Re\u328?\u328?i gara, ala on iki ba\u351?y,\par
\u221?eri-g\u246?gi birden tutup durupdyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, magrur bolma bu s\u246?ze\par
Hi\u231? be\u253?le janawer ilmemi\u351? g\u246?ze,\par
\u221?ene bir gudrat bar, \u253?edi kelpeze,\par
\u350?ol be\u253?ik \u253?ylany \u253?uwdup durupdyr.\par
\par
RYSWA JAHANDAN\par
G\u246?w\u252?nler k\u246?\u351?g\u252?nde bigam oturan,\par
Ol onki ki\u351?idir ryswa jahandan.\par
Aryp bolup, aklyn d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u253?etiren,\par
Gep urarmy\u351? \u253?etmi\u351? iki zybandan.\par
\par
\u221?ala\u328?a\u231? oturmy\u351? Haky zarla\u253?yp,\par
Pelek ony da\u328?-s\u228?herler barla\u253?yp,\par
G\u252?ndizi u\u231?army\u351? g\u246?ge parla\u253?yp,\par
\u199?oh lagnat d\u246?kermi\u351? \u253?ere asmandan.\par
\par
Zeberdest pirlere ermi\u351? halypa,\par
G\u252?nde b\u228?\u351? wagt u\u231?up geler Magryba,\par
Zeminden azm urar ol afytaba,\par
Akly\u328? \u253?etse sora \u351?uny, Gurhandan.\par
\par
Dokuz \u253?yllap suw i\u231?megen, a\u351? i\u253?m\u228?n,\par
\u221?igrim b\u228?\u351? \u253?yl gezer jahana inm\u228?n,\par
Elli \u253?yl \u253?a\u351? d\u246?ker gijesi dynman,\par
D\u246?ken \u253?a\u351?yn, baryp sorar ummandan.\par
\par
Segsen d\u246?rt guly bar, \u253?etmi\u351? a\u253?aly,\par
\u221?ene \u253?\u252?z b\u228?\u351?inde galmy\u351? hy\u253?aly,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge sygma\u253?ar \u253?ygnagan maly,\par
Ot i\u253?mez ha\u253?wan dek do\u253?ma\u253?ar nandan.\par
\par
On b\u228?\u351? ak \u246?\u253? gurup, tagt saldyrmy\u351?,\par
\u221?edi minarany ba\u351?dan galdyrmy\u351?,\par
Nagra tartyp, \u228?leme ot doldurmy\u351?,\par
En\u231?e sorup, g\u246?zi do\u253?ma\u253?ar gandan.\par
\par
G\u246?z\u252?nde ot \u253?anar, dahanda t\u252?t\u252?n,\par
\u214?z-\u246?zi i\u253?ermi\u351? gijeler etin.\par
Aly goparypdyr sag g\u246?zn\u252?\u328? \u231?etin,\par
Essine gelende ge\u231?\u253?\u228?r imandan.\par
\par
Magtymguly, akly bolan s\u246?z keser,\par
S\u246?z di\u253?i\u328?ler, erse ol nejis \u246?ser,\par
Kim biler, ol n\u228?rse d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni basar,\par
K\u246?pler namut bolar jesetde jandan.\par
\par
SAN BOLSAM\par
Jam g\u246?terip, baryp \u253?etdim bir bapdan,\par
Hyrka ge\u253?ip, il i\u231?inde san bolsam.\par
T\u252?n i\u231?inde baryp Be\u253?tulla tapdan,\par
Zar \u253?ygla\u253?an sahyplarda hun bolsam.\par
\par
Abu Se\u253?it, Omar Ha\u253?\u253?am, Hemedany,\par
Fird\u246?wsi, Nyzamy, Hapyz perwany,\par
Jelaleddin Rumy, Jamy elwany,\par
Olarny\u328? ja\u253?ynda menem k\u228?n bolsam.\par
\par
Damegandan 7 \u253?\u246?rgen ussat Nowa\u253?y,\par
\u171?\u199?ar diwany\u187?, \u171?Perhat-\u350?irin\u187?, ruba\u253?y,\par
Zahyreddin Babyr \u171?Mizan-\u246?wzany\u187?,\par
Ga\u351?laryna baryp men Mejnun bolsam.\par
\par
Okap bildim Sagdyny\u328? men \u171?Bossanny\u187?,\par
G\u246?r, ne ajap Hakanyny\u328? \u171?Mediany\u187?,\par
Ist\u228?r men \u171?\u350?anama\u187?, \u171?Sakynamany\u187?,\par
Halyf Omar bilen S\u252?le\u253?man bolsam.\par
\par
Salaman-Ebsaly serho\u351? e\u253?le\u253?ip,\par
B\u228?hram Gury tutup, mehru\u351? e\u253?le\u253?ip;\par
Azududd\u246?wl\u228?ni bir gu\u351? e\u253?le\u253?ip,\par
Abu M\u228?hfuz, Gyzyl Arslan han bolsam.\par
\par
Abu Bekr gan \u253?yglap Farsda galsa,\par
Aly, Mamun, Abisdama (?) de\u328? bolsa.\par
Z\u252?nnun baryp, ol R\u252?steme zor salsa,\par
R\u252?stemi\u328? derdine men derman bolsam.\par
\par
Galen, Eflatuna \u253?olun g\u246?rkezip,\par
Dawut, Osman bilen Aly \u252?rk\u252?zip,\par
Kubat pederi Hysrowy gorkuzyp,\par
Olar di\u253?gen bary din-iman bolsam.\par
\par
Arbalet golu\u328?da, e\u253? Magtymguly.\par
R\u252?steme Isgender hi\u231? tutmaz \u253?oly,\par
Ne bolsa, bilge\u253? sen ilat hy\u253?aly,\par
Dertliler alnynda men Lukman bolsam.\par
\par
BU DERDI\par
Ke\u351?t e\u253?ledim, gezdim y\u351?ky\u328? dagynda,\par
Ne beladyr, kimse \u231?eker bu derdi.\par
Y\u351?k dagyn asdylar g\u246?g\u252?\u328? bo\u253?nundan,\par
G\u246?k titre\u253?ip, \u231?eke bilmez bu derdi.\par
\par
Y\u351?k eser etmese, \u253?anmaz \u231?yraglar,\par
Y\u351?ka d\u252?\u351?se, gu\u351?lar e\u328?r\u228?p, gurt aglar,\par
Egiler ha\u253?batly, kuwwatly daglar,\par
Da\u351?lar erip, \u231?eke bilmez bu derdi.\par
\par
Kimdir y\u351?ky\u328? \u253?\u252?k\u252?n \u231?eken merdana,\par
Pelek g\u246?rdi, gorkup d\u252?\u351?di gerdana,\par
Zemin j\u252?nb\u252?\u351? e\u253?l\u228?p, geldi lerzana,\par
\u199?\u246?ller tap getirmez, \u231?ekmez bu derdi.\par
\par
Behi\u351?t ga\u231?yp \u231?ykmy\u351? ar\u351?y\u328? \u246?\u253?\u252?ne,\par
Tamug gorkup, inmi\u351? \u253?eri\u328? te\u253?ine,\par
Ga\u231?dy der\u253?a, adam aldy bo\u253?nuna,\par
D\u246?rt \u253?\u252?z \u253?yllap sorap ge\u231?mi\u351? bu derdi.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u231?ekse\u328? derdi-d\u252?g\u252?nden,\par
Asy bolup, \u351?ikat etme bu g\u252?nden,\par
Bu \u246?lmek, a\u253?rylmak galypdyr \u246?\u328?den,\par
Peder bize miras go\u253?mu\u351? bu derdi.\par
\par
ME\u327?ZEMEZ\par
E\u253?, seni\u328? dek bir peri, ga\u253?ry jenana me\u328?zemez,\par
Kirpik-hanjar ne\u351?teri, tiri-kemana me\u328?zemez.\par
\par
Ro\u253?y a\u253? dek jurga hallar, bendi kylar g\u246?reni,\par
\u350?uglasy \u228?lemi \u253?akar, mahy-tabana me\u328?zemez.\par
\par
Lebi nar-u aby-K\u246?wser, en\u231?e bijan tirgizer,\par
Bag\u351? e\u253?le\u253?ir ol k\u246?wseri, p\u228?li Karuna me\u328?zemez.\par
\par
Z\u252?lpi sy\u253?a s\u252?nb\u252?l peri, \u228?lemi kyldy\u328? bikarar,\par
Terk edip sen en\u231?e d\u252?kan, ga\u253?ry d\u252?kana me\u328?zemez.\par
\par
Ro\u253?u\u328? \u252?zre k\u252?lli \u228?lem, jemalyny bent kylyp,\par
Desmal tutup, k\u246?\u253?d\u252?rer sen, h\u252?\u253?r-gulmana me\u328?zemez.\par
\par
Bu pelegi\u328? \u231?arhyny sen, erki bilen e\u253?el\u228?p,\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni kyldy\u328? behi\u351?t, eski jahana me\u328?zemez.\par
\par
Ol \u221?usuby\u328? jemalyny, bag\u351? kylmy\u351? Hak owaly,\par
Iki jahan soltany sen, S\u252?le\u253?mana me\u328?zemez.\par
\par
Magtymguly \u228?lem i\u231?re, bar\u231?a jenan hem g\u246?zel,\par
Barysy bir kenizdir ki, Me\u328?li hana me\u328?zemez.\par
\par
SET JAN, E\u221?, DOST\par
G\u246?z\u252?me hergiz sensiz g\u246?r\u252?nmez jahan, e\u253?, dost.\par
Ne jahan, belki, tende bolsa ger set jan, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
Dostlaryga bu i\u351?ler biwepalyk ermesmi?\par
Jana jebri\u328? artdyrdy\u328? a\u231?dyk\u231?a zyban, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
Ol ki ruhsary\u328? g\u246?r\u252?p, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l gopdy sen \u253?ara,\par
Jan berme\u253? gutulmak \u253?ok, hi\u231? o\u328?a imkan, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
Wasly\u328?a umyt eden \u252?zm\u252?\u351? elin janydan,\par
\u199?e\u351?mi\u328? \u8722? jellady-jahan, ga\u351?y\u328?dyr keman, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
Destury-zaman budur, mazluma m\u252?rwet berler,\par
\u350?ererge \u351?owku\u328? artar, etdik\u231?e aman, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
Umytly a\u351?yklara wasl umydyn katg etdi\u328?,\par
A\u351?yklara jebr ondan bolga\u253?my bu \u253?an, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bir mahluk, men a\u351?ygam, sen - mag\u351?uk,\par
Ger di\u253?se\u328?: \u171?Istegim \u253?ok\u187?, bara\u253?yn ka\u253?an, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
HABAR, E\u221?, DOST\par
Bir s\u228?her d\u252?\u351?m\u252?\u351? erdi \u253?adyma di\u253?ar, e\u253?, dost,\par
Jan g\u252?w\u351?\u252?ne \u253?eti\u351?di bin\u228?g\u228?h habar, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
Ten m\u252?lk\u252?ni\u328? i\u231?inde jan durdy perwaz e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
\u350?owk ile ede n\u228?g\u228?h \u246?z\u252?ni nisar, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
Sabrym sefinesini syndyrdy \u351?owku\u328? sili,\par
Der\u253?a\u253?y-umman saldy matagy-karar, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
\u221?ar wasly-jemalyndan her du jahan ki k\u228?m\u253?ap,\par
Bagtym m\u252?\u351?terisine gurawer bazar, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
\u196?hli \u228?lem gark olmu\u351? harman-harman g\u252?l i\u231?re,\par
On \u253?yl \u253?\u246?rsem ugra\u351?maz, alnymdan bahar, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
Ho\u351? bakmy\u351? jahan i\u231?re, ho\u351?lanmy\u351? \u228?lem ondan,\par
\u196?lemde adam i\u231?re ma\u328?adyr gahar, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
Pyragy, g\u246?z ornundan \u253?yglap gan rowan oldy,\par
Ornuna elter ony, ger degse gubar, e\u253?, dost.\par
\par
GA\u350?Y \u221?A\u221?\par
Bir dilbere du\u351? geldim, gamzasy ok, ga\u351?y \u253?a\u253?,\par
G\u252?n ha\u253?randyr g\u246?rk\u252?nden, hyjalatda dolan A\u253?.\par
\par
Jany\u328? berse\u328?, ja\u253?yzdyr, be\u253?le sypat mahbuba,\par
Hi\u231? g\u246?rmedim onu\u328? de\u253? ba\u351?y dogry, bagry ta\u253?.\par
\par
Gulgula d\u252?\u351?di gopuz hem d\u252?\u351?di \u231?e\u328?i \u231?e\u328?e,\par
\u199?e\u328? \u351?owkundan ol nig\u228?r ne nalaga d\u252?\u351?di na\u253?,\par
\par
Ne e\u351?retdir a\u351?yga jennet i\u231?re jemaly,\par
A\u253?ralygy\u328? ata\u351?y \u8722? tamug i\u231?re we\u253?l-u wa\u253?.\par
\par
Ol dide\u253?i-dildardan bolmaga\u253? sen bib\u228?hre,\par
Galmaga\u253? sen meni\u328? de\u253? akla az-u g\u246?rke ba\u253?.\par
\par
Istese alymlary \u351?e\u253?tan eder ol dilber,\par
Halaganna Halyl dek oglanyna berer pa\u253?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, mydama doga kylar derg\u228?he,\par
Sa\u253?yl men, mahrum etme derg\u228?hi\u328?den, \u253?a Huda\u253?!\par
\par
JAHAN SENDEN BIHABAR\par
Sen-Sen ara\u253?y\u351?y-jan, hem jan Senden bihabar\par
Sen jahana doly Sen, jahan Senden bihabar.\par
\par
Endi\u351?e der\u253?asynda syrym sefinesini\par
\u221?\u252?z tarapa \u253?\u252?zd\u252?rdim, se\u253?ran Senden bihabar.\par
\par
Ger di\u253?seler k\u252?fr olar: \u171?E\u351?\u253?a Senden halydyr\u187?,\par
Menzil Senden mustagrak, mekan Senden bihabar.\par
\par
Zemin, asman, garb-u \u351?ark pert\u246?wi\u328?de gerdandyr,\par
Zamany\u253?a Sen gerdan, zaman Senden bihabar.\par
\par
Ist\u228?r Seni de\u328?izler \u253?a\u253?kany\u351?yp \u351?owku\u328?dan,\par
Sen olar i\u231?re m\u228?lim, umman Senden bihabar.\par
\par
Zemin dil\u228?r asmanda, asman dil\u228?r zeminde,\par
Bir-birine g\u252?manda, g\u252?man Senden bihabar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, g\u246?r indi, e\u351?\u253?alar ne i\u351?dedir,\par
\u221?ok imi\u351? bu e\u351?\u253?ada heman Senden bihabar.\par
\par
RO\u221?Y-SY\u221?ADAN GA\u221?RY\par
Barmydyr barmaga \u253?eri\u328? ba\u351?ga, Hudadan ga\u253?ry,\par
Armagany\u328? barmydyr ro\u253?y-sy\u253?adan ga\u253?ry.\par
\par
Gezdigi\u328?\u231?e \u231?arhy\u328? astynda jahanda jan \u231?ekip,\par
Ne talap bar sa\u328?a bu jebri-jepadan ga\u253?ry.\par
\par
Hak edip, n\u228?hak kylyp \u253?\u246?rse\u328? \u253?\u252?rekden gan d\u246?k\u252?p,\par
Hasyly\u328? nedir seni\u328? j\u252?rmi-g\u252?n\u228?den ga\u253?ry.\par
\par
I\u253?ip-i\u231?ip, mahbup gu\u231?up, \u253?atsa\u328? s\u228?her rahat bile,\par
Tagaty\u328? hany seni\u328? ro\u253?y-ry\u253?adan ga\u253?ry.\par
\par
G\u246?z g\u246?zelde, nebs i\u253?mekde, dil dahy gybat bile,\par
\u350?\u246?wketi\u328? \u8722? \u351?er, ba\u351?da \u253?ok be\u253?le howadan ga\u253?ry.\par
\par
Owwaly a\u328?lamadym, a\u328?lan s\u246?z\u252?ne gitmedim,\par
Bu belada kimse \u253?ok men binowadan ga\u253?ry.\par
\par
Pikir et Magtymguly, pany\u253?a bak ne g\u246?rner,\par
So\u328?y \u253?ok, aldagy \u231?oh, f\u246?wti-penadan ga\u253?ry.\par
\par
RY\u221?ADAN, \u221?A REP\par
Sag\u253? ile gutulmadym men bu beladan, \u253?a Rep,\par
\u199?yka bilmen j\u228?ht edip, ujb-u ry\u253?adan, \u253?a Rep.\par
\par
Talygym etdi tulug, a\u328?dym ony ahtary-bet,\par
Sen \u253?yrag et meni bu bagty-sy\u253?adan, \u253?a Rep.\par
\par
\u221?owmy-te\u351?ehhut a\u253?dar hal ma\u328?a, bir \u351?ahyd-a\u253?n,\par
Gutulyrmy gahba jan be\u253?le g\u252?w\u228?den, \u253?a Rep.\par
\par
Ten ybadatda ylal hem d\u246?wi, \u351?e\u253?tandyr bagal,\par
\u221?at edip, emri-ezel h\u246?kmi-ha\u253?adan, \u253?a Rep.\par
\par
Derg\u228?hi\u328?e, e\u253? Kirdig\u228?r, kylsam ybadat \u253?ok karar,\par
Etgenime \u253?ok ygtybar sowmy-saladan, \u253?a Rep.\par
\par
Men ist\u228?r men Senden Seni, Sen et yrak menden meni,\par
Hajat rowa kyl, \u253?a Gany, meni-m\u252?bteladan, \u253?a Rep.\par
\par
Magtymgulyny her zaman basdy bela, a\u231?dy zyban,\par
E\u253?lemesin her m\u246?minan mahrum dogadan, \u253?a Rep.\par
\par
BU NE TERHOS-T\u214?WELLADYR\par
\u221?\u252?z\u252?m \u253?ar \u253?\u252?z\u252?ne d\u252?\u351?se, dilim alhamdulilladyr,\par
Eger gahryna ugra\u351?sam, okyrym kulhuwalladyr.\par
\par
Bu derg\u228?hi durar kurbet, Il\u228?hi h\u228?di\u253?i-wahdet,\par
Muhabbeti\u328? makamynda onu\u328? az waspy l\u246?wladyr.\par
\par
Pelekler nerdibanydyr, zemin sa\u253?asyna m\u228?t\u228?\u231?,\par
Iki nagle\u253?ni ar\u351?y\u328? kellesinde t\u228?ji-agladyr.\par
\par
Eger misgin, eger bir ba\u253?, taparmy sensizin hi\u231? ra\u253?,\par
\u221?amandyr a\u253?ralyk, e\u253?-wa\u253?, arap labzynda we\u253?ladyr,\par
\par
Jewary\u328?dan jydalara, k\u246?\u253?\u252?\u328?de jan pidalara,\par
Seni ist\u228?n gedalara zekat husnu\u328?da \u246?wladyr.\par
\par
Erer men bir g\u252?n\u228?k\u228?ri\u328?, hemi\u351?e a\u351?yky-zary\u328?,\par
\u221?\u252?z\u252?n g\u246?rmesem ol \u253?ary\u328?, ha\u231?an k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m teselladyr.\par
\par
Pyragy, ni\u231?e wagt oldy, habar tapmas men ol \u253?ardan,\par
\u221?anar men ata\u351?y-y\u351?ka, bu ne terhos-t\u246?welladyr.\par
\par
BIKARARAM, DOGRUSY\par
E\u253?, peri, men a\u351?ygam sa\u328?a, \u253?anaram, dogrusy,\par
G\u246?rme\u253?in\u231?e g\u252?l \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328?i, bikararam, dogrusy.\par
\par
\u350?\u228?hri\u328?izde bir peri adyn e\u351?itdim men sizi\u328?,\par
Bilbili-bi\u231?\u228?re\u253?em, \u231?oh ahy-zaram, dogrusy.\par
\par
Bir bezirgenem menem, y\u351?ky\u328? matagyn sataram,\par
\u350?\u228?hri\u328?ize gelmi\u351?em, bes, s\u246?wdag\u228?rem, dogrusy.\par
\par
Gide bilmen \u351?\u228?hri\u328?ize, hyz-haramdan gorkaram,\par
\u221?edi piri\u328? lafzydan bir \u253?adyg\u228?rem, dogrusy.\par
\par
E\u253?, peri, z\u252?lp\u252?\u328? peri, walla, seni\u328? de\u253? huplara,\par
A\u253?dy\u253?ar Magtymguly, bir pi\u351?ek\u228?rem, dogrusy.\par
\par
PANY-JAHAN GEREKMES\par
Pelek, ma\u328?a mal berer sen, ol genji-k\u228?n gerekmes,\par
G\u246?zel \u253?arymy g\u246?rmesem, pany-jahan gerekmes.\par
\par
Baga girip ne\u253?le\u253?in men, jo\u351? uran anbary\u328?y,\par
Bilbilim \u253?esir kylyp sen, g\u246?zel re\u253?han gerekmes.\par
\par
Ilim-g\u252?n\u252?m hary-zardyr, gelsin d\u246?wlet le\u351?geri\u328?,\par
Dini h\u246?d\u252?r e\u253?le\u253?ir sen, ajap Gurhan gerekmes.\par
\par
Bizi\u328? ili\u328? \u351?a-gedasy, pelek, sa\u328?a \u253?\u252?k bolar,\par
Her kes \u246?zige soltandyr, han-u soltan gerekmes.\par
\par
Bu zemini lerzan kylyp, asman, j\u252?nb\u252?\u351? e\u253?ledi\u328?,\par
Ahyrzaman sary \u253?\u246?rd\u252?\u328?, mahy-taban gerekmes.\par
\par
Me\u253?lis kylar boldy bu g\u252?n il-g\u252?n\u252?mi\u328? barysy,\par
Gelmegin sen, ser go\u351?up ki, bize myhman gerekmes.\par
\par
Kylgyl \u246?mr\u252?mizi zy\u253?at, ga\u253?ry n\u228?rse istemen,\par
Bu aja\u253?yp \u231?aglarymda ajal-pe\u253?man gerekmes.\par
\par
\u199?arh \u252?st\u252?nde bina kylyp, bizleri sen ja\u253?lady\u328?,\par
Ka\u253?yl bola\u253? bu ja\u253?y\u328?a, emma gerdan gerekmes.\par
\par
Da\u253?ym \u246?mr\u252?m \u246?t\u252?re\u253?in, beren bahar paslyda,\par
Erkanadyr bilbil-sowsan, bize hazan gerekmes.\par
\par
Namartlary da\u351? e\u253?legil bu me\u253?lis etrapydan,\par
\u196?r \u253?igitler serho\u351? bolar, namart-zenan gerekmes.\par
\par
Her kime sen bag\u351? edip sen, \u253?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman bir g\u252?li,\par
Ol g\u252?llerden ga\u253?ry bize sahypjenan gerekmes.\par
\par
Magtymguly, sen s\u246?zlegil \u8722? di\u253?di go\u231?lar me\u253?lisi,\par
Sen g\u252?ftar sen bu me\u253?lisde, ga\u253?ry dessan gerekmes.\par
\par
T\u196? ALGAN\u199?A G\u214?Z\u220?NI\par
A\u351?yk ata\u351? g\u246?rse urar ata\u351? i\u231?re \u246?z\u252?ni,\par
G\u252?l ro\u253?una kylar nazar, t\u228? algan\u231?a g\u246?z\u252?ni.\par
\par
Bu y\u351?kny\u328? zulmy bilen en\u231?e jandyr hary-zar,\par
Mag\u351?ugyna bolsa du\u231?ar, tapmaz di\u253?jek s\u246?z\u252?ni.\par
\par
Bu pany jahana baky\u328?, gymmat e\u253?lemi\u351? y\u351?ky,\par
Da\u253?ym bit\u252?t\u252?n kylypdyr, g\u246?r\u252?\u328?, y\u351?ky\u328? k\u246?z\u252?ni.\par
\par
A\u351?yk g\u246?rse mag\u351?ugyny \u253?yly\u328? hazan paslynda,\par
\u214?z\u252?ni ol \u253?ana atar, unudyp ol \u253?azyny.\par
\par
K\u228?l i\u231?inde g\u246?rer bolsa k\u228?kiligi, tawusy,\par
Birini g\u246?ze alman, g\u246?zle\u253?ir ol gazyny.\par
\par
Simap kibi jan titrese, e\u351?ki aksa sil kibi,\par
Derdini unudyp ol, \u231?eker \u253?ary\u328? n\u228?zini.\par
\par
Ger onu\u328? ol mag\u351?ugy sahypjemal bolmasa hem,\par
Ga\u253?ry g\u246?zel jenanlara \u246?w\u252?rmez ol \u253?\u252?z\u252?ni.\par
\par
Jyda bolsa g\u246?zelinden, unudar pany-jahan,\par
Din-imany esse gelmez, ar\u351?a \u253?etir owazyny.\par
\par
Elem bilen g\u246?zel \u253?ara \u253?ylda \u253?eke gowu\u351?sa,\par
Du\u351?sa ol peri o\u328?a, gurar ki bijin bazyny.\par
\par
G\u252?ller i\u231?re bir g\u252?li bar, ga\u253?ry sowsan islemez,\par
\u350?ol g\u252?l di\u253?ip urar bolar her kanda ol \u246?z\u252?ni.\par
\par
Eger ol \u253?ar kylsa o\u253?un perilere ba\u351? go\u351?up,\par
\u221?\u252?reginden owaz e\u253?l\u228?r, go\u351?up o\u328?a sazyny.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu ne s\u246?zd\u252?r, sen ki a\u351?yk emes sen,\par
Ka\u253?sy ja\u253?da e\u351?itdi\u328? sen ol Mejnun ny\u253?azyny?\par
\par
ME\u327?LI \u221?ARYMDAN\par
Pelek \u228?lem ryswa kyldy, a\u253?yrypdyr zarymdan,\par
Ne i\u351? kylsam, habar bilem men ol Me\u328?li \u253?arymdan.\par
\par
Yns-jyns tug\u253?an e\u253?l\u228?p, zemin lerzana gelmi\u351?,\par
Asmanlar j\u252?nb\u252?\u351? kylyp, k\u246?wkep \u253?anmy\u351? narymdan.\par
\par
Bir rehimsiz \u351?a eripdir, g\u246?wn\u252?m i\u231?re ja\u253? tutup,\par
Bent e\u253?le\u253?ipdir Lukmany, habar almaz azarymdan.\par
\par
G\u252?nde bir wagt nazar salmaz, agdy serden derdimiz,\par
Jismim h\u228?kister boldy, janym d\u252?\u351?\u252?p kararymdan.\par
\par
Erse gyrgy pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228? bermez ba\u351?da t\u228?jini,\par
Hi\u231? u\u253?almaz, handan kylar, gorkmaz meni\u328? nazarymdan.\par
\par
G\u252?zerimi bendi kylsam, her g\u252?nde kyrk a\u231?adyr,\par
Aby-K\u246?wser z\u252?lalymy i\u231?ipdir ol g\u252?zerimden.\par
\par
\u221?anar otly Magtymguly, ot lybasyn sen ge\u253?ip,\par
Pany jahan otla\u253?yp sen, dilde bolan nary\u328?dan.\par
\par
BENDI BOLDUM\par
Me\u328?li hanym, e\u253?\u253?amy\u328?dan gorkup, bara bilme\u253? boldum,\par
G\u246?z bilen gara ga\u351?y\u328?dan gola d\u252?\u351?\u252?p, bendi boldum.\par
Jellatlar men bendi guly zynjyr bilen bent e\u253?le\u253?ir,\par
Ger ki sen-de goldamasa\u328?, nala\u231? eziz jan ne\u253?le\u253?ir.\par
\par
Nesimi dek so\u253?up meni, seglere \u351?am kylar indi,\par
L\u228?\u351? \u252?st\u252?nde garagu\u351?lar je\u328?\u328?i-s\u246?we\u351? salar indi.\par
\par
Ustuhanym \u253?el sowuryp, we\u253?il ja\u253?a wasyl e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
Bendi galan eziz jany bil, dowzaha hasyl e\u253?l\u228?r.\par
\par
Dowzah meni \u253?aka bilmez, berer z\u252?lp\u252?\u328? bir taryna,\par
Tor i\u231?inde saklap meni, gow\u351?yr \u253?yl\u231?yr ol mary\u328?a.\par
\par
Ol mar kowup j\u252?lgelerden, \u351?e\u253?tan bilen kylar hemra,\par
Kylgyl azat, Me\u328?li hanym, men misgini kylma g\u252?mra.\par
\par
Magtymguly ismi\u328? seni\u328?, bolsun gerekdir Pyragy,\par
Mar golundan dyndym di\u253?sem, geldi hijrany\u328? \u253?aragy.\par
\par
HEMRA E\u221?LEDI\par
G\u252?l \u253?\u252?z\u252?ni gizle\u253?ip \u253?ar, g\u246?z \u253?a\u351?ym der\u253?a e\u253?ledi,\par
Ga\u253?yp olup bu jahandan, \u253?owuzy hemra e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
G\u246?zle\u253?ip men bakdym her \u253?an iste\u253?ip ol \u253?arymy,\par
Tapmadym ki, ga\u253?tadan \u246?mr\u252?mi za\u253?a e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
G\u228?h turup \u351?am-u s\u228?herler, kaknus ererem zarla\u253?yp,\par
\u221?ene bu gaflatda galan g\u246?wn\u252?me bela e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
Di\u328?lemez ki, arzymy, be\u253?le ki zalym bolupdyr,\par
Bakma\u253?yp mal-u m\u252?lk\u252?me, baryn yr\u253?a e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
A\u253?dadyr Pyragy derdin, e\u253?le mi\u253?esser emin\par
Ga\u253?ta ba\u351?dan ot urup, ol baky d\u252?n\u253?\u228? e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
UNUDAR OL \u221?OLUNY\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, e\u351?tse Lukman derdimi\u328? bu halyny,\par
Terk eder ki, k\u252?lli watan, unudar ol \u253?oluny.\par
\par
\u171?H\u252?w\u187? di\u253?ip, men zary-efgan gije-g\u252?ndiz aglaram,\par
Ger e\u351?itse zarymy, Karun unudar p\u228?lini.\par
\par
Gara daglar katra-katra \u253?a\u351? d\u246?k\u252?ban halyma,\par
D\u246?redipdir ulug umman, Nuh \u253?\u252?zd\u252?rer salyny.\par
\par
Jan \u351?\u228?hrine saldy tala\u328?, geldi le\u351?ger tug bilen,\par
Bilmenem, ol \u231?\u246?zermik\u228?n bu watan ykbalyny?\par
\par
A\u253?dy\u328? ol \u253?aryma meni\u328? zyndan i\u231?re bolanym,\par
Sa\u231?laryny salla\u253?yp, kylsyn azat men guluny.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ady\u328? seni\u328? k\u252?lli \u228?leme dolup,\par
Kylsa adam baryn gapyl, gizle, berme bu malny.\par
\par
K\u214?\u221?EN JANYMA\par
\u221?asaw gurup girdi pelek jan \u351?\u228?hri-watanyma,\par
Kylmady nazary bir dem oda k\u246?\u253?en janyma.\par
\par
G\u252?nde Anka gu\u351?a du\u351?up, bir dem bile u\u231?mu\u351?am,\par
Pelek tutup ganatymdan, basdy hijran la\u253?yna.\par
\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, men pakyrda indi ga\u253?ry \u231?\u228?re \u253?ok,\par
Geda \u228?hli jem kylyp, pa\u231? salypdyr hanyma.\par
\par
\u199?irme bolup ga\u231?ar bolsam \u231?\u246?l-be\u253?ewan i\u231?inde,\par
Pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228? gyrgysy azm e\u253?le\u253?ir janyma.\par
\par
Derdim meni\u328? boldy hebes, Lukman gelmez ga\u351?yma,\par
Kimse baryp galat di\u253?di derdimi Lukmanyma.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?zlegil sen, \u246?mr\u252?\u328? senden gol \u252?zer,\par
Doga e\u253?l\u228?p ge\u231?er men, ol Azady ussadyma.\par
\par
HUNLAR D\u214?KERLER G\u214?Z\u220?NDEN\par
Dertliler derdimi g\u246?rse, utanarlar \u246?z\u252?den,\par
Tebip \u228?hli \u231?\u228?re tapman, hunlar d\u246?kerler g\u246?z\u252?den.\par
\par
G\u246?rse a\u351?yklar bu ody, unudar \u246?z ata\u351?yn,\par
\u199?ykar dag-u da\u351?lar \u252?zre, Mejnuny tapmaz d\u252?z\u252?den.\par
\par
Bir taryna \u253?arymy\u328? \u228?hli musulman tussagy,\par
Kapyrlar ist\u228?p adalat, zarlap \u253?\u246?rerler yzydan.\par
\par
E\u351?tse Nowa\u253?y, Nyzamy, Fird\u246?wsi kylan zarym,\par
Terki-d\u252?n\u253?\u228? e\u253?le\u253?ip, barysy ge\u231?er s\u246?z\u252?den.\par
\par
Gijeler nala \u231?ekip, g\u252?ndiz umydym \u253?ok meni\u328?,\par
Do\u253?ma\u253?ar bu a\u231? g\u246?zlerim bakyp \u253?ary\u328? \u253?\u252?z\u252?den.\par
\par
Pyragy, sen sabyr e\u253?l\u228?p unut gy\u351?y\u328? paslyny,\par
Ger unutsa ki bu g\u252?ni, pe\u253?da g\u246?rme\u253? g\u252?\u253?z\u252?den.\par
\par
NE HAJATDYR\par
G\u252?l\u231?ehre\u253?i sowsan anbar bu\u253? e\u253?le\u253?ip, salamatdyr,\par
Gol uzatsam g\u252?l m\u228?hwe\u351?im, \u253?eg bilme\u253? dur, ne hajatdyr?\par
\par
Webal bilen wabeste men, m\u252?rewwet \u253?ok men dek gula,\par
Gapyl jiger e\u253?l\u228?p lerzan, di\u253?er: dehri kesapatdyr.\par
\par
Lagly-merjendir bo\u253?nunda, aby-K\u246?wser dahanynda,\par
Nisar bolan men bend\u228?ge, rehim etmez, ne apatdyr?\par
\par
Ragna \u253?arym, serwi kamat bo\u253?lary\u328?a perwana men,\par
Suhanyma handan kylyp, ga\u351?yn kakar, ne adatdyr?\par
\par
Gola tutup y\u351?k oduny, men perwana h\u246?dr e\u253?le\u253?ir,\par
Elem bilen hasyl bolsam, pynhan kylar, ne a\u351?ratdyr?\par
\par
Jamyg e\u253?l\u228?p sagadatym, \u253?\u246?rsem, katl alnymdadyr,\par
Wehim kylmanam pelekden, \u253?\u246?ren ugrumda hasratdyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, sen de\u253? murga de\u351?tde sa\u253?\u253?at du\u231?ar geler,\par
Lahat i\u231?re \u253?al\u328?yz go\u253?ar, jandan jyda rahatdyr.\par
\par
RE\u221?HANA OG\u350?A\u221?YR\par
E\u253? peri, zyba peri, ro\u253?u\u328? tabana og\u351?a\u253?yr,\par
G\u252?l ro\u253?u\u328?da m\u252?\u351?ki-anbar re\u253?hana og\u351?a\u253?yr.\par
\par
Bu k\u246?\u253?en janyma besdir birje di\u253?en s\u246?zleri\u328?,\par
Ga\u351?lary\u328? ta\u253?ly kaky\u351?y\u328? Le\u253?li jana og\u351?a\u253?yr.\par
\par
Men gulu\u328? men, \u253?aksa\u328? janym, golu\u328?dadyr \u8722? ol \u253?esir,\par
H\u246?km\u252?rowan permanydyr, S\u252?le\u253?mana og\u351?a\u253?yr.\par
\par
\u214?rtese\u328? oda \u253?akyp, \u253?a ki \u253?\u252?zse\u328? tyg bilen,\par
Tygy dermana barabar, \u246?zi Lukmana og\u351?a\u253?yr.\par
\par
Iste\u253?ip jemaly\u328?y, ke\u351?t e\u253?ledim k\u252?lli jahan,\par
G\u246?zden d\u246?ken ganly \u253?a\u351?ym, ol ummana og\u351?a\u253?yr.\par
\par
Bu pelegi\u328? zulmy bilen gitdi sabyr-takatym,\par
Bu \u253?alan pany jahan bes bir zyndana og\u351?a\u253?yr.\par
\par
En\u231?eleri hums edip, kime berdi d\u246?wleti,\par
Ba\u351?ym \u231?ykmaz derde galdym, i\u351?i \u253?alana og\u351?a\u253?yr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, goja pele\u328? her g\u252?nde bir aw atar,\par
\u214?tse \u246?mri ol pakyry\u328?, tilki p\u228?lwana og\u351?a\u253?yr.\par
\par
Y\u350?K DOWZAHYNA\par
Her\u231?ent be\u253?le naly\u351? etsem ol Haky\u328? dergahyna,\par
Ga\u253?ta s\u246?z\u252?m di\u328?leme\u253?, salar y\u351?k dowzahyna.\par
\par
G\u246?wn\u252?mi tag\u253?yr kylyp y\u351?k, lukmadan hums e\u253?ledi,\par
G\u252?w\u351? tutma\u253? ol zaryma, sardy hijran \u231?arhyna.\par
\par
Tugun erdim, urdy zaglar, bir alajym \u253?ok meni\u328?,\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?in, sa\u253?\u253?at bolup, d\u252?\u351?d\u252?m murgy\u328? gahryna.\par
\par
En\u231?e naly\u351? e\u253?le\u253?ip men, il-g\u252?n bilen gan aglasam,\par
Zaryma handan kylar ol, barmaz s\u246?z\u252?mi\u328? parhyna.\par
\par
\u196?hli \u246?ten a\u351?yk-mag\u351?uk satsa y\u351?ky\u328? matasyn,\par
Golda bary-\u253?ogun berip, \u253?etmez y\u351?kym nyrhyna.\par
\par
E\u253?\u253?up kibi ten-u janymny \u253?uwdupdyr murlary,\par
Ustuhanymy getirip saldylar matbahyna.\par
\par
Wejhi bilen d\u252?\u351?se ro\u253?um, \u253?esir kylar gullary,\par
Pa\u253?y-destimi bent edip, atar Je\u253?hun bahryna.\par
\par
E\u253? \u253?aranlar, pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228? gyrgysy aldy \u253?esir,\par
Pakyr Magtymgulyny salar zemin lahatyna.\par
\par
HUNY BARDYR\par
K\u246?\u253?se \u246?mr\u252?m jebr y\u351?kyna, yzynda Mejnuny bardyr,\par
\u221?\u252?zleri handan e\u253?lese, \u231?e\u351?mide huny bardyr.\par
\par
Pe\u351?e bilen pili tutup, g\u246?r, bu pelek o\u253?un kylar,\par
Pe\u351?e di\u253?ip agyrtmagyl, jesetde jany bardyr.\par
\par
G\u246?zel ilden gider d\u246?wlet, merdi namarda d\u246?ner,\par
Namarda dil, merde g\u252?lki, bigadyr hany bardyr.\par
\par
Her g\u246?zelde bir a\u253?yp bar, onki syna ornuda,\par
S\u252?\u253?de si\u328?e nazar salsa\u328?, i\u231?inde gany bardyr.\par
\par
Leb \u252?st\u252?ne leb go\u253?up sen, zerre tagam bilmedi\u328?,\par
Emma \u253?ary\u328? lebinde, y\u351?k jawudany bardyr.\par
\par
Aza\u351?yban da\u328? s\u228?herde, wasyl olsa\u328? bir gapa,\par
Bag i\u231?inde \u351?ejer atly bir arguwany bardyr.\par
\par
Mejnun kibi y\u351?ka k\u246?\u253?se\u328?, adam ogly, untmagyl,\par
Dowzah odundan beter ata\u351?-suzany bardyr.\par
\par
Pelek salsa her bir \u253?ola, \u253?\u246?regil sen, ga\u253?tmagyl,\par
\u199?\u252?nki pelegi\u328? golunda, uly permany bardyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu watany, sen terk kylyp \u253?\u246?rmegil,\par
H\u252?\u253?r-peri, gulman-be\u351?er, en\u231?e jenany bardyr.\par
\par
BALLAR MESGENI\par
E\u253?-\u228?, dilber, jemaly\u328?da jugra hallar mesgeni,\par
Zybany\u328?da \u351?eker erkan, dahanda ballar mesgeni.\par
\par
Zynat kylyp \u231?ykdy dilber, tawus gu\u351? dek dalmynyp,\par
Mahy-taban u\u253?at e\u253?l\u228?r, \u253?arymda \u253?yllar mesgeni.\par
\par
Bady-saba geze bilmez dagy-de\u351?ti ke\u351?t edip,\par
Ne\u253?lesin ol bendi galdy, dilberde \u253?eller mesgeni.\par
\par
Arap zyban d\u252?\u351?di hara, hyrydary \u253?ok onu\u328?,\par
Bu pynhany kylsam \u228?\u351?g\u228?r, dilberde diller mesgeni.\par
\par
Serwi daragt bo\u253?ly peri, seni hijran \u246?rtedi,\par
Ger ki arzy\u328? s\u246?zlese\u328?, \u253?arymda teller mesgeni.\par
\par
E\u253?, Pyragy, g\u246?rkezip \u253?ol, \u246?z\u252?\u328? onda aza\u351?yp,\par
Gezer boldu\u328? di\u253?gil arzy\u328?, dilberde \u253?ollar mesgeni.\par
\par
HUN BILEN\par
G\u246?zel \u246?mr\u252?m takaty ga\u231?dy, ne\u253?le\u253? jan bilen,\par
Ku\u253?a\u351?ym mekan e\u253?l\u228?p, hemra bolmu\u351? hun bilen.\par
\par
Ne \u253?aman y\u351?ky\u328? ody, \u231?\u228?resi \u253?okdur onu\u328?,\par
\u221?anan jana d\u228?ri kylmaz, k\u246?\u253?dir, g\u246?r\u252?\u328?, suzan bilen.\par
\par
Kimleri\u328? ykbaly \u253?\u246?r\u252?p, kimse handyr, kim geda,\par
Kimse harsyd\u252?n\u253?\u228?, \u253?ygar, \u253?\u252?wr\u252?p pany jahan bilen.\par
\par
\u221?\u252?regimde \u253?andy narlar, bir perwana nazar kylmaz,\par
Magtymguly \u246?ter boldy bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?den arman bilen.\par
\par
HAKY\u327? PERMANYDYR\par
Dostlarym, g\u246?wn\u252?m i\u231?inde dowzahy\u328? suzanydyr,\par
Istemez men ol ata\u351?y, ne\u253?le\u253?, Haky\u328? permanydyr.\par
\par
Pany jahan gyrgysyny\u328? penjesinde galmy\u351?am,\par
Gyrgy \u228?hlini\u328? i\u231?inde \u253?amanlar \u253?amanydyr.\par
\par
Merdi o\u253?nar boldy pelek ilde ryswa e\u253?le\u253?ip,\par
Pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228? gerdi\u351?i \u8722? namartlar d\u246?wranydyr.\par
\par
\u214?mr\u252?mi\u328? her bir g\u252?ni \u246?ter boldy elem bilen,\par
Salym etrapy pelegi\u328? bir gussa gerdanydyr.\par
\par
Adam oglun bijin kimin, pelek her dem o\u253?na\u253?ar,\par
Ol Haky\u328? pelek \u252?\u231?in \u253?aradan ha\u253?wanydyr.\par
\par
G\u252?nde \u253?\u252?z katla \u246?ter men umman Hazar etrapydan,\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?in bu d\u228?li g\u246?wn\u252?m pelek natuwanydyr.\par
\par
Ne i\u351?leri kylar boldy ol Haky\u328? dergahynda,\par
Pelegi\u328? bu k\u228?rine j\u252?mle-jahan ha\u253?ranydyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?z di\u253?e\u328?de, s\u246?z ahyryn a\u328?lagyn,\par
Erse Azazyly \u351?e\u253?tan kylan ol zybanydyr.\par
\par
YGTY\u221?ARYM ALYPDYR\par
Pany pelek gerdi\u351?inde i\u231?digim gan bolupdyr,\par
G\u252?nde \u253?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? jebir bilen ygty\u253?arym alypdyr.\par
\par
Gaflat ukusynda \u253?atyp, se\u253?l etmedim bossanyma,\par
Bu g\u252?n nazar salsam ol \u253?an, \u231?i\u231?eklerim solupdyr.\par
\par
Bagbanymy alyp \u253?esir, g\u246?teripdir bu pelek,\par
Ugrunda sepil \u253?\u246?r\u252?p tapsam, \u231?a\u253?a salypdyr.\par
\par
Desti-pa\u253?a urup zynjyr, mejnun kibi da\u328?ylan,\par
Ol zyndany\u328? gapysynda zary-gir\u253?an galypdyr.\par
\par
Bendilikden bo\u351?adara bir gurbatym \u253?ok meni\u328?,\par
Ga\u253?rat aty ga\u253?ra tesip, \u246?mri-de gojalypdyr.\par
\par
Ol zyndany\u328? soltanyna di\u253?dim: \u171?Halas kyl ony\u187?,\par
Zary-gir\u253?anymy g\u246?r\u252?p, ol soltan u\u253?alypdyr.\par
\par
Di\u253?di soltan: \u171?Bent kyly\u328?lar alnymdadyr, bu guly\u187?,\par
Magtymguly \u246?z dilinden g\u246?r, bagry gan bolupdyr.\par
\par
G\u214?RM\u220?\u350?EM\par
Hemra e\u253?l\u228?p men namardy, birje zaman \u253?\u246?rm\u252?\u351?em,\par
D\u246?z\u252?p onu\u328? her derdine, kyldyk i\u351?in g\u246?rm\u252?\u351?em.\par
\par
Bir zamanda bir g\u252?l gelip, hasyl boldy bagyma,\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?in men ol sowsany, andalyba bermi\u351?em.\par
\par
Ol andalyp \u351?ady-horram boldy g\u252?le sata\u351?yp,\par
Aklym kesme\u253?, ne heka\u253?at baryn ondan sormu\u351?am.\par
\par
Di\u253?di: \u171?Perwana menem, y\u351?k elemine ba\u351? go\u351?up,\par
Bu sowsany\u328? derdi bilen \u246?z\u252?m nara urmu\u351?am\u187?.\par
\par
Gelip \u351?e\u253?tan, alyp g\u252?li ata\u351? i\u231?re atar boldy,\par
Suzanyny men unudyp, ata\u351? i\u231?re girmi\u351?em.\par
\par
Jany-tenim baryny h\u228?kister kyldy ata\u351?,\par
Bady-saba \u246?wser boldy, asmana sowrulmy\u351?am.\par
\par
Magtymguly, akmak oldum, nadanlygym \u253?eg eken,\par
Erse elem bilen gezem, bu ykbala begenmi\u351?em.\par
\par
JAN MATASYN ISTE\u221?IP\par
Pelegi\u328? bu pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228? bazarynda ne k\u228?ri,\par
\u214?zge mata g\u246?zlemez ol, jan matasyn iste\u253?ip.\par
\par
G\u246?zl\u252?ler g\u246?z\u252?n alar ol, aryplary\u328? dilini,\par
Garrylary go\u253?ar \u253?al\u328?yz, \u253?ol hasasyn iste\u253?ip.\par
\par
Mertleri namart kylyp, \u253?ykdy en\u231?e \u228?rleri,\par
M\u246?minleri e\u253?l\u228?r \u253?al\u328?yz ol lybasyn iste\u253?ip.\par
\par
A\u351?yklarda s\u246?ndi ata\u351?, perwanada ne g\u252?n\u228??\par
Jyda kyldy gan agladyp, ol hemrasyn iste\u253?ip.\par
\par
Magtymguly derde \u253?akyn, bu gojalan eziz jan,\par
Gorkaram, alar eken dil senasyn iste\u253?ip.\par
\par
Y\u350?K BAZARYMA\par
Pelek karardan d\u252?\u351?\u252?p, pida bolmu\u351? zaryma,\par
Bir aja\u253?yp zyba peri, girmi\u351? y\u351?k bazaryma.\par
\par
Her g\u246?renler hyrydardyr, \u351?ahy-geda hem guly,\par
Merdi-namart hem-de n\u228?kes s\u246?z \u253?etirer \u253?aryma.\par
\par
Kyla bilmen pynhan ony, d\u246?zme\u253?\u228?r ejiz k\u246?\u328?\u252?l,\par
Ger \u228?\u351?ig\u228?r kylsam \u253?\u252?z\u252?n, g\u246?ren d\u252?\u351?er gahryma.\par
\par
Asly behi\u351?t s\u252?nb\u252?lidir g\u252?l \u253?\u252?z\u252?nde z\u252?lpleri,\par
Erem i\u231?re biten narlar og\u351?amaz bu naryma.\par
\par
Gelen derdini men alyp, h\u252?wler \u231?ekiban gezerem,\par
Lukman gelip, g\u246?z a\u253?la\u253?yp, \u231?\u228?re kylmaz azaryma.\par
\par
Di\u253?r Pyragy, mert menem, \u228?\u351?g\u228?r ile mertligim,\par
Diri gitmez ga\u351?larymdan degen namys-aryma.\par
\par
DA\u350?YMYZA\par
\u350?um pelek girdaba saldy k\u246?p hy\u253?al ba\u351?ymyza,\par
\u199?yksak eger ki, kenara, tor gurar da\u351?ymyza.\par
\par
Ba\u351? alyp gidip bu \u253?urtdan, tutsam ki ga\u253?ry watan,\par
Geler ol pasly-baharda, \u253?agmyry gy\u351?ymyza.\par
\par
G\u246?\u231? turar g\u246?wn\u252?m go\u351?uny, bakyban permanyna,\par
G\u252?nde bir wekili \u253?ollar, arz edip ga\u351?ymyza.\par
\par
Ro\u253?y-kamatyny g\u246?rsem, \u253?ok kararym, ne\u253?l\u228?rem,\par
G\u252?ndizlerne naly\u351? etsem, gije girer d\u252?\u253?\u351?\u252?mize.\par
\par
\u214?l\u252?b\u228?n \u253?ar goludan, boldum ki men hem bes \u351?ehit,\par
Bir zaman rahat berme\u253?, gu\u351?lar gonar l\u228?\u351?imize.\par
\par
\u221?okdur rehmi \u351?um pelegi\u328?, a\u253?yrar dost-\u253?arydan,\par
G\u246?r, ni\u231?e e\u253?\u253?am \u246?t\u252?p, d\u252?\u351?mez g\u246?z garda\u351?ymyza.\par
\par
\u350?un\u231?a arz edip garasam, \u253?oluna g\u246?zler tutup,\par
\u221?\u252?regi da\u351?dan gaty, erimez naly\u351?ymyza.\par
\par
Garry molla \u8722? Pyragy, \u246?tdi \u253?igitlik paslymyz,\par
G\u252?nde \u253?\u252?z wagt naly\u351? etsem, \u231?\u228?re \u253?ok \u253?a\u351?ymyza.\par
\par
MYHMANYDYR\par
Dertdir bu jany\u328? zilleti, saglyk onu\u328? soltanydyr,\par
Ten m\u252?lk\u252?ni\u328? ser d\u246?wleti dynmaz \u246?ter, myhmanydyr.\par
\par
Nebs e\u253?le\u253?ip serke\u351?ligi ten tagtyny\u328? me\u253?danyda,\par
Rozy-ezel ruhu\u328?, \u253?akyn, \u351?ol \u228?hdi, \u351?ol pe\u253?manydyr.\par
\par
Bu bazara gelen ki\u351?i yhlasyn ary e\u253?lesin,\par
Kabyl bolan yhlasly gul merdanlary\u328? merdanydyr.\par
\par
Di\u253?se bolar set aperin, ruhun besl\u228?p, nebsin basan,\par
Hakykat onu\u328? bazary, Hak mejlisi me\u253?danydyr.\par
\par
Wa\u253? halyna nebsin s\u246?\u253?en, jan le\u351?gerin ejiz go\u253?an,\par
Rozy-jeza \u253?olda\u351? o\u328?a, bet i\u351?leri\u328? pu\u351?manydyr.\par
\par
\u196?r tapmadym - gulluk edem, \u253?ol tapmadym - haja gidem,\par
Bu iki i\u351? bu ten era bu janymy\u328? armanydyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly bu gamzede, t\u228? ke\u253? bu dert ile gider,\par
B\u228?\u351? g\u252?n bu pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de bir a\u351?ygy\u328? d\u246?wranydyr.\par
\par
BETNAM OLUR\par
Her emiri\u328?, ger weziri\u328? akly k\u252?teh, ham olur,\par
Ol emiri\u328? ady ahyr halk era betnam olur.\par
\par
Bir akyl \u8722? sahypkemaly\u328? goly birle i\u351? tutan,\par
I\u351?ini da\u351?dan alar, terpendik\u231?e, kam olur.\par
\par
Istese\u328? seri\u351?desin sen bu jahany\u328? serbe-ser,\par
El a\u231?an, gahryn ge\u231?en, binende\u253?i-e\u253?\u253?am olur.\par
\par
Gelleban arbaba d\u246?n\u252?p, bolmu\u351? arbaplar emir,\par
\u350?alara bolmaz etagat, ili naferjam olur;\par
\par
Di\u253?\u328? salam Magtymgulydan \u253?agy bolgan beglere,\par
A\u253? dolar, enj\u252?m batar, ryswa\u253?y-has-u a:m olur.\par
\par
K\u214?\u327?\u220?L\par
Bilmezem hi\u231?, ka\u253?sy derdi\u328? m\u252?btelasydyr k\u246?\u328?\u252?l,\par
\u221?a, Rep, ol bir biwepany\u328? \u231?oh h\u246?w\u228?sidir k\u246?\u328?\u252?l.\par
\par
Y\u351?k der\u253?adyr, d\u252?\u253?bi \u253?ok, hijran bir otdur, \u246?\u231?me \u253?ok,\par
Y\u351?ka me\u253?l etgen bu otlara \u253?anasydyr, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l.\par
\par
Bilme\u253?en atmy\u351? \u246?z\u252?n y\u351?k oduga perwana dek,\par
Imdi bilmez \u231?\u228?resin kim, ne kylasydyr k\u246?\u328?\u252?l.\par
\par
Isany\u328? demi muhal, Lukman o \u253?erde g\u252?\u328?-u lal,\par
\u221?a, Rep, bu derdi\u328? bu hal ne i\u351? dowasydyr, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l.\par
\par
Ger\u231?e y\u351?ky\u328? derdidir diwana\u253?a jan apaty,\par
A\u351?na \u228?hli bu gamy da\u253?ym a\u253?asydyr, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l.\par
\par
Ni\u231?e m\u228?hrem binowalar tapdylar ondan nowa,\par
Meng eden ondan meni bagtym sy\u253?asydyr, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l.\par
\par
\u221?ygla\u253?yp, Magtymguly, derg\u228?he arzy\u328? edewer,\par
Ne \u252?\u231?in k\u246?p \u253?yglagan bir g\u252?n g\u252?lesidir, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l.\par
\par
JAN \u199?YKAR\par
Ger tutsa halymdan habar, gury aga\u231?dan gan \u231?ykar,\par
Ynsan \u351?erarymdan eser tapsa teninden jan \u231?ykar.\par
\par
Karun kylyp malyn eda, set jan eder bolsa pida,\par
G\u252?n \u351?emgydan bolup jyda, nurun go\u253?up, pynhan \u231?ykar.\par
\par
Bir k\u246?\u351?ede bolsam mukym, k\u246?\u328?le getirsem gadry-sim,\par
Her k\u246?\u351?e\u253?i-we\u253?ranadan set genji-bipa\u253?an \u231?ykar.\par
\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?me gelen nagy\u351?lar g\u246?zlere pe\u253?da bolsa ger,\par
D\u252?\u351?se g\u246?zi nadanlary\u328?, k\u228?mil bolup, merdan \u231?ykar.\par
\par
Hi\u231? a\u328?lama\u253? zir-u zeber, ger tapsa jezb\u228?mden eser,\par
\u171?Elipden\u187?, \u171?biden\u187? bihabar, her demde bir Gurhan \u231?ykar.\par
\par
Jebr etdi Jem\u351?it janyna, ki erdi magdan k\u228?nine,\par
\u221?\u252?z \u253?yl okap pa\u253?anyna ne Zal-u ne Lukman \u231?ykar.\par
\par
Men hem Pyragy ol gadar, aklymy kyldym derbe-der,\par
Bir bah\u252?n\u228?r tapsa habar, per bagla\u253?yp, asman \u231?ykar.\par
\par
AL GANDYR\par
Gopdy A\u253?, G\u252?n \u253?erinden, galdy ky\u253?amat a\u253?aga,\par
Ukuly g\u246?z\u252?mi a\u231?sam, jahan \u253?\u252?zi al gandyr.\par
\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?G\u246?w\u252?n go\u351?ul ile, \u231?yk tyg alyp s\u246?we\u351?e\u187?,\par
N\u228?z e\u253?le\u253?ip geldi ol \u253?ar, di\u253?di: \u171?Ga\u351?ym kemandyr\u187?.\par
\par
Gapyl olma, adam ogly, bir g\u252?n \u246?mr\u252?\u328? bar seni\u328?,\par
\u214?tse \u253?igitlik pasly, g\u252?nde \u253?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? armandyr.\par
\par
G\u252?nde \u253?\u252?z wagt arz edip, ga\u253?dyp almaz sen ony,\par
\u214?t\u252?rmegil gapyl ba\u351?dan, \u246?sen \u351?emal d\u246?wrandyr.\par
\par
Her bir i\u351?e ba\u351? go\u351?up, alma ili\u328? k\u228?\u253?i\u351?in,\par
T\u228? \u246?m\u252?r ahyr gidermi\u351?, her gadamda zy\u253?andyr.\par
\par
Pynhan syryn a\u253?an e\u253?l\u228?p, Pyragy di\u253?di derdini,\par
Illerim alky\u351? oka\u253?ar, bildim, derde dermandyr.\par
\par
A\u221?A ME\u327?Z\u196?R\par
G\u246?w\u252?n i\u231?re sen g\u252?l peri,\par
Ro\u253?u\u328? dolan A\u253?a me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
Ha\u253?ran edip akly-seri,\par
Go\u253?nu\u328? behi\u351?t ja\u253?a me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Zagpyrandyr bagy-bossan,\par
De\u351?te d\u246?ndi der\u253?a-umman,\par
Baky\u328?, dostlar, pany-jahan\par
Bir we\u253?ran sara\u253?a me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Meni\u328? \u253?arym sahypjemal,\par
Perilerden gelmez kemal,\par
Kirpigi ok, ga\u351?y hilal,\par
Si\u328?e baksa\u328?, \u253?a\u253?a me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
G\u246?w\u252?n ist\u228?r ro\u253?un g\u246?rsem,\par
Zyban ist\u228?r kelam sorsam,\par
Gel di\u253?ende, serde \u253?\u246?rsem,\par
Akyl-hu\u351?um pa\u253?a me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Husnu\u328?dan geldim amana,\par
Nazar e\u253?le natuwana,\par
S\u246?zle dilber, men diwana,\par
\u221?ar, owazy\u328? na\u253?a me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Guba gazdyr k\u246?l i\u231?inde,\par
D\u246?wlet gudrat il i\u231?inde,\par
Bagda g\u252?ld\u252?r, \u231?\u246?l i\u231?inde,\par
Arap \u351?\u252?tri \u8722? ma\u253?a me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Kylar bolduk her bir i\u351?i,\par
Aldady pelek gerdi\u351?i,\par
Pany jahany\u328? te\u351?w\u252?\u351?i,\par
D\u252?\u253?bi dargan \u8722? ry\u253?a me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
N\u228?ler ist\u228?r, di\u253?, d\u252?kany\u328?,\par
Bere\u253? iman, \u351?irin janym,\par
G\u246?zel peri, se\u328? mekany\u328?,\par
K\u228?bede Be\u253?tulla me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Mahy-tabandyr jemaly,\par
Ro\u253?una tutmu\u351? desmaly,\par
Akly \u231?a\u351?an Magtymguly,\par
Il i\u231?inde \u351?e\u253?da me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
GY\u221?MAZ G\u214?Z\u220?M\par
N\u228?zli \u253?ar erkin \u253?atandyr,\par
O\u253?armaga gy\u253?maz g\u246?z\u252?m.\par
G\u246?zlerime \u231?\u246?p atandyr,\par
Laldyr dilim, \u231?ykmaz s\u246?z\u252?m.\par
\par
A\u231? g\u246?zlerim g\u246?rsem di\u253?ip,\par
Hyzmatynda dursam di\u253?ip,\par
Te\u351?ne lebden sorsam di\u253?ip,\par
Kararym \u253?ok, \u231?ytmaz \u253?\u252?z\u252?m.\par
\par
Pyragy di\u253?r, galyp pynhan,\par
S\u252?rme\u253? \u246?ld\u252?m, dostlar d\u246?wran,\par
Telwas urup jesetde jan,\par
\u199?yksam di\u253?er \u253?ara lazym.\par
\par
G\u220?LE ME\u327?Z\u196?R\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, \u253?ag\u351?y \u253?ary\u328?,\par
Go\u253?ny jennet, g\u252?le me\u328?z\u228?r,\par
S\u246?zlese, d\u252?rler sa\u231?ylar,\par
Dilleri bilbile me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Y\u351?k ody \u253?andyrdy bizi,\par
Sorama\u328?lar menden s\u246?zi,\par
\u221?ary\u328? e\u253?gi gyzyl \u253?\u252?zi\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? A\u253?a-G\u252?ne me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
N\u228?ler \u231?ekdim derdi-pyrak,\par
\u221?ete\u253? di\u253?sem, \u253?olum yrak,\par
Galam ga\u351?ly, badam gabak,\par
Sa\u231?lary s\u252?nb\u252?le me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Z\u252?lplerine urup \u351?ana,\par
Meni ol kyldy diwana,\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? ol - \u351?em, men - perwana,\par
\u221?andym, tenim k\u252?le me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
K\u246?\u253?en \u253?ok d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de men\u231?e,\par
Didar g\u246?rmek \u253?ok do\u253?yn\u231?a,\par
Di\u351?leri d\u252?r, agzy gun\u231?a,\par
Bili in\u231?e - gyla me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
G\u246?zi nerkes, bo\u253?y \u351?em\u351?at,\par
Kirpikleri misli polat,\par
Peri-pe\u253?ker serwi-azat,\par
Desse-desse g\u252?le me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
G\u246?ws\u252?nde bar go\u351?a nary,\par
Ak \u253?\u252?z\u252?nde j\u252?re haly,\par
Leblerinden akan baly,\par
\u350?\u228?ht ile \u351?ekere me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
\u214?z\u252?ne k\u246?pd\u252?r binasy,\par
Ge\u253?ip re\u328?be-re\u328? lybasy,\par
Eline go\u253?an hynasy,\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? gyzyl huna me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Magtymguly, boldu\u328? harap,\par
Istap tapman \u253?ary sorap,\par
Otury\u351?y\u328? \u253?ola garap,\par
\u221?ol tapmadyk k\u246?re me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
BARMY, \u221?ARANLAR\par
Y\u351?k \u253?olun h\u246?wes e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Gelen barmy, \u253?aranlar?\par
Derdimi be\u253?an etsem,\par
Bilen barmy, \u253?aranlar?\par
\par
Bolmu\u351?am mesti-\u351?e\u253?da,\par
Hezar pi\u351?e, set s\u246?wda,\par
\u196?lemde men de\u253? ryswa,\par
Bolan barmy, \u253?aranlar?\par
\par
Da\u351?ym dert, i\u231?im bir\u253?an,\par
Eder men nala-gir\u253?an,\par
Menim de\u253? mesti-ha\u253?ran,\par
Galan barmy, \u253?aranlar?\par
\par
\u221?alan d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de \u253?a\u253?nap,\par
Gezer sen g\u252?l\u252?p, o\u253?nap,\par
Y\u351?k matbahynda ga\u253?nap,\par
\u214?len barmy, \u253?aranlar?\par
\par
Y\u351?k du\u351? bolsa bir merde,\par
Toz bolar, d\u246?ner gerde,\par
Menim de\u253? \u246?z\u252?n derde,\par
Salan barmy, \u253?aranlar?\par
\par
Bardy halym \u246?l\u252?mge,\par
Tap etme\u253?en zulumga,\par
\u221?yglama\u253?yn halymga,\par
G\u252?len barmy, \u253?aranlar?\par
\par
Magtymguly jan \u231?ekse,\par
Rehm etmezler, \u253?a\u351? d\u246?kse,\par
Y\u351?ky\u328? \u253?olunda \u253?ogsa,\par
Talan barmy, \u253?aranlar?\par
\par
U\u221?AT E\u221?LE\u221?IR\par
Me\u328?li hanym golun di\u351?l\u228?p,\par
Bizden ki u\u253?at e\u253?li\u253?ir,\par
K\u228? daranyp, uz \u253?\u246?ri\u351?l\u228?p,\par
Bizden ki u\u253?at e\u253?li\u253?ir.\par
\par
A\u351?yk, gulak go\u253?gul s\u246?ze,\par
Sy\u253?a z\u252?lp \u253?ara\u351?ar \u253?\u252?ze,\par
S\u252?rme \u231?alyp gara g\u246?ze,\par
Bizden ki u\u253?at e\u253?li\u253?ir.\par
\par
Ge\u253?ipdir gyzyl-\u253?a\u351?yly,\par
Bilmen nedir \u253?ar hy\u253?aly,\par
G\u246?z edip \u253?omut, ahaly,\par
Bizden ki u\u253?at e\u253?li\u253?ir.\par
\par
Ykbal \u231?apmaz \u253?\u246?re\u253? di\u253?sem,\par
\u221?okdur malym, bere\u253? di\u253?sem,\par
A\u231?, ro\u253?u\u328?y g\u246?re\u253? di\u253?sem,\par
\u214?wr\u252?lip u\u253?at e\u253?le\u253?ir.\par
\par
G\u246?r\u252?\u351?eli, Me\u328?li hanym,\par
Ustuhanym, \u351?irin janym.\par
Pyragy di\u253?r, din-imanym,\par
\u221?etdirmez, u\u253?at e\u253?le\u253?ir.\par
\par
A\u221?A D\u214?NDI\par
\u221?\u252?zi mahy-tabanym,\par
G\u252?n \u253?aly A\u253?a d\u246?ndi.\par
\u199?arh oldy nerdiwanym,\par
G\u246?k pa\u253?a-pa\u253?a d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Bir g\u252?n a\u351?yk \u351?owk oldy,\par
Gam-gussasy \u253?ok oldy,\par
Her kirpigi\u328? ok oldy,\par
Ga\u351?lary\u328? \u253?a\u253?a d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
A\u351?ygy saldy\u328? oda,\par
Go\u253?du\u328? gitdi\u328? burada,\par
G\u252?norta berdi\u328? wada,\par
Wagt ge\u231?di, sa\u253?a d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Jan galmady bedende,\par
\u221?anar men ah edende,\par
G\u246?z\u252?m gelip-gidende,\par
Her g\u252?n\u252?m a\u253?a d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
M\u252?\u328? s\u246?wdam bar, bir ba\u351?ym,\par
Go\u253?dum ilim, garda\u351?ym,\par
Aglamakdan g\u246?z\u253?a\u351?ym\par
Jo\u351?gunly \u231?a\u253?a d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
\u221?ary\u328? k\u246?\u328?li \u231?ag oldy,\par
A\u351?yklar tussag oldy,\par
Dalda \u253?erim dag oldy,\par
D\u252?z \u253?erim ga\u253?a d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Ist\u228?r men g\u252?nde-g\u252?nde,\par
\u221?yglar men t\u252?nde-t\u252?nde,\par
Her z\u252?lp\u252?ne bir bende,\par
H\u252?\u253? sa\u253?a-sa\u253?a d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Dal pudaklar egildi,\par
G\u246?\u231?di bilbil, dagyldy,\par
Akar suwlar soguldy,\par
\u199?\u246?l \u253?erler \u231?a\u253?a d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Derman bolmaz alaja,\par
Zat bermezler m\u228?t\u228?je,\par
Ba\u253?lar d\u246?ndi gallaja,\par
Pakyrlar ba\u253?a d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Magtymguly, gezende,\par
Halap, Ka\u253?sar d\u252?z\u252?nde,\par
G\u246?zel \u253?ary\u328? yzynda,\par
\u214?mr\u252?miz za\u253?a d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
G\u214?Z\u220?M D\u220?\u350?DI\par
\u350?\u252?k\u252?r, alhamdulilla!\par
Janana g\u246?z\u252?m d\u252?\u351?di.\par
Me\u253?hanada me\u253? i\u231?dim,\par
Messana g\u246?z\u252?m d\u252?\u351?di.\par
\par
E\u253?, z\u252?lpi, sa\u231?y anbar,\par
M\u228?hrap ki \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328? m\u252?nber,\par
E\u253?, lagly-lebi g\u246?wher,\par
Ummana g\u246?z\u252?m d\u252?\u351?di.\par
\par
E\u253?, g\u246?zleri ahramy,\par
Gel, g\u246?zlegil \u253?aramy,\par
E\u253?, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?mi\u328? aramy,\par
Imana g\u246?z\u252?m d\u252?\u351?di.\par
\par
E\u253?, jady jeren g\u246?zli,\par
E\u253?, \u351?\u228?hd-u \u351?eker s\u246?zli,\par
E\u253?, \u350?ems-u Kamar \u253?\u252?zli,\par
Tabana g\u246?z\u252?m d\u252?\u351?di.\par
\par
Arzuwda gezer iller,\par
Hyzmata geler gullar,\par
T\u228?ze a\u231?ylan g\u252?ller,\par
Bossana g\u246?z\u252?m d\u252?\u351?di.\par
\par
Her sa\u231?lary bir s\u252?nb\u252?l,\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? ki menem bilbil,\par
E\u253?, jennet era bir g\u252?l,\par
Ryzwana g\u246?z\u252?m d\u252?\u351?i.\par
\par
Bu derdime sen derman,\par
K\u246?\u253?\u252?\u328?de bolam nalan,\par
Magtymguly di\u253?r, e\u253? jan,\par
Janana g\u246?z\u252?m d\u252?\u351?di.\par
\par
AT ISL\u196?RIN\par
Kerem etse\u328?, Kadyr Ta\u328?rym,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?likden at isl\u228?rin.\par
Talygym ukuda galmy\u351?,\par
Bir a\u231?ylmy\u351? bagt isl\u228?rin.\par
\par
\u221?oksullyk bir \u253?aman \u253?oldur,\par
Pakyr menem, golum galdyr,\par
Halal ryzk ber, kesp bildir,\par
Kim\u253?a atlyg ot isl\u228?rin.\par
\par
\u221?alan d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de \u253?\u246?rm\u228?ge,\par
D\u246?wlet ber e\u351?ret s\u252?rm\u228?ge,\par
\u214?m\u252?r ekl\u228?p, g\u252?n g\u246?rm\u228?ge,\par
Segsen \u253?yl nurbat isl\u228?rin.\par
\par
Hajy Bekda\u351?, Abdylkadyr,\par
Hoja Ahmet, Ymam Ryzadyr,\par
Feridun bir \u246?wl\u252?\u253?\u228?dir,\par
Baryndan h\u252?mmet isl\u228?rin.\par
\par
Pyragy, y\u351?ka ugra\u351?dym,\par
Der\u253?a girdim, m\u246?wje d\u252?\u351?d\u252?m,\par
Hor galmasyn pu\u351?tdyr-pu\u351?dum,\par
Berkarar d\u246?wlet isl\u228?rin.\par
\par
HINDISTANDA HY\u221?ALYM\par
Hak ugrunda gurbandyr,\par
Janym, d\u246?wletim, malym.\par
G\u246?w\u252?n \u253?ola rowandyr,\par
Hindistanda hy\u253?alym.\par
\par
\u221?yglap, g\u246?z\u252?m \u253?a\u351? etdim,\par
G\u246?w\u252?n i\u231?re nag\u351? etdim,\par
Il-g\u252?n\u252?me bag\u351? etdim,\par
Zyban i\u231?re asalym.\par
\par
Durdum adam sanyda,\par
Garamaty\u328? \u253?anyda,\par
Bir garda\u351?syz, panyda,\par
Ni\u231?ik \u246?ter ahwalym.\par
\par
Ol pe\u253?keri hara\u253?ym,\par
Bagy\u351? kyldym sara\u253?ym,\par
Pu\u351? e\u253?ledim, g\u246?r, ro\u253?um,\par
G\u246?terip men desmalym.\par
\par
\u221?\u246?rd\u252?m jebir k\u246?\u253?\u252?nde,\par
\u221?andym y\u351?ky\u328? \u246?\u253?\u252?nde,\par
Galdy zemin te\u253?inde,\par
Da\u253?ym berilen p\u228?lim.\par
\par
Janym ata\u351?a saldym,\par
Nar i\u231?inde men galdym,\par
Y\u351?kdan \u253?aradar boldum,\par
Lukman soramaz halym.\par
\par
Il g\u246?z\u252?ne ilip men,\par
Ilenimi bilip men,\par
\u221?ar ga\u351?yna gelip men,\par
N\u228? di\u253?erem \u8722? delilim.\par
\par
Pany-jahan i\u231?inde,\par
Pe\u253?kam keman i\u231?inde,\par
Mejnun umman i\u231?inde\par
Gark bolmu\u351? eski salym.\par
\par
Bir perige hyrydar,\par
Bu janym o\u328?a nisar,\par
Di\u253?dim \u253?ara: \u171?Arzym bar\u187?\par
Unutmy\u351?am sowalym.\par
\par
Me\u328?li jana ot salar,\par
Ody jismimde galar,\par
Magtymguly, u\u253?alar\par
Meni\u328? sahypjemalym.\par
\par
BU DAHANA\par
Akyl bu g\u252?n keser boldy,\par
Ne s\u246?z gelse bu dahana.\par
G\u246?r\u252?\u328?, pelek \u253?eser boldy,\par
Tala\u328? salyp bu jahana.\par
\par
Bent bolupdyr g\u246?ren g\u246?zler,\par
Sy\u253?a bolmu\u351? g\u246?zel \u253?\u252?zler,\par
Ajap asal-\u351?eker s\u246?zler,\par
\u221?esir bolmu\u351? bu zybana.\par
\par
Kim g\u246?r\u252?pdir d\u252?n\u253?\u228? te\u253?in,\par
Ka\u253?sy ja\u253?da, ka\u253?sy \u246?\u253?\u252?n,\par
I\u231?er boldum y\u351?ky\u328? me\u253?in,\par
A\u231? g\u246?z bilen gana-gana.\par
\par
Kapas i\u231?re \u253?esirdir jan,\par
Zyban di\u253?mez, bentdir dahan,\par
Bu \u253?alan\u231?y pany-jahan,\par
Go\u253?ma\u253?ar nurbat-amana.\par
\par
Dag ba\u351?ynda dumany bar,\par
Her bagy\u328? bir bagbany bar,\par
Adam ogly zenany bar,\par
G\u246?z\u252?m d\u252?\u351?mez ol jenana.\par
\par
Akyl haznasyn a\u231?anlar,\par
Pany jahana sa\u231?anlar,\par
Gonany bar, k\u246?p g\u246?\u231?enler,\par
Darga\u253?ypdyr, g\u246?\u231?\u252?p-gona.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y \u228?rde \u253?amanlyk bar,\par
Erse o\u328?a il hyrydar,\par
S\u246?z\u252?m di\u328?le, Perwerdig\u228?r,\par
Gow\u351?ur meni Me\u328?li hana.\par
\par
Uzak \u246?m\u252?r, \u253?ol agyrdyr,\par
Han i\u351?lese, bil agyrdar,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y s\u246?ze hyrydardyr,\par
\u221?ararmy\u351? geda, soltana.\par
\par
Dag ba\u351?yndan ga\u231?ar da\u351?y,\par
Her kimi\u328? bar \u246?z syrda\u351?y,\par
Kimse \u253?al\u328?yz \u8213? \u253?ok garda\u351?y,\par
G\u246?zi d\u252?\u351?mez bir dogana.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?z\u252?\u328? hakdyr,\par
Hak s\u246?ze ten beren \u253?okdur,\par
Gider bolsa\u328?, \u253?ol uzakdyr,\par
E\u253?ran, Turan, Hindistana.\par
\par
S\u214?W\u220?\u350? BILE\par
Myhman geler alys \u253?erden,\par
Gar\u351?ylasa\u328? s\u246?w\u252?\u351? bile,\par
Mert \u253?igitler ge\u231?er serden,\par
Al me\u253?danda d\u246?w\u252?\u351? bile.\par
\par
\u221?\u252?wr\u252?k \u253?etmez uzagyna,\par
D\u252?\u351?d\u252?m pelek duzagyna,\par
Me\u328?li gyzy\u328? \u253?\u252?z\u252?gine\par
Ga\u351?lar go\u253?sam k\u252?m\u252?\u351? bile.\par
\par
Gyz-u juwan uz \u253?\u246?re\u253?ip,\par
G\u246?z gider bagry\u328? ere\u253?ip,\par
K\u246?lde guba gaz \u253?\u246?re\u253?ip,\par
Suw seslener gamy\u351? bile.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?arytmadym,\par
Sederime darytmadym,\par
Perzent pohun arytmadym,\par
Mydam i\u351?im symy\u351? bile.\par
\par
D\u220?KAN G\u214?R\u220?NER\par
Adam ogly, se\u253?il kylsa\u328?,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de d\u252?kan g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
Bu panyga nazar salsa\u328?,\par
\u221?uwdarha-jahan g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Isgendere torun guran,\par
S\u252?le\u253?mana arza baran,\par
Karun-Harun \u8213? baryn uran,\par
Ol pelek p\u228?lwan g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Jebir g\u246?r\u252?p, \u253?anan janlar,\par
\u199?\u228?re tapma\u253?an dermanlar,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de \u231?ohdur ummanlar,\par
B\u228?\u351? sany umman g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Serine duman b\u252?renen,\par
G\u246?z\u253?a\u351?y \u253?erde s\u252?\u253?renen,\par
M\u228?hirli, da\u351?dan g\u246?r\u252?nen\par
Daglarda duman g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
\u199?yn-Ma\u231?ynda tagtyn guran,\par
E\u253?rany, Owgany soran,\par
Hindistan, Hotana baran\par
Atany\u253?az han g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Dag serinden g\u252?zer salsa\u328?,\par
Ol \u253?erde \u253?urt e\u253?l\u228?p galsa\u328?,\par
\u350?ol ja\u253?y\u328?dan nazar salsa\u328?,\par
Ulug Dehistan g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Perde tartyp \u253?\u252?zlerime,\par
Ra\u253?y\u351? berip s\u246?zlerime,\par
Magtymguly, g\u246?zlerime\par
\u221?eke Me\u328?li han g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
K\u196?RE D\u214?NDI\par
E\u253? garda\u351?lar, byradarym,\par
Ma\u328?a gar\u351?y k\u228?re d\u246?ndi.\par
Bialajam, Me\u328?li hanym,\par
\u221?a\u351?yn d\u246?k\u252?p, zara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Kapyrlar Ybra\u253?my tutdy,\par
Ahyr betni\u253?ete \u253?etdi,\par
Golun baglap, oda atdy,\par
Ot bary g\u252?lzara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Az berdiler, k\u246?p aldylar,\par
T\u252?\u253?s gara s\u252?\u253?thor boldular,\par
Her ke\u351?be girip geldiler,\par
Il bary ha\u253?\u253?ara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Bahyllar \u253?ele gezdiler,\par
Alymlar \u253?yldan azdylar,\par
Ky\u253?amatdan gol \u252?zd\u252?ler,\par
Barysy s\u252?\u253?thora d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Zit kyldy oglun Ysma\u253?yl,\par
Gelinler azdy \u253?ylba-\u253?yl,\par
Her kes i\u351?e bolma\u253? ka\u253?yl,\par
Uly il bik\u228?re d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Daglar s\u252?rer \u231?ohdan d\u246?wran,\par
Ajap ja\u253?lar boldy we\u253?ran,\par
Hakdan gelse bir g\u252?n perman,\par
Ol Ysrapyl sura d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Kazy, re\u253?s kanun tutman,\par
Bolan i\u351? so\u328?una \u253?etm\u228?n,\par
Bir bend\u228?ge rehim etm\u228?n,\par
Asdy, atdy, tire d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylarmyz \u253?aman boldy,\par
Daglar ba\u351?y duman boldy,\par
Namart bary aman boldy,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igit zibire d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Illerde \u253?ok zerre ga\u253?rat,\par
We\u253?ran boldy k\u246?p ymarat,\par
Nergiz g\u246?zli ol bedew at,\par
Namart golda hara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Pyragy sen, big\u252?n\u228? bol,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igitden taglymat al,\par
G\u246?wn\u252?m, gideli, b\u228?ri gel,\par
Ajap mekan zara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
HAR KYLDY\par
E\u253?-\u228?, dostlar, d\u228?li d\u252?n\u253?\u228?\par
\u221?ag\u351?y g\u252?nlerim har kyldy.\par
Iki \u253?\u252?zli, loly d\u252?n\u253?\u228?,\par
\u350?ady-horramym zar kyldy.\par
\par
Ba\u351?dan gerek \u253?ar \u253?igide,\par
Dost tapylmaz dar \u253?igide,\par
Asly \u253?eke - \u228?r \u253?igide\par
Zalym pelek, g\u246?r, zor kyldy.\par
\par
Kimim bar e\u351?itse derdim,\par
Tilki boldy pele\u328?, gurdum,\par
We\u253?ran boldy g\u246?zel \u253?urdum,\par
Gyzylba\u351? tary-mar kyldy.\par
\par
Goldan gidendir dessanym,\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? tenden \u231?ykdy janym,\par
G\u246?zi \u253?a\u351?ly Me\u328?li hanym,\par
\u221?\u252?regim i\u231?re nar kyldy.\par
\par
Atsyz galdy g\u252?\u253?\u231?li p\u228?lwan,\par
Be\u253?le boldy, ne\u253?le\u253?, zaman,\par
\u214?z\u252?n h\u246?d\u252?rle\u253?ip juwan,\par
Kalbymda, g\u246?r\u252?\u328?, mar kyldy.\par
\par
Magtymguly, kes tili\u328?i,\par
B\u252?kerler elip bili\u328?i,\par
Azara go\u253?ma ili\u328?i,\par
Barysy ygtybar kyldy.\par
\par
GELIP D\u220?\u350?DI\par
Diri du\u351?manym, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in,\par
Garry pelek gelip d\u252?\u351?di.\par
Derdimi\u328? baryn s\u246?\u253?l\u228?\u253?in,\par
Depe sa\u231?ym bir dem \u252?\u253?\u351?di.\par
\par
A\u253?yrdy g\u246?zde nurumdan,\par
Bagda alma-enarymdan,\par
Me\u328?li atly \u351?ol \u253?arymdan,\par
\u221?anyp \u253?\u252?rek, ga\u253?nap bi\u351?di.\par
\par
\u199?ykmaz boldy s\u246?hbet-sazym,\par
E\u351?itse, Alla owazym,\par
G\u246?r\u252?nmez boldy \u253?yldyzym,\par
A\u253?ym batdy, G\u252?n\u252?m \u253?a\u351?dy.\par
\par
Z\u228?herdir berilen a\u351?lar,\par
Bar, seret, gitdi garda\u351?lar,\par
Dagap g\u246?w\u252?nde\u351? \u8722? syrda\u351?lar,\par
E\u253?ran, Turan, Owgan a\u351?dy.\par
\par
\u221?at boldy yslamy\u328? \u253?oly,\par
Hi\u231? kims\u228?ni\u328? \u253?ok hy\u253?aly,\par
\u221?owuz d\u252?\u351?en Magtymguly,\par
Bes e\u253?legil, akly\u328? \u231?a\u351?dy.\par
\par
\u221?ANAN BARMY?\par
Jahanke\u351?desi \u8213? gedalar,\par
Meni\u328? kibi \u253?anan barmy?\par
Y\u351?k a\u351?ygy perwanalar,\par
Ol ata\u351?dan ganan barmy?\par
\par
Hi\u231? bir gapydan \u246?tme\u253?en,\par
Maksadyna bir etme\u253?en,\par
Akly-hu\u351?y pikr etme\u253?en,\par
\u196?lem i\u231?re nadan barmy?\par
\par
Bady-saba, geler boldu\u328?,\par
Her ja\u253?da bir galar boldu\u328?,\par
Pana nazar salar boldu\u328?,\par
Adalatly soltan barmy?\par
\par
Armany\u328? \u253?okdur jahandan,\par
Erenler, di\u253?i\u328?, zybandan,\par
Bo\u253? satyn alyp \u253?amandan,\par
Baky ondan dynan barmy?\par
\par
Saz e\u253?l\u228?r boldu\u328? gargydan,\par
Ba\u351?ym bendidir bergiden,\par
Murglarda bu gyrgydan,\par
Jahan i\u231?re aman barmy?\par
\par
Luw, di\u253?gil, umman \u253?\u252?zer sen,\par
De\u351?tden golu\u328?y \u252?zer sen,\par
Bar\u231?a ablary gezer sen,\par
Bir e\u351?retli mekan barmy?\par
\par
Pelek g\u246?zle\u253?ip bilmez,\par
A\u253?lanyp birje gelmez,\par
Baky maly egsilmez,\par
Bazarda d\u252?kan barmy?\par
\par
Zyban \u351?irin asaly,\par
Mahy-taban jemaly,\par
Ro\u253?unda hindi haly,\par
Mynasyp jenan barmy?\par
\par
Saba di\u253?erem pynhanda,\par
\u221?akar nary go\u253?dy janda,\par
Gezip sen pany jahanda,\par
G\u246?zl\u228?rem, Me\u328?li han barmy?\par
\par
Se\u253?l eder boldu\u328? ga\u351?ynda,\par
Kemerinde, ku\u253?a\u351?ynda,\par
Ol gojalan dag ba\u351?ynda\par
Baran bilen duman barmy?\par
\par
Pa\u253?yny la\u253?a batyran,\par
Suzan \u252?zre bir oturan,\par
Bu pelege azym uran\par
Panyda bir merdan barmy?\par
\par
Se\u253?l eder sen g\u252?n-a\u253?lary\par
Ne aja\u253?yp sara\u253?lary,\par
G\u246?rer sen her bir ja\u253?lary,\par
Ol ja\u253?larda Gurhan barmy?\par
\par
Bir serwi g\u246?zel bo\u253?unda,\par
Ol Remezan a\u253?ynda,\par
Panyny\u328? s\u252?\u253?thor ja\u253?ynda\par
Ata\u351? bilen zyndan barmy?\par
\par
Bir hulky bardyr s\u246?z\u252?nde,\par
Heka\u253?at bardyr g\u246?z\u252?nde,\par
Me\u328?li \u253?ary\u328? g\u252?l \u253?\u252?z\u252?nde\par
Bize gar\u351?y keman barmy?\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?zledi\u328? az,\par
Dert-yzhary\u328? kyldy\u328? be\u253?az,\par
K\u246?l i\u231?inde me\u253?lisde gaz,\par
Bizler \u252?\u231?in watan barmy?\par
\par
ARMANYM GALDY\par
Z\u252?be\u253?da, na\u231?arym, di\u328?le,\par
Kalbymda armanym galdy.\par
Ku\u253?a\u351?ymdan akdyrdym gan,\par
Zemine bak, ganym galdy.\par
\par
Bilbilem, \u231?ekmi\u351?em zary,\par
Sowuldy y\u351?ky\u328? bazary,\par
Uruldy hijran hanjary,\par
Aglap Me\u328?li hanym galdy.\par
\par
\u214?ten g\u252?nlerim d\u252?\u253?\u351? bolup,\par
Gezdim ilimden u\u253?alyp,\par
Baky\u328?, jesedim bo\u351? galyp,\par
Lahat i\u231?re janym galdy.\par
\par
G\u252?nbe-g\u252?nden derdim artyp,\par
\u221?\u246?rmedim jahany \u253?ortup,\par
Z\u228?hmet \u231?ekip, azar tartyp,\par
D\u252?zd\u252?gim dessanym galdy.\par
\par
Zalym pelek, gahba pelek,\par
\u199?oh janlary kyldy\u328? hel\u228?k,\par
L\u228?le, zemin, asman, melek,\par
Wah, mahy-tabanym galdy.\par
\par
Magtymguly, gara \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328?,\par
Di\u328?lemezler zaryn s\u246?z\u252?\u328?,\par
Z\u252?be\u253?d\u228?m, \u253?a\u351?lasa\u328? g\u246?z\u252?\u328?,\par
Harytsyz, d\u252?kanym galdy.\par
\par
N\u196?GEHAN PYRAK\par
Goldan aldy\u328? kararymy,\par
Gelip sen n\u228?gehan, pyrak.\par
G\u246?terdi\u328? Me\u328?li \u253?arymy,\par
Go\u253?up janda arman, pyrak.\par
\par
G\u246?zlerim \u253?olu\u328?da bende,\par
Ne ygty\u253?ar galdy mende,\par
E\u253?l\u228?p jebir gelen g\u252?nde,\par
Sere saldy\u328? pygan, pyrak.\par
\par
Arzymy di\u328?lemez \u351?ahym,\par
Batdy asmandaky mahym,\par
Daglary \u253?andyryp ahym,\par
Baryn kyldy we\u253?ran, pyrak.\par
\par
Galmaz meni\u328? ba\u351?ym aman,\par
G\u246?ren jebrim di\u253?er zyban,\par
G\u252?nde gelip Isa, Lukman,\par
Tapmaz derde derman, pyrak.\par
\par
Z\u252?lp\u252?karym aldy\u328? goldan,\par
A\u253?yrdy\u328? bir \u253?al\u328?yz saldan,\par
Ilim habar sormaz haldan,\par
Zy\u328?dy\u328? baryn E\u253?ran, pyrak.\par
\par
Oksuz galdy golda \u253?a\u253?ym,\par
Batdy meni\u328? G\u252?n\u252?m, A\u253?ym,\par
Goldamasa\u328? Sen, Huda\u253?ym.\par
Kylar meni gurban, pyrak.\par
\par
Magtymguly zar agla\u253?yp,\par
Jigerin nara dagla\u253?yp,\par
Ol Me\u328?li \u253?arym \u231?agla\u253?yp,\par
Her g\u252?n \u231?ekdir efgan, pyrak.\par
\par
A\u221?RYLDYM\par
Bilbilem, ahy-zar \u231?ekip,\par
T\u228?ze g\u252?lzardan a\u253?ryldym.\par
G\u246?zden ganly \u253?a\u351?ym d\u246?k\u252?p,\par
S\u246?wd\u252?gim \u253?ardan a\u253?ryldym.\par
\par
\u221?ara \u253?ara\u351?ar s\u252?rme\u231?e,\par
Sypatyn s\u246?\u253?l\u228?rem en\u231?e,\par
Agzy \u351?eker, lebi gun\u231?a,\par
Z\u252?lpi garadan a\u253?ryldym.\par
\par
\u350?irin janda \u253?okdur takat,\par
Jebri onu\u328? jana rahat,\par
Ga\u351?lary pitne\u253?i-apat,\par
\u199?e\u351?mi hunhordan a\u253?ryldym.\par
\par
A\u253?ryldym gun\u231?a-g\u252?l\u252?mden,\par
Sy\u253?a sa\u231?y s\u252?nb\u252?limden,\par
Ho\u351? owazly bilbilimden,\par
\u350?irin g\u252?ftardan a\u253?ryldym.\par
\par
D\u228?li k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m arzymany,\par
K\u252?lli g\u246?zelleri\u328? hany,\par
Sekiz jenneti\u328? bossany,\par
Bakjaly bardan a\u253?ryldym.\par
\par
Illeri bar de\u328?li-de\u328?li,\par
Sowuk suwly, ter \u246?le\u328?li,\par
Ili - g\u246?kle\u328?, ady - Me\u328?li,\par
N\u228?zli dildardan a\u253?ryldym.\par
\par
Magtymguly, a\u351?yk messan,\par
Bagladym \u351?anyna dessan,\par
Menzilg\u228?hi bag-u bossan,\par
Almaly nardan a\u253?ryldym.\par
\par
LERZANADYR\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, g\u246?zel \u246?mr\u252?m,\par
Garradyk\u231?a lerzanadyr.\par
G\u252?nbe-g\u252?nden artyp derdim,\par
D\u228?ri ist\u228?p perwanadyr.\par
\par
A\u351?yk \u253?ansa ol \u253?ar \u252?\u231?in,\par
Margir \u253?\u246?rse \u351?amar \u252?\u231?in,\par
Go\u231?aklar namys-ar \u252?\u231?in\par
Ata \u231?ykar, merdanadyr.\par
\par
Ne ajap elwanlar s\u252?ren,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman \u8722? baryn g\u246?ren,\par
Bizler bilen hemra \u253?\u246?ren\par
Aksakallar, bak, danadyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, elli \u253?a\u351?y\u328?,\par
Gamdyr, ga\u253?gydyr syrda\u351?y\u328?,\par
Gapyl bolma, galdyr ba\u351?y\u328?,\par
Garrylyk bir bahanadyr.\par
\par
HER \u221?ANA\par
\u221?arsyzlykdan \u253?aman i\u351? \u253?ok,\par
G\u246?z salyp gezsem her \u253?ana,\par
\u221?a, \u221?aradan, bir \u253?ar bergil,\par
K\u246?p mu\u351?akgat degdi jana.\par
\par
Bir \u253?ar bergil etli-ganly,\par
K\u246?\u328?li gi\u328?, g\u246?wsi me\u253?danly,\par
Dil bilen, akly kemally,\par
\u221?\u252?zi hem bolsun g\u246?rkana.\par
\par
Gadyr bilenden da\u351? etme,\par
N\u228?gadyra \u253?olda\u351? etme,\par
Dil bilmez bela du\u351? etme,\par
Sada dil bolsun - t\u252?rkana.\par
\par
Keremi\u328? g\u252?\u253?\u231?l\u252?dir, g\u246?rg\u252?l,\par
Di\u253?r sen: \u171?Doga kyl, el gergil\u187?,\par
Ne berse\u328?, tizir\u228?k bergil,\par
Ygtybar \u253?okdur bu jana.\par
\par
Bo\u253?y uzyn, pes bolmasyn,\par
Hetden a\u351?a mes bolmasyn,\par
Akylsyz, n\u228?kes bolmasyn,\par
Sadadan bolsun - t\u252?rkana.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y a\u253?al ele gelmez,\par
Nadan \u253?ag\u351?y\u328? gadryn bilmez,\par
A\u253?alsyza mydar bolmaz,\par
D\u246?nse\u328? h\u246?kmi-S\u252?le\u253?mana.\par
\par
Derw\u252?\u351?lere \u253?olsuzlygy,\par
\u221?igitlere malsyzlygy,\par
Ylahy, a\u253?alsyzlygy,\par
G\u246?rkezme hi\u231? musulmana.\par
\par
Magtymguly, k\u246?\u253?sem, bi\u351?sem,\par
Ynanmazlar oda d\u252?\u351?sem,\par
H\u246?wesim bar, bir gyz gu\u231?sam,\par
Di\u253?sem s\u246?z\u252?mi erkana.\par
\par
BU G\u220?N\par
Dogdy asmany\u328? Z\u246?hresi,\par
\u199?yn a\u351?yga d\u246?wran bu g\u252?n.\par
A\u231?yldy zemin l\u228?lesi,\par
I\u351?bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? re\u253?han bu g\u252?n.\par
\par
Her sa\u253?randa \u351?e\u253?da bilbil,\par
\u214?w\u351?\u252?n atar \u246?w\u252?sip g\u252?l,\par
A\u351?yk bolsa\u328?, muny \u253?at bil,\par
Mag\u351?uk sa\u328?a gurban bu g\u252?n.\par
\par
Dil senewer \u351?ekeristan,\par
\u196?lem-jahan g\u252?l-g\u252?l\u252?stan,\par
Go\u253?nu\u328? i\u231?re biten bossan,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igitler bagban bu g\u252?n.\par
\par
G\u252?l dessesin tirer bolsa\u328?,\par
G\u252?l\u351?en i\u231?re girer bolsa\u328?,\par
Menden habar sorar bolsa\u328?,\par
Toty g\u252?ftar zyban bu g\u252?n.\par
\par
Daglar ba\u351?y \u252?m\u252?r basan,\par
J\u252?lgesinde g\u252?ller \u246?sen,\par
Her deminde namart gysan,\par
Adyl \u351?adan perman bu g\u252?n.\par
\par
Dowamatdyr il merdine,\par
Awun bermez \u351?ir gurduna,\par
\u199?yn a\u351?ygy\u328? ol derdine,\par
Pyragydan derman bu g\u252?n.\par
\par
NARY DILBERI\u327?\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l \u351?\u228?hrine ot saldy,\par
Wah, ne\u253?le\u253?, nary dilberi\u328?.\par
Etrapymy duman aldy,\par
Gelendir gahry dilberi\u328?.\par
\par
Adam nesli d\u228?ldir meger,\par
H\u252?\u253?ri-gulman ba\u351?yn eger,\par
Handan e\u253?l\u228?p, bize deger,\par
Gorkaram, mary dilberi\u328?.\par
\par
G\u246?wher, \u253?akut \u253?ar bo\u253?nunda,\par
Pelek lerzandyr o\u253?nunda,\par
\u221?eti\u351?ipdir \u253?ar go\u253?nunda,\par
Pynhandyr nary dilberi\u328?.\par
\par
Oldur a\u351?yklar ata\u351?y,\par
Eripdir Mejnuny\u328? \u253?a\u351?y,\par
Kenizidir hem syrda\u351?y \u8722?\par
Behi\u351?ti\u328? h\u252?\u253?ri dilberi\u328?.\par
\par
\u221?andy, goja, \u253?\u252?rek \u253?ara\u328?,\par
Hyrydary sen bi\u231?\u228?r\u228?\u328?,\par
Magtymguly \u8722? bagty gara\u328?\par
Namysy, ary dilberi\u328?.\par
\par
BO\u221?LARY\u327?A\par
\u221?\u246?rse\u328?, \u253?arym, guwanar men,\par
Serwi kamat bo\u253?lary\u328?a.\par
G\u252?lden pu\u351?e\u351? \u253?ara\u351?ypdyr,\par
Ajap rahat bo\u253?lary\u328?a.\par
\par
Men \u8722? bilbile e\u253?l\u228?p azar,\par
Aldy\u328? \u351?irin janym nisar,\par
Z\u252?le\u253?hadan galan z\u252?nnar,\par
Bolsun hajat bo\u253?lary\u328?a.\par
\par
G\u246?rsem ro\u253?u\u328?, \u253?ok armanym,\par
Sensiz hazan ursun janym,\par
Ykbalym, dinim-imanym,\par
Kylam hormat bo\u253?lary\u328?a.\par
\par
Y\u351?ky\u328? bilen men dat e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
\u214?wrenip men, adat e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
\u214?m\u252?r-ahyr per\u253?at e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
\u221?etmez lahat bo\u253?lary\u328?a.\par
\par
G\u246?ren a\u351?yk pida bolar,\par
Il-g\u252?n\u252?nden jyda bolar,\par
Magtymguly geda bolar,\par
Din-keramat bo\u253?lary\u328?a.\par
\par
GARA G\u214?ZLERI\u327?\par
Seb\u228?p boldy \u253?anan jana,\par
Jellatdyr gara g\u246?zleri\u328?.\par
\u221?etirmez nurbat-amana,\par
Jellatdyr gara g\u246?zleri\u328?.\par
\par
Perim, \u253?al\u328?yz-\u253?eke \u253?\u246?rme,\par
\u221?aman \u228?hli\u328? \u253?\u252?z\u252?n g\u246?rme,\par
Sy\u253?a ga\u351?a \u231?alyp s\u252?rme,\par
Apatdyr gara g\u246?zleri\u328?.\par
\par
Jellat g\u246?zler, aman-aman,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u253?\u252?z\u252?n kyldy\u328? duman,\par
A\u351?yk \u228?hlin e\u253?l\u228?p bijan,\par
Rahatdyr gara g\u246?zleri\u328?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?ar armany,\par
Agladar be\u351?er-gulmany,\par
Musulmany\u328? din-imany,\par
Ymmatdyr gara g\u246?zleri\u328?.\par
\par
G\u220?LG\u220?ZAR O\u221?NA\u350?AR\par
Girsem baryp s\u246?wer dostu\u328? bagyna,\par
Asman galyp, ol g\u252?lg\u252?zar o\u253?na\u351?ar.\par
Se\u253?ran etsem duman basan dagyna,\par
Hemle urup, iki \u351?amar o\u253?na\u351?ar.\par
\par
Iki maral aby-K\u246?wser g\u252?zerde,\par
Men pakyry \u246?rt\u228?p nuran nazarda,\par
Y\u351?k s\u246?wdasy rowa\u231? tapan bazarda,\par
Satan bilen ol hyrydar o\u253?na\u351?ar.\par
\par
Girdim baga b\u252?tin d\u252?n\u253?\u228? har\u231? edip,\par
Bakdym g\u252?le, arman bilen hyr\u231? edip,\par
G\u252?ller bilen bilbil birge m\u246?w\u231? edip,\par
Alma-enar, injiri-nar o\u253?na\u351?ar.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y s\u246?zler ja\u253? e\u253?le\u253?ir dil i\u231?re,\par
N\u228?rse ga\u231?sa, dura bilmez sil i\u231?re,\par
\u196?r \u253?igitli, berkararly il i\u231?re,\par
Hi\u231? o\u328?u\u351?maz namys-u ar o\u253?na\u351?ar.\par
\par
Pelek gezer hijran-hemle aty\u351?yp,\par
Namart \u253?\u246?rmez mertler bilen gaty\u351?yp,\par
Magtymguly Me\u328?li \u253?ara sata\u351?yp,\par
B\u228?\u351? g\u252?n bizi\u328? bilen g\u252?l \u253?ar o\u253?na\u351?ar.\par
\par
BIZGE ROWANA\par
Nesip tartyp, biz hem d\u252?\u351?sek \u253?ollara,\par
Di\u253?i\u328? iller bolsun bize rowana.\par
Nuh golda\u253?yp girer bolsak syllara,\par
Pata beri\u328? nazar tutup ummana.\par
\par
Goja daglar serin egip, \u246?t\u252?rse,\par
Saba gelip, arzym \u253?ara \u253?etirse,\par
Yza d\u246?n\u252?p, \u253?ar jogabyn getirse,\par
H\u246?wes bilen ismin \u253?azsam dessana.\par
\par
Gojalykdan g\u246?wn\u252?m la\u253?a batypdyr,\par
Pelek o\u253?nap, ykbalymy satypdyr,\par
G\u246?z\u252?n \u253?umup, elli okun atypdyr,\par
Gelip orun tapyp girmi\u351? bu jana.\par
\par
Mejnun menem Me\u328?li hany\u328? odunda,\par
\u221?anyp-k\u246?\u253?sem, \u253?okdur onu\u328? \u253?adynda,\par
Perhat-\u350?irin, Z\u246?hre-Tahyr adynda,\par
Taglym alyp, boldum menem perwana.\par
\par
Hindi hallar g\u252?l \u253?\u252?z\u252?nde jugradyr,\par
Zar e\u253?le\u253?ip, \u231?eken ahym nagradyr,\par
Hijran wasyl, jigerimi dogradyr,\par
Owazasy dolup onu\u328? E\u253?rana.\par
\par
Magtymguly, unutmagyl ili\u328?i,\par
Uzyn \u253?aly, gysgaldawer dili\u328?i,\par
\u221?ol \u253?\u246?rir men di\u253?se\u328?, bagla bili\u328?i,\par
Bezirgenler gider Mazanderana.\par
\par
NAMYS BILEN AR\par
Pelek, hijran sary aty\u328? \u231?apar sen,\par
Gerekmesmi sa\u328?a namys bilen ar.\par
G\u246?kde u\u231?an murgy bir dem gapar sen,\par
Myrada \u253?etirm\u228?n kyldy\u328? hary-zar.\par
\par
Ne pe\u253?da bar a\u351?na kylsa\u328? gi\u253?ewden,\par
Bizi\u328? daglar pa\u253?yn almy\u351? ol g\u228?wden,\par
A\u351?yklary jyda kylyp birewden,\par
G\u252?l ro\u253?una e\u253?le\u253?ip sen intizar.\par
\par
\u221?at edermen bir \u253?aradan Hudany,\par
Gazanyp men \u231?oh s\u246?zle\u253?ip g\u252?n\u228?ni,\par
\u214?zi \u253?etip e\u253?lemese penany,\par
Pelek meni kyldy nara giriftar.\par
\par
Hak syla\u253?yp bermi\u351?, bize bu dili,\par
G\u252?l \u252?st\u252?nde bent e\u253?lemi\u351? bilbili,\par
Me\u328?li hany\u328? g\u252?l ro\u253?unda s\u252?nb\u252?li,\par
Handan kylyp, bezenmi\u351?dir bir \u351?amar.\par
\par
Kimse tutmaz, \u253?a \u221?aradan, emri\u328?i,\par
Bereni\u328?de az berip sen \u246?mr\u252?\u328?i,\par
Pelek, indi bes e\u253?legil jebri\u328?i,\par
Ha\u253?baty\u328?dan ilim-g\u252?n\u252?m bikarar.\par
\par
Pany jahan \u351?irin jany \u253?andyran,\par
Nar \u252?st\u252?ne ata\u351?yny indiren,\par
R\u252?stem Zaly ga\u253?rat atna m\u252?nd\u252?ren,\par
\u196?\u351?k\u228?r kylsam, bili\u328?, ol Ispendi\u253?ar.\par
\par
\u214?tenden, ge\u231?enden ykbalym sardym,\par
Il basmaz ja\u253?yna g\u252?nde b\u228?\u351? bardym,\par
Aklym kesme\u253?, \u231?oh i\u351?lere ba\u351? urdum,\par
Bilmemi\u351?em, pany jahan bazyg\u228?r.\par
\par
Sil akanda, \u253?elesinde da\u351? galar,\par
Bedew \u246?lse, la\u231?ynlara l\u228?\u351? galar,\par
Haky\u328? beren ajap ja\u253?y bo\u351? galar,\par
Men ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in jandan ga\u253?ry zernig\u228?r.\par
\par
Handan e\u253?l\u228?p, etrapymy \u253?ol etdi\u328?,\par
Gury tiken serwi kylyp, sal etdi\u328?,\par
Kimseleri\u328? z\u228?herini bal etdi\u328?,\par
Kimseleri kyldy\u328? gury rozyg\u228?r.\par
\par
Y\u351?k me\u253?inden i\u231?ip galdym ga\u351? tutup,\par
Bahar \u231?agy ukla\u253?yp men no\u351? tutup,\par
Pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228? di\u253?enine g\u252?w\u351? tutup,\par
Ha\u253?ran galyp kylyp o\u328?a bir bawer.\par
\par
Pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228? gelip \u246?ten jenanlar,\par
Hesip e\u253?l\u228?p gutarmadym ne janlar,\par
Mejnun bolan Magtymguly, \u253?aranlar,\par
Hijran dagda bolmu\u351? Me\u328?l\u228? sezewar.\par
\par
G\u214?ZEL SEN\par
G\u252?n hanjary g\u246?kden \u253?ere inende,\par
G\u252?ne gar\u351?y dogan A\u253?y, g\u246?zel sen.\par
Ussa Jagfar i\u351?i, senjap j\u252?pbesi,\par
Yspyhanda gurlan \u253?a\u253?y, g\u246?zel sen.\par
\par
Sa\u231?bagy\u328? ujuny\u328? simdir i\u351?mesi,\par
\u220?st\u252?\u328?den \u253?ol d\u252?\u351?se, kyndyr a\u351?masy,\par
Agzy\u328? aby-ha\u253?at, Zemzem \u231?e\u351?mesi,\par
A\u253?nal-baky suwnu\u328? la\u253?y, g\u246?zel sen.\par
\par
Gyzyl di\u253?sem - gyzyl, al di\u253?sem - al sen,\par
Hindistanda - \u351?eker, Bulgarda - bal sen,\par
Y\u351?k bilen a\u231?ylan bir t\u228?ze g\u252?l sen,\par
\u221?usup-Z\u252?le\u253?hany\u328? ta\u253?y, g\u246?zel sen.\par
\par
Her kim g\u252?\u253?\u231?li bolsa, o\u328?a \u171?pir\u187? di\u253?rler,\par
\u171?Dertli gulu\u328? dermanyny bi\u253?r\u187? di\u253?rler,\par
\u171?Gawuny\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn \u351?agal i\u253?r\u187? di\u253?rler,\par
Ykbally bend\u228?ni\u328? pa\u253?y, g\u246?zel sen.\par
\par
Owaza\u328? \u199?yn-Ma\u231?yn, daglar a\u351?asy,\par
Seni g\u246?renleri\u328? akly \u231?a\u351?asy,\par
Hindistany\u328? re\u328?kli gyzyl \u351?i\u351?esi,\par
Sura\u253?y \u231?ilimi\u328? na\u253?y, g\u246?zel sen.\par
\par
Magtymguly halkdan syryn gizlese,\par
Di\u351?ini u\u351?ady\u328?, \u253?alan s\u246?zlese,\par
Owalda, ahyrda E\u253?\u228?m g\u246?zlese,\par
Garyp bi\u231?\u228?r\u228?ni\u328? pa\u253?y, g\u246?zel sen.\par
\par
G\u214?RD\u220?\u327?MI\par
\u221?agty salar gider zulmat t\u252?n\u252?nde,\par
Meni\u328? sahypjemalymy g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?mi?\par
Bahar e\u253?\u253?amynda, he\u253?hat g\u252?n\u252?nde,\par
Meni\u328? sahypjemalymy g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?mi?\par
\par
Anka sypat turup, \u171?Hak!\u187? di\u253?p galkan gu\u351?,\par
Gijesi tirikdir, g\u252?ndizi bihu\u351?,\par
Redaly, jindeli, egni hyrka pu\u351?,\par
Meni\u328? sahypjemalymy g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?mi?\par
\par
Gan edipdir pelek bagrym pyrakda,\par
Elmydam gezer men \u253?ar di\u253?p sorakda,\par
K\u228?be etrapynda, \u350?amda, Yrakda,\par
Meni\u328? sahypjemalymy g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?mi?\par
\par
Haremde, Gypjakda, \u199?ynda-Ma\u231?ynda,\par
Asmany\u328? \u252?st\u252?nde, ar\u351?y\u328? i\u231?inde,\par
Yklym degresinde, pelek bur\u231?unda,\par
Meni\u328? sahypjemalymy g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?mi?\par
\par
A\u351?yklar ahynda, Gulzum d\u246?wr\u252?nde,\par
Gubbatyl-yslamda, Je\u253?hun bahrynda,\par
Sidre s\u228?hrasynda, Isa \u351?\u228?hrinde,\par
Meni\u328? sahypjemalymy g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?mi?\par
\par
Hezret Aly etge\u231? \u228?lemge dawy,\par
Kapdan Kaba d\u252?\u351?di hezreti\u328? \u231?awy,\par
\u221?a, yklym e\u253?esi Ahmet \u221?asawy,\par
Meni\u328? sahypjemalymy g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?mi?\par
\par
Mesgen tutmu\u351? gara dagy\u328? burnunda,\par
Alyny\u328? m\u252?lk\u252?nde, Isa ornunda,\par
\u221?eri\u328? arkasynda, g\u246?g\u252?\u328? garnynda,\par
Meni\u328? sahypjemalymy g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?mi?\par
\par
Magtymguly \u231?eker \u253?ary\u328? gamyny,\par
Gezip, tapa bilmez ro\u253?y-zemini,\par
\u221?a, ady Jebra\u253?yl - Haky\u328? emini,\par
Meni\u328? sahypjemalymy g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?mi?\par
\par
GYZMALY BOLDUM\par
Y\u351?k der\u253?asy doldy, da\u351?dy, ga\u253?nady,\par
T\u228?ze hyru\u231? e\u253?l\u228?p, gyzmaly boldum.\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l tagty m\u246?w\u231? \u252?st\u252?nde o\u253?nady,\par
Onda guwwas bolup, \u253?\u252?zmeli boldum.\par
\par
\u221?atyrdym d\u252?\u253?\u351? g\u246?rd\u252?m, tisgindim, turdum,\par
Y\u351?k bir m\u252?\u351?gil i\u351?dir, okadym, g\u246?rd\u252?m,\par
\u350?owkun \u8722? \u351?irin g\u246?rd\u252?m, bu \u253?ola girdim,\par
Imdi \u231?\u228?re \u253?okdur, d\u246?zmeli boldum.\par
\par
\u221?ary\u328? \u253?eli \u246?sdi, \u246?zi gizlendi,\par
Umyt elin gerdi, \u351?un\u231?a g\u246?zlendi,\par
Hijran kuwwatlandy, y\u351?k ekezlendi,\par
Ol matbahda ga\u253?nap, gyzmaly boldum.\par
\par
\u221?olda \u253?olukdyrdym \u231?e\u351?mi-jadyny,\par
U\u231?radym \u8722? el \u231?o\u253?dum y\u351?ky\u328? oduny,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l g\u246?zg\u252?sine \u253?ary\u328? adyny,\par
Heka\u253?at e\u253?le\u253?ip, \u253?azmaly boldum.\par
\par
Bu pikirden, bu hy\u253?aldan da\u351? bolup,\par
Nefsi-howa, kibr, kinden bo\u351? bolup,\par
Ol bazarda y\u351?k talana du\u351? bolup,\par
Belli, jandan umyt \u252?zmeli boldum.\par
\par
Gana-gana i\u231?dim dostu\u328? z\u228?hrini,\par
Z\u228?hrin \u351?ypa sansam, salmaz m\u228?hrini,\par
Bu g\u246?wrede gurlan k\u246?\u328?\u252?l \u351?\u228?hrini\par
Y\u351?ka n\u246?ker bolup, bozmaly boldum.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ol menzile, di\u253?ara,\par
Giren, ga\u253?dyp \u231?yka bilmez kenara,\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, barmy bu derde \u231?\u228?re,\par
\u214?rtenip, jowranyp gezmeli boldum.\par
\par
DURASY\u327? GELER\par
G\u246?zel bardyr, g\u246?zellerden zy\u253?ada,\par
Onu\u328? hyzmatynda durasy\u328? geler.\par
Edepli, erkanly, myla\u253?ymzada,\par
T\u228? \u246?lin\u231?\u228?\u328? bile \u253?\u246?resi\u328? geler.\par
\par
G\u246?zel bardyr, uzyn bo\u253?ly, alkymy -\par
Gara\u328?ky gijede d\u252?\u351?er \u253?alkymy,\par
S\u246?zlegen s\u246?zleri misli bal kimi,\par
\u221?a\u328?agyndan posa alasy\u328? geler.\par
\par
G\u246?zel bardyr, g\u252?nde-g\u252?nde g\u246?rmeli,\par
\u350?ol g\u246?zeli\u328? sy\u253?a z\u252?lp\u252?n \u246?rmeli,\par
D\u246?k\u252?p, hazynany\u328? zerin bermeli,\par
Onu\u328? s\u246?wdasynda bolasy\u328? geler.\par
\par
Bagzy g\u246?zel sirke basar sa\u231?yny,\par
Artmaz, \u253?uwmaz, tabagyny, da\u351?yny,\par
Sylamaz atasyn, ene, \u253?a\u351?yny,\par
Onu\u328? hyzmatyndan ga\u231?asy\u328? geler.\par
\par
G\u246?zel bardyr, ak kagyz dek bilegi,\par
Jan i\u231?inde bile bolar \u253?\u252?regi,\par
Andag g\u246?zel mert \u253?igidi\u328? geregi,\par
Ne hajat istese, beresi\u328? geler.\par
\par
Magtymguly, syn gerekdir g\u246?zele,\par
Herne kysmat bolsa, tartar ezele,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? malyn har\u231? et \u253?ag\u351?y g\u246?zele,\par
\u221?amany\u328? \u253?anyndan ga\u231?asy\u328? geler.\par
\par
I\u199?ME\u221?IN JAMYM\par
D\u246?zmenem, do\u253?manam, durmanam, e\u253? \u253?ar,\par
Bu saky d\u246?wr\u252?nde i\u231?me\u253?in jamym.\par
Jamy-me\u253? sundugy\u328? g\u246?rmesin ag\u253?ar,\par
Gelmenem aklyma g\u246?rme\u253?in k\u228?mim.\par
\par
Bolmu\u351?am guwwas-u, \u253?\u252?zm\u252?\u351?em k\u246?li,\par
Tapmy\u351?am hemrahy, tutmu\u351?am \u253?oly,\par
\u350?owku\u328? \u351?erabyndan bolmu\u351?am d\u228?li,\par
Bilmen ni\u231?ik ge\u231?er \u231?\u228?\u351?tim-u \u351?amym.\par
\par
T\u228? nepes tendedir, tende jan bardyr,\par
Dil sa\u328?a ma\u253?yldyr, \u231?e\u351?m intizardyr,\par
\u199?ekdigim pygandyr, werzi\u351?im zardyr,\par
T\u228? ki bu dert ile ge\u231?er e\u253?\u253?amym.\par
\par
G\u246?zleri\u328? jellatdyr, dilleri\u328? a\u253?\u253?ar,\par
Gamza\u328? bimar eder, \u253?\u252?zleri\u328? timar,\par
Mansur belasyna bolsam giriftar,\par
Giderem sen sary s\u252?\u253?re\u253?ip hamym.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ho\u351? hap i\u231?re \u253?atyrdym,\par
Emri\u328?e ugradym, iman getirdim,\par
\u214?z\u252?mi unutdym, hu\u351?um \u253?itirdim,\par
\u171?Pyragy\u187? di\u253?p \u231?agyra\u253? sen bu namym.\par
\par
ILDEN U\u221?ALMAK\par
A\u351?yky-ezel men, sonam, men sa\u328?a,\par
Ne edep-erkan bar, ilden u\u253?almak,\par
Iltifat etmedi\u328? hergiz sen ma\u328?a,\par
E\u253?lemez bu i\u351?i bir gara galpak.\par
\par
Meni\u328? de\u253? y\u351?ky\u328?da \u231?ohlar sen \u253?ary\u328?,\par
G\u252?ndiz giriftary\u328?, gijeler zary\u328?.\par
\u214?mr\u252?m pa\u253?maly\u328?dyr janym nisary\u328?,\par
Bolsa\u253?dy wasly\u328?a bir \u231?\u228?re kylmak.\par
\par
Eger ki hi\u231? isem, sana geler men,\par
H\u246?\u351?k ustuhan isem, gana geler men,\par
Murda set sal isem, jana geler men,\par
Bolsa\u253?dy bezm i\u231?re bir \u253?ada salmak.\par
\par
Ahym \u351?ererinden \u252?\u253?n salyp otlar,\par
Bardylar derg\u228?he e\u253?le\u253?ip datlar,\par
Eridi, ap oldy j\u252?mle jematlar,\par
\u214?\u328?den-so\u328?a barmy hi\u231? be\u253?le bolmak.\par
\par
Bend\u228?\u328?em, ger di\u253?se\u328?: \u171?Nan beren alsa\u187?.\par
Mydam m\u228?t\u228?ji\u328? men, k\u228?n beren alsa.\par
Ger zowky-wysaly\u328? jan beren alsa,\par
\u221?ara\u351?ar Pyraga jan berip almak.\par
\par
NE\u221?LE\u221?IN, BI\u199?\u196?RE\u221?EM\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?in men, bu pelegi\u328? zulmy bilen galmy\u351?am,\par
Degdi sere, gitdi hu\u351?um, ne\u253?le\u253?in, bi\u231?\u228?re\u253?em.\par
Bady-saba erdi geldi, urdy, janym, \u246?lm\u252?\u351?em,\par
Degdi sere, gitdi hu\u351?um, ne\u253?le\u253?in, bi\u231?\u228?re\u253?em.\par
\par
Me\u328?li hanym aldy gitdi jismim i\u231?re janymy,\par
Sormazdan ykbaly pelek \u253?apdy hijran donumy,\par
Bir n\u228?kese bag\u351? e\u253?lemi\u351? pelek Me\u328?li hanymy,\par
Degdi sere, gitdi hu\u351?um, ne\u253?le\u253?in, bi\u231?\u228?re\u253?em.\par
\par
Dana bolma\u253? keser hu\u351?um ba\u351?da\u351?ymdan a\u253?rylyp,\par
Aklym \u231?a\u351?dy, serim bo\u351?dur, g\u246?r, hu\u351?umdan a\u253?rylyp,\par
\u221?owuz galyp, gan \u253?yglaram, garda\u351?ymdan a\u253?rylyp,\par
Degdi sere, gitdi hu\u351?um, ne\u253?le\u253?in, bi\u231?\u228?re\u253?em.\par
\par
Nesimini dabanyndan so\u253?dular-da, go\u253?dular,\par
Meni \u228?lem ryswa kylyp, iki g\u246?z\u252?m o\u253?dular,\par
Ilde-g\u252?nde \u253?okdur \u253?\u252?z\u252?m, pynhanymy a\u253?dylar,\par
Degdi sere, gitdi hu\u351?um, ne\u253?le\u253?in, bi\u231?\u228?re\u253?em.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?edi yklym zar bilen gan \u253?ygla\u253?yp,\par
\u214?z\u252?\u328? gapyl e\u253?le\u253?ip sen da\u253?ym pynhan \u253?ygla\u253?yp,\par
Terk e\u253?ledi maly-m\u252?lk\u252?\u328? gelip hijran \u253?ygla\u253?yp,\par
Degdi sere, gitdi hu\u351?um, ne\u253?le\u253?in, bi\u231?\u228?re\u253?em.\par
\par
K\u214?\u327?\u220?LDIR WE\u221?RAN\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?\u221?\u252?zi tabana\u187?. Di\u253?di: \u171?Me\u328?z\u228?r!\u187? Me\u328?li han.\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?Go\u253?du\u328? armana\u187?. Di\u253?di: \u171?K\u246?\u328?\u252?ldir we\u253?ran\u187?.\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?\u214?lerem imdi\u187?. Di\u253?di: \u171?Galar sen aman\u187?.\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?Ok kirpikleri\u328?\u187?. Di\u253?di: \u171?Ga\u351?larym keman\u187?.\par
