\par
ZYBANA ME\u327?LI\par
Perileri\u328? i\u231?inde og\u351?ar soltana Me\u328?li,\par
Ger sa\u253?rasa bilbiller, bentdir zybana Me\u328?li,\par
Y\u351?k oduna bat berip, saldy suzana Me\u328?li,\par
Soltan bolmu\u351?, ne\u253?le\u253?in, genji-nahana Me\u328?li,\par
Men pakyram bi\u231?\u228?re go\u253?mu\u351? armana Me\u328?li.\par
\par
Arzym bar derg\u228?hi\u328?de, e\u253?lese\u328? ma\u328?a nazar,\par
Men bir d\u252?kan gura\u253?yn, sen-sen ol y\u351?ky-bazar,\par
Y\u351?k bagynda aza\u351?yp, boldum nara sezewar,\par
Nakyl bardyr, a\u351?yklar g\u246?rse bir-birin, gyzar,\par
Sen-sen y\u351?ky\u328? ata\u351?y men bir perwana, Me\u328?li.\par
\par
Nergiz seni\u328? g\u246?zleri\u328?, ol ga\u351?lary\u328? kemandyr,\par
Dahan i\u231?inde asal bu ne \u351?irin zybandyr,\par
Simap kibi bikarar \u252?st\u252?\u328?de perwaz jandyr,\par
G\u252?l ro\u253?u\u328?y g\u246?rmesem, g\u246?zde \u253?a\u351?ym rowandyr,\par
Me\u328?ze\u253?ipdir g\u246?z \u253?a\u351?ym, ne\u253?le\u253?, ummana, Me\u328?li.\par
\par
Pany jahan Eremdir, sen ol bossany\u328? g\u252?li,\par
Men ki pakyr wabeste kapas i\u231?re bilbili,\par
G\u252?l ro\u253?u\u328?da nikapdyr ol Le\u253?lini\u328? s\u252?nb\u252?li,\par
Ne seb\u228?pdir, harlar sen meni\u328? kibi zelili,\par
Ol jemaly\u328? y\u351?kynda boldum diwana, Me\u328?li.\par
\par
Suraty\u328? A\u253?a og\u351?ar en\u231?e surat i\u231?inde,\par
Han bolmu\u351?dyr syraty\u328? ni\u231?e syrat i\u231?inde,\par
Ne gymmatdyr jemaly\u328? en\u231?e gymmat i\u231?inde,\par
Bossany\u328? kylsam taryp g\u246?kle\u328?, \u253?omut i\u231?inde,\par
Nazar salsa\u328?, bu de\u351?tim og\u351?ar bossana, Me\u328?li.\par
\par
Men y\u351?ky\u328?a geda men, k\u246?\u253?d\u252?rdi\u328? men perwany,\par
Sensiz indi ne\u253?le\u253?in men bu pany jahany,\par
G\u252?l ro\u253?u\u328?y g\u246?rsem, istemen be\u351?er-gulmany,\par
\u221?akdy janym, ne\u253?le\u253?in bu dowzahy\u328? suzany,\par
Bu janyma jebr e\u253?l\u228?p, go\u253?du\u328? pygana, Me\u328?li.\par
\par
ISTEMEN\par
G\u252?l \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328?e perwana men, ga\u253?ry re\u253?han istemen,\par
Bakyban m\u228?hri\u328?den do\u253?dum, bagy-bossan istemen\par
Ro\u253?u\u328? erer \u351?emsi-kamar, ol mahy-taban istemen,\par
Baky\u351?y\u328?, \u351?ah kyldy, bilgin, zowky-d\u246?wran istemen,\par
Z\u252?lp\u252?\u328?e bent e\u253?ledi\u328? dost, ga\u253?ry zyndan istemen.\par
\par
Z\u252?lpi sy\u253?a, dostum e\u253?, hasyly-s\u246?wda jan bilen,\par
\u199?agyrdy jellatlaryny, gorkar bilipdir gan bilen,\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?E\u253?, gan ne\u253?lesin, kylma hemra hijran bilen\u187?,\par
E\u253?ledim pynhanym a\u253?an, kowdy ol perman bilen,\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?Dost g\u246?rd\u252?m \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328?ni, bilgin, arman istemen\u187?.\par
\par
Jan berip gam y\u351?kyna, Mejnun boluban gezerem,\par
Tenim - depder, golum - galam, ajap waspy\u328? \u253?azaram,\par
G\u246?rme\u253?ip kenaryny, y\u351?k hazan i\u231?re \u253?\u252?zerem,\par
Simnar bolup sen \u252?\u231?in, tylla k\u246?\u351?kler d\u252?zerem,\par
Ga\u253?ry adalatly h\u228?kim, hany-soltan istemen.\par
\par
Ke\u253?wany geler estime, baksam ki gara g\u246?zlere,\par
Myrryh meni bent e\u253?le\u253?ir, g\u246?zlesem, dost \u253?\u252?zlere,\par
M\u252?\u351?teri gapyl otyrmy\u351?, bent bolup, bil, s\u246?zlere,\par
Z\u246?hre, N\u228?zperi, Huma\u253?, Dursuti ha\u253?ran sizlere,\par
Be\u253?le adalatly \u351?a sen, Gyzyl Arslan istemen.\par
\par
\u350?a bolup, perman berip sen, bildim \u171?Heft pe\u253?kere\u187?,\par
B\u228?hram Gur tagt unudyp, arz edipdir Isgendere,\par
Tug g\u246?terip kyldy\u328? s\u246?we\u351?, gol urup sen \u351?em\u351?ire,\par
E\u253?le ki zalym bolarmy, gara g\u246?zli dilber-\u228?.\par
Gorkaram men kamaty\u328?dan, jyza-keman istemen.\par
\par
\u199?ykdy Z\u252?be\u253?da alnymdan, ah, ne\u253?le\u253?, bagtym gara,\par
Golum baglap z\u252?lp\u252?\u328?e, tab\u351?yrarlar a\u382?dara,\par
\u221?uwudar ol demine, zalym bolup sen, dilber-\u228?.\par
Zulum kylma \u253?ara\u351?maz sen kibi pygambere,\par
Saldy\u328?, e\u253?, \u231?ykmaz dertge, indi derman istemen.\par
\par
Ismim erer ki Pyragy, \u253?as tutarmy\u351? illerim,\par
S\u246?zleri\u328? ho\u351? wagt bolup, lal boldy, dost dillerim,\par
Girdi\u328?, e\u253?, sen se\u253?il edip, bagda gurban g\u252?llerim,\par
Bent olup g\u246?z\u253?a\u351?yma, ne\u253?le\u253? ki, akmaz sillerim,\par
Go\u253?nu\u328? i\u231?re bitmi\u351? bossan, men l\u228?mekan istemen.\par
\par
\u221?ARYM, \u221?A ALLA\par
Jan jo\u351?guna geldi, \u253?andym, \u253?aryldym,\par
Bagy\u351?lasa\u328? ne\u253?l\u228?r, \u253?arym, \u253?a, Alla.\par
Sangysyz s\u246?\u253?\u252?\u351?dim, \u246?\u253?s\u252?z a\u253?ryldym,\par
Bagy\u351?lasa\u328? ne\u253?l\u228?r, \u253?arym, \u253?a, Alla.\par
\par
S\u246?zle\u351?erdim, syrla\u351?ardym \u253?ar bile,\par
\u221?\u252?reginde \u253?ar hy\u253?aly bar bile,\par
Imdi, le\u253?kin, a\u253?yrdylar zor bile,\par
Bagy\u351?lasa\u328? ne\u253?l\u228?r, \u253?arym, \u253?a, Alla.\par
\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l ho\u351?dur \u253?ada salyp gezm\u228?nde,\par
\u221?adyma salmanda, y\u351?kym gyzmanda,\par
Meni gamda go\u253?ma ony armanda,\par
Bagy\u351?lasa\u328? ne\u253?l\u228?r, \u253?arym, \u253?a, Alla.\par
\par
Yhlas ile \u253?ar meni di\u253?r, men \u253?ary,\par
Jowrandy jigeri, gitdi karary,\par
Ol onda ah \u231?eker, men munda zary,\par
Bagy\u351?lasa\u328? ne\u253?l\u228?r, \u253?arym, \u253?a, Alla.\par
\par
Bardy pynhan-pynhan \u351?irin s\u246?z\u252?miz,\par
Bolan i\u351?e ha\u253?ran galdyk \u246?z\u252?miz,\par
Bir-bire bakmakdan do\u253?maz g\u246?z\u252?miz,\par
Bagy\u351?lasa\u328? ne\u253?l\u228?r, \u253?arym, \u253?a, Alla.\par
\par
Elim Sa\u328?a \u253?etmez arzym etm\u228?ge,\par
I\u351?imi\u328? rowajy \u253?okdur bitm\u228?ge,\par
Dilber derdi go\u253?maz meni \u253?atmaga,\par
Bagy\u351?lasa\u328? ne\u253?l\u228?r, \u253?arym, \u253?a, Alla.\par
\par
Magtymguly, d\u252?n\u253?\u228? k\u246?ne jahandyr,\par
S\u246?\u253?\u252?\u351?meklik bu dessury-zamandyr,\par
J\u252?rm\u252?m \u231?oh bolsa hem, keremi\u328? k\u228?ndir,\par
Bagy\u351?lasa\u328? ne\u253?l\u228?r, \u253?arym, \u253?a, Alla.\par
\par
DERT OLDY\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l berdim bir biwepa mahbuba,\par
\u199?ykdy elden, dagy jana dert oldy.\par
A\u351?yk di\u253?r: \u171?Bakmanam indi ol huba\u187?,\par
\u221?ol \u252?st\u252?nde du\u351?dy, g\u246?z\u252?m d\u246?rt oldy.\par
\par
Menlik bilen etdim i\u351?imi za\u253?a,\par
Ykbalym e\u351?egin batyrdym la\u253?a,\par
\u221?a bir merde \u253?ykyl, \u253?a-da Huda\u253?a,\par
Bende i\u351?i ba\u351? tutmady, art oldy.\par
\par
Tugunym tur bolup ga\u231?dy sa\u253?\u253?atdan,\par
G\u246?wre gamdan doldy, \u253?\u252?rek hem otdan,\par
Gorkaram, \u253?ar bizi \u231?ykarar \u253?atdan,\par
A\u253?ry \u253?erde mesgen tutdy, \u253?urt oldy.\par
\par
Sonam el bermedi, saldym bazymy,\par
La\u231?yn kowdy, garga aldy gazymy,\par
\u350?un\u231?a pakyrlyga urdum \u246?z\u252?mi,\par
Tilkilenip gezdim, adym gurt oldy.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?\u252?regimde dert d\u246?r\u228?r,\par
Kim g\u246?r\u252?pdir, ko\u253? i\u231?inden gurt d\u246?r\u228?r,\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, mert \u253?igitden mert d\u246?r\u228?r,\par
Ka\u231?an turdy - namart ogly mert oldy.\par
\par
KEREM ISL\u196?RIN\par
Owwal ba\u351?da, Kadyr Alla,\par
Senden bir kerem isl\u228?rin.\par
Badam gabak, alma \u253?a\u328?ak,\par
Bir zyba senem isl\u228?rin.\par
\par
Ta\u328?ry bermese, n\u228?deli,\par
Ba\u351? alyp, ka\u253?da gideli,\par
Otur\u351?y-tur\u351?y edaly,\par
Ga\u351?lary galam isl\u228?rin.\par
\par
\u214?z\u252?ne hormat getiren,\par
\u196?rni\u328? hyzmatyn bitiren,\par
Ga\u351?-gabak \u231?ytma\u253? oturan,\par
Ma\u328?la\u253?y g\u252?len isl\u228?rin.\par
\par
\u221?igrimi \u253?a\u351? \u246?tdi menden,\par
Hezl etmedim, d\u252?n\u253?\u228? senden,\par
Tili s\u252?\u253?ji, lebi handan,\par
Bir go\u253?na salan isl\u228?rin.\par
\par
Gul Magtym, geldim jahana,\par
Bir \u253?ar bergil akly dana,\par
Du\u351?dum \u252?m bilmez nadana,\par
Bir gadrym bilen isl\u228?rin.\par
\par
BAGRYM DILENIM\par
Dertli dilber, dille\u351?er sen, gel b\u228?ri,\par
Dullukdyr meni\u328?-de bagrym dilenim.\par
Sora\u253?yr men, men hem sen de\u253? bir \u253?ary,\par
Seni soramakda \u253?okdur \u253?alanym.\par
\par
Eger ge\u328?e\u351? salsam \u253?ada, bili\u351?e,\par
Di\u253?rler: \u171?\u350?irin asal \u253?aga geli\u351?e\u187?,\par
S\u228?her, \u253?azygym \u231?\u252?n tutsam naly\u351?a,\par
Owwal bir \u253?ar bolar \u253?ada salanym.\par
\par
Bilen \u253?anda me\u328?z\u228?r gymmat d\u252?re sen,\par
Tanymaza du\u351?up, degme \u253?ere sen,\par
Kadyr kysmat etse, ma\u328?a bara sen,\par
Seni\u328? kimin \u253?ardyr meni\u328? \u246?lenim.\par
\par
Her dilber kim, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m \u246?\u253?\u252?n \u253?arydar,\par
\u221?atan bagtyn ol \u221?aradan \u253?\u246?r\u252?der,\par
Gargy\u351?ym da\u351?lary mum de\u253? erider,\par
P\u252?r-pudak \u253?a\u253?radar alky\u351? kylanym.\par
\par
G\u246?zel g\u246?rk\u252?\u328? g\u246?kde G\u252?nden a\u253?ynmaz,\par
G\u252?li, dessembili ysgan do\u253?unmaz,\par
Magtymguly, ba\u351? bermese ba\u253?ynmaz,\par
M\u228?hrimi inderip, nazar salanym.\par
\par
\u221?AR BIZIM SARY\par
Gulzumy garsanyp kyrk \u253?ol ge\u231?er men,\par
Eger ki me\u253?l etse \u253?ar bizim sary.\par
Gadam \u253?erne ganat baglap u\u231?ar men,\par
Di\u253?se dilber: \u171?A\u351?yk, \u253?\u246?r bizim sary!\u187?\par
\par
Kyrk \u253?yl gol gow\u351?uryp, gullukda dursam,\par
Alty g\u252?n\u231?e g\u246?rmen altmy\u351? \u253?yl \u253?\u246?rsem,\par
Bir \u351?un\u231?akly bolsa, g\u246?rsem, jan bersem,\par
Jemalyn arz etse bir bizim sary.\par
\par
Ne la\u253?ykly \u253?\u252?z\u252?m bardyr tutarga,\par
Ne a\u253?ry gapym bar ondan giderge,\par
Umydym bar, go\u253?ma\u253? bela-beterge,\par
Derg\u228?hinden a\u231?sa der bizim sary.\par
\par
Bir kimse \u253?olukdy desti \u351?eraply,\par
\u221?elden ja\u253?namazly, suwdan m\u228?hraply,\par
Egni ak redaly, \u253?a\u351?yl nikaply,\par
Ugra\u351?dy bir ajap \u228?r bizim sary.\par
\par
\u221?olda\u351? bolup, bile \u253?\u246?rd\u252?m bir me\u253?dan,\par
Me\u253?dan i\u231?re dolup oturmy\u351? merdan,\par
Bir e\u253?wan \u252?st\u252?nde \u231?yrlap d\u246?rt \u253?erden,\par
Di\u253?diler: \u171?Golu\u328?ny ber bizim sary\u187?.\par
\par
\u171?Pyragy!\u187? di\u253?p \u231?agyrdylar, eltdiler,\par
\u171?Kandady\u328??\u187? di\u253?p, gulagymdan tutdular,\par
Ustuhanym altmy\u351? para etdiler,\par
Di\u253?diler: \u171?Mert bolsa\u328?, dur bizim sary\u187?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, b\u228?\u351? g\u252?n e\u351?ret s\u252?rm\u228?ge,\par
Ja\u253? imesdir eglenm\u228?ge, durmaga,\par
Kararym \u253?ok oturmaga, turmaga,\par
Agzyn a\u231?yp durmu\u351? \u253?er bizim sary.\par
\par
\u221?AR SENDEN\par
Bilbilleri \u253?esir eden g\u252?l-handan,\par
\u221?a, Rep, habar bilerinmi, \u253?ar senden.\par
\u221?edi yklym ma\u328?a g\u246?r\u252?ner zyndan,\par
\u221?a, Rep, habar bilerinmi, \u253?ar senden.\par
\par
Ispendi\u253?ar g\u246?zi R\u252?stem Zalynda,\par
\u350?am, Nejepde, Mekke, Dyma\u351?k ilinde,\par
Arzy-Karsda, Kerbelany\u328? \u231?\u246?l\u252?nde,\par
\u221?a, Rep, habar bilerinmi, \u253?ar senden.\par
\par
\u350?erap i\u231?ip, serho\u351? bolup, segresem,\par
Ganym janyn gy\u253?ym-gy\u253?ym dograsam,\par
G\u246?rogly dek dagdan-daga ugrasam,\par
\u221?a, Rep, habar bilerinmi, \u253?ar, senden.\par
\par
Bir g\u252?l kokar g\u246?zel \u253?ary\u328? bagynda,\par
Bilbil h\u252?j\u252?m e\u253?l\u228?r sol-u sagynda,\par
Be\u253?tullany\u328? Sapa, Merwe dagynda,\par
\u221?a, Rep, habar bilerinmi, \u253?ar, senden.\par
\par
\u350?yh Sengan de\u253? uzyn ga\u253?ga ulansam,\par
\u350?ibli kimin toz-topraga bulansam,\par
K\u228?b\u228? baryp, \u253?edi keret dolansam,\par
\u221?a, Rep, habar bilerinmi, \u253?ar, senden.\par
\par
\u221?usup kibi zyndan i\u231?re aglasam,\par
Jirjis kibi jan \u253?olunda \u231?aglasam,\par
\u221?unus kibi Haka gulluk baglasam,\par
\u221?a, Rep, habar bilerinmi, \u253?ar, senden.\par
\par
Doga kylyp, elim G\u246?ge galdyrsam,\par
G\u252?l, Ferhar dek gyzyl me\u328?zim soldursam,\par
Gopuz alyp, be\u253?ik nagra \u231?aldyrsam,\par
\u221?a, Rep, habar bilerinmi, \u253?ar, senden.\par
\par
Isa kibi hylwat tutsam semada,\par
Idris kibi gulluk etsem zy\u253?ada,\par
Hydyr, Yl\u253?as kibi girsem zulmata,\par
\u221?a, Rep, habar bilerinmi, \u253?ar, senden.\par
\par
Magtymguly, a\u351?yklary\u328? mestinde,\par
Nerkes g\u246?zi ha\u253?ran eder destinde,\par
\u221?edi \u253?erde, dokuz pelek \u252?st\u252?nde,\par
\u221?a, Rep, habar bilerinmi, \u253?ar, senden.\par
\par
NOWRUZDAN SENI\par
Bolmady bizge nesibi\u328?, istedim g\u252?\u253?zden seni,\par
Di\u253?di\u328?: \u171?\u214?ts\u252?n gy\u351?, tapar men t\u228?ze nowruzdan seni\u187?.\par
Sa\u253?ladym, se\u231?dim, sonam, bir b\u246?lejik gyzdan seni,\par
Ne\u231?\u252?n bili\u328?ni gu\u231?madym men tapyp d\u252?zden seni,\par
Isterem Hakdan, gowu\u351?dyrga\u253? ma\u328?a tizden seni.\par
\par
Hak katynda s\u246?z\u252?m \u246?tmez, men kibi awara \u253?ok,\par
Il-g\u252?n rehim e\u253?lemezler, men kibi bi\u231?\u228?re \u253?ok,\par
\u221?\u252?regim set para dekdir, hi\u231? tenimde \u253?ara \u253?ok,\par
Sen garyp sen, men pakyr men, sende-mende \u231?\u228?re \u253?ok,\par
S\u246?wd\u252?gim, takdyry-Hakdyr a\u253?yrgan bizden seni.\par
\par
S\u246?wd\u252?gim, sen g\u252?nde bir gez \u253?ady\u328?a salsa\u328? meni,\par
G\u252?nde \u253?\u252?z katla til\u228?r men \u253?aradan Hakdan seni,\par
Ba\u351?ky g\u252?n sen oda saldy\u328? men parahat bend\u228?ni,\par
Hak g\u246?tersin aradan, \u351?e\u253?le rakyp-\u351?ermend\u228?ni,\par
Kyl behil bizden \u253?a\u328?a ynjytsalar s\u246?zden seni.\par
\par
Bagy\u328?a girsem s\u228?her, bilbil bolup salsam o\u253?un,\par
Gaflata galsa rakyp, bir dem saly\u351?sak gol bo\u253?un,\par
Hakdan \u246?zge \u231?\u228?re \u253?okdur, ne kyla\u253? men, ne\u253?le\u253?in,\par
In\u231?e bil, \u351?irin zyban, kepder topuk sen, gaz bo\u253?un,\par
Saklasyn Ta\u328?ry penahynda \u253?aman g\u246?zden seni.\par
\par
Ha\u253?ry\u328?y du\u351?man g\u246?rer, dostu\u328? \u231?eker jebri-jepa\u328?,\par
\u221?ar-a, dildarlyk bolarmy s\u252?rme\u253?in zowky-sapa\u328?,\par
Salsalar mizana Balkan dagy bolmazdyr p\u228?he\u328?,\par
A\u253?dadyr Magtymguly \u228?hdi\u328? \u253?alan, \u253?okdur wepa\u328?,\par
Biwepalar hup sowutmy\u351?lar, sonam, bizden seni.\par
\par
A\u350?YK BOLMU\u350?AM\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar bir \u253?\u252?zi g\u252?l, a\u253?a a\u351?yk bolmu\u351?am,\par
Bar\u231?alar maksudy - g\u252?l ragna\u253?a a\u351?yk bolmu\u351?am.\par
Bilbilem, bag i\u231?re bir gowga\u253?a a\u351?yk bolmu\u351?am,\par
\u214?zi ga\u253?yp, z\u252?lpleri \u253?elda\u253?a a\u351?yk bolmu\u351?am,\par
Menzilim bag i\u231?redir, s\u228?hra\u253?a a\u351?yk bolmu\u351?am.\par
\par
\u199?\u252?n pelek saldy meni ol g\u252?n pena topragyna,\par
D\u252?\u351?di se\u253?rim da\u253?yma Mekge, Medine dagyna,\par
Bilbil oldum, sa\u253?radym, girdim Eremi\u328? bagyna,\par
Pa\u253?y-bent oldum o g\u252?n gam \u228?hlini\u328? duzagyna\par
\u221?\u252?z bela-m\u228?hnetli bir s\u246?wda\u253?a a\u351?yk bolmu\u351?am.\par
\par
G\u246?wr\u228?m i\u231?re \u253?ar gamydyr, menzilim s\u228?hrada, he\u253?,\par
Pu\u351?e\u351?im gam-gussadyr, men d\u246?nm\u252?\u351?em Perhada, he\u253?,\par
Saldy y\u351?ky\u328?, dilber-\u228?, jan-u jigerim oda, he\u253?,\par
Wadaryg-a, ge\u231?di \u246?mr\u252?m za\u253?a berdim bada, he\u253?,\par
Ahy \u231?oh, efgany \u231?oh, bir k\u246?\u253?e a\u351?yk bolmu\u351?am.\par
\par
Bilmenem, ol ne bahrdyr, ne mugazzam dagydyr,\par
Aldy k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m, gitdi aklym, ten mydam n\u228? \u231?agydyr,\par
Ony nisbet etmek olmaz, gumry, bilbil, zagydyr,\par
A\u253? garaz her z\u252?lp\u252?ne, \u253?etmi\u351? m\u252?\u328? \u228?r tussagydyr,\par
Kaddy-kamaty belent, zyba\u253?a a\u351?yk bolmu\u351?am.\par
\par
Dost, howa\u253?y-wasly\u328?y men \u351?un\u231?a \u231?yndan isterem,\par
Damy-z\u252?lp\u252?\u328? ka\u253?dyna \u246?z\u252?mi zyndan isterem,\par
Di\u253?me: \u171?Gamdan bir zaman k\u246?\u328?l\u252?mi handan isterem\u187?,\par
Bir garyp a\u351?yk menem, \u253?ar, seni senden isterem,\par
Gije-\u253?u g\u252?ndiz, bili\u328?, h\u252?w-ha\u253?a a\u351?yk bolmu\u351?am.\par
\par
Galmy\u351?am ha\u253?ran olup, ga\u253?ry mydarym \u253?ok meni\u328?,\par
Aldy janym y\u351?ky\u328? ody, ygty\u253?arym \u253?ok meni\u328?,\par
Tende jan perwaz eder a\u253?ry durarym \u253?ok meni\u328?,\par
Gelse, aklym dagydar, gitse kararym \u253?ok meni\u328?,\par
Gamzasy ok, ga\u351?lary ol \u253?a\u253?a a\u351?yk bolmu\u351?am.\par
\par
A\u253?dadyr Magtymguly, men onda k\u228?ne ugradym,\par
Se\u253?r edip bardym pelege, l\u228?mekana ugradym,\par
\u199?\u252?n meni ryswa kylan y\u351?ky-\u253?egana ugradym.\par
\u221?etmi\u351? iki \u351?\u228?hr i\u231?inde m\u252?\u328? bir d\u252?kana ugradym,\par
\u350?un\u231?a sergerdan-sepil-u za\u253?a a\u351?yk bolmu\u351?am.\par
\par
BULUDA GARDY MENI\par
Y\u351?k \u253?\u252?regimde ga\u253?nap, \u253?andyrdy derdi meni,\par
T\u252?t\u252?nim bada berip, buluda gardy meni.\par
Pelek bilegim towlap, \u231?arhyna sardy meni,\par
Hyrydar g\u246?zi bile kim gelip g\u246?rdi meni,\par
Hijran \u253?agmyry \u253?agyp, gam sile berdi meni.\par
\par
Gam sili birle gidip, y\u351?k \u252?lkesine baryp,\par
Hy\u253?alym pikre dolup, aklymy \u253?el aparyp,\par
Ol ha\u253?rat me\u253?danynda men garyp galdym aryp,\par
Y\u351?k hanjaryn \u231?ekib\u228?n, hijran \u253?\u252?regim \u253?aryp,\par
\u196?leme dessan edip, aftaba serdi meni.\par
\par
Ne jeset i\u231?re jan bar, ne kuwwat galdy tende,\par
Hem serge\u351?te, hem ha\u253?ran, bu i\u351?e galdym bende,\par
Ne hassa\u253?am, ne bimar, ne murda\u253?am, ne zinde,\par
Gam h\u252?j\u252?m e\u253?l\u228?p g\u246?kden, zemin sary inende,\par
Pelek elimden tutup, howala berdi meni.\par
\par
Bir ahwala du\u351? boldum, gam h\u252?jm etdi, \u246?ld\u252?rdi,\par
Bu i\u351?i\u328? seri\u351?tesin y\u351?k okadyp bildirdi,\par
Wysala rehmi inip, elim tutup galdyrdy,\par
Jemal bir jilwe berdi, i\u231?im \u351?owka doldurdy,\par
S\u246?zleme\u253?in ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in, \u253?aranlar, \u253?ardy meni.\par
\par
Magtymguly, begligim \u253?ar jemaly gul etdi,\par
Wysal umydyn berip, m\u252?\u328? dilli bilbil etdi,\par
A\u253?ralyk oda saldy, pyrak turdy, \u253?el etdi,\par
Y\u351?k \u231?ekdi zybanasyn, \u253?akyp-\u246?rt\u228?p, k\u252?l etdi,\par
Hijran \u8722? pyrak\u231?y alyp, \u253?ele sowurdy meni.\par
\par
ME\u327?Z\u196?R H\u214?K\u220?MLI\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?ller k\u246?\u351?k\u252?nde hy\u253?aly\u328? hany\par
\u214?wlady-h\u252?\u328?kara me\u328?z\u228?r h\u246?k\u252?mli.\par
A\u351?yk \u231?eker nalany,\par
\u221?asa salar l\u228?l\u228?ni,\par
\u221?erde be\u351?er paty\u351?ahy,\par
Huda\u253?ymny\u328? halany,\par
Gamza\u328? garak\u231?ysy salsa tala\u328?y,\par
Kirpigi\u328? ok, ga\u351?y\u328? \u253?a\u253?dyr \u231?ekimli.\par
\par
G\u246?zelleri\u328? waspyn etseler kanda,\par
\u196?lem agzy tamam jem ola sende,\par
T\u228? jan bardyr bu tende,\par
Arzuwmendim bar sende,\par
Ady\u328? Ruma d\u252?\u351?di, owaza\u328? gitdi Hinde,\par
Le\u253?li sa\u328?a kenizek, Z\u252?le\u253?ha bolsun bende,\par
Men hem seni\u328? derdi\u328?den galyp erdim dermende,\par
Bagda g\u252?l\u231?ehre sen bulgur basymly.\par
\par
Y\u351?ky\u328? ata\u351?yny sa\u231?yp sen d\u252?ze,\par
Jan polatdan bolsa, d\u246?zmez bu k\u246?ze,\par
Dokunsa dilber, k\u246?ze,\par
Zyban geler her s\u246?ze,\par
G\u246?rk\u252?\u328? G\u252?ne\u351?i dogsa, ne san bardyr \u253?yldyza,\par
Alma zenehdana, bu k\u252?m\u252?\u351? \u253?\u252?ze,\par
Sy\u253?a z\u252?lp\u252?\u328? suratgerdir d\u246?k\u252?mli.\par
\par
Huma\u253? otury\u351?ly, la\u231?yn turu\u351?ly,\par
Kebuter topukly, maral g\u246?r\u252?\u351?li,\par
T\u228?ze hilal ga\u351?ly, merwerit di\u351?li,\par
Tawus gu\u351? zynatly, Dawut towu\u351?ly,\par
Tezerw \u351?iweli, k\u228?kilik \u253?\u246?ri\u351?li,\par
Tugun gu\u351? timarly, tarlan bakymly.\par
Baglanyban \u231?yksa\u328? \u351?itde\u253?i-g\u252?lzar,\par
Husnu\u328? hy\u253?alaty \u228?lemi aldar,\par
A\u351?yk a\u253?dar: \u171?E\u253? dildar,\par
G\u246?rki G\u252?ne ta\u253? dildar,\par
Tapar hajy\u328? sogabyn -\par
Her kim bir garyp goldar,\par
Magtymguly, sen dek g\u246?rmedim, dildar,\par
Bu jana taraly, k\u246?\u328?le \u253?akymly.\par
\par
PANY-JAHAN G\u214?ZELIM\par
Bere\u253? \u351?irin janymy, gelgil-nahan g\u246?zelim,\par
Sensiz g\u246?ze almanam pany-jahan, g\u246?zelim.\par
Perileri\u328? sahy sen, g\u246?zel soltan g\u246?zelim,\par
Kirpikleri\u328? jellatdyr, nurbat-aman, g\u246?zelim,\par
Bu pelek gerdi\u351?inde \u253?okdur jenan, g\u246?zelim,\par
G\u252?l ro\u253?u\u328?da bent bolmu\u351? mahy-taban, g\u246?zelim,\par
Nazar e\u253?le g\u246?z\u252?me, bentdir umman, g\u246?zelim.\par
\par
G\u252?l ro\u253?u\u328?da bilmedim, bardyr ol jugra haly\u328?,\par
Kemana azm urmu\u351?, \u231?e\u351?m \u252?st\u252?nde hilaly\u328?,\par
Soltany sen Le\u253?lini\u328?, ol Z\u252?le\u253?ha z\u252?laly\u328?,\par
Go\u253?nu\u328? i\u231?re \u253?eti\u351?mi\u351? fird\u246?ws eren nahaly\u328?,\par
Mahy-taban bent boldy g\u246?r\u252?p sahypjemaly\u328?,\par
G\u252?l ro\u253?u\u328?dan g\u246?tergil \u8213? nazar sala\u253? \u8213? desmaly\u328?,\par
Men y\u351?ky\u328?da bolmu\u351?am d\u228?li-mejnun, g\u246?zelim.\par
\par
Gen\u231?-hazyna saklawy sallanyp dur \u351?amary\u328?,\par
Ol \u351?amary\u328? astynda \u253?atypdyr go\u351?a nary\u328?,\par
Kylsa\u328? biadyl perman, di\u253?men: \u171?\u221?aman azary\u328?\u187?,\par
Jan \u351?\u228?hrinde g\u246?rd\u252?m men seni\u328? y\u351?ky bazary\u328?,\par
Aman, dilber, \u246?rtedi, ne aja\u253?yp nazary\u328?,\par
Men Perhadam, telmuryp y\u351?ky\u328?da hary-zary\u328?,\par
\u350?irin kibi daransa\u328?, \u253?okdur arman, g\u246?zelim.\par
\par
S\u246?zle dilber, e\u351?de\u253?in, gaflatdan \u231?yksyn g\u246?z\u252?m,\par
N\u228?z e\u253?le\u253?ip bakar sen, bilmen, ne di\u253?en s\u246?z\u252?m,\par
Pany jahan i\u231?inde y\u351?ky\u328?a messan \u246?z\u252?m,\par
\u214?m\u252?r ahyr d\u252?\u351?medi jemaly\u328?a bu \u253?\u252?z\u252?m,\par
Gutaryp men k\u228?tip kylyp 16 , golda bary be\u253?azym,\par
Sen-sen pelek \u231?arhynda g\u246?wn\u252?mde dilnowazym,\par
Derdim enj\u252?men kylyp, men natuwan, g\u246?zelim.\par
\par
Fuzun bolsa-da derdim, \u253?eti\u351?er sen Lukmanym,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de genji-k\u228?nim, sen-sen dini-imanym,\par
Bag i\u231?inde bark uran anbarym sen, re\u253?hanym,\par
G\u246?rer g\u246?z\u252?m g\u246?reji, kelam di\u253?sem zybanym,\par
G\u246?wn\u252?m bagynda bitmi\u351? g\u246?zelim, arguwanym,\par
S\u228?her saba tolganan sen serwi-huramanym,\par
Janym i\u231?inde biten sen jawydan, g\u246?zelim.\par
\par
Kabul kylsa\u328? men guly, da\u253?ym hyzmat kyla\u253?yn,\par
Ta\u328?rydan ne dert inse, baryn \u246?z\u252?m ala\u253?yn,\par
Ezra\u253?yly\u328? alnynda men sadaka bola\u253?yn,\par
Ger ki, g\u246?zel, istese\u328?, janym nara sala\u253?yn,\par
Bazyg\u228?ri\u328? ornunda o\u253?nap da\u253?ym gala\u253?yn,\par
Sen Gurhanym nazar sal, bu \u253?\u252?z\u252?me syla\u253?yn,\par
Meni\u328? kibi bir gulda sahypkyran, g\u246?zelim.\par
\par
Di\u253?seler sen dek g\u246?zel inmi\u351? pany jahana,\par
Bawer kylman, ynangyl, ol galat bir suhana,\par
Hergiz se\u253?il e\u253?lese\u328?, nazar salgyl bu jana,\par
Y\u351?k bilen zowk e\u253?l\u228?p girdim daryl-amana,\par
Jugra haly\u328? \u253?esiri, men ol hala perwana,\par
\u214?m\u252?r ahyr d\u252?\u351?mez ro\u253? bagda sen dek sowsana,\par
Nar i\u231?inde tolgansam, bilgil, ahsan, g\u246?zelim.\par
\par
Ba\u351?dan-pa\u253?a synladym, bili\u328?dedir z\u252?nnary\u328?,\par
\u221?anan janyma gonar ol ata\u351? bi\u351?umary\u328?,\par
Nisar kylsam janymy men pakyr giriftary\u328?,\par
Ka\u253?sy ja\u253?a ba\u351? go\u253?sa\u328?, alny\u328?da sezewary\u328?,\par
\u221?anan jana rehm eder, \u246?w\u252?r ajap nazary\u328?,\par
G\u252?nde bir dem g\u246?rmesem, \u253?etmez sabr-u kararym,\par
Go\u253?nu\u328? i\u231?inde g\u246?rd\u252?m men l\u228?mekan, g\u246?zelim.\par
\par
Magtymguly perwana y\u351?ky\u328? bilen ot alar,\par
T\u228? h\u228?kister bolgan\u231?a, perwana narda galar,\par
Ro\u253?u\u328? g\u246?r\u252?p ol behi\u351?t, \u171?h\u252?w\u187? \u231?ekmi\u351?dir, u\u253?alar,\par
Seni\u328? kibi bir g\u246?zel, meger, fird\u246?wsde bolar,\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?in bagtym gara, pelek badagyn salar,\par
Bermenem \u253?ar janyny, meni\u328? janymy alar,\par
Berer boldum jany\u328?a g\u252?nde on jan, g\u246?zelim.\par
\par
BIR SAGAT BILE\par
\u214?m\u252?r b\u228?\u351? g\u252?n, menzili \u252?\u231?,\par
D\u246?wrany\u328? bir sagat bile.\par
\u221?\u246?rir kerwen, \u231?ekiler g\u246?\u231?,\par
\u221?atyp sen parahat bile.\par
\par
Sen di\u253?me birew el gerer,\par
Akyllar munda i\u351? g\u246?rer,\par
Biakyllar he\u328?\u328?am gurar,\par
E\u351?ret ist\u228?p rahat bile.\par
\par
Kapyr nebs ile \u351?e\u253?tan \u351?um,\par
I\u351?ler tutar e\u253?l\u228?p h\u252?j\u252?m,\par
Bir g\u252?n \u231?ykar sen-h\u228? mahrum,\par
Gezme ho\u351? kanagat bile.\par
\par
Jana jepa ber, nebse ha\u253?,\par
I\u351? et, ahyr\u253?et gamyn i\u253?,\par
Pygambere salawat di\u253?,\par
\u350?owk etse\u328? \u351?epagat bile.\par
\par
Bende bolsa\u328?, adamzat bol,\par
Jepbar di\u253?m\u228?ndir: \u171?Jellat bol!\u187?\par
Ha\u253?yr i\u351?l\u228?p, bar, azat bol,\par
Utanma hyjalat bile.\par
\par
Adam ogly \u246?z\u252?n bilmez,\par
Nebs ugrunja bik\u228?r bolmaz,\par
Kysmaty\u328?dan gary\u351? galmaz,\par
Gezse\u328? \u253?\u252?z hy\u253?alat bile.\par
\par
Magtymguly di\u253?er, \u253?aran,\par
Halk tutan i\u351?e men ha\u253?ran,\par
Ge\u231?er pursat, \u246?ter d\u246?wran,\par
G\u252?\u253?menewer tagat bile.\par
\par
DI\u350? GITMEK\par
Tagam lezzetin alar,\par
Dahany\u328?dan di\u351? gitmek.\par
A\u328?yrsyzy azdyrar,\par
G\u246?tin d\u246?wlet pi\u351? gitmek.\par
\par
\u350?e\u253?tan \u253?olun bek e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
Gara \u253?\u252?z\u252?n ak e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
\u221?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? g\u252?n\u228? \u253?ok e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
S\u228?her g\u246?zden \u253?a\u351? gitmek.\par
\par
Peltesiz \u253?ag \u231?yraga\par
Y\u351?yk salmaz gyraga,\par
Ilin salar a\u253?aga,\par
A\u253?ak galyp, ba\u351? gitmek.\par
\par
Ni\u231?e pise zar bolup,\par
\u221?atsa\u328? \u253?eg bimar bolup,\par
Ho\u351?dur \u253?ag\u351?a \u253?ar bolup,\par
Bir \u253?amandan da\u351? gitmek.\par
\par
Ula\u351?maganlar gama,\par
\u350?\u252?kr etmezler ho\u351? deme,\par
Abyra\u253?dyr adama,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y gelip, ho\u351? gitmek.\par
\par
\u221?aman dil - \u253?ol \u253?itirer,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y - rehmet getirer,\par
\u196?re sangy artdyrar,\par
Kyrkdan a\u351?yp, \u253?a\u351? gitmek.\par
\par
Pyragy d\u252?n\u253?\u228? d\u252?\u253?\u351?d\u252?r,\par
D\u252?\u253?\u351? g\u246?rse\u328?, d\u252?\u253?bi hi\u231?dir,\par
Jahanda \u253?aman i\u351?dir,\par
Gury gelip, bo\u351? gitmek.\par
\par
\u199?ALDY GITDI\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? bazyg\u228?rdir,\par
Bazysyn \u231?aldy gitdi.\par
G\u252?mra etdi ni\u231?\u228?ni,\par
\u221?olda\u351? di\u253?p aldy gitdi.\par
\par
Akyl, pikr et her ha\u231?an,\par
\u221?\u252?z gonan bar, \u253?\u252?z g\u246?\u231?en,\par
Tagty asmandan u\u231?an\par
S\u252?le\u253?man \u246?ldi gitdi.\par
\par
\u221?a, m\u252?rewwetli \u351?ahym,\par
