\par
JO\u350? BOLMASYN\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar \u8722? musulmanlar,\par
D\u228?li k\u246?\u328?\u252?l jo\u351? bolmasyn.\par
\u221?ene bir \u253?ag\u351?y \u253?igide,\par
\u221?aman hatyn du\u351? bolmasyn.\par
\par
Her kim alsa Hakdan rehmet,\par
Gider ga\u253?gy, galmaz m\u228?hnet,\par
Abat bolmaz, durmaz d\u246?wlet,\par
Hi\u231? \u252?lke biba\u351? bolmasyn.\par
\par
Ta\u328?ry dest bersin yslama,\par
T\u228?sip edip at besl\u228?ne,\par
Haram i\u351?l\u228?p, \u351?er isl\u228?ne,\par
Uzak \u246?m\u252?r - \u253?a\u351? bolmasyn.\par
\par
Her kimi\u328? \u246?z synasynda,\par
Akly g\u246?rner be\u253?nisinde,\par
Iki dostu\u328? arasynda,\par
\u221?aman-\u253?owuz i\u351? bolmasyn.\par
\par
Her ki\u351?ini\u328? \u246?z z\u252?r\u253?ady, -\par
Jan ho\u351?y - k\u246?\u328?\u252?l kuwwaty,\par
Artsyn jomardy\u328? d\u246?wleti,\par
Muhannesde a\u351? bolmasyn.\par
\par
Bir y\u351?k d\u252?\u351?se adam serne,\par
Uky ga\u231?ar, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l urna,\par
Iki s\u246?\u253?g\u252?li bir-birne\par
\u221?akyn olsun, da\u351? bolmasyn.\par
\par
S\u246?z\u252?m a\u253?dylsa her \u231?aklar,\par
Akyly bolan ger\u231?ekler,\par
Bir i\u351? d\u252?\u351?ende go\u231?aklar,\par
I\u351? g\u246?rmedik \u253?a\u351? bolmasyn.\par
\par
Il i\u231?inde \u246?z\u252?n \u246?wer,\par
Dil dumany ba\u351?dan agar,\par
\u221?agyda nogsany deger,\par
Namartlar \u253?olda\u351? bolmasyn.\par
\par
S\u246?zle, he\u253?, a\u351?ygym, s\u246?zle,\par
Gel, ky\u253?amat i\u351?in g\u246?zle,\par
Magtymguly, syry\u328? gizle,\par
Her namarda pa\u351? bolmasyn.\par
\par
DON GEREK\par
Ne bela sen adamzat,\par
\u199?yplak dogdu\u328?, don gerek.\par
Ak s\u252?\u253?t emdi\u328?, ulaldy\u328?,\par
Agla\u253?yr sen, nan gerek.\par
\par
