\u221?ognalar bili\u328?, bendi\u328?,\par
On b\u228?\u351?de arzuwmendi\u328?,\par
Gyz gerek, juwan gerek.\par
\par
Juwan tapdy\u328? gu\u231?maga,\par
A\u253?\u351?-u e\u351?ret a\u231?maga,\par
Ondan so\u328? i\u253?p-i\u231?m\u228?ge,\par
Bir t\u252?kenmez nan gerek.\par
\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?n ynjydyp halky\u328?,\par
Ho\u351?nut etse\u328? \u246?z hulku\u328?,\par
Rum, Pere\u328? bolsa m\u252?lk\u252?\u328?,\par
Heniz \u171?azdyr\u187?, k\u228?n gerek.\par
\par
\u221?atsa\u328? d\u252?\u351?ekde bimar,\par
Yssyg etmez mal-u k\u228?r,\par
Zer d\u246?kse\u328? harwar-harwar,\par
G\u246?ze ilmez, jan gerek.\par
\par
Doga bilen \u228?r g\u246?g\u228?r,\par
\u221?agmyr bilen \u253?er g\u246?g\u228?r,\par
\u196?r oldur - alky\u351? alar,\par
\u221?erlere baran gerek.\par
\par
Ajal geler o\u253?da \u253?ok,\par
G\u246?rmek \u253?ylda, a\u253?da \u253?ok,\par
Hi\u231? bir zatdan pe\u253?da \u253?ok,\par
Bir nury-iman gerek.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?zle\u253?en,\par
Ni\u231?e mahfy gizle\u253?en,\par
Bir many p\u228?him e\u253?le\u253?en,\par
Akylly \u253?aran gerek.\par
\par
JO\u350?A \u221?ETDI\u327?\par
Bir g\u252?n ata\u328? y\u351?k etdi,\par
Sulbundan jo\u351?a \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
Owwal suwdu\u328?, gan boldu\u328?,\par
Gandan so\u328? l\u228?\u351?e \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
H\u246?km e\u253?ledi ol Huda\u253?,\par
Dokuz sagat, dokuz a\u253?,\par
\u221?edi endam ja\u253?ba-ja\u253?,\par
S\u252?\u328?\u328?e ula\u351?a \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
G\u252?w\u351? berdi, dahan berdi,\par
Dahana zyban berdi,\par
Akyl berdi, jan berdi,\par
G\u246?z berdi, ga\u351?a \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
\u221?a\u351?dy\u328?, ele ula\u351?dy\u328?,\par
\u221?\u246?rip, \u253?ola ula\u351?dy\u328?,\par
S\u246?zl\u228?p, tile ula\u351?dy\u328?,\par
Nan i\u253?di\u328?, a\u351?a \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
\u221?edi\u328?de mekdep g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?,\par
Okady\u328?, \u253?olu\u328? bildi\u328? ,\par
Gyz bile bazy gurdu\u328?,\par
T\u228? on d\u246?rt \u253?a\u351?a \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
Hak berdigin i\u253?p-i\u231?di\u328?,\par
Her \u253?ola bir ba\u351? go\u351?du\u328?,\par
Mahbup bile s\u246?\u253?\u252?\u351?di\u328?,\par
Bile \u231?ola\u351?a \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
\u221?igrim t\u246?rt \u253?a\u351?a geldi\u328?,\par
\u221?igit bolup, sen \u253?eldi\u328?,\par
At m\u252?nd\u252?\u328?, gyly\u231? aldy\u328?,\par
Je\u328?e-s\u246?we\u351?e \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
Otuzy\u328?da \u253?eri\u328?den,\par
Duman gitmez seri\u328?den,\par
\u221?igitligi\u328? zorundan,\par
Gezdi\u328? toma\u351?a \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
S\u252?rd\u252?\u328?, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni s\u252?rd\u252?\u328?,\par
Ahyr wepasyn g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?,\par
Kyrky\u328?a gadam urdu\u328?,\par
K\u228?mil sen, hu\u351?a \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
Bar almady\u328? bagy\u328?dan,\par
Hazan urdy tagy\u328?dan,\par
Elli, sakal agy\u328?dan,\par
Utan, bir \u253?a\u351?a \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
Altmy\u351?a \u253?a\u351? \u253?etirdi\u328?,\par
Ba\u351?y\u328? gama batyrdy\u328?,\par
Ho\u351? g\u252?nleri\u328? \u246?t\u252?rdi\u328?,\par
\u221?azy\u328? \u253?ok, gy\u351?a \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
\u221?etmi\u351?de \u171?Hak!\u187? di\u253?p galdy\u328?,\par
Kuwwaty\u328? \u253?ok, \u253?ykyldy\u328?,\par
Gojaldy\u328?, i\u351?den galdy\u328?,\par
S\u246?\u253?le, ne pi\u351?\u228? \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
Segsene \u253?eti\u351?se sal,\par
Ni\u231?ik ge\u231?er be\u253?le hal,\par
\u214?tdi gyzgynly mahal,\par
Oraksyz ho\u351?a \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
Togsanda \u253?a\u328?ylar s\u246?z,\par
Gara bolup g\u246?rner boz,\par
Gow\u351?ar s\u252?\u253?ek, alar g\u246?z,\par
\u221?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? endi\u351?\u228? \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
Magtymguly oturdy\u328?,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328? gapyl \u246?t\u252?rdi\u328?,\par
Hak \u231?\u252?n ne i\u351? bitirdi\u328?,\par
Eger \u253?\u252?z \u253?a\u351?a \u253?etdi\u328?.\par
\par
GARRYLYKDYR \u221?ARANLAR\par
\u221?igitligi\u328? zory gitdi bili\u328?den,\par
Dert \u253?amany garrylykdyr \u253?aranlar.\par
Alajy \u253?ok onu\u328? ga\u253?ry \u246?l\u252?mden,\par
Dert \u253?amany garrylykdyr \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Hassalar gutular, garry gutulmaz,\par
Bu derde hi\u231? kimden \u231?\u228?re \u253?etilmez,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l gu\u351?y u\u231?ar gider tutulmaz,\par
Dert \u253?amany garrylykdyr \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Hi\u231? tagam i\u253?m\u228?ge di\u351?leri batmaz,\par
Uzakdan g\u246?zlese g\u246?zleri \u253?etmez,\par
Ogul gyz s\u246?z\u252?ne hi\u231? gulak asmaz,\par
Dert \u253?amany garrylykdyr \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
\u221?etmi\u351?i\u328? \u246?\u253?\u252?ne girende \u253?a\u351?y,\par
Yranyp bir \u253?erde durma\u253?dyr ba\u351?y,\par
\u199?\u246?rek \u231?e\u253?ne\u253? bilmez talhandyr a\u351?y,\par
Dert \u253?amany garrylykdyr \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Di\u253?se\u328? s\u246?z e\u351?itmez, gulak ker bolar,\par
Oturyp-turmagy derdeser bolar,\par
S\u252?\u253?ekler syzla\u351?yp derbeder bolar,\par
Dert \u253?amany garrylykdyr \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Agzyny g\u246?zlese\u328? bir di\u351?i bolmaz,\par
D\u252?\u351?ek, \u253?assyk bilen hi\u231? i\u351?i bolmaz,\par
\u221?anynda gadyrdan de\u328?-du\u351?y bolmaz,\par
Dert \u253?amany garrylykdyr \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Ogul-gyz, geline \u253?igrenji bolar,\par
Olar mydam s\u246?z\u252?\u328? g\u246?rginji bolar,\par
\u221?yrtyk-\u253?irik d\u252?\u351?ek \u246?rt\u252?nji bolar,\par
Dert \u253?amany garrylykdyr \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Gitdi tamam gadyr bilen de\u328?-du\u351?u\u328?,\par
Imdi saglyk \u246?tdi, dertdir \u253?olda\u351?y\u328?,\par
Bardyk\u231?a \u253?yl-\u253?yldan m\u246?w\u231? urar gy\u351?y\u328?,\par
Dert \u253?amany garrylykdyr \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Galan ga\u231?an bolsa \u246?\u328?\u252?ne bi\u253?rler,\par
Yssy-\u253?yly bolmaz \u351?uny i\u253? di\u253?rler,\par
Her kime s\u246?zlese gepleme di\u253?rler,\par
Dert \u253?amany garrylykdyr \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Tende kuwwat galmaz, \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328?de g\u246?rk\u252?\u328?,\par
Oturyp-turmaga \u253?eti\u351?mez erki\u328?,\par
A\u351? i\u231?ilip bolmaz, s\u252?\u253?ekde \u246?rki\u252?\u328?,\par
Dert \u253?amany garrylykdyr \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar garrama\u328? beter,\par
\u221?etmi\u351?i\u328?, segseni\u328? arasy \u253?eter,\par
\u214?z oglanlary gelip depel\u228?p \u246?ter,\par
Dert \u253?amany garrylykdyr \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
S\u214?\u221?M\u220?\u350?EM SENI\par
\u221?a habyp, Hak resuly sen,\par
\u199?yn jandan s\u246?\u253?m\u252?\u351?em seni.\par
Derw\u252?\u351?ler gadyr gijesin,\par
S\u246?\u253?en dek s\u246?\u253?m\u252?\u351?em seni.\par
\par
