Misli Ybra\u253?ym Sarany\par
S\u246?\u253?en dek s\u246?\u253?m\u252?\u351?em seni.\par
\par
\u221?akup \u253?urt etdi Kengany,\par
Ogludyr M\u252?s\u252?r soltany,\par
Misli \u221?usup Z\u252?le\u253?hany\par
S\u246?\u253?en dek s\u246?\u253?m\u252?\u351?em seni.\par
\par
\u221?alan\u231?yny tutdy ady,\par
Olardyr y\u351?ky\u328? bin\u253?ady,\par
Mejnun Le\u253?li perizady\par
S\u246?\u253?en dek s\u246?\u253?m\u252?\u351?em seni.\par
\par
Dildi daglary\u328? zirini,\par
Tapma\u253?yn biri-birini,\par
A\u351?yk Perhat ol \u350?irini\par
S\u246?\u253?en dek s\u246?\u253?m\u252?\u351?em seni.\par
\par
Egdi meni d\u252?n\u253?e maly,\par
Bolmady y\u351?kym kemaly.\par
Se\u253?pelmelek Mahjemaly\par
S\u246?\u253?en dek s\u246?\u253?m\u252?\u351?em seni.\par
\par
Basdy muhabbet ny\u351?any.\par
Ke\u351?t e\u253?ledi \u231?ar k\u246?\u351?\u228?ni,\par
\u221?emende Warka G\u252?l\u351?any\par
S\u246?\u253?en dek s\u246?\u253?m\u252?\u351?em seni.\par
\par
Gitdi elden ygty\u253?ary,\par
Galmady namysy-ary.\par
A\u351?yk Nowruz, G\u252?l-Ferhary\par
S\u246?\u253?en dek s\u246?\u253?m\u252?\u351?em seni.\par
\par
