A\u351?yk Garyp \u350?asenemi\par
S\u246?\u253?en dek s\u246?\u253?m\u252?\u351?em seni.\par
\par
Magtymguly, d\u252?n\u253?\u228? pany,\par
\u214?t\u252?pdir R\u252?stemler, kany?\par
A\u253?, G\u252?n-u Zemin, asmany\par
S\u246?\u253?en dek s\u246?\u253?m\u252?\u351?em seni.\par
\par
\u350?OL M\u196?HRIBANYM GELDI\par
Dogry magryp tarapdan,\par
\u350?ol m\u228?hribanym geldi.\par
\u221?\u252?z i\u351?we\u253?i-n\u228?z birlen,\par
Jany-jananym geldi.\par
\par
Men \u253?ary\u328? serneguny,\par
Bagla\u253?yr bu u\u253?uny,\par
D\u246?kdi jigerden huny,\par
\u350?ahy-soltanym geldi.\par
\par
\u196?leme \u351?ahy-perwer,\par
Boldy ymmata serwer,\par
Jahan boldy m\u252?newwer,\par
D\u252?rri-galtanym geldi.\par
\par
Kamaty serwi, tuba,\par
Kaddy, \u246?zi m\u252?nteha,\par
Wejhi-ro\u253?y wazzuha,\par
Serwi-rowanym geldi.\par
\par
Nikabyn \u253?\u252?ze salan,\par
\u221?\u252?z g\u246?rsetip, jan alan,\par
Mun\u231?a arzuwlap, \u253?anan,\par
Ahy-pyganym geldi.\par
\par
Melek permana bakan,\par
Sidreti s\u228?hra \u231?ykan\par
Ah ursa, Ar\u351?y \u253?akan,\par
Sahypkyranym geldi.\par
\par
Magtymguly binowa,\par
G\u246?zlemez senden sewa,\par
Ymmatym di\u253?p, da\u253?yma\par
Hezret i\u351?anym geldi.\par
\par
ROWAN OLDY\par
Mekgeden \u231?ykdy bir g\u246?zel,\par
Medin\u228?ge rowan oldy.\par
G\u246?ren t\u228?\u231? etdi serine,\par
G\u246?rm\u228?ni\u328? bagry gan oldy.\par
\par
Hakdan o\u328?a indi Kelam,\par
Ady \u351?am\u231?yragyl-yslam,\par
Mutyg oldy j\u252?mle \u228?lem,\par
\u350?e\u253?le sahyp zaman oldy.\par
\par
Dosta \u253?etdi bara-bara,\par
\u221?edi g\u246?gi \u253?ara-yara,\par
Her kim m\u252?\u328?k\u252?rdir ol \u228?re,\par
Kapyrdyr, biiman oldy.\par
\par
Gol g\u246?terip, Resul aglar,\par
Gow\u351?a\u351?dy gun\u231?alar, baglar,\par
Bedri\u328? uru\u351?ynda daglar\par
\u221?edi a\u253?lap duman oldy.\par
\par
Sap urdy batyr be\u328?\u328?iler,\par
D\u246?w\u252?\u351?e \u231?ykdy ze\u328?\u328?iler,\par
Gana batdy \u252?ze\u328?\u328?iler,\par
Alyny\u328? desti gan oldy.\par
\par
Mukatyl etmedi te\u351?w\u252?\u351?,\par
Aly bilen saldy d\u246?w\u252?\u351?,\par
Toprak, demir, polat, k\u252?m\u252?\u351?,\par
Galalary we\u253?ran oldy.\par
\par
Magtymguly, Rumystana,\par
\u199?aldy gyly\u231? Hindistana,\par
Badah\u351?ana, T\u252?rk\u252?stana,\par
\u221?edi yklyma han oldy.\par
\par
TUMAR G\u214?RD\u220?M\par
Hakykat depderin a\u231?dym,\par
Bir \u253?azylan tumar g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
Bu \u253?urtdan ol \u253?urda g\u246?\u231?d\u252?m,\par
\u221?urduny ygtybar g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
\par
Bir \u246?\u253?de bar on iki jan,\par
Ho\u351? gelip siz, eziz myhman,\par
Bir suprada d\u246?rt yssy nan,\par
\u220?st\u252?nde \u253?edi nar g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
\par
Mustapaga indi warak,\par
M\u252?\u328?k\u252?r bolan \u8722? dinden yrak,\par
Bir \u246?\u253?de bar onki \u231?yrag,\par
D\u246?rt ma\u351?al, bir \u253?anar g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? gyragynda,\par
\u350?ejerler bitmi\u351? bagynda\par
B\u228?\u351? alma bar pudagynda,\par
Asylmy\u351?, berkarar g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ne pikri\u328? bar,\par
\u214?m\u252?rden ge\u231?di rozyg\u228?r,\par
\u221?etmi\u351? iki s\u252?ri dowar,\par
\u199?opany bir bakar g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
\par
\u221?\u220?Z BOLAR\par
Bolsa \u246?zi mert \u253?igit,\par
Her bir ja\u253?da \u253?\u252?z bolar.\par
Namartlar bilse\u328?iz \u8213? it,\par
Her kese \u253?\u252?z-g\u246?z bolar.\par
\par
Ne g\u252?n\u228? bar Idrisde?\par
Otdan \u253?egdir heris-de,\par
Saz bolmagan me\u253?lisde\par
G\u252?rle\u351?se\u328? hem saz bolar.\par
\par
Men ykbalym unudam,\par
Panydan aldym gadam,\par
\u214?z\u252?n o\u328?armaz adam\par
Her \u253?etene s\u246?z bolar.\par
\par
Ne ga\u253?ratly bu daglar,\par
Bihasap aw-awlaglar,\par
K\u246?le giripdir zaglar,\par
Mysaly bir gaz bolar.\par
\par
Namartlardan \u8213? \u253?aman \u253?eg,\par
Her zulumdan \u8213? pe\u253?man \u253?eg,\par
Ni\u231?e gyzdan juwan \u253?eg,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y, \u253?aman gyz bolar.\par
\par
Ozal ba\u351?dan bermese,\par
Ga\u253?gy-hasrat g\u246?rmese,\par
Pelek tygyn urmasa,\par
Gy\u351? paslymyz \u253?az bolar.\par
\par
Hak bermese ozalda,\par
Bir zulumdyr ezelde,\par
Ajap n\u228?rse g\u246?zelde\par
Ga\u351?yn kaksa, n\u228?z bolar.\par
\par
Her g\u252?ne \u351?\u252?kr e\u253?lese\u328?,\par
Elemi\u328? zikr e\u253?lese\u328?,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni pikr e\u253?lese\u328?,\par
Te\u351?w\u252?\u351?i\u328?, g\u246?r, baz bolar.\par
\par
Bir dertlini\u328? \u253?anynda,\par
Bolsa\u328? adam sanynda,\par
A\u351?yklary\u328? janynda\par
Baky s\u246?nmez k\u246?z bolar.\par
\par
Isl\u228?nin bu g\u246?z g\u246?rse,\par
G\u246?wn\u228?nin bu dil sorsa,\par
Bir \u253?igdi\u328? gu\u351?y tursa,\par
Her bir s\u246?zi d\u252?z bolar.\par
\par
Di\u253?erler, ahyrzaman,\par
Ata\u351?-suzandan \u253?aman,\par
Bawer kylmagyl g\u252?man,\par
Be\u253?le te\u351?w\u252?\u351? tiz bolar.\par
\par
Gymmaty bar zenany\u328?,\par
Taryp kylsam bar zadyn,\par
Badam gabak jenany\u328?\par
Bo\u253?lary deraz bolar.\par
\par
Ni\u231?e isl\u228?r uly mal,\par
Ni\u231?eler etmez hy\u253?al,\par
Pelegi kylsa\u328? ahmal,\par
Asmanda perwaz bolar.\par
\par
Pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228? gezendi\u328?,\par
Sen elemden bezendi\u328?,\par
Akylsyz, \u253?a\u328?ra \u253?igdi\u328?\par
Ilde gadry az bolar.\par
\par
Kimler zer lybas ge\u253?se,\par
En\u231?eler z\u228?her i\u253?se,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y dost bir s\u246?z di\u253?se,\par
Jany\u328? i\u231?re duz bolar.\par
\par
Pany te\u351?w\u252?\u351?e go\u253?ar,\par
Kimler pynhanyn a\u253?ar,\par
Kempir \u246?z\u252?n gyz sa\u253?ar,\par
Emma go\u253?ny buz bolar.\par
\par
Muhammedi\u328? ymmaty,\par
Bo\u253?nundadyr s\u252?nneti,\par
Her g\u246?zeli\u328? gymmaty\par
\u221?\u252?zde imti\u253?az bolar.\par
\par
Derdim kylynsa ahsan,\par
\u221?\u252?rekde biter bossan,\par
Kyldygym ajap dessan\par
Mejnuna ny\u253?az bolar.\par
\par
Ne i\u351? g\u246?rdi g\u246?zlerim,\par
Gabahatdyr \u253?\u252?zlerim,\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?zlerim\par
Saza go\u351?sa\u328?, uz bolar.\par
\par
BEHEM EDER\par
Kim\u253?any topraga \u231?alsa\u328?,\par
Toprakdan zer behem eder.\par
Her ne ki \u253?ere seper sen,\par
Sepdigi\u328? \u253?er behem eder.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman bolmaz m\u228?lim,\par
Her kim \u246?z bilenne alym,\par
Jahana ot \u231?akdy zalym,\par
\u221?yl-\u253?yldan \u351?er behem eder.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y \u253?igit \u253?ol \u253?itirmez,\par
J\u228?ht kysmatdan k\u246?p getirmez,\par
M\u252?\u328? ga\u253?gy bir i\u351? bitirmez,\par
T\u246?wekgel - ner behem eder.\par
\par
Berimi\u328? bolsa her kanda,\par
G\u246?ren sa\u328?a bolar bende,\par
Beth\u252?\u253?\u252?\u328? - du\u351?man \u253?anynda,\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylyk - \u253?ar behem eder.\par
\par
Magtymguly s\u246?\u253?l\u228?r s\u246?zde,\par
Ga\u253?rat - \u246?tde, ha\u253?a \u8722? g\u246?zde,\par
\u221?yl-\u253?yldan bu \u253?urdumyzda\par
Zulm artyp, zor behem eder.\par
\par
BIBAT G\u214?R\u220?NER\par
\u221?aranlar, pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328?,\par
Ahyry bibat g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
Jan gu\u351?uny aldap tutar,\par
\u350?um pelek sa\u253?\u253?at g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Aldagyna d\u252?\u351?me bu g\u252?n,\par
K\u246?k\u252?\u328? keser bogun-bogun,\par
G\u246?r, loly d\u252?n\u253?\u228? dostlugyn,\par
G\u252?nbe-g\u252?nden \u253?at g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Pelek bolmaz mi\u253?esseri\u328? -\par
Ni\u231?e \u253?erde derdeseri\u328?,\par
G\u246?r, ogulsyz bendeleri\u328?,\par
\u221?urdy \u253?ok, berbat g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
G\u246?r\u252?nse \u253?ag\u351?y ykbaly,\par
G\u252?n-g\u252?nden ho\u351? \u246?ter haly,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igidi\u328? pis a\u253?aly,\par
Janyna jellat g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y \u253?ary\u328? go\u253?ny mata,\par
Synasy me\u328?z\u228?r jennete,\par
G\u246?zel g\u246?rmegen s\u246?l\u252?te,\par
G\u246?ze perizat g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Dilde \u231?e\u253?n\u228?r \u351?eker-kandy,\par
Hi\u231? kim kabul etmez pendi,\par
Gara gargany\u328? perzendi,\par
\u214?z\u252?ne surat g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
\u221?ara\u351?ar tirki\u351?-hatary,\par
Hatarynda esrik neri,\par
Bir gedany\u328? m\u252?nen hary,\par
Teblesinde at g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
S\u246?we\u351?de gerek ussatlar,\par
\u350?ir \u253?\u252?rekli, algyr gurtlar.\par
\u221?agy g\u246?rende, namartlar,\par
N\u228?\u231?aglap, arwat g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Magtymguly di\u253?r, bu demde,\par
Bardyr umydym keremde,\par
Rozy etse ahyr demde,\par
Imanym myrat g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
BA\u350? \u220?ST\u220?NDE\par
Namart kimdir, biler bolsa\u328?,\par
Ne di\u253?se\u328?, di\u253?r \u171?Ba\u351? \u252?st\u252?nde!\u187?\par
Azma\u253?y\u351?yn kylar bolsa\u328?,\par
Hi\u231? tapylmaz i\u351? \u252?st\u252?nde.\par
\par
Murtun towlap, her\u253?an tartar,\par
Ha\u253?baty pele\u328?den artar,\par
G\u246?k dek g\u252?rl\u228?r, damak \u253?yrtar,\par
H\u228?zir bolan a\u351? \u252?st\u252?nde.\par
\par
A\u351? \u252?st\u252?nde alp dek arlar,\par
\u221?ersiz-\u253?ere har dek harlar,\par
Her tilki bir \u351?ir dek g\u252?rl\u228?r.\par
Myrdar \u246?len l\u228?\u351? \u252?st\u252?nde.\par
\par
\u199?\u246?l \u253?erde g\u246?wre galdyrma,\par
Ol-da ho\u351?dur, syr bildirme,\par
Lap edip dahan doldurma,\par
Je\u328? nan degil di\u351? \u252?st\u252?nde.\par
\par
Di\u253?seler: \u171?Atlan-ha, atlan!\u187?\par
S\u252?\u328?k \u231?en\u228?p i\u253?r arda syrtlan,\par
\u221?ow g\u252?ni ga\u253?rata gatlan,\par
Lagnat go\u253?ma ri\u351? \u252?st\u252?nde.\par
\par
Ynsabyn elden byrakmaz,\par
M\u228?lim, adamlykdan \u231?ykmaz,\par
Bu s\u246?z\u252?m ha\u253?wana \u253?okmaz,\par
Adam saklar g\u252?w\u351? \u252?st\u252?nde.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?we\u351? bolar,\par
\u221?igidi\u328? syry pa\u351? bolar,\par
\u221?a ba\u351? berer, \u253?a ba\u351? alar,\par
Go\u231?aklar \u253?olda\u351? \u252?st\u252?nde.\par
\par
ATY GEREK\par
At gazanar go\u231? \u253?igidi\u328?,\par
Owwal bedew aty gerek.\par
Gelene gar\u351?y durmaga,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y muhabbeti gerek.\par
\par
Mert gerek jepa \u231?ekm\u228?ge,\par
At gerek zereh s\u246?km\u228?ge,\par
Supra \u253?a\u253?yp, nan d\u246?km\u228?ge\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?ni\u328? h\u252?mmeti gerek.\par
\par
El g\u246?tergin ham hy\u253?aldan,\par
Sa\u328?a yssyg \u253?okdur maldan,\par
Rozyg\u228?r ge\u231?se halaldan,\par
Aryplar s\u246?hbeti gerek.\par
\par
\u221?\u246?rise\u328? gulluk kylmaga,\par
Pygamber \u253?olun bilm\u228?ge,\par
Derw\u252?\u351?ler k\u246?\u328?l\u252?n almaga\par
Elinde d\u246?wleti gerek.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bir geda\u253?dyr,\par
Bar\u231?any saklan Huda\u253?dyr,\par
Eger misgin, eger ba\u253?dyr -\par
Gelene hyzmaty gerek.\par
\par
ATA ME\u327?Z\u196?R\par
Oba ujundaky depe,\par
E\u253?erlenen ata me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
Akylsyz \u228?rler zer bilen,\par
\u221?azylan bet hata me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? bir d\u252?\u253?ps\u252?z der\u253?a,\par
Gark eder, bolma biperwa,\par
Magrur bolma maly-d\u252?n\u253?\u228?,\par
Gezekli nobata me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Garda\u351?syza kuwwat \u253?okdur,\par
Ogulsyza d\u246?wlet \u253?okdur,\par
A\u253?alsyza e\u351?ret \u253?okdur,\par
Ho\u351? g\u252?ni hasrata me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
\u221?amandan \u253?ag\u351?y set bolmaz,\par
Asly \u253?ag\u351?ydan bet bolmaz,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?likden d\u246?wlet bolmaz,\par
Ogul \u231?yn d\u246?wlete me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Bur\u231? bilen duz t\u228?ze \u253?ara,\par
Awy gatar rozyg\u228?re,\par
\u221?aman hatyn \u253?ag\u351?y \u228?re,\par
Sowulmaz t\u246?hmete me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
\u221?atan \u253?eri \u253?ylan go\u253?ny,\par
Asylany iti\u328? bo\u253?ny,\par
Pis \u228?ri\u328? \u253?ag\u351?y hatyny,\par
D\u252?rri-bigymmata me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
Magtymguly, namyradam,\par
Iller ho\u351?dur, men n\u228?\u351?adam,\par
S\u246?z manysyn a\u328?maz adam,\par
Bir gu\u253?ruksyz ite me\u328?z\u228?r.\par
\par
AGLARYN\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, \u246?mr\u252?mden,\par
Ge\u231?di di\u253?ip aglaryn.\par
Gitdi aklym ornundan,\par
\u199?a\u351?dy di\u253?ip aglaryn.\par
\par
Giden d\u246?nmez \u253?olundan,\par
D\u252?\u351?mez \u253?aman p\u228?linden,\par
Di\u253?anat halk elinden,\par
U\u231?dy di\u253?ip aglaryn.\par
\par
H\u228?zir bizi\u328? zamanda,\par
\u221?aman s\u246?zler zybanda,\par
Zulum i\u351?ler jahanda,\par
Jo\u351?dy di\u253?ip aglaryn.\par
\par
Bu e\u253?\u253?amda betk\u228?rler,\par
\u221?\u252?z dil bile aldarlar,\par
Hany ni\u231?e dildarlar,\par
Ge\u231?di di\u253?ip aglaryn.\par
\par
Ni\u231?e sada de\u328?-du\u351?lar,\par
\u350?e\u253?tan biligin ba\u351?lar,\par
\u221?\u252?z \u231?\u246?w\u252?rip garda\u351?lar,\par
Ga\u231?dy di\u253?ip aglaryn.\par
\par
G\u246?r\u252?\u328? pelegi\u328? o\u253?nun,\par
\u220?zer alymy\u328? bo\u253?nun,\par
Ni\u231?e janlar \u253?er go\u253?nun,\par
Gu\u231?dy di\u253?ip aglaryn.\par
\par
Magtymguly di\u253?r merde,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? bentdir, ten perde,\par
Bir ba\u351?ym sansyz derde,\par
Du\u351?dy di\u253?ip aglaryn.\par
\par
AT\u199?A BOLMAZ\par
Hary\u328? i\u351?i hardyr, dostlar,\par
M\u252?\u328? magtasa\u328?, at\u231?a bolmaz.\par
Bedasyla emel \u253?etse,\par
Bili\u328?, asylzat\u231?a bolmaz.\par
\par
Pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge ynanma\u328?,\par
Altyn-k\u252?m\u252?\u351?e guwanma\u328?,\par
Gi\u253?ewlere k\u246?\u328?\u252?l berm\u228?\u328?,\par
Bir dogan z\u252?r\u253?at\u231?a bolmaz.\par
\par
K\u246?p \u253?ollary g\u246?rse g\u246?z\u252?\u328?,\par
Her manydan bilse\u328? \u246?z\u252?\u328?,\par
Bir nadana a\u253?dan s\u246?z\u252?\u328?,\par
\u214?s\u252?p giden bat\u231?a bolmaz.\par
\par
Ba\u351?y\u328? \u253?assyga \u253?etende,\par
Sabr-u karar bolmaz sende,\par
G\u252?\u253?j\u252?\u328?-kuwwaty\u328? gidende,\par
Ogul-gyzy\u328? \u253?at\u231?a bolmaz.\par
\par
Magtymguly ajap \u231?aglar,\par
Kimse g\u252?ler, kimse aglar,\par
D\u252?rli miwe beren baglar,\par
Sowular, jennet\u231?e bolmaz.\par
\par
K\u214?\u221?M\u196?N \u221?IGIDE\par
Ulalanda i\u351? ho\u351? gelmez,\par
\u221?a\u351?lykda k\u246?\u253?m\u228?n \u253?igide.\par
D\u246?wlet gelse, \u246?z\u252?n bilmez,\par
Dogaly do\u253?man \u253?igide.\par
\par
\u221?amana \u246?w\u252?t hebesdir,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y \u228?re bir s\u246?z besdir,\par
\u221?\u246?ri\u351?ini \u253?al\u328?y\u351? basdyr,\par
\u221?a\u328?y don ge\u253?m\u228?n \u253?igide.\par
\par
J\u252?pbe, j\u246?w\u351?en, zereh-sowut,\par
Keserli gyly\u231?, arap at,\par
S\u246?we\u351? g\u252?ni gider u\u253?at\par
Ga\u253?raty bolman \u253?igide.\par
\par
\u199?opan adam \u231?oka bolmaz,\par
Ala garga oka gelmez,\par
K\u246?p \u253?ygylsa, terhos almaz,\par
A\u328?yrsy bolman \u253?igide.\par
\par
Gulluk \u253?etirgin jany\u328?dan,\par
A\u253?ama par\u231?a nany\u328?dan,\par
Ganly bolsa, ge\u231? gany\u328?dan,\par
Bir garyp myhman \u253?igide!\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de hi\u231? kim galmandyr,\par
Mal jana \u253?olda\u351? bolmandyr,\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? gelm\u228?ndir\par
Bir \u246?wlat galman \u253?igide.\par
\par
Almaza k\u252?m\u252?\u351? mis g\u246?rner,\par
Dula gyrnak t\u252?\u253?\u252?s g\u246?rner,\par
Perizat hatyn pis g\u246?rner\par
Bir hulky s\u246?\u253?m\u228?n \u253?igide.\par
\par
Mal d\u246?ner \u231?y\u253?an-\u231?irmege,\par
Durar et-gany\u328? sormaga,\par
Malyndan zekat berm\u228?ge,\par
G\u246?zleri gy\u253?man \u253?igide.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?oldan \u231?ykmaz,\par
\u221?amana \u253?ag\u351?y s\u246?z \u253?akmaz,\par
M\u252?\u328? s\u246?z a\u253?tsa\u328?, biri \u253?okmaz\par
Ta\u328?rysy gu\u253?man \u253?igide.\par
\par
K\u214?\u327?\u220?L JO\u350?UNDADYR\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l bir beden \u351?ahydyr,\par
Her s\u246?z k\u246?\u328?\u252?l jo\u351?undadyr.\par
\u221?edi yklymy\u328? tagtynda\par
Her biri bir i\u351?indedir.\par
\par
Daglary\u328? \u231?ykyp-inmesi,\par
\u199?ohlary\u328? g\u246?\u231?\u252?p-gonmasy,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? agyp-d\u246?nmesi,\par
Pelegi\u328? gerdi\u351?indedir.\par
\par
Kimdir bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de galan,\par
Ma\u328?a \u231?yndyr, size \u253?alan,\par
Bir akdyr, bir gara \u253?ylan -\par
S\u252?le\u253?many\u328? ga\u351?yndadyr.\par
\par
Degresi z\u252?merret da\u351?ly,\par
Ner babaly, kerk garda\u351?ly,\par
Altyn tagtly, almaz t\u228?\u231?li,\par
D\u246?w begleri da\u351?yndadyr.\par
\par
A\u253?lanar, ge\u231?er e\u253?\u253?amlar,\par
Gojalar gurlan e\u253?wanlar,\par
G\u252?ndiz \u253?ara a\u351?na janlar,\par
Gije \u253?atsa, d\u252?\u253?\u351?\u252?ndedir.\par
\par
\u220?\u231? essesi d\u228?li der\u253?a,\par
Bir esse \u253?erde m\u252?\u328? gowga,\par
Kim biler bu k\u246?ne d\u252?n\u253?\u228?,\par
\u221?a, Rep, ni\u231?e \u253?a\u351?yndadyr?!\par
\par
Magtymguly di\u253?r, hara\u253?dyr,\par
Ajal okdur, pelek \u253?a\u253?dyr,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? bir gahba hele\u253?dir,\par
Adamzady\u328? da\u351?yndadyr.\par
\par
N\u196?LER G\u214?R\u220?NER\par
Se\u253?l edeli\u328? bu jahana,\par
Jahanda n\u228?ler g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
Isgender, Jem\u351?it saldyran\par
Be\u253?ik binalar g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Bi\u351?eleri \u351?ir, pele\u328?li,\par
G\u252?lg\u252?zar, now\u231?a bele\u328?li,\par
G\u252?n d\u252?\u351?me\u253?en ter \u246?le\u328?li,\par
\u199?e\u351?meli zawlar g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
\u221?aradan bar etdi \u253?okdan,\par
Daglar d\u252?n\u253?\u228? s\u252?rer \u231?ohdan,\par
Sorsa\u328? habar berer Nuhdan,\par
Garrygan awlar g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
\u199?aglan, \u253?alan d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u231?aglan,\par
Ne g\u252?len galar, ne aglan.\par
Gar-\u253?agmyrlar, burjy baglan\par
Sapaly \u231?a\u253?lar g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Serinden dumany gitmez,\par
E\u253?\u253?am ge\u231?ip, \u253?ere batmaz,\par
Garryp galmaz, \u246?lmez, \u253?itmez,\par
Gorganly daglar g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Ne k\u252?lbe galar, ne \u231?eten,\par
Senemler se\u253?l edip \u246?ten,\par
Toty, bilbil mesgen tutan,\par
Howaly baglar g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Magtymguly, kim bar \u246?lmez?\par
Ajal do\u253?maz, zemin dolmaz,\par
Asman inmez, \u253?er \u231?\u246?wr\u252?lmez,\par
G\u252?n \u253?\u246?rir, A\u253?lar, g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
NE I\u350? GELER BA\u350?YMYZA\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, bilmek olmaz,\par
Ne i\u351? geler ba\u351?ymyza.\par
G\u246?r\u252?\u328? bu gahba pelegi,\par
Awy go\u351?ar a\u351?ymyza.\par
\par
Ajal geler, agzyn a\u231?ar,\par
In\u231?e bili zemin gu\u231?ar,\par
G\u252?l\u252?p gelen aglap ge\u231?er,\par
Rehm etmez g\u246?z \u253?a\u351?ymyza.\par
\par
Da\u253?anma\u328? bagta, ykbala,\par
Dolanar \u253?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? hy\u253?ala,\par
Ygtybar \u253?ok genje, mala,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? me\u328?z\u228?r d\u252?\u253?\u351?\u252?mize.\par
\par
Pelek bize egri bakyp,\par
El uzadyp, efsun okyp,\par
Orta \u253?erde d\u228?ne d\u246?k\u252?p,\par
Tor gurupdyr da\u351?ymyza.\par
\par
Magtymguly, barsa\u328? mundan,\par
Ha\u253?yr-\u351?er sorarlar senden,\par
\u350?irin jan a\u253?rylsa tenden,\par
Gum guwanar l\u228?\u351?imize.\par
\par
KARARSYZ \u196?RDEN\par
G\u246?rd\u252?k sa\u253?y k\u246?\u328?\u252?l sowar,\par
Sabyrsyz-kararsyz \u228?rden.\par
Yssy beren k\u246?pek \u253?egdir\par
U\u253?atsyz-ykrarsyz \u228?rden.\par
\par
A\u253?landyk\u231?a d\u246?wran, d\u246?w\u252?r,\par
Ykbaly\u328? \u253?\u252?z k\u246?\u253?e \u246?wir,\par
Dura-bara dosty sowyr,\par
Garyp galan barsyz \u228?rden.\par
\par
It zeri\u328? minnetin \u231?ekmez,\par
A\u328?lamaza s\u246?z\u252?m \u253?okmaz,\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?\u328? isl\u228?n i\u351?ler \u231?ykmaz,\par
Nan \u253?agysy - k\u228?rsiz \u228?rden.\par
\par
Her g\u246?z s\u228?herde bidardyr,\par
E\u253?esinden \u252?l\u252?\u351? bardyr,\par
Hak, pygamber, halk bizardyr\par
S\u246?zi ygtybarsyz \u228?rden.\par
\par
Magtymguly many sa\u231?ar,\par
Her kim s\u246?z lezzetin i\u231?er,\par
Bara-bara k\u246?\u328?\u252?l ge\u231?er,\par
T\u228?sibi \u253?ok, arsyz \u228?rden.\par
\par
IKI HELALAN\par
Namut eken nazarym,\par
G\u246?rdi iki helalan.\par
Janym rahatyn aldy,\par
Ondan husny-jemalan.\par
\par
Bar ondan \u228?g\u228? boldy,\par
\u214?z\u252?ni yrak saldy,\par
E\u351?k g\u246?zden rowan oldy,\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? degmi\u351? mugylan.\par
\par
Muttasyl e\u351?kim akyp,\par
Go\u253?maz g\u246?rere bakyp,\par
Nebsim h\u252?\u253?\u252?ne \u231?ekip,\par
Yhlasymdan \u253?alanan.\par
\par
R\u246?wende-\u253?u a\u253?ende,\par
Zyban seni gu\u253?ende,\par
Mydam olup ju\u253?ende,\par
Dil seni\u328? \u231?\u252?n nalanan.\par
\par
Y\u351?k hanjaryn e\u253?l\u228?p tiz,\par
Olup sen \u253?ene hunriz,\par
Tapman onu\u328?-le hergiz,\par
\u350?emme\u253?i ez wysalan.\par
\par
Pikr ile pany boldy,\par
Gurbatda ha\u253?ran galdy,\par
Y\u351?ky\u328? go\u351?uny saldy,\par
Aklym m\u252?lk\u252?ne talan.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u351?eb-u ruz,\par
Jan g\u252?daz-u \u253?\u252?rek suz,\par
Bul seb\u228?pden berf-u buz,\par
Bagra basar suw alan.\par
\par
IKI D\u220?N\u221?\u196?NI\u327? SOLTANY\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, musulmanlar,\par
Iki d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? soltany.\par
Rozy-ezelde \u253?aratdy,\par
Resul jesedinde jany.\par
\par
\u221?erde Musany\u328? Turundan,\par
G\u246?kde behi\u351?di\u328? h\u252?\u253?r\u252?nden,\par
\u221?aratdy Resul nurundan,\par
A\u253?, G\u252?ni, \u221?eri, Asmany.\par
\par
Arzuw e\u253?l\u228?p g\u252?l ruhsary\u328?,\par
Gezdim dagynda ebrary\u328?,\par
Soragyny salyp \u253?ary\u328?,\par
Ke\u351?t etdi k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni.\par
\par
Aklym ha\u253?ran bolup \u231?a\u351?dym,\par
Ahyr bir \u228?re sata\u351?dym,\par
Altmy\u351? alty dagdan a\u351?dym,\par
Ge\u231?dim on iki der\u253?any.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bikarar sen,\par
Bu ne otdyr, sen \u253?anar sen,\par
Bar\u231?a zatdan bikenar sen,\par
Bilmez sen sud-u zy\u253?any.\par
\par
ILI G\u214?ZL\u196?R\par
Ilinden a\u253?ra d\u252?\u351?en -\par
Ah urar, ili g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\u221?olundan a\u253?ra d\u252?\u351?en -\par
J\u228?ht edip, \u253?oly g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
G\u246?kde pelek gerdandyr,\par
Halk \u253?erde sergerdandyr,\par
Ne bazyg\u228?r jahandyr,\par
G\u246?z a\u231?an maly g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
Kimlerde altyn t\u228?\u231?dir,\par
Kimler sa\u253?yl, m\u228?t\u228?\u231?dir,\par
Kimler d\u252?\u253?pden galla\u231?dyr,\par
Kim par\u231?a, haly g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
Kim nan tapmaz i\u253?m\u228?ge,\par
Kim \u253?er tapmaz go\u253?maga,\par
Kim don tapmaz ge\u253?m\u228?ge,\par
Kim tirme \u351?aly g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
Bu jahan bir pu\u351?tadyr,\par
Kim zinde, kim k\u252?\u351?tedir,\par
Her bende bir i\u351?dedir,\par
Her kim bir haly g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
He\u328?\u328?am uzyn, \u246?m\u252?r az,\par
\u199?ahar pasla ba\u351?dyr \u253?az,\par
G\u246?kde ganat \u253?a\u253?an gaz -\par
G\u246?zleri k\u246?li g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
Magtymguly, hu\u351? e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Gezgin did\u228?\u328? \u253?a\u351? e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
D\u228?li k\u246?\u328?\u252?l jo\u351? e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
\u221?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? hy\u253?aly g\u246?zl\u228?r.\par
\par
I\u199?EN \u221?ALYDYR\par
\u221?aman \u253?ag\u351?a \u253?olda\u351? bolsa,\par
Awulyk i\u231?en \u253?alydyr,\par
A\u253?ryla bilse awusy,\par
I\u231?inden \u246?\u231?en \u253?alydyr.\par
\par
Adam \u351?erm etmez ri\u351?inden,\par
Gorkar \u253?atanda d\u252?\u253?\u351?\u252?nden\par
E\u253?\u253?ama baksam, i\u351?inden\par
Bu k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m ge\u231?en \u253?alydyr.\par
\par
Bedasyl ykbaly \u253?\u246?rmek,\par
\u214?\u253?s\u252?z eline mal girmek,\par
Akmaga syry\u328?y bermek -\par
\u214?z a\u253?by\u328? a\u231?an \u253?alydyr.\par
\par
\u214?tdi \u246?mr\u252?\u328? d\u252?n\u253?\u228? se\u253?li\u328?,\par
Hak \u253?oluna bagla bili\u328?,\par
Agzy ala bolan ili\u328?,\par
D\u246?wleti ga\u231?an \u253?alydyr.\par
\par
Gep a\u328?yp, g\u246?rende gizl\u228?n,\par
Akyldyr - i\u351? so\u328?un g\u246?zl\u228?n,\par
Gepin tapyp, \u253?ag\u351?y s\u246?zl\u228?n,\par
Misli d\u252?r sa\u231?an \u253?alydyr.\par
\par
\u196?rden gitse ygtybarlar,\par
Sowar ondan dost-u \u253?arlar,\par
H\u252?n\u228?rli, ykbally \u228?rler,\par
Mal-u pul u\u231?an \u253?alydyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, yllatly g\u246?z,\par
Haraba d\u246?ner degse duz,\par
M\u228?rekede bir ja\u253?syz s\u246?z,\par
\u199?ermenip ... \u253?alydyr.\par
\par
HA\u221?RANDADYR-HA\u221?RANDA\par
A\u351?yklar Hak y\u351?kynda,\par
Ha\u253?randadyr-ha\u253?randa.\par
G\u246?zler zagyf yzynda,\par
Gir\u253?andadyr-gir\u253?anda.\par
\par
Kyldy o\u328?a Hak rehmet,\par
Nury-tejelli gudrat,\par
Hyrka ge\u253?en Hoja Ahmet,\par
Sa\u253?ramdadyr-Sa\u253?ramda.\par
\par
\u221?erden \u231?ykan aga\u231?lar,\par
Dili senaly gu\u351?lar,\par
Suhan s\u246?\u253?en derw\u252?\u351?ler,\par
D\u246?wrandadyr-d\u246?wranda.\par
\par
A\u253?yl, a\u351?ygym, a\u253?yl,\par
Mejnun bol, halka \u253?a\u253?yl,\par
Halyl ogly Ysma\u253?yl,\par
Gurbandadyr-gurbanda.\par
\par
Tur dagynda duranlar,\par
Ni\u231?e ga\u253?yp erenler,\par
Jemaly\u328?y g\u246?renler,\par
Permandadyr-permanda.\par
\par
Dolduran bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni,\par
S\u246?zl\u228?n her du jahany,\par
K\u252?lli i\u351?i\u328? be\u253?any,\par
Gurhandadyr-Gurhanda.\par
\par
Magtymguly, a\u231? diller,\par
Gulluk kyl a\u253?lar, \u253?yllar,\par
Erte gulluksyz gullar,\par
Armandadyr-armanda.\par
\par
H\u214?WESIDIR\par
Adam ogly, pikri\u328?-zikri\u328?,\par
\u221?alan\u231?yny\u328? h\u246?wesidir.\par
H\u228?zir bu pikre gider sen,\par
Bir g\u252?n derde go\u253?asydyr.\par
\par
Bir g\u252?n girer \u253?ere ba\u351?y\u328?,\par
Unudar kowum-garda\u351?y\u328?,\par
Namazy\u328?, roza\u328? \u253?olda\u351?y\u328?,\par
Bir-de dili\u328? senasydyr.\par
\par
A\u328?da\u351?arlar sagda, solda -\par
\u350?e\u253?tan \u253?ol keser bu \u253?olda,\par
Erkli gorgan, agyr dalda,\par
\u350?erigaty\u328? galasydyr.\par
\par
Bu jahany\u328? serma\u253?asy,\par
Ryzk seb\u228?bi, Hak sa\u253?asy,\par
\u221?er diregi, g\u246?k pa\u253?asy,\par
Derw\u252?\u351?leri\u328? dogasydyr.\par
\par
Ge\u231?er \u246?m\u252?r, \u246?ter bu dem,\par
Ne \u253?\u246?r\u252?r sen gedem-gedem,\par
Pili ra\u253?a salan adam,\par
Seni gur\u231?uk i\u253?esidir.\par
\par
Daglar bardyr, da\u351?lar bardyr,\par
\u221?azlar bardyr, gy\u351?lar bardyr,\par
\u221?aman-\u253?owuz i\u351?ler bardyr,\par
Ba\u351?a gelen du\u253?asydyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, y\u351?k me\u253?dandyr,\par
Bu me\u253?dana giren jandyr,\par
Jany\u328? hem tende myhmandyr,\par
Beren bir g\u252?n alasydyr.\par
\par
GIDER\par
Adam ogly, pelek seni\u328?,\par
Bir g\u252?n donu\u328? bi\u231?er gider.\par
Sa\u328?a urar hanjaryny,\par
Jellat gany\u328? sa\u231?ar gider.\par
\par
Gezme d\u252?n\u253?\u228? me\u253?il edip,\par
Bihuda \u253?erde se\u253?l edip,\par
\u214?\u328?ki gonanlary\u328? \u246?t\u252?p,\par
G\u246?z a\u231?yn\u231?a\u328? ge\u231?er gider.\par
\par
\u214?lse\u328?, seni kimi\u328? \u253?atlar,\par
Ha\u253?kyr galar bedew atlar,\par
Ony m\u252?nen go\u231? \u253?igitler,\par
Gara toprak gu\u231?ar gider.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? so\u328?y bibatdyr,\par
Binamazy\u328? ja\u253?y otdur,\par
\u214?l\u252?m bir ajy \u351?erbetdir,\par
Her kim ondan i\u231?er gider.\par
\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l a\u253?dadyr \u246?lmese\u328?,\par
Lahatda tenha galmasa\u328?,\par
E\u253?\u228?\u328?e dogry bolmasa\u328?,\par
Iman senden ga\u231?ar gider.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu ne ja\u253?dyr,\par
Ajap bir kerwensara\u253?dyr,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? bir loly hele\u253?dir,\par
Bir g\u252?n seni gu\u231?ar gider.\par
\par
ALAJAKDYR\par
Adam ogly, bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge,\par
Go\u253?maz, seni alajakdyr.\par
Halal, haram - \u253?ygan maly\u328?,\par
So\u328?ra senden galajakdyr.\par
\par
Her \u231?ent ki \u253?a\u351?asa\u328? \u246?z\u252?\u328?,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman galar s\u246?z\u252?\u328?,\par
Humar g\u246?z\u252?\u328?, g\u252?l dek \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328?\par
Hazan urup solajakdyr.\par
\par
Tenden jyda bolar gany\u328?,\par
Bikar galar ustuhany\u328?,\par
\u350?on\u231?a \u253?ylky duran jany\u328?,\par
A\u253?ryba\u351?ga bolajakdyr.\par
\par
\u214?tdi \u253?azy\u328?, geldi gy\u351?y\u328?,\par
Namaz, roza bolsun i\u351?i\u328?,\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de soltan ba\u351?y\u328?,\par
Ne s\u246?wdalar g\u246?rejekdir.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge gelen janlar,\par
Biri-birine myhmanlar,\par
Hoja-se\u253?it, beg-u hanlar\par
Ahyr so\u328?y \u246?lejekdir.\par
\par
Hyzmat kyl kadyr Huda\u253?a,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328?i \u246?t\u252?rme za\u253?a,\par
I\u351?iksiz, t\u252?\u253?n\u252?ksiz ja\u253?a,\par
Bir g\u252?n eltip salajakdyr.\par
\par
Berhem bolar galar ja\u253?y\u328?,\par
Bozular k\u246?\u351?k-u sara\u253?y\u328?,\par
\u221?aradan kadyr Huda\u253?y\u328?\par
Tenha \u246?zi galajakdyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly asy gulu\u328?,\par
K\u252?f\u252?r s\u246?zden sakla dili\u328?,\par
Ky\u253?amatda dogry \u253?olu\u328?,\par
Syrat k\u246?pri bolajakdyr.\par
\par
G\u214?R\u220?M G\u214?R\u220?LMEGEN \u221?ERDE\par
Yzzat, hormat, syn etmegin,\par
G\u246?r\u252?m g\u246?r\u252?lmegen \u253?erde.\par
Akyl bolan s\u246?z a\u231?army?\par
Nobat berilmegen \u253?erde.\par
\par
Akly \u253?ag\u351?ylar unutmaz,\par
Gury agaja \u253?aprak bitmez,\par
Akylly \u228?r mesgen tutmaz,\par
Hulky s\u246?\u253?\u252?lmegen \u253?erde.\par
\par
Batyl galan aryk akmaz,\par
Her na\u351?ydan kerem \u231?ykmaz,\par
It g\u246?zlemez, pi\u351?ik bakmaz,\par
Supra \u253?a\u253?ylmagan \u253?erde.\par
\par
Haj e\u253?lese\u328?, jara d\u246?ner,\par
G\u252?l a\u231?ylsa, hara d\u246?ner,\par
Hyzmat etmek hara d\u246?ner,\par
Gadry\u328? bilinmegen \u253?erde.\par
\par
Namart go\u351? \u252?st\u252?nde harlar,\par
\u214?ter, a\u351? \u252?st\u252?nde g\u252?rl\u228?r,\par
S\u246?we\u351? gurup, gyly\u231? parlar,\par
Jyza urulmagan \u253?erde.\par
\par
\u214?\u253? i\u231?inde hyra d\u246?ner,\par
Muhannes bir nere d\u246?ner,\par
Tilki, \u351?agal \u351?ire d\u246?ner,\par
S\u246?we\u351? gurulmagan \u253?erde.\par
\par
Parasat kyl, bakyp akla,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igidi\u328? s\u246?z\u252?n hakla,\par
Magtymguly, dili\u328? sakla,\par
Habar soralmagan \u253?erde.\par
\par
GITMEZMI\u350?\par
Iller, he\u253?, Mejnun dagyny\u328?,\par
Serinden duman gitmezmi\u351?.\par
M\u252?\u328?k\u252?re bilin bereni\u328?,\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?nden g\u252?man gitmezmi\u351?.\par
\par
Go\u253?na garda\u351? bolmaz gurtdan,\par
Dileg etme her namartdan,\par
T\u228? \u246?lin\u231?\u228? go\u231? \u253?igitden\par
Myzrak, tir, keman gitmezmi\u351?.\par
\par
Gapyl adam ogly bilmez,\par
\u214?l\u252?mini \u253?ada salmaz,\par
Maly\u328?-m\u252?lk\u252?\u328? yssyg kylmaz,\par
\u221?anyndan iman gitmezmi\u351?.\par
\par
Zamana \u253?akyn gelende,\par
\u221?eri, g\u246?gi suw alanda,\par
Alladan ga\u253?ry \u246?lende,\par
On sekiz mekan gitmezmi\u351?.\par
\par
\u221?er bilen g\u246?kden kuwwatly,\par
\u350?ol Ezra\u253?yldan ha\u253?batly,\par
B\u228?\u351? ki\u351?ini\u328? Hary\u351? atly,\par
\u214?\u328?\u252?nden \u253?ylan gitmezmi\u351?.\par
\par
A\u351?yklar terki-jan etsin,\par
G\u246?zde \u253?a\u351?yn rowan etsin,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igitler yhsan etsin,\par
Yhsany re\u253?gan gitmezmi\u351?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, galgyn derde,\par
I\u351?i\u328? d\u252?\u351?enden namarda,\par
Ky\u253?amat g\u252?ni jomarda,\par
Dowzahdan zy\u253?an \u253?etmezmi\u351?.\par
\par
\u196?R \u221?ANYNDA BELLIDIR\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylygy pis bilmez -\par
\u196?r \u253?anynda bellidir.\par
G\u246?rer g\u246?z\u252?\u328? gymmaty,\par
K\u246?r \u253?anynda bellidir.\par
\par
D\u228?li k\u246?\u328?\u252?l da\u253?anjy,\par
\u221?okdur d\u252?n\u253?\u228? ynanjy,\par
Sag gulagy\u328? guwanjy,\par
Ker \u253?anynda bellidir.\par
\par
Eger pir sen, eger \u253?a\u351?,\par
Kylma syry\u328? halka pa\u351?,\par
Syr saklagan m\u228?hek da\u351?,\par
Zer \u253?anynda bellidir.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? myrady -\par
At, zagyfdyr, z\u252?r\u253?ady,\par
Arwanany\u328? kuwwaty,\par
Ner \u253?anynda bellidir.\par
\par
Bolsa gamdan halasym,\par
\u221?aza d\u246?nse gy\u351? paslym,\par
Magtymguly, yhlasym,\par
\u221?ar \u253?anynda bellidir.\par
\par
E\u221?LEDI\u327? MENI\par
E\u253?, Huda\u253?-a, gudraty\u328?dan,\par
\u221?okdan bar e\u253?ledi\u328? meni.\par
De\u328?-du\u351?lardan ga\u253?ra kylyp,\par
Gamgusar e\u253?ledi\u328? meni.\par
\par
T\u228?le\u253?-bagtym gi\u328?den salma\u253?,\par
Dileglerim kabul kylma\u253?,\par
Ylmy-d\u252?n\u253?\u228? ata kylma\u253?,\par
Mala zar e\u253?ledi\u328? meni.\par
\par
Garda\u351?-u ata-enemden,\par
A\u253?ryly\u351?yp doganymdan,\par
Jyda d\u252?\u351?\u252?p il-\u253?urdumdan,\par
Mysapyr e\u253?ledi\u328? meni.\par
\par
Magtymguly pygan e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
G\u246?zde \u253?a\u351?yn rowan e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
Haka zary-nalan e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
Be\u253?le har e\u253?ledi\u328? meni.\par
\par
EMIRE D\u214?NER\par
\u220?lkede sahyp bolmasa,\par
Arbaplar emire d\u246?ner.\par
\u220?\u231? \u253?yl \u351?ire u\u231?ramasa,\par
Tilki-\u351?agal \u351?ire d\u246?ner.\par
\par
Gahba pelek ka\u351?yk salar,\par
Birne bi\u253?r, birinden alar,\par
Her kime bir nobat geler,\par
\u220?lke agar, tora d\u246?ner.\par
\par
\u350?ir her \u231?akda bir aw atar,\par
Di\u253?r: \u171?Awuma kim el gatar\u187?.\par
Pil burnun pelege tutar,\par
Kerk g\u246?rse, hamyra d\u246?ner.\par
\par
Ajal \u253?eter, adam du\u253?maz,\par
D\u246?wran ge\u231?er, \u246?m\u252?r do\u253?maz,\par
Tilki sarkydyn \u351?ir i\u253?mez,\par
Ger i\u253?se, z\u228?here d\u246?ner.\par
\par
Dert - \u253?\u252?rekde bir ot bolar,\par
S\u246?z - jahanda bir at bolar,\par
Pakyra a\u351?na \u253?at bolar,\par
Mallansa, \u253?at \u253?ara d\u246?ner.\par
\par
Mertler je\u328?de - to\u253? i\u231?inde,\par
A\u231? b\u246?r\u252?dir \u8722? ko\u253? i\u231?inde,\par
Namart guran \u246?\u253? i\u231?inde,\par
Barsa\u328?, hyra-hyra d\u246?ner.\par
\par
Magtymguly, budur derdi\u328?,\par
Sahyby gerek her \u253?urdu\u328?,\par
\u350?ir zarbyn g\u246?rme\u253?en gurdu\u328?,\par
Her murty bir tire d\u246?ner.\par
\par
DONLY G\u214?RNER\par
Dogry bakmazlar jully\u253?a,\par
G\u246?ze gyzyl donly g\u246?rner.\par
S\u246?z p\u228?hm etmez akmak-gedi,\par
\u214?z \u253?anyndan dilli g\u246?rner.\par
\par
Ba\u351?a degme\u253?in\u231?\u228? gurtlar,\par
Kast etm\u228?\u328?, gerekdir \u253?urtlar,\par
\u221?agyda tanalar mertler,\par
Il i\u231?inde mally g\u246?rner.\par
\par
Pikr et ba\u351?a i\u351? d\u252?\u351?m\u228?nde,\par
Yssy \u253?okdur so\u328? pu\u351?manda,\par
At \u8722? me\u253?danda, \u228?r \u8722? du\u351?manda,\par
To\u253?da tirme \u351?ally g\u246?rner.\par
\par
Jany sagy\u328? s\u246?zl\u228?r dili,\par
Jomardy\u328? dek durmaz eli,\par
Her ki\u351?ini\u328? \u246?z akyly,\par
\u214?z\u252?ne kemally g\u246?rner.\par
\par
Gadymdan setdir \u253?ag\u351?ylyk,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y zatdyr \u253?ag\u351?y gylyk,\par
Mert \u253?igide az \u253?ag\u351?ylyk,\par
Az hem s\u246?\u253?g\u252?li g\u246?rner.\par
\par
Gel, akyl dolandyr indi,\par
\u221?\u252?rek pe\u253?wendi, jan bendi,\par
Her ki\u351?ini\u328? \u246?z perzendi,\par
\u214?z\u252?ne jemally g\u246?rner.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?z bin\u253?ady\u328?\par
Agzynda \u253?akyny\u328?, \u253?ady\u328?,\par
H\u252?n\u228?r \u253?ok, s\u246?z bilen ady\u328?,\par
Halk i\u231?inde belli g\u246?rner.\par
\par
D\u214?WLETI-MALY BOLMASA\par
Go\u231? \u253?igidi\u328? ady \u231?ykmaz,\par
D\u246?wleti-maly bolmasa.\par
Endi\u351?eli i\u351? bitirmez,\par
Me\u253?danda d\u228?li bolmasa.\par
\par
Bolmasa \u253?igdi\u328? z\u252?r\u253?ady,\par
\u214?lende tutulmaz ady,\par
Tuta\u351?maz synany\u328? ody,\par
Ba\u351?da hy\u253?aly bolmasa.\par
\par
Almaz gu\u351?lar awa \u231?apmaz,\par
H\u252?n\u228?rsiz \u246?z syrtyn \u253?apmaz,\par
M\u228?rekede orun tapmaz,\par
Akly-kemaly bolmasa.\par
\par
Gonmak t\u228?ze \u253?urda \u253?ag\u351?y,\par
Haly d\u252?\u351?ek t\u246?rde \u253?ag\u351?y,\par
Ol \u253?igitler g\u246?rde \u253?ag\u351?y,\par
Ba\u351?y gowgaly bolmasa.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bolsa ba\u351?ly,\par
U\u253?almaz gyly\u231?ly, a\u351?ly,\par
Duzy zor, du\u351?many g\u252?\u253?\u231?li,\par
Dosty wepaly bolmasa.\par
\par
DA\u350?DA BELLIDIR\par
\u221?ag\u351?yny\u328? gadryn il bilmez,\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylar da\u351?da bellidir.\par
M\u246?wlam nazar salsa kime -\par
Bolajak ba\u351?da bellidir.\par
\par
\u214?\u253?de \u253?atyp etme g\u252?n\u228?,\par
Gol-a\u253?agy\u328? bolar g\u252?w\u228?,\par
Ile pynhan, Haka \u228?g\u228?,\par
Asl adam i\u351?de bellidir.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de maldyr g\u246?rk\u252?\u328?,\par
Her bir \u253?ere \u253?eter erki\u328?,\par
\u214?\u253?\u252?nde lap urar her kim,\par
Batyr s\u246?we\u351?de bellidir.\par
\par
Hynany \u253?aksa\u328?, re\u328? bolar,\par
Gyzyly s\u246?kse\u328?, se\u328? bolar,\par
Hemme bedewler de\u328? bolar,\par
Bedew \u231?apy\u351?da bellidir.\par
\par
Hoja, se\u253?it selasatly,\par
Pakyrlara delalatly,\par
Ho\u351? tebess\u252?m, mylakatly -\par
Her kim de\u328?-du\u351?da bellidir.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u351?owku\u328? g\u252?ni,\par
\u221?ag\u351?ydyr yslamy\u328? dini,\par
\u221?ene has g\u246?zeli\u328? syny,\par
G\u246?z bilen ga\u351?da bellidir.\par
\par
DAG SA\u221?AR\par
Daglar \u253?eri\u328? myhydyr,\par
Depe \u246?z\u252?n dag sa\u253?ar.\par
\u199?ekik \u246?z\u252?n bilbil di\u253?r,\par
\u199?arlak \u246?z\u252?n zag sa\u253?ar.\par
\par
Kemlik e\u253?le - kemal bar,\par
Menlik etme - zowal bar,\par
Her ba\u351?da bir hy\u253?al bar,\par
Gul \u246?z\u252?ni ig sa\u253?ar.\par
\par
G\u252?\u253?j\u252?nden, kuwwatyndan,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? nobatyndan,\par
Bir ki\u351?i yzzatyndan\par
Bedasyl \u246?z\u252?n beg sa\u253?ar.\par
\par
Nadanam, zat bilmenem,\par
Bir g\u252?n\u228?li gul menem,\par
Sirke a\u253?dar: \u171?Bal menem\u187?,\par
Nebit \u246?z\u252?n \u253?ag sa\u253?ar.\par
\par
Habar alsa\u328? birewden,\par
\u214?z\u252?n kem sa\u253?maz d\u246?wden,\par
\u214?z \u253?anyndan bedewden,\par
E\u351?ek \u246?z\u252?n \u253?eg sa\u253?ar.\par
\par
Dert \u231?ekenler dert biler,\par
Namart \u246?z\u252?n mert biler,\par
Tilki \u246?z\u252?n gurt biler,\par
Garsak \u246?z\u252?n seg sa\u253?ar.\par
\par
Magtymguly bir guldur,\par
Gullugyna ka\u253?yldyr,\par
Akmak \u246?z\u252?n akyl di\u253?r,\par
\u214?le\u328? \u246?z\u252?n bag sa\u253?ar.\par
\par
DA\u327? ATMAZDAN BURUN\par
Adam ogly, \u253?atma gapyl,\par
Tur-ha da\u328? atmazdan burun.\par
\u221?igitlikde tagat kylgyl,\par
Garrylyk \u253?etmezden burun.\par
\par
Garrylyk tagat kyldyrmaz,\par
I\u351?i\u328? ebesdir, bildirmez,\par
Pelek agladar, g\u252?ld\u252?rmez,\par
S\u252?r d\u246?wran \u246?tmezden burun.\par
\par
Bend\u228?ge e\u253?leme kasdy,\par
Agyrtmagyl \u253?ary-dosty,\par
Bir g\u252?n gelip, ajal desti,\par
\u221?aka\u328?dan tutmazdan burun.\par
\par
Garda\u351?lary\u328? \u253?yglap galar,\par
\u221?e\u328?, \u253?akasyz dona salar,\par
Bir g\u252?n amanady\u328? alar,\par
Sen toba etmezden burun.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge gelen ge\u231?er,\par
Hala\u253?yk ol me\u253?den i\u231?er,\par
Bir a\u382?darha agzyn a\u231?ar,\par
Wehm e\u253?le \u253?uwtmazdan burun.\par
\par
Me\u351?gul sen d\u252?n\u253?\u228? o\u253?nuna,\par
Girer sen \u253?eri\u328? go\u253?nuna,\par
Ajal bend\u228?ni\u328? bo\u253?nuna,\par
Ga\u253?dawer m\u252?nmezden burun.\par
\par
Ajal bar\u231?any edalar,\par
Galmazlar \u351?ah-u gedalar,\par
Haramdan ga\u231?, kethudalar,\par
Rusy\u253?a bolmazdan burun.\par
\par
Sakla gybatdan dili\u328?i,\par
Otdan baglarlar eli\u328?i,\par
A\u231?ylan t\u228?ze g\u252?l\u252?\u328?i,\par
Alla soldurmazdan burun.\par
\par
Bend\u228?ge etme hy\u253?anat,\par
Bar\u231?a gul Ta\u328?ryga ra\u253?at,.\par
Bu s\u246?zde bar hadys, a\u253?at,\par
P\u228?hm e\u253?le \u246?lmezden burun.\par
\par
Tur s\u228?her, Ta\u328?ryga \u253?ygla,\par
\u171?Hak\u187? di\u253?ip \u253?\u252?regi\u328? dagla,\par
Toba gorun m\u228?k\u228?m bagla,\par
Kyrky\u328?a gelmezden burun.\par
\par
Magtymguly, dogry s\u246?\u253?le,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328? gelip, ge\u231?er be\u253?le,\par
Zynhar, \u253?a\u351?uly\u328?y syla,\par
Ba\u351? g\u246?re girmezden burun.\par
\par
\u221?YKMA\u221?AN \u196?RDEN\par
Hi\u231? k\u246?\u328?\u252?l \u351?atlygy \u231?ykmaz,\par
Bir k\u246?\u328?\u252?l \u253?ykma\u253?an \u228?rden.\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylyk tamasyn etm\u228?\u328?,\par
\u221?amanlyk \u231?ykma\u253?an \u228?rden.\par
\par
Her kim ile beglik eder,\par
Bir jem bilen \u253?ola gider,\par
Kethudalyk yrak gider,\par
\u221?aman s\u246?z \u231?ekme\u253?en \u228?rden.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y \u228?r il a\u253?byn a\u231?maz,\par
G\u246?re-bile haram i\u231?mez,\par
\u221?aradan \u253?azygyn ge\u231?mez,\par
G\u246?z\u253?a\u351?yn d\u246?kme\u253?en \u228?rden.\par
\par
Eglenmez, e\u253?\u253?am \u246?wr\u252?ler,\par
Zaman \u246?ter, nyrh \u231?\u246?wr\u252?ler,\par
Agyr d\u246?wletler a\u253?rylar,\par
Bir agza bakma\u253?an \u228?rden.\par
\par
\u214?z-\u246?z\u252?nden akly \u253?etmez,\par
Akyllary\u328? s\u246?z\u252?n tutmaz,\par
\u221?oksullyk \u253?ok bolup gitmez,\par
On i\u351? terk etme\u253?en \u228?rden.\par
\par
Go\u231?aklara \u253?asaw g\u252?ni,\par
\u221?yglyp gelse go\u351?un k\u228?ni,\par
Pygamber bizar \u253?ow g\u252?ni,\par
\u221?olda\u351?a bakma\u253?an \u228?rden.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?angyl, \u246?\u231?g\u252?l,\par
\u221?a lal otur, \u253?a d\u252?r sa\u231?gyl,\par
Bir gu\u253?ruksyz itdir, ga\u231?gyl,\par
Nesihat \u253?okma\u253?an \u228?rden.\par
\par
\u221?AR GEREKDIR\par
Menem di\u253?en go\u231? \u253?igide,\par
Bir mynasyp \u253?ar gerekdir.\par
Arap at, \u253?owly \u253?igide,\par
Almaz z\u252?lp\u252?kar gerekdir.\par
\par
\u221?igit oldur - \u253?urt \u252?st\u252?nde,\par
Janyn berse din \u252?st\u252?nde,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igitler il \u252?st\u252?nde,\par
Namys bilen ar gerekdir.\par
\par
B\u228?\u351? g\u252?n k\u246?\u328?\u252?l ho\u351? etm\u228?ge,\par
Supra \u253?a\u253?yp, nan d\u246?km\u228?ge,\par
Abra\u253? alyp, at etm\u228?ge,\par
Gollarynda bar gerekdir.\par
\par
Mekg\u228? baran bolar hajy,\par
A\u253?ralyk \u246?l\u252?mden ajy,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igide din gylyjy,\par
A\u351?yga didar gerekdir.\par
\par
Artdyr pelek ahy-zary\u328?,\par
Alar elden ygty\u253?ary\u328?,\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?wer \u253?ary\u328?,\par
Sy\u253?a z\u252?lpi tar gerekdir.\par
\par
\u221?OLDA\u350? BOLAN\par
\u221?ag\u351?y s\u246?zi jana \u253?arar,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y bilen \u253?olda\u351? bolan.\par
Ga\u231?yp gutulmaga uwnar\par
Bir \u253?aman go\u328?\u351?a du\u351? bolan.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? so\u328?y \u246?tmekdir,\par
Myrat - munda i\u351? bitmekdir,\par
I\u351?i gussa \u253?uwutmakdyr,\par
\u221?aman bilen garda\u351? bolan.\par
\par
Bir \u253?aman s\u246?z \u253?\u252?rek bular,\par
\u221?ag\u351?yny \u228?lem arzuwlar,\par
\u221?atdan \u231?ykmaz, g\u246?rmek dil\u228?r,\par
Birewden k\u246?\u328?li ho\u351? bolan.\par
\par
Her kimde-ki h\u252?n\u228?r \u253?okdur,\par
Du\u351?manyna heder \u253?okdur,\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylyk etse \u253?er \u253?okdur,\par
\u350?u e\u253?\u253?amda \u253?uwa\u351? bolan.\par
\par
Magtymguly \u246?w\u252?t a\u253?dar,\par
A\u328?lan gulagynda g\u252?\u253?der,\par
\u214?z\u252?ni \u253?\u252?\u328?sakgal eder,\par
Bozulan ile ba\u351? bolan.\par
\par
\u221?OLDA\u350?Y\u327? GALAR\par
Gapyl adam, gider bolsa\u328?,\par
Keremli \u253?olda\u351?y\u328? galar.\par
Jellat gelip, jan alanda,\par
\u221?ygla\u351?yp, garda\u351?y\u328? galar.\par
\par
Tende myhman eziz jany\u328?,\par
Gazangyl nury-imany\u328?,\par
Supra \u253?a\u253?yp, d\u246?kg\u252?l nany\u328?,\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de a\u351?y\u328? galar.\par
\par
Jellat hanjaryn salanda,\par
Ezra\u253?yl jany\u328? alanda,\par
Iki sorag\u231?y gelende,\par
Ba\u351?da akyl-hu\u351?u\u328? galar.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni tutma gyzgyn,\par
\u221?oldan \u231?ykyp, bolma azgyn,\par
Biwepadyr, umyt \u252?zg\u252?n,\par
Gum guwanar, l\u228?\u351?i\u328? galar.\par
\par
N\u228?m\u228?hrem g\u246?ren g\u246?zleri\u328?,\par
\u350?ol gybat eden s\u246?zleri\u328?,\par
E\u328?re\u351?er ogul-gyzlary\u328?,\par
G\u246?re girip, g\u252?w\u351?\u252?\u328? galar.\par
\par
Barsa\u328? imany\u328?y alyp,\par
Ol b\u228?\u351? gez bize dolanyp,\par
Gara topraga bulanyp,\par
Zemin i\u231?re ba\u351?y\u328? galar.\par
\par
Ajal geldi, nobat \u253?etdi,\par
Kimse bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni tutdy,\par
Magtymguly, \u246?mr\u252?\u328? \u246?tdi,\par
Dat edip, syrda\u351?y\u328? galar.\par
\par
TASA GAR\u350?Y\par
Agyz a\u231?dym, g\u246?z \u253?umdum,\par
Gol sundum tasa gar\u351?y.\par
Tas \u252?st\u252?nde \u253?atypdyr,\par
Galandar \u253?asa gar\u351?y.\par
\par
Saky turdy, ses etdi,\par
Kim gi\u231? galdy, kim \u253?etdi,\par
Galandar tasyn tutdy,\par
D\u252?\u351?d\u252?m h\u246?w\u228?se gar\u351?y.\par
\par
Men bikemal ol \u253?erde,\par
Y\u351?k i\u231?re d\u252?\u351?d\u252?m derde,\par
G\u252?l \u253?\u252?zde g\u252?lg\u252?n perde,\par
Tutdy palasa gar\u351?y.\par
\par
Habar tutan jahandan,\par
A\u253?rylar hanymandan,\par
A\u351?yklar ge\u231?er jandan,\par
Tutulsa k\u228?se gar\u351?y.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? bir sara\u253?dyr,\par
Gelen ge\u231?ip bara\u253?dyr,\par
Magtymguly hara\u253? di\u253?r,\par
Hydyr, Yl\u253?asa gar\u351?y.\par
\par
\u350?ALAR GALMAZLAR\par
Gam \u231?ekme, garyp adam,\par
Begler-\u351?alar galmazlar.\par
Azym-azym \u351?\u228?herler,\par
Ak otaglar galmazlar.\par
\par
Galsa s\u246?zden gyzyl dil,\par
Jan j\u246?wherdir, ten bir gil,\par
Hezar mukamly bilbil,\par
Be\u253?ik daglar galmazlar.\par
\par
\u350?uny kesipdir aklym,\par
\u221?ykylar \u253?edi yklym,\par
\u221?er bolar b\u252?kl\u252?m-b\u252?kl\u252?m,\par
Erir, daglar galmazlar.\par
\par
Hakdan \u253?eti\u351?se perman,\par
Ne \u231?\u228?re bar, ne derman,\par
Asman, G\u252?n-u A\u253? lerzan\par
Hem \u253?yldyzlar galmazlar.\par
\par
Ne \u253?er galar, ne \u253?urtlar,\par
Ne t\u252?rk galar, ne k\u252?rtler,\par
Ne gu\u351? galar, ne gurtlar,\par
Perrendeler galmazlar.\par
\par
Ne gert galar, ne gerdan,\par
Ne mert galar, ne merdan,\par
Pil, pe\u351?e-\u253?u kergedan,\par
Derrendeler galmazlar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?a\u351? s\u252?ren,\par
Agyr he\u328?\u328?amlar guran,\par
Lemmer-lemmer m\u246?w\u231? uran,\par
\u350?ol der\u253?alar galmazlar.\par
\par
SIL BIL\u196?NI\par
Belent daglary\u328? ba\u351?ynda,\par
Bulut o\u253?nar sil bil\u228?ni.\par
Go\u231? \u253?igide to\u253?dur-ba\u253?ram\par
Her i\u351? gelse il bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Dil bilenler g\u252?\u328? bolupdyr,\par
Altyn, k\u252?m\u252?\u351? ze\u328? bolupdyr,\par
Pe\u351?e ha\u231?an de\u328? bolupdyr\par
Ugra\u351?anda pil bil\u228?ni?\par
\par
Otlaga ga\u231?ar buzawlar,\par
\u214?\u328?\u252?n ba\u351?lar \u253?ag\u351?y g\u228?wler,\par
Tanalar hasse bedewler,\par
K\u246?ne, \u253?yrtyk jul bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Haram i\u351?den ga\u231?ar pirler, -\par
Tilki sarkydyndan \u351?irler,\par
Gusdurmany go\u253?maz di\u253?rler,\par
Gu\u253?tmak i\u253?se\u328? gyl bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Hak bendesi Haka \u231?okar,\par
\u221?aman \u246?z p\u228?linden tapar,\par
Magtymguly, a\u253?byn \u253?apar,\par
A\u351?, gylyj-u dil bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
\u214?\u221?LENGIN\par
\u221?igit haly\u328? garrylyga,\par
Sala\u253?yn di\u253?se\u328?, \u246?\u253?lengin.\par
Kethudalyk endi\u351?esin,\par
Kyla\u253?yn di\u253?se\u328?, \u246?\u253?lengin.\par
\par
Kethudalyk g\u246?zel \u253?oldur,\par
Ga\u253?gy garrydar, gam \u246?ldir,\par
\u221?igitlik bir gyzyl g\u252?ld\u252?r,\par
Sola\u253?yn di\u253?se\u328?, \u246?\u253?lengin.\par
\par
\u214?\u253?, il gerek, \u253?organ-d\u252?\u351?ek,\par
Perzent bentdir, a\u253?al \u8722? du\u351?ak,\par
\u221?\u252?ke werzi\u351?g\u228?r boz e\u351?ek.\par
Bola\u253?yn di\u253?se\u328?, \u246?\u253?lengin.\par
\par
Gezer sen o\u253?nap, dala\u351?yp,\par
Galar sen gama bula\u351?yp,\par
Hasrata, derde ula\u351?yp,\par
Gala\u253?yn di\u253?se\u328?, \u246?\u253?lengin.\par
\par
Jo\u351?gun eder sen \u246?z\u252?\u328?den,\par
A\u253?rylar sen ho\u351? \u253?azy\u328?dan,\par
T\u252?kenmez derdi\u328? yzyndan,\par
\u221?ele\u253?in di\u253?se\u328?, \u246?\u253?lengin.\par
\par
\u214?tir \u253?igitlik zamanyn,\par
Getir garrylyk dumanyn,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? \u253?ag\u351?y, \u253?amanyn,\par
Bile\u253?in di\u253?se\u328?, \u246?\u253?lengin.\par
\par
\u221?igitlik bir gyzyl g\u252?l\u351?en,\par
Garrylykda \u246?\u231?er r\u246?w\u351?en.\par
Gujak-gujak gara \u253?ow\u351?an,\par
\u221?ola\u253?yn di\u253?se\u328?, \u246?\u253?lengin.\par
\par
Magtymguly, gezip her ta\u253?,\par
Etmezdi\u328? jahanda perwa\u253?,\par
Pygamber s\u252?nnetin berja\u253?,\par
Kyla\u253?yn di\u253?se\u328?, \u246?\u253?lengin.\par
\par
G\u220?LEN BARMY?\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, musulmanlar,\par
Aglama\u253?yn, g\u252?len barmy?\par
\u221?alan\u231?y-pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228?den,\par
Giden ga\u253?dyp gelen barmy?\par
\par
Pelek, kimleri \u351?at etdi\u328?,\par
Kimi gamdan azat etdi\u328?,\par
Birni\u231?eleri mat etdi\u328?,\par
Senden razy bolan barmy?\par
\par
Kimse wepa tohmun eker,\par
Kimse ajal z\u228?hmin \u231?eker,\par
Kimi gamdan azat eder,\par
Sargarma\u253?yn, solan barmy?\par
\par
Bildim bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u231?aglygyn,\par
Gam-gaflatda o\u253?aglygyn,\par
Hassa bolma\u253?yn, saglygy\u328?\par
Ganymatyn bilen barmy?\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? iki gyrakdyr,\par
Biri gara, biri akdyr,\par
Menzil iki, \u253?ol yrakdyr,\par
Onu\u328? pikrin kylan barmy?\par
\par
Magtymguly, gelen, ge\u231?er,\par
Bu g\u252?zere gonan g\u246?\u231?er,\par
\u221?igitlik \u231?yragy \u246?\u231?er,\par
Bu s\u246?z\u252?mde \u253?alan barmy?\par
\par
DERT I\u327?\u327?ILD\u196?R\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, musulmanlar,\par
\u221?\u252?regimde dert i\u328?\u328?ild\u228?r,\par
Bir ba\u253? ogluny\u328? elinde,\par
Sadran\u231? o\u253?nap, nert i\u328?\u328?ild\u228?r.\par
\par
Gelip-gitme mundan namart,\par
Akly\u328? \u231?a\u351?ar, bolarsy\u328? mat,\par
Belent dagda \u253?akarlar ot,\par
Gury \u253?anyp, \u246?l i\u328?\u328?ild\u228?r,\par
\par
Gyz g\u246?rd\u252?m t\u252?rkmen g\u246?\u231?\u252?nde,\par
M\u252?\u351?k-u-anbar bar sa\u231?ynda,\par
\u221?a\u253?lada, \u253?ylky i\u231?inde,\par
Boz gulan ta\u253?lar i\u328?\u328?ild\u228?r.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?z\u252?m hakdyr,\par
Hak s\u246?ze ten beren \u253?okdur,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igitde ogul \u253?okdur -\par
Ojak \u253?itip, \u253?urt i\u328?\u328?ild\u228?r.\par
\par
NARY BOLMASA\par
Bagban\u231?y bagy ne\u253?lesin,\par
Bagynda nary bolmasa,\par
Atadan ogul dogmasyn,\par
Namysy-ary bolmasa.\par
\par
Bilbile je\u328?\u328?el bag olmaz,\par
A\u253?raga depe dag olmaz,\par
Bedew \u253?abydan \u253?eg olmaz,\par
Meger reftary bolmasa.\par
\par
\u350?erbet i\u231?se\u328?, bala d\u246?ner,\par
Her bir g\u252?ni \u253?yla d\u246?ner,\par
G\u252?l dek re\u328?\u328?i k\u252?le d\u246?ner,\par
G\u246?zeli\u328? \u253?ary bolmasa.\par
\par
Magtymguly, nahan di\u253?rler,\par
Jan s\u246?wene janan di\u253?rler,\par
Ol \u253?igide ha\u253?wan di\u253?rler,\par
\u350?irin g\u252?ftary bolmasa.\par
\par
JAN EGLENMEZ\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, musulmanlar,\par
Amanatdyr, jan eglenmez.\par
Saglyga \u253?okdur ygtybar,\par
Tut mysal, myhman eglenmez.\par
\par
Kimse s\u228?her turar irden,\par
Kimse ba\u351? g\u246?termez \u253?erden,\par
\u350?e\u253?da dilli g\u246?zellerden,\par
Dil gider zyban eglenmez.\par
\par
Belent dagdan ha\u253?bat gider,\par
\u221?erlerden bereket gider,\par
Rum \u351?\u228?hrinden kuwwat gider,\par
Ussada d\u252?kan eglenmez.\par
\par
Ezra\u253?yl \u253?ol a\u231?ar bir g\u252?n,\par
Jan \u351?erbetden i\u231?er bir g\u252?n,\par
\u196?rden d\u246?wran ge\u231?er bir g\u252?n,\par
At \u246?ler, me\u253?dan eglenmez.\par
\par
\u350?erigatdan enzil olma\u328?,\par
Hak i\u351?ine bendil olma\u328?,\par
Adam ogly, gapyl olma\u328?,\par
G\u246?\u231? gider, kerwen eglenmez.\par
\par
Binamaz, ugrar sen gama,\par
Onda dady\u328? \u253?eter kime,\par
Munda zor berse\u328? \u231?ilime,\par
Jesetde iman eglenmez.\par
\par
Magtymguly, budur ykrar,\par
Hak \u253?olynda duran \u231?yn \u228?r,\par
Kims\u228?\u328? yzynda ogul bar,\par
Kimsede ny\u351?an eglenmez.\par
\par
YNSAN UGRA\u350?SA\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l a\u231?ylar, jem bolar,\par
Bir-bire ynsan ugra\u351?sa.\par
Hu\u351? gider, akyl kem bolar,\par
Dil bilmez ha\u253?wan ugra\u351?sa.\par
\par
S\u246?we\u351?de mert ba\u351?dan ge\u231?er,\par
Namart akyl-hu\u351?dan ge\u231?er,\par
Bedew segr\u228?p, l\u228?\u351?den ge\u231?er,\par
\u221?aby inmez gan ugra\u351?sa.\par
\par
Merdi\u328? sygnany Alladyr,\par
Muhannes ba\u351?a beladyr,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igit demir galadyr,\par
Her \u253?erde du\u351?man ugra\u351?sa.\par
\par
Pyragy, bagry\u328? paradyr,\par
Syna\u328? hem ujy \u253?aradyr,\par
M\u252?\u328?k\u252?ri\u328? \u253?\u252?zi garadyr,\par
Mag\u351?ar g\u252?n mizan ugra\u351?sa.\par
\par
\u221?AR OLMAGYL\par
Gel, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m, nesihat berem,\par
L\u228?mekana \u253?ar olmagyl.\par
Her \u253?etene \u253?arym di\u253?ip,\par
Yzynda bimar olmagyl.\par
\par
Ge\u328?e\u351? bergil de\u328?e-du\u351?a,\par
Ahyr \u246?l\u252?m geler ba\u351?a,\par
Bir bi\u231?\u228?re - \u253?al\u328?yz ki\u351?\u228?,\par
S\u252?tem e\u253?l\u228?p, zor olmagyl.\par
\par
Dilegi\u328? Allaga \u253?etse,\par
Derg\u228?hinde kabul etse,\par
\u214?z g\u252?n\u252?\u328? \u246?z\u252?\u328?den \u246?tse,\par
\u221?alan\u231?yda hor olmagyl.\par
\par
\u221?ygyn me\u253?dana d\u252?\u351?ende,\par
Namardy\u328? akly \u231?a\u351?anda,\par
Ol ganyma ugra\u351?anda,\par
De\u328?-du\u351?u\u328?dan b\u228?ri olmagyl.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?okdur \u253?alan,\par
Durman \u246?ter munda gelen,\par
Bir akylsyz biwe\u231? bilen,\par
De\u328?-du\u351? olup, jora olmagyl.\par
\par
\u221?\u214?R BIL\u196?NI\par
Gel, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l, \u253?ara gideli,\par
Hemra bolsa\u328?, \u253?\u246?r bil\u228?ni.\par
\u221?ar \u253?olunda gadam go\u253?sak,\par
Pa\u253? ornuna ser bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Asmany\u328? g\u246?rki enwerdir,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? g\u246?rki sim-u zerdir,\par
Jeset-toprak, jan-j\u246?wherdir,\par
Alyp bolmaz zer bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
\u350?unkary\u328? peri \u253?etiler,\par
K\u246?p da\u351?y yrak atylar,\par
\u221?igidi\u328? ady tutular,\par
Garynda\u351? hossar bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Guwanmagyl syratyna,\par
M\u252?ner sen gahar atyna,\par
Du\u351? bolsa\u328? \u253?aman hatyna,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328? \u246?ter \u351?er bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Bahyl ba\u253?da berim bolmaz,\par
Merdi\u328? s\u246?z\u252?n bawer kylmaz,\par
Arwanany\u328? \u253?\u252?ki galmaz,\par
\u221?ola girse\u328? ner bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Ganymatdyr garda\u351? \u253?\u252?zi,\par
Dowadyr gadamy-tozy,\par
Bir eblehi\u328? n\u228?kes s\u246?zi,\par
Barabardyr nar bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Pisi\u328? gar\u351?ysynda durma,\par
Bahyly\u328? \u253?\u252?z\u252?ni g\u246?rme,\par
Ker bilen hylwat s\u246?z urma,\par
\u221?ola girme k\u246?r bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
\u221?aman bilen \u253?olda\u351? bolma,\par
Du\u351?man bile syrda\u351? bolma,\par
Tagamda tabakda\u351? bolma,\par
\u220?flis, haramhor bil\u228?ni!\par
\par
\u221?aman hi\u231? nesihat tutmaz,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y s\u246?ze gulak g\u252?\u253?tmez,\par
Hi\u231? bir s\u246?z\u252?\u328? \u246?r\u228? gitmez,\par
N\u228?kes suhan\u351?or bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Ili\u328?den gitse\u328? awara,\par
\u350?onda bolar sen bi\u231?\u228?re,\par
Go\u328?\u351?y bolsa\u328? haramhora,\par
S\u252?tem e\u253?l\u228?r zor bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Algyl pendim, akmak ki\u351?i,\par
\u214?z\u252?\u328?e kylma k\u228?\u253?i\u351?i,\par
G\u246?termese d\u246?wlet gu\u351?y,\par
U\u231?up bolmaz per bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?yga \u246?z\u252?\u328? \u253?ar e\u253?le,\par
Mejlisinde bazar e\u253?le,\par
Reft-amet kyl, mydar e\u253?le,\par
S\u246?we\u351? etme \u351?ir bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?akyn, \u253?atlar,\par
Gamgynlar-u k\u246?\u328?\u252?l \u351?atlar, -\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? gelen bar\u231?a zatlar,\par
\u221?egsan bolar \u253?er bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
BA\u350?DAN, DOGRUSY\par
E\u351?it, perim, a\u351?yk boldum,\par
Men ilki ba\u351?dan, dogrusy.\par
Birje g\u246?rm\u228? ma\u253?yl boldum,\par
G\u246?z bilen ga\u351?dan, dogrusy.\par
\par
G\u246?wn\u252?mi\u328? ho\u351?g\u228?hi sen-sen,\par
K\u252?lli \u228?lem \u351?ahy sen-sen,\par
\u221?edi pelek mahy sen-sen,\par
Sil rowan \u253?a\u351?dan, dogrusy.\par
\par
\u221?\u252?z\u252?\u328? Z\u252?le\u253?hany\u328? g\u246?rki,\par
A\u253?lanar pelegi\u328? \u231?arhy,\par
Bildirmez adamy\u328? parhy,\par
Syn bilen da\u351?dan, dogrusy.\par
\par
Gyz alynar galy\u328? bilen,\par
Adam solar zulum bilen,\par
Nesibedir, \u246?l\u252?m bilen\par
Dynar te\u351?w\u252?\u351?den, dogrusy.\par
\par
Diller \u253?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman sa\u231?ar,\par
Her ki\u351?iden d\u246?wran ge\u231?er,\par
Namart \u253?igit a\u253?byn a\u231?ar,\par
Syzdyryp di\u351?den, dogrusy.\par
\par
G\u252?ndize G\u252?n, gij\u228? mahtap,\par
Der\u253?a lebi - oldur Lebap,\par
I\u231?er bolsa her kes \u351?erap,\par
Galarmy\u351? hu\u351?dan, dogrusy.\par
\par
Galmagaldan bela geler,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman bary biler,\par
Kimse aglar, kimse g\u252?ler,\par
G\u252?n \u231?ykar \u231?\u228?\u351?den, dogrusy.\par
\par
Gapla\u328? g\u252?rl\u228?r \u231?a\u253? i\u231?inde,\par
Gur\u231?uk \u253?\u246?rer la\u253? i\u231?inde,\par
Garyp bolsa ba\u253? i\u231?inde,\par
Agarar sa\u231?dan, dogrusy.\par
\par
Ger, Pyragy, hemra bolsa\u328?,\par
Na\u231?ar galan g\u246?w\u252?n alsa\u328?,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y bilen o\u253?nap-g\u252?lse\u328?,\par
A\u253?yrmaz hu\u351?dan, dogrusy.\par
\par
BIL\u196?NI\par
Dag-dereler lerzan urar,\par
Owsun atyp, sil bil\u228?ni.\par
Aza\u351?anlar y\u351?ka \u253?ortar,\par
A\u253?ra d\u252?\u351?\u252?p, \u253?ol bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Namart i\u231?de syr saklamaz,\par
Akylsyz hi\u231? s\u246?z beklemez,\par
Mert \u253?igit baryn \u253?oklamaz,\par
Her i\u351? gelse il bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
K\u246?mek etse\u328?, \u253?atdan gitmez,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y dost dostun unutmaz,\par
Aglamakdan bir i\u351? bitmez,\par
Ga\u253?gy gitmez pal bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
\u214?lin\u231?\u228?\u328? gezerler serho\u351?,\par
Namarda syr kylmagyl pa\u351?,\par
Il du\u253?mazdan kylsa\u328? her i\u351?,\par
\u221?\u252?ze \u231?ykar dil bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? malyn \u253?ygar ba\u253?lar,\par
Ok sypdyrar garry \u253?a\u253?lar,\par
We\u253?ran bolar be\u253?ik ja\u253?lar\par
\u221?agmyr ile, \u253?el bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Der\u253?alary jo\u351?durar sil,\par
Bir birewden a\u253?yrar dil.\par
Ganat kakyp sa\u253?ran bilbil\par
Me\u253?lis e\u253?l\u228?r g\u252?l bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Ser\u231?eden gorkan ekmez dary,\par
S\u252?nb\u252?llerin b\u246?ler peri,\par
H\u252?j\u252?m e\u253?l\u228?r bar\u231?a ary,\par
Gabat gelse bal bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Karun gezdi \u231?oh mal alyp,\par
Hary\u351? urdy efsun \u231?alyp,\par
Magtymguly, mejnun bolup\par
Gitsem gerek \u231?\u246?l bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
BIR K\u196?RE D\u214?NDI\par
E\u253?-\u228?, dostlar, adam bary,\par
Her biri bir k\u228?re d\u246?ndi.\par
Karun kibi \u253?ygyp maly,\par
Barysy ha\u253?\u253?ara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Haram \u253?ygar boldy ba\u253?lar,\par
\u221?a\u351?dy g\u252?n-u g\u246?zel a\u253?lar,\par
Bizi\u328? bu e\u351?retli ja\u253?lar\par
Gul-gyrnak bazara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Daglarda bent boldy siller,\par
\u214?sme\u253? galdy gelen \u253?eller,\par
G\u252?rgen, g\u246?kle\u328? ajap iller,\par
\u221?agydan g\u252?zere d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Tylla tagt-da gapylar,\par
D\u246?w\u252?r a\u253?lanyp \u253?apylar,\par
I\u351?an, molla, pir, sopular\par
Ilata azara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Dermansyz galandyr dertler,\par
We\u253?ran boldy k\u246?\u351?ki-\u253?urtlar,\par
Ata \u231?ykan bizi\u328? mertler\par
Zyndanda bi\u231?\u228?r\u228? d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
\u221?\u246?ren bolmady sogaba,\par
Haramy d\u246?ndi gassaba.\par
S\u228?her \u231?agy \u246?sen saba,\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?, indi nara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?, g\u252?nbe-g\u252?nden \u253?aman,\par
Il-g\u252?n\u252?mi tutdy duman,\par
Mert astynda ajap \u231?aman,\par
Bak, bu g\u252?n ol hara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Diller di\u253?er g\u246?r\u252?p-g\u246?r\u252?p,\par
Akyl keser sorup-sorup,\par
En\u231?e mertler bo\u253?un burup,\par
Namartda \u253?esire d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
U\u253?atdan galdy zenanlar,\par
Namart boldy \u231?oh merdanlar,\par
Il i\u231?inde \u351?alar, hanlar,\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? sokjak mara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Bir peri oturmaz syna,\par
Gark bolupdyr d\u252?n\u253?e huna,\par
Namartlar og\u351?ap Mejnuna,\par
Lolular g\u246?r \u253?ara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Bir s\u246?z di\u253?dim, bilse\u328?, ba\u253?ak,\par
\u350?ondan dadar boldum ta\u253?ak,\par
Nadan haram sopy-sy\u253?ak\par
Pe\u351? ge\u253?ipdir, pire d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylar \u252?st\u252?nden \u228?tl\u228?p,\par
Pulun tamamlanda datlap,\par
Bihuda Ta\u328?ryny \u253?atlap,\par
Namart janyn bi\u253?re d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Akyldan a\u253?ryldy ba\u351?lar,\par
Der\u253?a boldy akan \u253?a\u351?lar,\par
Hak bermegen gury hu\u351?lar,\par
Akyl s\u246?zl\u228?p, sere d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Alar boldy her kes ygyp,\par
Ba\u253? alda\u253?yp, malyn \u253?ygyp,\par
Il i\u231?inde misgin so\u253?up,\par
Bahyllar s\u252?\u253?thora d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
Ere\u253?ipdir daglar da\u351?y,\par
Namart boldy mert garda\u351?y,\par
Magtymgulyny\u328? g\u246?z\u253?a\u351?y\par
Ol de\u328?zi-Hazara d\u246?ndi.\par
\par
ZAMANYDYR\par
A\u253?dy\u328? ar-namyssyz \u253?igde,\par
Bu g\u252?n onu\u328? zamanydyr.\par
\u221?ygsyn Karun kibi mallar,\par
Hazyna bo\u351? \u8722? d\u246?wranydyr.\par
\par
Ah, ne\u253?le\u253?in, bagtym gara,\par
\u221?\u252?rek, bagrym boldy para,\par
Arzym a\u253?dy\u328? s\u246?wer \u253?ara,\par
Bu derdimi\u328? dermanydyr.\par
\par
\u199?a\u351?dy gyzykly bazarym,\par
Artdy g\u252?n-g\u252?nden azarym,\par
Kesmez boldy \u351?ul nazarym,\par
Alnynda dag dumanydyr.\par
\par
\u221?al\u328?yz perzent \u8722? ro\u253?u\u328?, g\u246?r\u252?p,\par
Gelip men Hywadan \u253?\u246?r\u252?p,\par
\u199?\u246?l i\u231?inden bedew s\u252?r\u252?p\par
Geldim, Haky\u328? permanydyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, derdi\u328? a\u253?an,\par
Baryn ajap kyldy\u328? be\u253?an,\par
Dili\u328? \u253?yg sen, bardyr zy\u253?an,\par
Akyl onu\u328? ha\u253?ranydyr.\par
\par
WE\u221?RAN E\u221?LEDI\par
Garyp g\u246?wn\u252?mi\u328? binasyn,\par
G\u246?r, pelek we\u253?ran e\u253?ledi.\par
Aldyryp goldan namysyn,\par
Kalbymda arman e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
Hakdan bize d\u246?wlet gelse,\par
\u221?yglan g\u246?zler o\u253?nap, g\u252?lse,\par
Misginler \u253?urt gadryn bilse,\par
\u221?\u252?rekde hijran e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
Mert \u253?igit bolsun garda\u351?y\u328?,\par
Bolmasa, hi\u231? galmaz ba\u351?y\u328?,\par
A\u253?yp tapyp, bil, syrda\u351?y\u328?,\par
Illere a\u253?an e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
Aty gerekdir mertleri\u328?,\par
Erse ady \u253?ok gurtlary\u328?,\par
Bakja-sara\u253?ly \u253?urtlary\u328?\par
Ja\u253?yny me\u253?dan e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
Magtymguly, akly \u231?a\u351?an,\par
S\u246?zl\u228?p gidermi garta\u351?an,\par
Da\u328? s\u228?her \u231?agy arla\u351?an\par
Pele\u328?ler se\u253?ran e\u253?ledi.\par
\par
MERT BOLMAZ\par
Mert \u253?igit mert \u228?rden \u246?ner,\par
Namart asyl-ha mert bolmaz.\par
Gurdu\u328? g\u246?z\u252?nde ot \u253?anar,\par
\u350?agal-tilkiler gurt bolmaz.\par
\par
S\u246?zlegil bileni\u328? dilden,\par
Bilbil a\u253?ra d\u252?\u351?se g\u252?lden,\par
E\u351?it adam, dogan ilden,\par
Ga\u253?ry m\u228?hriban \u253?urt bolmaz.\par
\par
Bu \u228?lem aja\u253?yp bolsa,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u253?\u252?zi nurdan dolsa,\par
Ozal Ta\u328?ry rehim kylsa,\par
Ne ten, ne janda dert bolmaz.\par
\par
Magtymguly, akyl-hu\u351?u\u328?,\par
Akdy g\u246?zden ganly \u253?a\u351?y\u328?,\par
Ell\u228? \u253?etdi gamly ba\u351?y\u328?,\par
Mundan ga\u253?ry per\u253?at bolmaz.\par
\par
OWAZYM\par
E\u253?, pelek, nadan pelek,\par
Di\u328?le meni\u328? owazym.\par
D\u252?n\u253?ewi, we\u253?ran pelek,\par
E\u351?dermi sen bu sazym.?\par
\par
Hy\u253?al bir i\u351? bitirmez,\par
Gola n\u228?rse getirmez,\par
Her bir a\u351?yk g\u246?termez,\par
Agyrdyr y\u351?ky-narym.\par
\par
\u350?e\u253?le zaman, garda\u351?lar,\par
Agardy sakal-ba\u351?lar,\par
Asmanda u\u231?ar gu\u351?lar,\par
K\u246?llerde guba-gazym.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? bir bazardyr,\par
Kimse g\u246?rm\u228?ge zardyr,\par
Sa\u253?\u253?at golunda hardyr,\par
Meni\u328? g\u246?zel \u351?abazym.\par
\par
\u221?\u246?rd\u252?m ykbal ugrunda,\par
Sepil d\u252?n\u253?e barynda,\par
Tir-u keman ornunda\par
Dilden \u231?ykan elfazym.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? \u351?iri kerkdir,\par
\u350?alara mesgen erkdir,\par
Tutduk bina\u253?ym berkdir,\par
Aja\u253?ypdyr afzalym.\par
\par
Jahany \u253?andyr y\u351?kym,\par
Ummana d\u246?ner e\u351?kim,\par
Tylla tagtym hem k\u246?\u351?k\u252?m,\par
Oldur ki serferazym.\par
\par
\u196?lem ro\u253?y G\u252?ndedir,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? derdi mendedir,\par
Behi\u351?t i\u231?re bendidir,\par
Ol g\u246?zel dilnowazym.\par
\par
G\u246?w\u252?n bir hy\u253?al almy\u351?,\par
Hy\u253?al i\u231?re u\u253?almy\u351?,\par
Jahana pida bolmu\u351?\par
\u221?erden \u231?ykyp fird\u246?wsim.\par
\par
Bir arzym Suhanadyr,\par
Dert a\u253?an \u8213? Lukmanadyr,\par
Arylar perwanadyr,\par
Zyban i\u231?re asalym.\par
\par
Men k\u246?\u253?en bagty gara,\par
Y\u351?k k\u246?l\u252?nde bi\u231?\u228?re,\par
Gow\u351?ursa g\u246?zel \u253?ara,\par
Budur Haka terhosym.\par
\par
Ba\u351?dan sylasa Huda,\par
K\u252?lli \u228?lem bor pida,\par
Men bir garda\u351?dan jyda,\par
Bilge\u253? sen imti\u253?azym.\par
\par
\u350?e\u253?le boldy zamanlar,\par
\u350?ehit boldy k\u246?p janlar,\par
Keniz bolsun jenanlar\par
Budur \u253?ara ny\u253?azym.\par
\par
Magtymguly ilinde,\par
Bilbil sa\u253?rar g\u252?l\u252?nde,\par
Il-ulusy\u328? dilinde\par
Meni\u328? misgin hadysym.\par
\par
BELA BOLDY\par
Bizi\u328? mertler wepat kylyp,\par
Pelek ba\u351?a bela boldy.\par
Z\u252?r\u253?adyn pederden alyp,\par
Pelek ba\u351?a bela boldy.\par
\par
Ot boldy bu \u253?alan jahan,\par
Ne hy\u253?alda k\u246?\u328?\u252?l g\u252?man,\par
Go\u253?mady birini aman,\par
Pelek ba\u351?a bela boldy.\par
\par
Karuny p\u228?lden a\u253?yrdy,\par
Nuhy, bak, saldan a\u253?yrdy,\par
Bilbili g\u252?lden a\u253?yrdy,\par
Pelek ba\u351?a bela boldy.\par
\par
Ajal amanat kastynda,\par
Magtymguly, pa\u253? astynda,\par
Bu \u253?alan jahan \u252?st\u252?nde,\par
Pelek ba\u351?a bela boldy.\par
\par
DUMAN GITMEZ\par
Be\u253?ik daglary\u328? ba\u351?yndan,\par
Gy\u351?y-\u253?azy duman gitmez.\par
Synag bolmaz \u228?r da\u351?yndan,\par
Ne pa\u253?y-dest gylgyn a\u253?tmaz.\par
\par
Biri g\u246?\u231?er, biri gonsa,\par
Haram e\u253?l\u228?r, il guwansa,\par
A\u351?yk g\u246?z\u252?nde ot \u253?ansa,\par
Haka \u253?albaryp, dat etmez.\par
\par
Bu panyda terhosym bar,\par
Iki did\u228?mdir intizar,\par
Mert \u253?igit bolsa hary-zar,\par
\u214?m\u252?r tutan \u253?oldan ga\u253?tmaz.\par
\par
Pelek tutsa adam demin,\par
Lukman tapmaz onu\u328? emin,\par
Alan janyn gara zemin,\par
Ga\u253?dyp hyrydara satmaz.\par
\par
Mest \u253?igit sygmaz donuna\par
\u220?flasy tartar \u253?anyna,\par
Namartlar \u246?z juwanyna,\par
Pikir kylma\u328?, \u228?rlik etmez.\par
\par
Dilim uzyn, galdym derde,\par
Ne akyl-hu\u351? galdy serde,\par
Howatyry bolan \u253?erde,\par
\u221?\u252?rek edip, namart \u253?atmaz.\par
\par
Magtymguly, jebir g\u246?ren,\par
Jebir bilen yrak \u253?\u246?ren,\par
\u221?aradana s\u246?z\u252?n beren\par
\u214?l\u252?n\u231?\u228? ony unutmaz.\par
\par
GE\u199?IP BARAR\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, g\u246?zel \u246?mr\u252?m\par
Gojalypdyr, ge\u231?ip barar.\par
\u199?\u228?resiz, synamda derdim\par
G\u246?z\u252?n \u253?umup, u\u231?up barar.\par
\par
Istedim s\u246?wer garda\u351?y,\par
Pelek yrak atdy da\u351?y,\par
Jo\u351?gun atyp g\u246?z\u252?m \u253?a\u351?y,\par
\u214?r\u228?n hetden a\u351?yp barar.\par
\par
Derdim artdy bihasap,\par
Lukman soramaz nygtap,\par
Asmanymda mahytap,\par
Gol serip, \u253?a\u351?yp barar.\par
\par
M\u228?hnet indi ba\u351?yma,\par
Zalym geldi ga\u351?yma,\par
Namart-\u252?flas da\u351?yma,\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?in, \u252?\u253?\u351?\u252?p barar.\par
\par
K\u246?wkepler ba\u351?yn b\u252?r\u228?p,\par
Pelek \u231?arhyna sarap,\par
Jigerim narda kebap,\par
\u221?\u252?regim bi\u351?ip barar.\par
\par
Ne kuwwat bar, ne ga\u253?rat,\par
Ba\u351?yma d\u252?\u351?di apat,\par
Ol tutdygym ymarat,\par
We\u253?randyr, \u231?a\u351?yp barar.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? g\u246?rg\u252?si,\par
Gitmez ba\u351?dan bergisi,\par
Pany jahan gyrgysy\par
Z\u228?herin sa\u231?yp barar.\par
\par
Rahat \u253?atyrman d\u252?n\u253?\u228?,\par
Tutsa, sypdyrman d\u252?n\u253?\u228?,\par
Gu\u253?ruk tutdurman d\u252?n\u253?\u228?,\par
Gu\u351? kibi u\u231?up barar.\par
\par
Sylamaz begi-hany,\par
Dagy-dere, dumany,\par
Alda\u253?yp, alyp jany,\par
G\u246?r, pelek ga\u231?yp barar.\par
\par
B\u228?\u351? g\u252?n serim a\u253?la\u253?yn,\par
Merdi hemra e\u253?l\u228?\u253?in,\par
Magtymguly, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in\par
Ezra\u253?yl \u253?ap\u351?yp barar.\par
\par
O\u221?ANMAZ\par
E\u253?-\u228?, dostlar, \u231?\u246?ken bagtym,\par
Gije-g\u252?ndizi o\u253?anmaz.\par
Miwesin d\u246?ken daragtym,\par
Ne bahar-\u253?azy o\u253?anmaz.\par
\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, musulmanlar,\par
Ne p\u228?kiz \u246?tdi jenanlar.\par
La\u253? i\u231?inde \u231?\u246?ken janlar,\par
K\u246?llerim gazy o\u253?anmaz.\par
\par
Solupdyr baglary\u328? g\u252?li,\par
\u214?w\u252?smez Hazary\u328? \u253?eli,\par
Zakgun boldy arap dili,\par
Hindi owazy o\u253?anmaz.\par
\par
De\u328?im-du\u351?um dosty-\u253?aran.\par
Pelek bagrym \u253?\u252?zdi parran,\par
Magtymguly, pany jahan\par
I\u253?er-i\u231?er, jandan ganmaz.\par
\par
JANA GELDI\u327?\par
Adam ogly, g\u246?z\u252?\u328? bagly,\par
Ne \u252?\u231?in sen jana geldi\u328??\par
\u221?ortup jahany ulagly,\par
Gol m\u252?n\u252?p, zemine geldi\u328?.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?amana bakmady\u328?,\par
Gussa silinde akmady\u328?,\par
Bo\u253?nu\u328?a tanap dakmady\u328?,\par
Erkana zyndana geldi\u328?.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de \u253?okdur wepa,\par
\u199?eker boldu\u328? jebri-jepa,\par
Sezewar sen bir biwepa,\par
Biwepa jahana geldi\u328?.\par
\par
G\u252?ler me\u328?zi\u328?i solduran,\par
Nowg\u252?l\u252?n bagda \u253?olduran,\par
G\u246?z\u252?ni gana dolduran,\par
Bu jellat hareme geldi\u328?.\par
\par
Geldi\u328? munda jebr g\u246?rm\u228?ge,\par
M\u228?hnet \u231?ekip, \u253?urt \u253?\u246?rm\u228?ge,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?amany g\u246?rm\u228?ge,\par
Bu pany-\u253?alana geldi\u328?.\par
\par
Ho\u351? g\u252?n\u252?\u328? azdyr ba\u351?y\u328?da,\par
Je\u253?hun silidir da\u351?y\u328?da,\par
\u221?igrimi b\u228?\u351? sen \u253?a\u351?y\u328?da,\par
Bir ajap d\u246?wrana geldi\u328?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu ne akyl,\par
Di\u253? s\u246?z\u252?\u328?i, bolma bahyl,\par
Ozal-ahyr bardyr nakyl,\par
Sen indi pu\u351?mana geldi\u328?.\par
\par
ALAR BOLDU\u327?\par
Pelek, pelek, ne\u253?le\u253? pelek,\par
G\u246?zde nurum alar boldu\u328?.\par
En\u231?e janlar e\u253?l\u228?p hel\u228?k,\par
Zyndany\u328?a salar boldu\u328?.\par
\par
Pelek, pelek, gy\u253?a bakyp,\par
Jan alar sen hanjar sokup,\par
En\u231?e jany oda \u253?akyp,\par
Aman \u246?z\u252?\u328? galar boldu\u328?.\par
\par
Pelek seni\u328? namart gurdu\u328?,\par
We\u253?ran etdi g\u246?zel \u253?urdum,\par
Artdyryp ba\u351?ymda derdim,\par
Gazap e\u253?l\u228?p, alar boldu\u328?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?esir gu\u351?u\u328?,\par
Zyndandan galdyrmaz ba\u351?yn,\par
Pelek urupdyr garda\u351?y\u328?,\par
Gahar e\u253?l\u228?p geler boldu\u328?.\par
\par
AZ E\u221?LEDI\u327?\par
Ne\u253?le\u253?, pelek, gahba pelek,\par
\u350?at g\u252?nlerim az e\u253?ledi\u328?.\par
Kylyp n\u228?hak janlar hel\u228?k,\par
Dertlerime duz e\u253?ledi\u328?.\par
\par
\u221?umurdy\u328? belent daglary,\par
\u221?as kyldy\u328? ajap \u231?aglary,\par
Asman \u252?zre sen zaglary,\par
Ummanlara gaz e\u253?ledi\u328?.\par
\par
Han e\u253?l\u228?p il perrajyny,\par
Bo\u351?adyp sen a\u382?daryny,\par
Urup ajal hanjaryny,\par
Ga\u253?ta ba\u351?dan n\u228?z e\u253?ledi\u328?.\par
\par
Nuhy sen guwwas e\u253?le\u253?ip,\par
\u221?\u252?zd\u252?rdi\u328? yhlas e\u253?le\u253?ip,\par
\u350?at g\u252?nlerim \u253?as e\u253?le\u253?ip,\par
Gelip onda saz e\u253?ledi\u328?.\par
\par
Aza\u351?anlar girse \u253?ola,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l isl\u228?n ilse gola,\par
G\u246?zi \u253?a\u351?ly Magtymgula\par
Handan kylyp, baz e\u253?ledi\u328?.\par
\par
MERT BIL\u196?NI\par
\u199?yn \u228?rlerde galmaz arman,\par
D\u246?w\u252?\u351? kylsa mert bil\u228?ni.\par
Hijran bagtym kyldy we\u253?ran,\par
Ilim bilen, \u253?urt bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Pelek now\u231?a g\u252?ller \u253?olar,\par
Bilbili\u328? kararyn alar,\par
Ga\u253?a zarlap \u351?onda galar,\par
Akmasa sil kert bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Ajal \u246?\u328?\u252?nden gutarmaz,\par
Hemra di\u253?ip, \u228?r g\u246?termez,\par
Pele\u328?e zy\u253?an getirmez,\par
\u221?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? \u351?agal, gurt bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Pelek ba\u351?ym kyldy bendi,\par
\u221?umruldy ykbalym bendi,\par
Y\u351?kym s\u246?ndi, bagtym syndy,\par
Magtymguly, dert bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
PANY JAHANA DEGMEZ\par
Bir ni\u231?\u228?ni\u328? d\u246?wrany,\par
Pany jahana degmez.\par
En\u231?\u228?ni\u328? \u253?a\u328?\u328?y saly\par
Der\u253?a ummana degmez.\par
\par
K\u246?r golunda ta\u253?agy,\par
G\u246?z ornunda ta\u253?agy,\par
En\u231?eleri\u328? a\u253?agy\par
Ne har, \u231?amana degmez.\par
\par
Daglar ba\u351?y dumandyr,\par
\u221?eller da\u253?ym rowandyr,\par
En\u231?e daglar we\u253?randyr,\par
Gadry dumana degmez.\par
\par
Kimlere bermi\u351? maly,\par
Kimse g\u246?rer webaly,\par
Ni\u231?eleri\u328? ykbaly\par
Pany jahana degmez.\par
\par
G\u246?rki bar mermerleri\u328?,\par
Hudahydyr \u253?erleri\u328?,\par
G\u246?r\u252?\u328?, ni\u231?e pirleri\u328?\par
Goly Gurhana degmez.\par
\par
Menden ga\u253?ry \u253?ok otly,\par
Da\u253?ym ondan adatly,\par
Magtymguly hasratly,\par
Goly dessana degmez.\par
\par
OZAN GELER\par
D\u246?wlet ile geler bolsa,\par
Ba\u351?dan-burun ozan geler.\par
D\u246?wlet ilden giden bolsa,\par
Molla bilen tozan geler.\par
\par
Her kes \u246?z\u252?n mert di\u253?p sansa,\par
Ba\u351?yn uru\u328?, eger d\u246?nse,\par
Il i\u231?inde y\u351?yk \u253?ansa,\par
Ozal y\u351?ka gyzan geler.\par
\par
It g\u252?j\u252?gi ata \u231?eker,\par
La\u253?y g\u246?rse, do\u328?uz \u231?\u246?ker,\par
\u199?e\u351?me gazsa\u328?, suwy \u231?ykar,\par
Isl\u228?p, ony gazan geler.\par
\par
Hijran yraga atylsa,\par
\u214?ld\u252?rerler, gurt tutulsa,\par
Magtymguly, at tutulsa,\par
Ozal dessan \u253?azan geler.\par
\par
S\u214?Z MANYSYN BILMEGIN\u199?\u196?\par
Akyl s\u246?ze g\u252?ler nadan,\par
S\u246?z manysyn bilmegin\u231?\u228?.\par
Dag ba\u351?ynda durar duman,\par
Hazardan \u253?el gelmegin\u231?\u228?.\par
\par
Akly bolan \u351?erap i\u231?mez,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y ilden adam g\u246?\u231?mez,\par
\u221?aradan \u253?azygyn ge\u231?mez,\par
Gurhan \u253?\u252?ze sylmagyn\u231?a.\par
\par
Aryp akyl s\u246?z\u252?n s\u246?zl\u228?r,\par
Namart-pisat da\u351?yn g\u246?zl\u228?r,\par
\u199?\u246?le \u231?ykyp, ma\u253?a bozlar,\par
Torum g\u246?ze ilmegin\u231?\u228?.\par
\par
Dag ba\u351?yndan gary gitmez,\par
Namart ili\u328? \u253?um\u351?un etmez,\par
\u196?r \u253?igidi\u328? g\u246?wni bitmez,\par
Se\u231?ip jenan almagyn\u231?a.\par
\par
Goja \u253?igit paslyn \u231?aglar,\par
Bihuda jigerin daglar,\par
\u196?r \u253?igitler da\u253?ym aglar,\par
Merde hemra bolmagyn\u231?a.\par
\par
\u214?m\u252?r saly la\u253?a batar,\par
G\u252?nbe-g\u252?nden derdi artar,\par
Arly \u253?igit kine tutar,\par
Aryn ja\u253?a salmagyn\u231?a.\par
\par
Bu jahanda baky galmaz,\par
Pelek bize hemra bolmaz,\par
\u221?a\u351? balany\u328? gadry bolmaz,\par
Bir dem o\u253?nap g\u252?lmegin\u231?\u228?.\par
\par
G\u246?zele il hyrydardyr,\par
\u221?azany Perwerdig\u228?rdir,\par
Merdan \u253?igit bikarardyr,\par
\u221?ar go\u253?nuna dolmagyn\u231?a.\par
\par
G\u246?zler ni\u231?e \u253?aman g\u246?rir,\par
Diller \u253?aman-\u253?ag\u351?y soryr,\par
Ol sa\u253?\u253?atlar daga \u253?\u246?rir,\par
T\u228? gojalyp galmagyn\u231?a.\par
\par
Ismim d\u252?\u351?di ilden-ile,\par
Nag\u351? ederler dilden-dile,\par
Magtymguly, gongul g\u252?le,\par
Hazan urup solmagyn\u231?a.\par
\par
AMAN-AMAN\par
Beglermiz kylar ge\u328?e\u351?i,\par
Nadan pelek, aman-aman.\par
Ba\u351?a go\u253?ar sen te\u351?w\u252?\u351?i,\par
Nadan pelek, aman-aman.\par
\par
D\u246?wlet gu\u351?y asman galdy,\par
Hak sylady, nazar saldy,\par
A\u253?-g\u252?nler g\u246?r\u252?p u\u253?aldy,\par
Nadan pelek, aman-aman.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylar ge\u328?e\u351?in tutan,\par
Pelegi baky\u253?a atan,\par
Zyndan i\u231?re gapyl \u253?atan,\par
Nadan pelek, aman-aman.\par
\par
En\u231?e jebir kylar boldu\u328?,\par
Amanady alar boldu\u328?,\par
\u199?oh gerdi\u351?e salar boldu\u328?,\par
Nadan pelek, aman-aman.\par
\par
Namartlar \u253?olbars bolupdyr,\par
Zenan bary bars bolupdyr,\par
Ilim-g\u252?n\u252?m hyrs bolupdyr,\par
Nadan pelek, aman-aman.\par
\par
K\u246?p \u231?ekip men jebri-jepa\u328?,\par
Ro\u253?un g\u246?rmemi\u351?em sapa\u328?,\par
Destin tutdum ajap turpa\u328?,\par
Nadan pelek, aman-aman.\par
\par
Magtymguly di\u253?er aman,\par
\u221?akyn geldi ahyrzaman,\par
Dag serinde hijran duman,\par
Nadan pelek, aman-aman.\par
\par
BOLMAK HAKDYR\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, adam ogly,\par
Boz toprakdan bolmak hakdyr.\par
Asly h\u228?kden \u246?nen adam,\par
Guma garlyp galmak hakdyr.\par
\par
Kimler ga\u253?gy-hasrat bilen,\par
Kimler gamy-m\u228?hnet bilen,\par
Be\u253?an bolmu\u351? A\u253?at bilen,\par
\u214?lmek hak, direlmek hakdyr.\par
\par
Asy bolsa\u328? du\u351?du\u328? derde,\par
Ga\u253?gyda, hasratda, zarda,\par
Gara\u328?ky zulmatda \u8722? g\u246?rde,\par
Sorag-sowal bolmak hakdyr.\par
\par
Gelip \u253?aka\u328? tutsa ajal,\par
Ga\u253?yp bolar g\u246?zden bu hal,\par
Huru\u231? e\u253?l\u228?p \u231?yksa De\u231?jal,\par
A\u253?-G\u252?n zahyr kylmak hakdyr,\par
\par
\u350?erigat i\u351?ler galanda,\par
Zulmatdan \u228?lem dolanda,\par
Wadasy \u253?akyn gelende,\par
Ahyrzaman gopmak hakdyr.\par
\par
Kapyrlar \u231?oh gussa \u253?uwdup,\par
Resul derg\u228?hine \u253?etip,\par
Esrafyl mizanyn tutup,\par
Ha\u253?yr-\u351?eri\u328? \u231?ekmek hakdyr.\par
\par
Ol g\u252?n bolar ha\u253?bat, zulmat,\par
Ajap mizany-arasat,\par
Diwandyr Kazy\u253?y-Hajat,\par
Resul \u351?afkat kylmak hakdyr.\par
\par
Kim Syratdan gu\u351? dek u\u231?ar,\par
Kimseler m\u252?\u328? \u253?ylda ge\u231?er,\par
Asy gullar \u253?anar-\u246?\u231?er,\par
Tamug i\u231?re galmak hakdyr.\par
\par
Suwsana z\u228?her i\u231?dirler,\par
Ajyksa zakgun i\u253?dirler,\par
\u220?st\u252?nden i\u231?\u253?an \u253?agdyrlar,\par
\u221?ylan-m\u246?\u253?ler sokmak hakdyr.\par
\par
Onda galan bende aglar,\par
Otda jiger-bagryn daglar,\par
Ejiz galyp \u253?anan \u231?aglar,\par
\u220?\u253?ni sema \u231?ykmak hakdyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly aldym di\u253?r sen,\par
G\u252?\u253?\u231? bil\u228?ni kimden i\u253?r sen,\par
\u199?\u228?r\u228?\u328? \u253?okdur onda bi\u253?r sen,\par
Almak hakdyr, bermek hakdyr.\par
\par
JEM BOLUP\par
\u199?alyndyk\u231?a, jahan \u231?yr\u231?ygy artar,\par
Ha\u231?an k\u246?\u328?\u252?l karar tapar jem bolup?\par
Ahyret i\u351?i\u328? g\u246?r, mundan ba\u351? gutar,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni kim tutdy? - \u214?ter g\u252?m bolup.\par
\par
Dyrnak bilen daglar dilen Benijan,\par
Suwa, \u253?ele h\u246?kmi ge\u231?en S\u252?le\u253?man,\par
Hany ol Isgener, R\u252?stem p\u228?liwan,\par
Sen d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni tutajak sen kim bolup?\par
\par
Bu nurbatsyz d\u246?wranyndan - dat g\u252?n\u252?\u328?,\par
Eglenji \u253?ok, b\u246?kdenji \u253?ok - bat g\u252?n\u252?\u328?,\par
Oglanlykda, \u253?igitlikde - \u351?at g\u252?n\u252?\u328?,\par
Garrylykda ga\u253?dyp basar gam bolup.\par
\par
M\u228?lim i\u351?dir - ga\u253?dajakdyr gelenler,\par
Barar \u253?eri\u328? i\u351?in g\u246?rdi bilenler,\par
Ga\u253?gysyz \u253?atanlar, gapyl bolanlar,\par
Wa-hasrat-a, bo\u351? gitdiler kem bolup.\par
\par
Tapa bilse\u328? hakykaty\u328? merdini,\par
\u199?e\u351?mi\u328?e totu\u253?a kylgyl gerdini,\par
Gulzum de\u253? g\u252?n\u228?hi\u328? tere\u328?-derdini,\par
\u199?yn toba gurudar o\u328?a em bolup.\par
\par
Owwal \u246?z\u252?\u328? yhlasy\u328?y d\u252?zlegin,\par
Her k\u246?\u351?eden ny\u253?az okun gezlegin,\par
Bildigi\u328?\u231?e, mydam \u253?ag\u351?y s\u246?zlegin,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y s\u246?z tapmasa\u328?, otur sem bolup.\par
\par
Magtymguly, Alla adyn zikr e\u253?le,\par
\u221?amana sabr e\u253?le, \u253?ag\u351?a \u351?\u252?kr e\u253?le,\par
G\u246?r\u252?stany g\u246?r-de, otur, pikr e\u253?le,\par
Mun\u231?a men di\u253?enler, \u253?atyr gum bolup!\par
\par
A\u221?Y\u327? \u221?AG\u350?YSYN\par
\u221?igrimi d\u246?rt sagat on iki a\u253?da,\par
Remezan di\u253?erler a\u253?y\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
Pena d\u246?wranynda, \u253?eri\u328? \u253?\u252?z\u252?nde,\par
\u350?amy-\u351?erip di\u253?rler ja\u253?y\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
\par
\u221?a, \u253?aradan Kadyr, gudraty\u328? k\u228?ndir,\par
Ol gudrat i\u351?lere akyl ha\u253?randyr,\par
Pikir \u253?etmez, \u253?a Rep, ni\u231?ik pynhandyr,\par
Zulmat i\u231?re go\u253?du\u328? suwu\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
\par
Garga gu\u351? \u253?ara\u351?maz be\u253?ik baglarda,\par
G\u252?l \u252?st\u252?nde bilbil sa\u253?rar \u231?aglarda,\par
\u221?eri\u328? arkasynda, gen\u231?li daglarda,\par
A\u382?darha e\u253?el\u228?r zawy\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
\par
Eli\u328? \u253?etse, arzy\u328? a\u253?tsa\u328? Suhana,\par
Akyl ha\u253?ran bolar be\u253?le diwana,\par
\u221?\u252?rekde dert bolup deger hem jana,\par
\u350?agal \u253?aryp gitse awu\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
\par
Y\u351?k meni \u253?andyrdy, janym keseldir,\par
Dert ba\u351?dan a\u351?adyr, i\u351?im osaldyr,\par
Bu gadymdan bolup gelen meseldir,\par
Kirpi \u253?olar gider gawun \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
\par
Munys bolar dilin bilse\u328? wag\u351?yny\u328?,\par
Hakyn n\u228?hak e\u253?lemegin go\u328?\u351?yny\u328?,\par
Akly\u328? bolsa, abyra\u253?ly ki\u351?ini\u328?,\par
\u221?amanyn \u246?rt\u252?b\u228?n, \u253?a\u253?y\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu d\u246?wrana-zamana,\par
\u221?ag\u351?yny \u253?ygladyp, du\u351?yr \u253?amana,\par
Garda\u351?lary \u221?usup kimin janana,\par
Rowa g\u246?rmediler ja\u253?y\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
\par
AT \u221?ANYNDA BELLIDIR\par
E\u351?ek \u246?z\u252?n egsik sa\u253?maz bedewden,\par
Gymmat etse\u328?, at \u253?anynda bellidir.\par
Bedew di\u253?ge\u231?, hemme bedew de\u328? bolmaz,\par
\u199?yn bedewler me\u253?danynda bellidir.\par
\par
Oglanlykda bilmez idi\u328?, beg idi\u328?,\par
\u221?amana hi\u231? \u253?okmaz s\u246?z\u252?\u328?, \u246?w\u252?di\u328?,\par
Aryp bolsa\u328?, aslyn sorma \u253?igidi\u328?,\par
Edebinde, erkanynda bellidir.\par
\par
Bu jahanda do\u253?maz g\u246?z\u252?\u328? sir bolmaz,\par
Her \u253?olbarsdan gapla\u328? bolmaz, \u351?ir bolmaz,\par
\u221?igit di\u253?ge\u231?, hemme \u253?igit bir bolmaz,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igitler myhmanynda bellidir.\par
\par
D\u246?wlet gonsa bolajagy\u328? ba\u351?ynda,\par
Hema\u253?aty \u8722? ili gerek da\u351?ynda,\par
\u221?igit \u246?z\u252?n m\u228?lim eder i\u351?inde,\par
Gylyjynda, zybanynda bellidir.\par
\par
Magtymguly, garyplary\u328? g\u246?z\u253?a\u351?y,\par
Daglary \u253?andyryp, erider da\u351?y,\par
Pakyra zulum eden zalymy\u328? i\u351?i,\par
Rozy-mag\u351?ar diwanynda bellidir.\par
\par
JO\u350?Y \u221?ANDYRAR\par
Wagt olar ki, bir \u253?el d\u252?\u351?er serime,\par
Hy\u253?al h\u252?j\u252?m e\u253?l\u228?p, jo\u351?y \u253?andyrar.\par
\u221?\u252?regim jo\u351? berse, aklym jem bolar,\par
Pikir basar, ga\u253?gy hu\u351?y \u253?andyrar.\par
\par
S\u228?her wagty derw\u252?\u351? naly\u351?a gelse,\par
Bilinden \u253?\u252?p alyp, bo\u253?nuna salsa,\par
Ta\u328?ry s\u246?\u253?en bende bet doga kylsa,\par
Pelegi titreder, ar\u351?y \u253?andyrar.\par
\par
Akmak \u246?z\u252?n akyl bilen de\u328? e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
Bir i\u351? tutar, so\u328?rasyndan a\u328? e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
Zehini\u328? k\u228?\u253?ider, akly\u328? te\u328? e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
Di\u253?digi\u328? e\u253?lemez, na\u351?y \u253?andyrar.\par
\par
Hak s\u246?\u253?\u252?pdir Aly de\u253?in welisin,\par
Gadym setdir yzzat etmek ulusyn,\par
\u221?etmi\u351? iki millet g\u246?mer \u246?l\u252?sin,\par
Segparaz milleti l\u228?\u351?i \u253?andyrar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, Hakdan py\u253?ala \u231?ekse,\par
Py\u253?ala jo\u351? berip, hy\u253?ala \u231?ekse,\par
A\u351?yklar bagryndan bir nala \u231?ekse,\par
Dagy elendirer, da\u351?y \u253?andyrar.\par
\par
JO\u350? GELSE\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de ni\u231?e i\u351? bardyr, \u253?amandyr,\par
Biri ol kim, \u253?ersiz gahry jo\u351? gelse.\par
A\u351?yga her bir g\u252?n ahyrzamandyr,\par
\u221?ardan yrak d\u252?\u351?\u252?p, ara da\u351? gelse.\par
\par
Dostu\u328?y egleme, nepden galmasyn,\par
Du\u351?many\u328? saklama, syry\u328? bilmesin,\par
A\u231?da algy\u328?, bege bergi\u328? bolmasyn,\par
I\u351? m\u252?\u351?gildir, a\u328?lamaza du\u351? gelse.\par
\par
Zemin seni h\u228?li-h\u228?li \u253?uwtarmy,\par
Akyl be\u253?le \u253?erde bigam \u253?atarmy,\par
Hi\u231? bir masgaralyk mundan \u246?termi,\par
Giden gury gitse, gelen bo\u351? gelse.\par
\par
On gat \u246?\u253?\u252?\u328? bolsa demir galadan,\par
Ajal tapar emr bolsa Alladan,\par
Hakykat \u228?r \u253?\u252?z d\u246?ndermez beladan,\par
Hak ryzasy bilen ba\u351?a da\u351? gelse.\par
\par
Sopy men di\u253?p, lap urarlar \u253?alandan,\par
Manysyny sorgul belli bilenden,\par
Il g\u246?z\u252?n\u231?e \u253?\u252?z \u253?yl tagat kylandan,\par
\u221?ag\u351?ydyr bir s\u228?her g\u246?zden \u253?a\u351? gelse.\par
\par
Ba\u253?lar baglap sahawaty\u328? gapysyn,\par
K\u246?pelder tamugy\u328? m\u246?\u253?\u252?n-apysyn,\par
G\u246?r\u252?\u328? bu e\u253?\u253?amy\u328? \u8722? wagty\u328? sopusyn,\par
Dannamaz-da dykar otyr a\u351? gelse.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?\u253?le akly\u328? \u253?etin\u231?\u228?,\par
Ky\u253?amaty\u328? gazan bik\u228?r \u253?atyn\u231?a,\par
Tamugdadyr t\u228? d\u252?n\u253?\u228?den \u246?tin\u231?\u228?,\par
\u221?aman hatyn \u253?ag\u351?y \u228?re du\u351? gelse.\par
\par
AR BILE\par
Dyrnagy demirden tala\u328?\u231?y d\u252?n\u253?\u228?,\par
I\u351?i\u328? \u253?okdur namys bile, ar bile.\par
Jebri-jepasy k\u246?p, \u253?alan\u231?y d\u252?n\u253?\u228?,\par
Go\u253?maz sen gezm\u228?ge \u253?ary-\u253?ar bile.\par
\par
Muhabbet \u246?wj\u252?nden \u253?ar bir gel di\u253?se,\par
Matlaby\u328?y ist\u228?p, menden al di\u253?se,\par
Bir g\u252?n durdu\u328?, bir gije hem gal di\u253?se,\par
Gadam go\u253?sam a\u253?ak \u253?erne ser bile.\par
\par
\u214?sd\u252?k\u231?e \u246?wj artdyr d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? \u253?eli,\par
Kast etse, gurudar der\u253?a\u253?y-Nili,\par
Bir g\u252?nde esredip, mest eder pili,\par
Bir g\u252?nde nist e\u253?l\u228?r pe\u351?e per bile.\par
\par
Zemini\u328? \u252?st\u252?nde daglar \u231?\u246?k\u228?r sen,\par
Toma\u351?ag\u228?r bolup, kes\u228? \u231?ykar sen,\par
Her nesn\u228?ni bir wesile \u253?akar sen,\par
J\u252?lg\u228?ni g\u252?n bile, dagy gar bile.\par
\par
Dalmynyp, dat etse, gulak tutmaz sen,\par
\u221?yglap, \u253?a\u351? d\u246?kene rehim etmez sen,\par
Jan matagyn alsa\u328?, ga\u253?dyp satmaz sen,\par
\u221?ene d\u246?n\u252?p almak olmaz zer bile.\par
\par
Le\u253?li \u252?\u231?in ne jebr etdi\u328? Mejnuna,\par
Zalym, ynsap e\u253?le bu n\u228?hak huna,\par
G\u252?nde kyrk at bez\u228?p berdi\u328? Karuna,\par
Isa mydar berdi\u328? \u253?eke har bile.\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, i\u351?i\u328? tala\u328?dyr,\par
Bu nobat \u231?ohlardan ge\u231?ip gelendir,\par
Ygtybary\u328? \u253?okdur, s\u246?z\u252?\u328? \u253?alandyr,\par
Dost go\u253?mady\u328?, \u253?egsan etdi\u328? \u253?er bile.\par
\par
ADAMZAT\par
\u221?atsa-tursa hy\u253?alyndan \u231?ykarmaz,\par
Ha\u253?sy i\u351?e ma\u253?yl bolsa adamzat.\par
Garyplygy\u328? gamy k\u246?\u328?l\u252?n \u231?\u246?kermez,\par
A\u253?al ist\u228?p, sa\u253?yl bolsa adamzat.\par
\par
G\u252?n\u228?den gorkmany\u328? \u253?\u252?zi sy\u253?adyr,\par
Munu\u328? m\u228?lim g\u252?ni rozy-jezadyr,\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? m\u252?lk\u252?nde soltandyr, \u351?adyr,\par
Kysmatyna ka\u253?yl bolsa adamzat.\par
\par
Ykballyny\u328? ugran i\u351?i o\u328? g\u246?rner,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u253?\u252?zi ele girse, te\u328? g\u246?rner,\par
Jahyllykda ge\u231?en i\u351?ler ge\u328? g\u246?rner,\par
Kyrkdan a\u351?yp, a\u253?yl bolsa adamzat.\par
\par
Her ki\u351?i kim, s\u246?z manyga d\u252?\u351?m\u228?ndir,\par
Bir dertlidir \u8722? o\u328?a derman du\u351?mandyr,\par
Ky\u253?amat g\u252?n bar talaby pu\u351?madyr,\par
Hak i\u351?ine k\u228?hil bolsa adamzat.\par
\par
Akyl et jahany\u328? ra\u253?yn, r\u246?w\u351?\u252?n,\par
Ygtybar etmegin d\u252?n\u253?\u228? duru\u351?yn,\par
Magtymguly, \u253?ag\u351?y g\u246?rerdi i\u351?in,\par
Kyrkyndan so\u328? jahyl bolsa adamzat.\par
\par
BIWEPALARDAN\par
G\u246?zl\u228?p k\u246?\u328?\u252?l berme biwepalara,\par
Bak, kim wepa g\u246?rm\u252?\u351? biwepalardan.\par
Go\u253?ma \u246?z\u252?\u328? \u253?ersiz bu jepalara,\par
Kim b\u228?hre tapypdyr bu jepalardan.\par
\par
Y\u351?ky\u328? owazasyn di\u328?le da\u351?yndan,\par
Jan jebrinden gorksa\u328?, barma ba\u351?yndan,\par
Seri\u351?d\u228?\u328? kem bolsa y\u351?ky\u328? i\u351?inden,\par
Bar, habar al g\u246?ren m\u252?btelalardan.\par
\par
S\u246?z\u252?m nesihatdyr, bir gulak saly\u328?,\par
Bendesi men s\u246?ze hyrydar gulu\u328?,\par
Kyrk o\u253?na\u351?ly hatyn \u253?ag\u351?ydyr, bili\u328?,\par
\u350?ere\u328?\u328?iz k\u246?p dilli kethudalardan.\par
\par
\u350?eraban-tahurdan kime jam bolar,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l g\u246?zgi kimin nur-enwer bolar,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u253?edi ba\u351?ly \u253?almawuz bolar,\par
Ga\u231?anlar gutulmaz bu belalardan.\par
\par
\u221?atma, Magtymguly, e\u351?reti\u328? s\u246?\u253?\u252?p,\par
Mun\u231?a \u253?atajak sen kepeni\u328? ge\u253?ip,\par
Hajatyn taparmy, hojasyn go\u253?up,\par
Dileg eden kimse gul-gedalardan!?\par
\par
A\u221?-G\u220?N\u220?\u327?IZ BATMAGA\par
Altmy\u351? \u253?a\u351?ly, \u253?etmi\u351? \u253?ylky sopular,\par
Az galypdyr A\u253?-G\u252?n\u252?\u328?iz batmaga.\par
\u199?\u246?l-derede tazy g\u246?rm\u228?n tilkiler,\par
Hy\u253?al eder \u253?atan \u351?iri atmaga.\par
\par
Garga a\u253?dar: \u171?\u221?okdur men dek \u351?abaza\u187?,\par
M\u252?\u328? garga \u253?ygylsa, degmez bir baza,\par
G\u252?ne gargy\u351? eden sary kelpeze,\par
Dem \u231?ekedir a\u382?darhany \u253?uwtmaga.\par
\par
\u221?eke ke\u253?ik \u253?\u252?z torsuga tutdurmaz,\par
\u350?ir be\u231?esi togsan tilk\u228? atdyrmaz,\par
\u214?li \u253?ylan \u253?\u252?z kelpez\u228? \u253?uwtdurmaz,\par
Hany akly\u328? bu i\u351?lere \u253?etm\u228?ge.\par
\par
\u221?etmi\u351? \u253?a\u351?ap, \u253?at etmezler tobany,\par
Horram bile o\u253?nadyrlar gahbany,\par
Kapyrlar kast edip \u253?yksa K\u228?b\u228?ni,\par
M\u252?\u328?k\u252?r barar agajyny satmaga.\par
\par
G\u246?r\u252?\u328? bu e\u253?\u253?amy, baky\u328? gerdi\u351?i,\par
Pakyra zulum etmek boldy werzi\u351?i,\par
Hak \u253?olunda dogry gezen derw\u252?\u351?i,\par
Go\u253?madylar \u246?z halyna \u253?atmaga.\par
\par
\u221?\u252?regim sabyrdan, gider karardan,\par
\u221?aman i\u351?dir buguz bolmak \u228?r \u228?rden,\par
Bizara gelip men be\u253?le di\u253?ardan,\par
J\u252?r bolup men ba\u351?ym alyp gitm\u228?ge.\par
\par
Magtymguly bildim, bagtym biwe\u231?dir,\par
Gybatym g\u252?\u253?\u231?l\u252?dir, ykbalym ke\u231?dir,\par
Ni\u253?etim K\u228?bedir, hy\u253?alym ha\u231?dyr,\par
Yhlasym bar ha\u231? togabyn etm\u228?ge.\par
\par
D\u220?\u221?\u350?\u220?NE DEGMEZ\par
\u221?oksullykda ni\u231?eleri\u328? d\u246?wrany,\par
\u221?atyp, \u253?ag\u351?y g\u246?ren d\u252?\u253?\u351?\u252?ne degmez.\par
Ni\u231?eler hasratda tapyp h\u246?\u351?k nany,\par
Bir lezzetli tagam di\u351?ine degmez.\par
\par
Soran bolsa, synam i\u231?re suzlar bar,\par
\u221?\u252?z t\u252?menden \u253?egdir, ni\u231?e s\u246?zler bar,\par
Ne\u253?sansyz, nebatsyz ni\u231?e \u253?azlar bar,\par
Ho\u351?luk bilen ge\u231?en gy\u351?yna degmez.\par
\par
Akyllar bar \u8722? ba\u351?a baglap ke\u231?eler,\par
I\u231?gin-i\u231?gin sorsa\u328?, many se\u231?eler,\par
Akmaklykda \u246?z\u252?n bez\u228?p ni\u231?eler,\par
Kellesine saran pe\u351?ine degmez.\par
\par
A\u328?lamaza a\u253?at s\u246?zlerin di\u253?se\u328?,\par
Pygamber hadysyn \u246?\u328?\u252?nde go\u253?sa\u328?,\par
Gy\u253?mazlykda m\u252?\u328? s\u246?z be\u253?nisne gu\u253?sa\u328?,\par
Ol s\u246?zler gulagny\u328? da\u351?yna degmez.\par
\par
Ynjytsa ogul-gyz ene-atasyn,\par
Toba kylma\u253?, Hak ge\u231?irmez hatasyn,\par
D\u246?wran gelse bilmez, ne i\u351? tutasyn,\par
Her kimi\u328? her i\u351?de ba\u351?yna degmez.\par
\par
Ni\u231?eler mal tapmaz, te\u328?i-dest bolar,\par
Ni\u231?eler bar - d\u252?n\u253?\u228?likde mest bolar,\par
Ni\u231?eler bar - \u253?igitlikde nist bolar,\par
Ni\u231?eler bar - s\u252?ren \u253?a\u351?yna degmez.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ger\u231?e i\u351?im namazdyr,\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?m peri\u351?andyr, s\u228?hwim derazdyr,\par
\u196?rler bar - m\u252?\u328? t\u252?men i\u253?dirse\u328? azdyr,\par
Adam bardyr - i\u253?en a\u351?yna degmez.\par
\par
DUZ HEM BOLMASA\par
Togsan d\u252?rli tagam bolsa ga\u351?y\u328?da,\par
Ne lezzet i\u231?inde duz hem bolmasa.\par
Ne biler sen ne i\u351? bardyr ba\u351?y\u328?da,\par
M\u252?\u351?gil i\u351?dir ba\u351?da g\u246?z hem bolmasa.\par
\par
A\u253?ak bar \u253?\u246?rm\u228?ge, el bar almaga,\par
Hany bende, saglyk \u351?\u252?kr\u252?n kylmaga,\par
Gulak bardyr e\u351?idenin bilm\u228?ge,\par
Kim d\u252?zeder dilde s\u246?z hem bolmasa.\par
\par
\u221?ok \u253?erden jan berip, \u253?etirdi nany,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l bossanynda biter imany,\par
Ady\u328? bende bolsa, E\u253?\u228?\u328?i tany,\par
Gelip, sa\u328?a \u253?\u252?zbe-\u253?\u252?z hem bolmasa.\par
\par
Kysmatyn hak bilen ryzkyn azlamaz,\par
S\u246?z bilenler bilen s\u246?z\u252?n gizlemez,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l jo\u351?a gelmez, dil hem s\u246?zlemez,\par
Her \u253?\u252?rekde y\u351?kdan k\u246?z hem bolmasa.\par
\par
\u221?yl-\u253?yldan fazyhat artar e\u253?\u253?ama,\par
Haky\u328? \u214?zi getirmese enjama,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? s\u246?zi me\u328?z\u228?r duzsuz tagama,\par
S\u246?z i\u231?inde gelin-gyz hem bolmasa.\par
\par
\u221?um g\u246?z\u252?\u328?i, gysyp gezgin di\u351?i\u328?i,\par
\u221?aza \u253?etse\u328?, unutmagyn gy\u351?y\u328?y,\par
T\u246?wekgel et, Ta\u328?ra tab\u351?yr i\u351?i\u328?i,\par
Sabyr bilen biter tiz hem bolmasa.\par
\par
Magtymguly, hy\u253?al d\u252?\u351?\u252?p \u246?z\u252?me,\par
K\u246?p toma\u351?a gelip, ge\u231?er g\u246?z\u252?me,\par
E\u351?idenler, a\u253?p etmesin s\u246?z\u252?me,\par
Iller kimin s\u246?z\u252?m uz hem bolmasa.\par
\par
DA\u350? D\u214?KER\par
Akmak bilen syrda\u351? bolsa\u328? bir sagat,\par
Pynhan syry\u328? sakla bilme\u253?, da\u351? d\u246?ker.\par
Dostluk a\u231?sa\u328? bir biwepa \u253?ar bilen,\par
Ga\u253?gy birlen dahany\u328?dan di\u351? d\u246?ker.\par
\par
Bedasyl g\u246?termez b\u228?\u351? g\u252?n mesligi,\par
Kelpez\u228? \u253?uwtdurmaz a\u382?dar maslygy,\par
Bilgil, uzak gitmez a\u253?y dostlugy,\par
Gahry gelse, dep\u228?\u328? \u252?zre da\u351? d\u246?ker.\par
\par
Bedewi tanymaz har bakan-besl\u228?n,\par
Jomardy il tanar, adyly \u8722? diwan,\par
Aty me\u253?dan tanar, h\u252?mmeti \u8722? myhman,\par
Jomart ogly supra \u253?a\u253?yp, a\u351? d\u246?ker.\par
\par
\u221?igidi\u328? maksady: mahbup, \u253?arag, at,\par
Il \u252?st\u252?nde namys getir biga\u253?rat,\par
Obada je\u328? tapsa, sansyz bid\u246?wlet,\par
Mert ogluny\u328? depesinden mu\u351? d\u246?ker.\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, \u253?igitler ba\u351?y,\par
Mejlisde k\u246?p bolar onu\u328? syrda\u351?y,\par
Je\u328? wagtynda \u253?igitleri\u328? ba\u351?da\u351?y -\par
Il \u252?st\u252?nde namys bilen ba\u351? d\u246?ker.\par
\par
D\u214?WRAN TAPYLMAZ\par
Dogama du\u351? gelen g\u246?gerer g\u252?l dek,\par
G\u252?l\u252?\u328? m\u246?ws\u252?mi dek d\u246?wran tapylmaz.\par
Gahrymy\u328? ata\u351?y k\u246?\u253?d\u252?rer k\u252?l dek,\par
K\u252?l ornundan ga\u253?dyp bossan tapylmaz.\par
\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l mysapyrdyr, jeset \u253?urtdadyr,\par
Janym jo\u351?gundadyr, \u253?\u252?rek dertdedir,\par
K\u252?\u253?\u252?m k\u228?mildedir, g\u246?z\u252?m mertdedir,\par
\u350?um \u351?ert\u228?mden hi\u231? bir merdan tapylmaz.\par
\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l go\u253?gul g\u246?zel Alla k\u246?\u253?\u252?ne,\par
Me\u351?gul bolup \u253?atma mala, o\u253?una,\par
Adamzat myhmandyr d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u246?\u253?\u252?ne,\par
Bir g\u252?n \u246?\u253? i\u231?inde myhman tapylmaz.\par
\par
Gaflat i\u231?re gapyl \u253?atma, turawer,\par
Her ne berse\u328?, \u246?z eli\u328?-le berewer,\par
Dirilikde \u246?l\u252?m i\u351?in g\u246?rewer,\par
Bir g\u252?n jeset i\u231?re bu jan tapylmaz.\par
\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l awla\u253?yn di\u253?p ugrasam her \u253?an,\par
Dawadyr, d\u246?w\u252?\u351?dir, k\u228?\u253?i\u351? tapar jan,\par
A\u253?dylmaz nesihat, okalmaz Gurhan,\par
Jana \u253?akar edep-erkan tapylmaz.\par
\par
Derg\u228?he dogam k\u246?p, naly\u351?ym bihet,\par
T\u228?le\u253?im zebundyr, tenim bikuwwat,\par
Ga\u231?gynym k\u246?pl\u252?kdir, istegim hylwat,\par
Ma\u328?a hi\u231? bir ja\u253?y-pynhan tapylmaz.\par
\par
Magtymguly, jan takdyra ten berdi,\par
Her kim \u246?z\u252?n sakla\u253? bilse, i\u351? g\u246?rdi,\par
Ha\u253?, ne \u253?aman zatdyr, a\u328?lamaz derdi,\par
Jahyllyk derdine derman tapylmaz.\par
\par
DA\u350?Y SYNDYRAR\par
Ykbaly\u328? o\u253?ansa, d\u246?wlet \u253?ar bolsa,\par
Daga azy ursa\u328?, da\u351?y syndyrar.\par
T\u228?le\u253?i\u328? ters gelse, bagty\u328? \u351?or bolsa,\par
\u171?Paluda\u187? di\u253?en a\u351? di\u351?i syndyrar.\par
\par
Ajaly\u328?dan gorkup girse\u328? ummana,\par
Gorkudan ne pe\u253?da gidejek jana,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328? ahyr bolup, dolsa pe\u253?mana,\par
Ha\u351?ha\u351?y\u328? samany ba\u351?y syndyrar.\par
\par
Bar s\u246?z\u252?ne gulak go\u253?gul bileni\u328?,\par
Ahyry hi\u231? \u253?ere \u253?etmez \u253?alany\u328?,\par
\u214?m\u252?r saly artar alky\u351? alany\u328?,\par
Gargy\u351? galyndyrmaz, \u253?a\u351?y syndyrar.\par
\par
Akyly\u328? s\u246?z\u252?ne k\u246?\u328?\u252?l s\u246?\u253?\u252?ner,\par
Akmagy\u328? i\u351?ine zehin k\u228?\u253?iner,\par
Muhannes gi\u328? \u253?erde akyl sa\u253?ynar,\par
Dar \u253?erde akyly-hu\u351?y syndyrar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u231?\u246?lde gezen na\u351?yny,\par
Bilik sorma, k\u246?p s\u252?rdi di\u253?p \u253?a\u351?yny,\par
Dar mejlisde doly berse\u328? k\u228?\u351?ini,\par
A\u351?yn i\u253?e bilmez, k\u228?\u351?i syndyrar.\par
\par
\u199?AGDYR BU \u199?AGLAR\par
S\u228?her wagty gapyl bolma\u328?, \u253?aranlar,\par
Derg\u228?hler a\u231?ylar \u231?agdyr bu \u231?aglar.\par
Rehmete du\u351? geldi bu wagt erenler,\par
Hak nury sa\u231?ylar \u231?agdyr bu \u231?aglar.\par
\par
Asy bolma, g\u252?n\u228?hi\u328?den \u253?anawer,\par
\u214?z\u252?\u328? tany, menligi\u328?den inewer,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y wagtdyr, toba kylyp, d\u246?newer,\par
\u221?azyklar ge\u231?iler \u231?agdyr bu \u231?aglar.\par
\par
Hak seni saklasyn hijran \u8722? \u253?alyndan,\par
Aza\u351?magyn \u253?ol\u231?ulary\u328? \u253?olundan,\par
Muhabbet jamlary dostu\u328? elinden,\par
H\u228?zir bol, i\u231?iler \u231?agdyr bu \u231?aglar.\par
\par
\u221?\u252?z \u253?yl gezse\u328? \u253?alan\u231?yny s\u252?r\u252?b\u228?n,\par
Ten topraga d\u246?ner bir g\u252?n erib\u228?n,\par
\u221?okluk me\u253?danynda mejlis guruban,\par
Menlikden ge\u231?iler \u231?agdyr bu \u231?aglar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, gitdi\u328? d\u252?n\u253?\u228? k\u246?\u253?\u252?ne,\par
Jahyllykda k\u246?\u328?\u252?l go\u253?du\u328? o\u253?una,\par
Imdi a\u253?ak basdy\u328? otuz \u246?\u253?\u252?ne,\par
G\u246?z \u253?a\u351?y sa\u231?ylar \u231?agdyr bu \u231?aglar.\par
\par
BIR-BIRINE BEZENIP\par
Musulmanlar, maly-d\u252?n\u253?\u228? ma\u253?asy,\par
G\u246?r\u252?nmekdir bir-birine bezenip.\par
\u221?igitler n\u228?z, gyz kere\u351?me e\u253?esi,\par
P\u228?liwanlar me\u253?dan g\u246?zl\u228?r d\u252?zenip.\par
\par
Ajal go\u253?mu\u351? ok-kezini kiri\u351?e,\par
Bilip bolmaz, n\u228?wagt jana eri\u351?e,\par
Ne durup sen aga-d\u246?ne \u253?\u246?ri\u351?e,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328? ugur alyp gitmez uzanyp.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? da\u351?y\u328? demir duzak torla\u253?yp,\par
Ajal \u351?iri a\u328?tap \u253?atyr g\u246?zle\u253?ip,\par
Sen parahat ukusynda horla\u253?yp,\par
Kaza gyly\u231? \u231?ekip durmu\u351? gezenip.\par
\par
Utanmady\u328? Hakdan, agardyp ri\u351?i\u328?,\par
Gybatdan dil d\u246?nmez, haramdan - di\u351?i\u328?,\par
Penada g\u246?rewer bakalyk i\u351?i\u328?,\par
Gapyl galyp \u253?atma her dem i\u328?renip.\par
\par
Hamu kimse g\u246?rer hasaply demi,\par
Takdyr ajalyny\u328? tapylmaz emi,\par
Magtymguly, galmaz egsigi-kemi,\par
Her kim bara bilse iman gazanyp.\par
\par
BU I\u350?I\par
Bende, sen bet i\u351?e batyrlyk etme,\par
Alny\u328?da go\u253?arlar ol g\u252?n bu i\u351?i.\par
Nebse u\u253?ma, \u351?e\u253?tan ra\u253?yna gitme,\par
Hyjalata go\u253?ar, bilgin bu i\u351?i.\par
\par
Nebsi\u328? a\u253?dar: \u171?Urgun, bu bir h\u246?zirdir!\u187?\par
Jany\u328? a\u253?dar: \u171?Ha\u253?, dur, Ta\u328?ry h\u228?zirdir!\u187?\par
Sen g\u246?rmese\u328?, Ol-ha sa\u328?a nazyrdyr,\par
Utangyn, e\u253?mengin, go\u253?gun bu i\u351?i.\par
\par
Bir \u253?olda g\u252?n\u228? bar, bir \u253?olda sogap,\par
Arasatda senden ist\u228?rler jogap,\par
Halala hasap bar, harama - azap,\par
\u350?eki \u253?okdur, \u253?ada salgyn bu i\u351?i.\par
\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328? ge\u231?ip baran \u253?azdyr bir sagat,\par
Ne bolar, bu \u253?azda e\u253?lese\u328? tagat,\par
Sogaba \u351?atlyk bar, j\u252?rme - hyjalat,\par
Bo\u253?nu\u328?a almagyn, gelgin, bu i\u351?i.\par
\par
Ba\u351?y\u328? g\u246?ge, g\u246?ws\u252?\u328? \u253?ele g\u246?terme,\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?\u328?e gorkyny \u231?ala getirme,\par
\u221?\u252?rekde \u253?ok s\u246?zi dile getirme,\par
Yhlas gulagyna \u231?algyn bu i\u351?i.\par
\par
Mysapyr sen, mukym i\u351?in gurar sen,\par
Bibaka d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de ni\u231?e durar sen,\par
Munda ne i\u351? etse\u328?, onda g\u246?rer sen,\par
\u221?ag\u351?ydyr, \u253?amandyr ol g\u252?n bu i\u351?i.\par
\par
\u350?e\u253?tan a\u253?dar: \u171?\u350?irin i\u351?dir, azago\u253?!\u187?\par
Rahman a\u253?dar: \u171?Nebs umydyn \u252?zego\u253?!\u187?\par
Magtymguly: \u171?Tur golu\u328?y k\u246?ze go\u253?,\par
Eger d\u246?ze bilse\u328?, kylgyn bu i\u351?i!\u187?\par
\par
BIR G\u214?R\u220?P GITSE DA\u350?YMDAN\par
Hemdert olup, i\u231?gin-i\u231?gin sorma\u253?yn,\par
N\u228? bilsin bir g\u246?r\u252?p gitse da\u351?ymdan.\par
K\u228?mil bolup, jan gulagyn burma\u253?yn,\par
A\u253?da bilmen \u246?ten i\u351?i ba\u351?ymdan.\par
\par
A\u328?la\u253? bilmen, ahyrym ne terze men,\par
K\u246?p wagtlar go\u351?ulmadym herze men,\par
\u221?aradandan \u253?etmi\u351? \u253?edi ryza men,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman, her ne gelse ba\u351?ymdan.\par
\par
E\u253? hakarat bile bakan bizlere,\par
Mejaz bilip, m\u252?\u328?k\u252?r bolma s\u246?zlere,\par
Halal lukma \u253?agtylyk bi\u253?r g\u246?zlere,\par
Tutuldygy\u328? bilgil, nan-u a\u351?ymdan.\par
\par
Arpa nany besdir, tapsa\u328? damaga,\par
\u214?m\u252?r bakasyzdyr, d\u252?\u351?me tamaga,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l \u171?H\u252?w!\u187? di\u253?r turar, su\u253?y-asmana,\par
El \u252?zsem di\u253?r, k\u246?w\u252?\u351?, muze, pe\u351?imden.\par
\par
Magtymguly \u231?ekip du\u351?man neharyn,\par
Pi\u351?\u228?m \u253?uwutmakdyr \u253?aman gaharyn,\par
\u214?t\u252?rip men \u253?igitligi\u328? baharyn,\par
Gutulmak \u253?ok garrylygy\u328? gy\u351?yndan.\par
\par
BERME PELEGE\par
Pelek bazy bermi\u351? j\u252?mle-jahana,\par
Meni\u328? ygty\u253?arym berme pelege.\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l gu\u351?y u\u231?up gitse her \u253?ana,\par
M\u228?t\u228?\u231? etme ganat, gu\u253?ruk, \u253?elege.\par
\par
Bid\u246?wlet \u8722? ynanja\u328?, k\u228?sip \u8722? k\u228?\u253?inje\u328?,\par
\u221?edi \u253?eser bolsa, biri g\u246?w\u252?nje\u328?,\par
Ba\u253? halky \u253?a\u328?ra bor, garry \u8213? \u246?w\u252?nje\u328?,\par
\u199?alyp bolmaz \u231?al agarsa \u231?elege.\par
\par
Orda ba\u351?y bolmak \u228?re kyn bolar,\par
Par\u231?a ge\u253?se, gyz-oglana syn bolar,\par
Dul g\u246?z\u252?ne garry n\u228?zenin bolar,\par
\u221?ene g\u246?z\u252?n a\u253?lar k\u246?re, \u231?olaga.\par
\par
\u199?epine a\u253?lanan \u231?arhy-pelekdir,\par
Adam ogly - gelen bary hel\u228?kdir,\par
\u221?etmi\u351? iki millet b\u246?lek-b\u246?lekdir,\par
Bu b\u246?lekden go\u351?ma \u246?zge b\u246?lege.\par
\par
\u221?ol \u252?st\u252?nde \u246?lsem, \u253?ola atsalar,\par
Razy men \u252?st\u252?mden basyp \u246?tseler,\par
\u171?Magtymguly\u187? di\u253?ip adym tutsalar,\par
G\u246?ren g\u246?z jort atar e\u351?den gulaga.\par
\par
A\u221?RYLMA\par
Mestana \u253?\u246?rin\u231?\u228?\u328? ga\u253?ry \u253?urdunda,\par
\u214?n\u252?p-\u246?sen \u246?z \u253?urdu\u328?dan a\u253?rylma.\par
Magrur k\u228?kilik de\u253? nebsi\u328? ugrunda\par
Dama d\u252?\u351?\u252?p, ganaty\u328?dan a\u253?rylma.\par
\par
T\u246?wekgel et, halka syry\u328? berip bar,\par
Sabyr e\u253?legil, bisabyrlyk hem bik\u228?r,\par
Her \u253?ere barsa\u328?yz, nesib\u228?\u328?iz bar,\par
Ba\u253? bola\u253? di\u253?p, hezzeti\u328?den a\u253?rylma.\par
\par
Namartlar hem muhannesler - na\u231?arlar,\par
Tagam\u328?y i\u253?p, i\u351?i\u328? bolsa ga\u231?arlar,\par
Syry\u328?ny pa\u351? edip, a\u253?by\u328? a\u231?arlar,\par
Gadry\u328? bilen \u252?lpeti\u328?den a\u253?rylma.\par
\par
Gedalary\u328? k\u246?\u328?li \u351?alygy istir,\par
Nadan k\u246?\u328?li \u253?alan s\u246?ze rast di\u253?ir,\par
Bigadyrlar du\u351?manyna dost di\u253?ir,\par
T\u228?lim beren ussady\u328?dan a\u253?rylma.\par
\par
Kimse ka\u351?\u351?ak bolup, kimse ba\u253? bolar,\par
Her kims\u228?ni\u328? bagty-ykbaly biler,\par
Herne gelse ba\u351?a, dili\u328?den geler,\par
Magtymguly, halk \u253?adyndan a\u253?rylma.\par
\par
K\u196?R BILE\par
Gapyl adam, gam astynda \u253?atyp sen,\par
\u214?tdi \u246?mr\u252?\u328? u\u351?ak-d\u252?\u351?ek k\u228?r bile.\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? mardyr, \u253?assanyp sen, \u253?atyp sen,\par
Ynjalarmy bile \u253?atan mar bile?\par
\par
Iman gazan, ynsaby\u328?y \u253?uwtmagyl,\par
G\u246?re-bile, \u246?z\u252?\u328? oda atmagyl,\par
Munda bidar ge\u231?ewergil, \u253?atmagyl,\par
Mun\u231?a d\u246?z\u252?p \u253?atajaksy\u328? g\u246?r bile.\par
\par
Her \u253?an gitse\u328? barar \u253?eri\u328? g\u246?r bolar,\par
Ha\u253?yr gazan, \u253?atan \u253?eri\u328? nur bolar,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y bolsa\u328?, ja\u253?y\u328? jennet-h\u252?\u253?r bolar,\par
\u221?aman bolsa\u328?, k\u246?\u253?d\u252?rerler nar bile.\par
\par
G\u246?z\u252?\u328? \u253?umdu\u328?, senden a\u253?rylar maly\u328?,\par
\u214?lenso\u328? tirikler ne biler haly\u328?,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman, her ne eden agmaly\u328?,\par
Gar\u351?y\u328? alyp durar mydam bar bile.\par
\par
Asly kapyr musulmana gaty\u351?maz,\par
\u199?yn musulman haram i\u351?e tutu\u351?maz,\par
Menzil kesmez, hi\u231? bir \u253?ana \u253?eti\u351?mez,\par
Ba\u351?\u231?y tutup, \u253?ola giren k\u246?r bile.\par
\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328?e aldanma, \u246?tene \u253?anma,\par
Maly\u328?a guwanma, m\u252?lke da\u253?anma,\par
Munda bet i\u351?leme, onda utanma,\par
Hasap g\u252?ni ha\u253?ry\u328? alyp bar bile.\par
\par
Magtymguly, dogry s\u246?ze ten bergil,\par
Sogap mundan \u246?tmez, tapsa\u328?, nan bergil,\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?\u328? tapan dost \u253?olunda jan bergil,\par
I\u351?i\u328? nedir seni di\u253?mez \u253?ar bile.\par
\par
K\u214?Z BILE\par
Kims\u228?m bardyr, \u253?ara arzym \u253?etirsin,\par
Y\u351?k oduna k\u246?\u253?d\u252?m gitdim k\u246?z bile.\par
Gelip, eli bile odum \u246?\u231?\u252?rsin,\par
\u221?ogsa s\u246?nmez baran bile, buz bile.\par
\par
Gelen ge\u231?di, gelejege \u253?urt go\u253?dy,\par
A\u351?nalygy namart a\u231?dy, mert go\u253?dy.\par
\u221?ar synamda dag \u252?st\u252?nde dert go\u253?dy,\par
Dert \u252?st\u252?ne bur\u231? go\u253?updyr duz bile.\par
\par
Mag\u351?ugym tapdyrmaz, tapsam, el bermez,\par
Ykbalym o\u253?anmaz, bagtym hem turmaz,\par
\u221?\u252?rek hem ynjalmaz, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l hem durmaz,\par
Dost jemalyn g\u246?rmegin\u231?\u228? g\u246?z bile.\par
\par
Bir derde du\u351?up men, hi\u231? kimse bilmez,\par
Isa a\u328?maz, Lukman \u231?\u228?resin kylmaz,\par
Geler - turmaz, duman ba\u351?dan sowulmaz,\par
Her zaman bir dert egser men s\u246?z bile.\par
\par
M\u252?\u328? y\u351?k ile maly-d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u253?ygar sen,\par
Bir \u351?a\u253?y \u231?\u252?n \u253?\u252?z k\u246?\u328?\u252?le deger sen.\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? - der\u253?a, ten bir saldyr, agar sen,\par
Ha\u231?ana de\u328? ta\u253? gider sen d\u252?z bile.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? malyndan kim eltdi bir zat,\par
Owwaly gam-ga\u253?gy, ahyry berbat,\par
Bolajagy\u328? budur seni\u328?, adamzat,\par
\u221?ok bolar sen toprak bile, toz bile.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ne menzildir, durar sen,\par
\u221?urt kimi\u328?dir, agyr i\u351?ler gurar sen,\par
Kysmat olsa, gary\u351? \u253?ere girer sen,\par
Nesip etse, alty ar\u351?yn biz bile.\par
\par
K\u214?\u327?\u220?L \u221?ATMAZ HI\u199?\par
Alla \u253?ady bilen tirik bolan dil,\par
G\u246?z \u253?umulmak bilen k\u246?\u328?\u252?l \u253?atmaz hi\u231?.\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l bossanynda iman t\u228?ze g\u252?l,\par
Bir a\u231?ylsa durar, solup \u253?itmez hi\u231?.\par
\par
Bar nygmatdan \u253?egdir saglyk mazasy,\par
Bar gullukdan \u253?ag\u351?y Haky\u328? ryzasy,\par
Eger dogry gelse ajal kazasy,\par
M\u252?\u328? \u253?albarmak bilen k\u246?\u328?\u252?l g\u252?\u253?tmez hi\u231?.\par
\par
\u221?igitler, s\u246?z\u252?me bir gulak asy\u328?,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? dostlugyny\u328? tamasyn kesi\u328?,\par
Ha\u253?sy \u253?an k\u246?p bolsa y\u351?ky\u328?, h\u246?wesi\u328?,\par
\u221?atsa\u328?-tursa\u328? hy\u253?aly\u328?dan gitmez hi\u231?.\par
\par
Adam ogly, d\u252?n\u253?\u228? geldi\u328? gitm\u228?ge,\par
G\u246?r\u252?p dur sen bargu \u253?eri\u328? \u253?atmaga,\par
J\u228?ht eder sen \u231?alnyp jahan tutmaga,\par
Bu i\u351?lere, meger, akly\u328? \u253?etmez hi\u231?.\par
\par
E\u253?, jahan m\u252?lk\u252?nde gezen serferaz,\par
Bir bende men, k\u246?p s\u246?zle\u253?ip bilmen, az,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? bazarynda pelek - humarbaz,\par
Hi\u231? s\u246?\u253? bile ynsan ony utmaz hi\u231?.\par
\par
A\u351?-suw bilen ger\u231?e tapar ten maza,\par
\u350?irin s\u246?zd\u252?r jan gulagna ge\u328? maza,\par
Jan \u246?\u253?\u252?nden ho\u351? nesihat a\u328?maza,\par
Gaty da\u351?a degen suw dek \u246?tmez hi\u231?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?igitlik bir \u253?az g\u246?rner,\par
Jany saga mydam s\u246?hbet-saz g\u246?rner,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y g\u252?nler \u253?\u252?z \u253?yl ge\u231?se, az g\u246?rner,\par
\u221?aman g\u252?nler az hem bolsa, \u246?tmez hi\u231?.\par
\par
BAGLAR, HE\u221?\par
Kysmat olsa, gidem uzak \u253?ollara,\par
Nesip go\u253?maz, gider \u253?olum baglar, he\u253?.\par
Ha\u253?ran-mejnun bolup, \u231?ykam \u231?\u246?llere\par
Baryp, mesgen tutam sizi, daglar, he\u253?.\par
\par
O\u253?un bilen oglanlygy\u328? deminden,\par
\u214?td\u252?m, geldim k\u228?milligi\u328? \u231?eminden,\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?m lerzan boldy d\u252?n\u253?\u228? gamyndan,\par
Tutdy synam \u231?apraz-\u231?apraz daglar, he\u253?.\par
\par
Ga\u253?da-ga\u253?da oglanlygy\u328? ra\u253?yndan,\par
\u221?etip geldim k\u228?milligi\u328? pa\u253?yndan,\par
Batdy ba\u351?ym, \u231?yka bilmen la\u253?yndan,\par
\u221?ada d\u252?\u351?er \u246?\u328?ki gezen \u231?aglar, he\u253?.\par
\par
Jahyllykda \u231?ar tarapa aty\u351?an,\par
Bilmezlikde hamu i\u351?e gaty\u351?an,\par
Ejiz galyp, garrylyga \u253?eti\u351?en,\par
\u214?z-\u246?z\u252?nden dert edib\u228?n aglar, he\u253?.\par
\par
Many a\u328?lan Magtymguly s\u246?z\u252?nden,\par
Pikre d\u252?\u351?er, \u253?a\u351?lar akar g\u246?z\u252?nden,\par
Hemme zatlar tag\u253?yr tapar \u246?z\u252?nden,\par
\u221?a, Rep, \u253?ykylmazmy be\u253?ik daglar, he\u253?.\par
\par
KE\u199?DIR, \u221?ARANLAR\par
Namazhon derw\u252?\u351?ler, d\u246?wletli ba\u253?lar,\par
Pelegi\u328? gerdany ke\u231?dir, \u253?aranlar.\par
Minnetde okalan namaz \u253?ol almaz,\par
D\u246?wlete da\u253?anma\u328?, pu\u231?dur, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Sykylsa burunlar, sararsa \u253?\u252?zler,\par
Gurysa dodaklar, bolmasa s\u246?zler,\par
G\u246?gerse dyrnaklar, alarsa g\u246?zler,\par
Imandan \u246?zgesi hi\u231?dir, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Asly\u328? bir owu\u231? gum, dem bir nepesdir,\par
\u214?z\u252?\u328?e bir dolan, i\u351?i\u328? hebesdir,\par
Jeset bir menzildir, ten bir kapasdyr,\par
Jan bir g\u246?zi bagly gu\u351?dur, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Gapyl bolma\u328?, d\u252?n\u253?\u228? gelen \u246?terler,\par
Munda ho\u351?wagt bolma\u328?, bardyr beterler,\par
\u199?ekiler kerwenler, \u253?\u246?rir hatarlar,\par
Bir yzy \u252?z\u252?lmez g\u246?\u231?d\u252?r, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Ajal \u253?aka\u328? tutar, bir g\u252?n bagyrdar,\par
Giden ga\u253?dyp gelmez, bu bir ugurdyr,\par
Menziller yrakdyr, \u253?\u252?kler agyrdyr,\par
Irter\u228?k terpeni\u328?, gi\u231?dir, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Gutular sen Hak \u253?olunda jan berse\u328?,\par
H\u252?lle bolar silkip-silkip don berse\u328?,\par
Sa\u253?a bolar m\u228?t\u228?\u231?lere nan berse\u328?,\par
Bir aja nan bermek ha\u231?dyr, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? di\u253?geni\u328? iki warakdyr,\par
\u221?arysy garadyr, \u253?arysy akdyr\par
Bir gije d\u252?\u253?\u351? g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?, ertiri \u253?okdur,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? tymsaly d\u252?\u253?\u351?d\u252?r, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Magtymguly bo\u253?un go\u253?gul bu emre,\par
Mala me\u351?gul bolup, galmagyl g\u252?mra,\par
\u221?\u252?z \u253?yllyk tet\u228?rik b\u228?\u351? g\u252?nl\u252?k \u246?mre,\par
Akyl e\u253?l\u228?\u328?, ni\u231?ik i\u351?dir, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
BATDY, \u221?ARANLAR\par
D\u246?rt m\u252?\u328? d\u246?rt \u253?\u252?z \u253?a\u351?an Lukman hekimi\u328?,\par
Ba\u351?y gara guma batdy, \u253?aranlar.\par
Kerk bedewli, agyr g\u252?rzli R\u252?stemi\u328?,\par
Ajal jylawyndan tutdy, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
\u221?usuby\u328? arzuwy \u221?akup \u253?anynda,\par
S\u246?\u253?g\u252?si bagrynda, derdi janynda,\par
Kimi\u328? gadry bardyr \u231?arhy\u328? \u253?anynda,\par
\u221?usuby gul edip satdy, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
\u196?leme h\u246?km eden Isgender soltan,\par
Ajal tedbirine tapmady derman,\par
Tagtyny \u253?el \u231?eken h\u246?kmi-S\u252?le\u253?man,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de galmady, \u246?tdi \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
\u220?\u231? \u253?\u252?z on \u252?\u231? mursal galmady biri,\par
Hany Asaf \u8722? S\u252?le\u253?many\u328? weziri?\par
Hany ol Hak resul, Haky\u328? \u214?z \u351?iri,\par
Gara \u253?er hemmesin \u253?uwtdy, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, gapyl oturma\u328?,\par
Gyl\u231?a jany uzyn ga\u253?ga batyrma\u328?,\par
\u221?alan\u231?yny hasrat bilen \u246?t\u252?rm\u228?\u328?,\par
Bir pasyl d\u246?wrandyr, \u246?tdi, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
G\u214?KDEN INMEZ, \u221?ARANLAR\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l perwaz e\u253?l\u228?p, galdy \u253?erinden,\par
Howalanmy\u351?, g\u246?kden inmez, \u253?aranlar,\par
Bir hy\u253?ala d\u252?\u351?m\u252?\u351?, \u231?ykmaz serinden,\par
Bu hy\u253?aldan ga\u253?dyp d\u246?nmez, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
No\u351? edipdir muhabbeti\u328? gandyndan,\par
Gulak tutmaz zahytlary\u328? pendinden,\par
Turdy mekanyndan, \u231?ykdy bendinden,\par
Dolanyp, ornunda gonmaz, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Y\u351?k i\u351?ini akyl eden, hu\u351? eden,\par
A\u253?ylarmy y\u351?ka d\u252?\u351?\u252?p, jo\u351? eden,\par
\u221?ar elinden ary bada no\u351? eden,\par
Agzyn go\u253?sa i\u231?er, ganmaz, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Bir hat bardyr ol Patmany\u328? sa\u231?ynda,\par
Okudarlar mag\u351?ar halkyn se\u231?ende,\par
Bir ot bardyr a\u351?yklary\u328? i\u231?inde,\par
Bu otlar dek, belli, \u253?anmaz, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, y\u351?k \u246?z\u252?nden bat e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
Y\u351?k i\u351?idir, a\u351?nalary \u253?at e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
\u221?alynsyz \u253?andyrar, \u253?elsiz ot e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
Bir zybana \u231?ekse, s\u246?nmez, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
DERMAN, \u221?ARANLAR\par
Bir bela du\u351?up men, Lukmanym bilmez,\par
Bu derdime tapmaz, derman, \u253?aranlar.\par
Asman per\u253?at baglar, ebirim \u253?agmaz,\par
Gy\u351? paslynda gu\u253?dy ne\u253?san, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Alnymda lahatdyr, j\u252?pb\u228?m kependir,\par
Ser salyp bardygym a\u382?dar zemindir,\par
M\u252?fti s\u246?zi \u8722? ry\u253?a, namart \u8722? emindir,\par
Mesgen tutmu\u351? munda \u253?aman, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Akybet mejalsyz n\u228?he\u328? agzynda,\par
Hasrat bilen galdym y\u351?ky\u328? k\u246?z\u252?nde,\par
Uftada men, dostlar, pelek bazynda,\par
Usul i\u231?re boldy rowan, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Desterhan alnymda hums galyp men,\par
Ezma\u253?y\u351? di\u253?p ki\u351?tim Je\u253?hun salyp men,\par
Mejmagyl-Bahre\u253?ne hasyl bolup men,\par
Mu\u351? \u253?arypdyr, salym we\u253?ran, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Munakga\u351? astynda galan perwan men,\par
Bent bolan der\u253?a men, \u231?\u246?ken umman men,\par
Jigeri set para, zaty gir\u253?an men,\par
Mejnun kibi men sergezdan, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ekser tapmaz bu derdim,\par
Buzahor pir boldy, namartdyr merdim,\par
Pe\u351?e bolup, tugun yzyn e\u253?erdim,\par
Jenupdan ide\u253?ip taban, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
GAM BILE\par
Bina\u253?y-behi\u351?tde ol g\u252?n ho\u351? \u253?\u252?zer,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de hemhana bolan gam bile.\par
Ne halka biriger, ne a\u253?ry gezer,\par
\u199?yn derw\u252?\u351? halk i\u231?re gezer hem bile.\par
\par
Kime \u351?ekawatdan gurulsa bin\u253?at,\par
\u196?lem terbi\u253?eti e\u253?lemez abat,\par
Her kimi\u328? kim, derdi bolsa maderzat,\par
Efsun okap, aram gelmez em bile.\par
\par
Ha\u253?sy gul derg\u228?he halys bendedir,\par
S\u246?\u253?g\u252?si \u253?\u252?rekde, y\u351?ky jandadyr.\par
Her ki\u351?i kim, Hak zikrinden zindedir,\par
K\u246?\u328?li tag\u253?yr tapmaz bolsa jem bile.\par
\par
Hak dosty kemelmez, k\u246?ne jahandyr,\par
Le\u253?ken jahan i\u231?re dosty pynhandyr,\par
Dost bolana bu iki i\u351? ny\u351?andyr:\par
\u221?\u252?rek y\u351?kdan dola, dide nem bile.\par
\par
D\u246?wleti\u328? gu\u351?uny ga\u231?yrma destden,\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylyk isteme a\u328?lamaz mestden,\par
Zynhar el \u252?zmegin dil bilen dostdan,\par
Abyra\u253?y\u328? arar, alar \u252?m bile.\par
\par
Ger\u231?e dilde dost hem bolsa \u351?any\u328?da,\par
Bir it bilip, aga\u231? sakla \u253?any\u328?da,\par
Bir g\u252?n bolar, yllat go\u253?ar jany\u328?da,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328?de ugra\u351?yp gezse\u328? \u351?um bile.\par
\par
Pyragy \u8722? murdadyr, \u253?yllar \u253?yl \u231?ekse,\par
A\u253?lar ebr salsa, g\u252?nler g\u252?n \u231?ekse,\par
Yl\u253?as aby d\u246?kse, Hydyr el \u231?ekse,\par
Zinde bolmaz Isa ursa dem bile.\par
\par
GUL BOLGUL\par
Bir bid\u246?wlet ili\u328? begi bolyn\u231?a\u328?,\par
D\u246?wletlini\u328? gapysynda gul bolgul.\par
Bedasyl beg gullugynda galyn\u231?a\u328?,\par
Asyl begi\u328? sa\u253?asynda k\u252?l bolgul.\par
\par
\u221?amany go\u253?, \u253?ag\u351?ylyga g\u246?z ildir,\par
Kelheme\u231? hem: \u171?\u214?z oglanym g\u246?zel di\u253?r\u187?.\par
Gargy\u351? gurdu\u328? z\u252?r\u253?adyny azaldyr,\par
Go\u253?un kimin \u231?ar tarapa il bolgul.\par
\par
S\u252?le\u253?man sen, mura bir gulak go\u253?gul,\par
S\u246?z\u252?ni di\u328?legil, jogabyn a\u253?gyl,\par
H\u228?kim bolsa\u328?, halky G\u252?n kibi \u231?o\u253?gul,\par
Akarda suw, \u253?a \u246?serde \u253?el bolgul.\par
\par
Ne i\u351?dendir - \u253?atyp, nebsi\u328? beslese\u328?,\par
Akmaklykdyr \u246?z\u252?\u328? \u253?ag\u351?y toslasa\u328?,\par
Her bazarda rowa\u231? bolmak islese\u328?,\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylary\u328? kisesinde pul bolgul.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bardyr demi\u328? hesibi,\par
Ir-gi\u231? \u253?eter her bend\u228?ni\u328? nesibi,\par
Ki\u351?i bolsa\u328?, go\u253?gul gury t\u228?sibi,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y, \u253?aman, bar\u231?alara dil bolgul.\par
\par
GUMLY \u199?YKYPDYR\par
Haktagala, bu ne-ni\u231?ik ahwaldyr,\par
Dury di\u253?p i\u231?digim gumly \u231?ykypdyr.\par
Ne \u253?eser, bihuda, \u351?um-ke\u231? ykbaldyr,\par
Halal di\u253?p i\u253?digim jimli \u231?ykypdyr.\par
\par
Kimse syrym bilmez, \u246?z\u252?n \u246?ld\u252?rse,\par
Pakyr bendelere Ta\u328?ry bildirse,\par
Ile \u351?atlyk, \u351?ady\u253?anlyk g\u252?ld\u252?rse,\par
Ma\u328?a hemra bolan gamly \u231?ykypdyr.\par
\par
Amuhta men \u246?rtenm\u228?ge, bi\u351?m\u228?ge,\par
Ki\u351?i \u253?ok s\u246?zle\u351?ip, dert a\u253?dy\u351?maga,\par
Oba ujundan bardym \u246?\u253? sora\u351?maga, -\par
\u221?a laldyr, \u253?a agzy mumly \u231?ykypdyr.\par
\par
Menden \u351?ikat eder elim gerenim,\par
Galbirden \u351?al \u231?ykar syrym berenim,\par
Pakyr di\u253?p, pa\u351?magna elim uranym,\par
Deprenende, d\u246?wden demli \u231?ykypdyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, hasaby \u253?ok g\u246?renim,\par
Tama tutup, umyt elin gerenim,\par
Obasyna \u228?rmi\u351? di\u253?ip baranym,\par
Etegne el ursam, ... \u231?ykypdyr.\par
\par
ELDE BARY BOLMASA\par
Zamana be\u253?ledir - g\u246?ze ilmezler,\par
Her \u253?igidi\u328? elde bary bolmasa.\par
\u221?\u252?z t\u252?menlik s\u246?z\u252?n \u351?a\u253?a almazlar,\par
Her ki\u351?ini\u328? ygtybary bolmasa.\par
\par
Ten bir dar kapasdyr, jan bir wag\u351?ydyr,\par
Dile gelen s\u246?zler k\u246?\u328?\u252?l nag\u351?ydyr,\par
Otly, suwly tamug ondan \u253?ag\u351?ydyr,\par
Her \u252?lk\u228?ni\u328? bir bazary bolmasa.\par
\par
Begzadalar galdy \u231?opan t\u228?hrine,\par
Ten ha\u231?an d\u246?z geler \u253?ylan z\u228?hrine,\par
Bibat bolup, d\u246?ner Lutu\u328? \u351?\u228?hrine,\par
Her \u252?lk\u228?ni\u328? h\u228?kim \u228?ri bolmasa.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de a\u328?lardan a\u328?lamaz k\u228?ndir,\par
Bilmez bir beladyr, bilenler - jandyr,\par
Ol \u253?igitler adam dilli ha\u253?wandyr,\par
S\u246?z a\u328?masa hem ygrary bolmasa.\par
\par
\u221?igide \u253?oksullyk \u253?aman beladyr,\par
S\u246?z\u252?ni de\u328?-du\u351?dan ga\u253?ra saladyr,\par
\u221?aman gylyk dosty du\u351?man kyladyr,\par
Guryp galsyn il derkary bolmasa.\par
\par
Hak her kime bir \u253?ag\u351?y \u253?ar berm\u228?ndir,\par
S\u246?zi ahdyr, i\u231?i doly armandyr,\par
\u221?\u252?z \u253?a\u351?asa, b\u228?\u351? g\u252?n \u246?m\u252?r s\u252?rm\u228?ndir,\par
Her kimi\u328? mynasyp \u253?ary bolmasa.\par
\par
Magtymguly, Haka tab\u351?yr \u246?z\u252?\u328?i,\par
Her namarda, sarartmagyn \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328?i,\par
Terhosym bar terk etgil bu s\u246?z\u252?\u328?i,\par
N\u228?ge gerek hyrydary bolmasa.\par
\par
G\u220?MAN G\u214?R\u220?NER\par
Bu dem ganymatdyr, ne\u231?\u252?n bilmez sen,\par
\u199?yksa dem, girmegi g\u252?man g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
Bizden burun gelen g\u246?\u231?\u252?pdir ta\u328?la,\par
\u221?ol uzak, gara\u328?ky, duman g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Akyl olsa\u328? iste bu \u253?olda bir pir,\par
Ryzky\u328?a kepildir Alla \u8722? mukaddir,\par
Altyn-k\u252?m\u252?\u351?, almaz, \u253?akut ile d\u252?r,\par
Hakdan ga\u253?ry tamam zy\u253?an g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Allany unudyp, akly\u328? \u253?itirme,\par
Her nepes \u228?g\u228? bol, gaflat getirme,\par
Bihuda, bipe\u253?da \u246?mr\u252?\u328? \u246?t\u252?rme,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? bakasyzdyr, a\u253?an g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Hoja, se\u253?it, pat\u351?a - soralmaz nesep,\par
Ha\u351?r-ne\u351?r bolsa, alarlar hasap,\par
Harama azap bar, \u351?\u252?bh\u228?ge ytap,\par
Munda \u253?ag\u351?y, onda \u253?aman g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
Magtymguly, habar aldym Gurhandan,\par
Eser \u253?okdur owwal giden kerwenden,\par
Ta\u328?la \u253?al\u328?yz \u253?atmaklygy\u328? ol g\u246?rden,\par
Garda\u351?, \u253?ylan bilen i\u231?\u253?an g\u246?r\u252?ner.\par
\par
GALANDAR BILE\par
G\u246?rerge sapa men, tanyrga dilke\u351?,\par
Diwana\u253?y-dehrem galandar bile.\par
\u199?ekdigim naladyr, \u253?\u252?regim gamke\u351?,\par
H\u246?regim ata\u351?dyr semender bile.\par
\par
Jesedim ho\u351?nema, jigerim bir\u253?an,\par
\u221?\u252?regim p\u252?rgamdyr, g\u246?zlerim gir\u253?an,\par
Dilim gu\u351? dilidir, suratym - ynsan,\par
Hemzybanam bar\u231?a \u231?emender bile.\par
\par
Pelek kine \u231?ekmi\u351?, e\u253?\u253?am ant etmi\u351?,\par
D\u246?wletim bo\u253?nuna gyl kement atmy\u351?,\par
Ykbalym i\u351?igin bagtym bent etmi\u351?,\par
Da\u351?yn demir, i\u231?in k\u252?l\u252?nder bile.\par
\par
Hajatym ber, \u253?a Hak, e\u253?le tedbirim,\par
Maksadym \u351?anyna tokuna tirim,\par
Dermende galyp men, e\u253?le destgirim,\par
Hydyr ata, Isa pygamber bile.\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, \u253?er \u253?\u252?z\u252?n \u253?\u252?zse\u328?,\par
Ahyry \u246?l\u252?mdir d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni d\u252?zse\u328?,\par
\u220?\u231? \u253?\u252?z elli alty \u253?yl \u228?lemi gezse\u328?,\par
Pylkus ogly \u351?ahy-Iskender bile.\par
\par
G\u214?ZE MYHMANDYR\par
Gara da\u351?dan gara gyly sa\u253?lan g\u246?z,\par
\u199?\u246?\u328?\u328?eler g\u246?reji\u328?, g\u246?ze myhmandyr.\par
Gelen a\u351? di\u253?p gelmez, tur\u351?utmagyl \u253?\u252?z,\par
Nana m\u228?t\u228?\u231? d\u228?ldir, s\u246?ze myhmandyr.\par
\par
Agyrdyr he\u328?\u328?amlar, uzakdyr \u253?ollar,\par
Sora\u351?sa \u253?igitler, s\u246?zle\u351?se diller,\par
Baharda a\u231?ylan re\u328?be-re\u328? g\u252?ller,\par
Bir pasyl a\u231?ylar - \u253?aza myhmandyr.\par
\par
Ne azym h\u252?n\u228?rler, ne syrly i\u351?ler,\par
Ne howaly daglar, belent aga\u231?lar,\par
Altmy\u351? elwan, \u253?etmi\u351? d\u252?rli i\u253?mi\u351?ler,\par
Aga\u231?dan a\u253?rylar, g\u252?\u253?ze myhmandyr.\par
\par
\u221?igidi\u328? bolmasa \u253?aragy, aty,\par
\u350?uny belli bili\u328?, \u253?okdur ga\u253?raty,\par
Gojaldyk\u231?a, gider s\u252?\u328?\u328?\u252?\u328? kuwwaty,\par
\u221?igitligi\u328? zory dyza myhmandyr.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328?e g\u252?l\u252?m-g\u252?l\u252?mdir,\par
Pi\u351?esi jepadyr, jebr-u zulumdyr,\par
Her ni\u231?e \u253?a\u351?asa\u328?, ahyr \u246?l\u252?mdir,\par
Eziz janlar tende bize myhmandyr.\par
\par
Haky \u253?ada salsa\u328?, Hakdan gorky\u328?a,\par
\u350?e\u253?tan ara d\u252?\u351?er, go\u253?maz erki\u328?e,\par
Guba juwan, guwanmagyl g\u246?rk\u252?\u328?e,\par
Gojalar sen, g\u246?rk\u252?\u328? \u253?\u252?ze myhmandyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, a\u253?dar, iller s\u246?z\u252?m-de,\par
\u214?l\u252?m \u253?adymdadyr, gorky g\u246?z\u252?mde,\par
Her ni\u231?e \u253?a\u351?asa\u328? \u253?eri\u328? \u253?\u252?z\u252?nde,\par
Adam ogly b\u228?\u351? g\u252?n duza myhmandyr.\par
\par
GELEN-DE BARDYR\par
G\u252?nde \u253?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? g\u246?\u231? hem bolsa ol d\u252?n\u253?\u228?,\par
Ol mukdar bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? gelen-de bardyr.\par
\u221?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? akmak bolup, gitse ra\u253?yna,\par
\u221?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? \u246?z\u252?n \u253?ola salan-da bardyr.\par
\par
\u221?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? derw\u252?\u351? syna daglap oturan,\par
Ry\u253?azatda bilin baglap oturan,\par
Ni\u231?e \u253?erde g\u246?rse\u328?, aglap oturan,\par
Ni\u231?e \u253?erde bigam g\u252?len-de bardyr.\par
\par
Se\u253?ran etse\u328? bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? d\u246?rt bur\u231?un,\par
Gary\u351?ypdyr halal-haram, arwah-jyn,\par
Ni\u231?eler t\u228?mizl\u228?p \u253?ol giderler \u231?yn,\par
Ni\u231?e \u253?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? g\u252?mra bolan-da bardyr.\par
\par
Ugursyz e\u253?\u253?amlar, a\u328?lamaz \u228?rler,\par
K\u228?\u351?gi soran bolsa, sa\u231?a\u253?dym d\u252?rler,\par
Hany ol S\u252?le\u253?man, R\u252?stemler, \u351?irler,\par
Di\u253?me, busup-sypyp galan-da bardyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, k\u246?\u328?le ga\u253?gy getirme,\par
Bu bir i\u351? wagtydyr, \u246?z\u252?\u328? \u253?itirme,\par
S\u246?z\u252?m a\u328?lan \u253?ok di\u253?p, \u252?ms\u252?m oturma,\par
Jahan gi\u328?dir, \u231?endan bilen-de bardyr.\par
\par
GELMEZMI\par
Pelek, seni\u328? bu d\u246?wletli gerdany\u328?,\par
Bizi\u328? sary \u246?wr\u252?lmezmi, gelmezmi?\par
L\u228?\u351?in \u253?ere saldy\u328? ni\u231?e merdany\u328?,\par
Zemin ynsap e\u253?lemezmi, dolmazmy?\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?, seni\u328? bu gezekli gerdi\u351?i\u328?,\par
Gyzyl gandan gyrmyz bolupdyr di\u351?i\u328?,\par
Ge\u231?i, gurt dostlugna me\u328?z\u228?r edi\u351?i\u328?,\par
Gamly \u351?at olmazmy, aglan g\u252?lmezmi?\par
\par
Oraksyz orar sen, tygsyz keser sen,\par
\u221?umruksyz \u253?\u252?zer sen, \u253?\u252?ps\u252?z asar sen,\par
El-a\u253?aksyz bir bihabar basar sen,\par
\u221?ykan basar \u253?atar, ga\u253?dyp galmazmy?\par
\par
Pelek o\u253?nap, utar uru\u351?sa\u328?, s\u246?\u253?se\u328?,\par
G\u246?wr\u228?\u328?i g\u246?terip, ganaty\u328? \u253?a\u253?sa\u328?,\par
\u214?l\u252?m zulmun adam bo\u253?nuna go\u253?sa\u328?,\par
Gorkusyndan saralmazmy, solmazmy?\par
\par
Magtymguly, her s\u228?herden, sabadan,\par
Haly galma bu naly\u351?dan, dogadan,\par
Butparazlar butdan alsa myradyn,\par
Hajatyny Hakdan dil\u228?n almazmy?\par
\par
GARA RE\u327? BOLAR\par
Hozu\u328? da\u351? postuny, azergun g\u252?li,\par
Suwun sa\u231?a \u231?alsa\u328?, gara re\u328? bolar.\par
I\u231?i\u328? \u351?erden sakla, gybatdan dili,\par
Saklamasa\u328? k\u246?\u328?\u252?l g\u246?zgi\u328? ze\u328? bolar.\par
\par
Her ki\u351?i kim, \u253?amanlyga kast e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
Iki d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u246?z i\u351?ine kest e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y gylyk du\u351?many\u328?y dost e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
Gylygy\u328? bet bolsa, i\u351?i\u328? je\u328? bolar.\par
\par
\u221?igidi\u328? bolmasa, s\u246?zde keseri,\par
E\u253?men\u231?dir, a\u253?rylmaz a\u253?akdan seri,\par
Her kimde bolmasa iman eseri,\par
\u221?\u252?regi erimez, sy\u253?a se\u328? bolar.\par
\par
Adam ogly awaradyr, asydyr,\par
Bir s\u246?z di\u253?se\u328? \u253?ag\u351?y \u228?re, besidir,\par
Bilip bolmaz Haky\u328? dosty ha\u253?sydyr,\par
Alky\u351?y k\u246?p alsa\u328?, i\u351?i\u328? o\u328? bolar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?z\u252?m gysga, \u351?erhi k\u246?p,\par
Bilmeze hi\u231?, bilen \u253?anda nyrhy k\u246?p,\par
\u221?eri\u328? \u253?erden, \u228?ri\u328? \u228?rden parhy k\u246?p,\par
M\u252?\u351?gil budur - s\u246?zle\u351?ende de\u328? bolar.\par
\par
GEZEMEK BILEN\par
\u221?etmi\u351? \u253?a\u351?ly garda\u351?, girmegil \u253?a\u253?a,\par
Oku\u328? doly ge\u231?mez gezemek bilen.\par
Guwanma kesekden gurlan bina\u253?a,\par
Kesek bina tutmaz d\u252?zemek bilen.\par
\par
Adamzatdan \u231?ykar adamlyk ysy,\par
Galp adamy\u328? basym biliner misi,\par
M\u246?mine azar bi\u253?r adamy\u328? pisi,\par
D\u246?n\u252?p, dawa tutar duz-emek bilen.\par
\par
Uzak \u253?ola bid\u246?wleti ba\u351? etme,\par
Allany\u328? emrinden k\u246?\u328?l\u252?\u328? da\u351? etme,\par
Akmaga i\u231? berip, syry\u328? pa\u351? etme,\par
Galbirde suw durmaz g\u246?zemek bilen.\par
\par
Dost tutma k\u246?p \u253?a\u351?ly adam k\u246?sesin,\par
Baryn \u253?ok di\u253?p, bo\u351? g\u246?rkezer kisesin,\par
Biribar bo\u351? etse akly\u328? k\u228?sesin,\par
Ne pe\u253?da da\u351?yndan bezemek bilen.\par
\par
Owwal, Magtymguly, \u246?z\u252?\u328? d\u252?zetgil,\par
Halk d\u252?n\u253?e di\u253?r, sen ky\u253?amat g\u246?z etgil,\par
Az i\u253?gil, az \u253?atgyl, s\u246?z\u252?\u328? az etgil,\par
Ne bar manysyz s\u246?z uzamak bilen.\par
\par
GITDI BU RA\u221?A\par
Maly\u328?a, m\u252?lk\u252?\u328?e magrur olunma,\par
E\u253?, \u253?ok \u253?erden gelen gitdi bu ra\u253?a.\par
Bolar-bolmaz i\u351?ler \u252?\u231?in ulunma,\par
\u199?ohlar gelip, batyp galmy\u351? bu la\u253?a.\par
\par
K\u246?p gerdi\u351?ler ge\u231?irmi\u351?dir bu \u253?urtlar,\par
Ni\u231?e synalarda r\u246?w\u351?en bu dertler,\par
\u221?\u252?z \u246?w\u252?rdi mundan birni\u231?e mertler,\par
Birni\u231?eler bal di\u253?p, batmy\u351? bela\u253?a.\par
\par
E\u253?, akyly aryg \u253?igit, munda gel,\par
Birni\u231?e s\u246?z\u252?m bar, jandan gulak sal,\par
Nirde derw\u252?\u351? g\u246?rse\u328?, baryp, alky\u351? al,\par
Derw\u252?\u351?den \u253?eg hi\u231? kim \u253?okdur Huda\u253?a!\par
\par
Tamugy\u328? dykanjy zekatsyz ba\u253?dyr,\par
Derw\u252?\u351?e tagn eden segi-bija\u253?dyr,\par
Derw\u252?\u351? \u253?erde \u8722? der\u253?a, \u253?a g\u246?kde \u8722? A\u253?dyr,\par
Do\u328?uz der\u253?a ne\u253?l\u228?r, it \u252?\u253?r\u252?p A\u253?a.\par
\par
\u221?alan\u231?y \u253?eri d\u228?l, adam uklasyn,\par
Kim gulak bi\u253?r, di\u328?l\u228?p, s\u246?z\u252?m haklasyn,\par
Magtymguly, nesihat kyl, saklasyn,\par
T\u228?ze gelen \u228?rler k\u246?ne sara\u253?a.\par
\par
GA\u199?A BA\u350?LADY\par
Indi bildim zamanany\u328? azanyn,\par
\u221?amanlar \u253?ag\u351?ydan ga\u231?a ba\u351?lady.\par
Ga\u253?ta bedasyllar asylzadadan,\par
Pisint etme\u253?, t\u246?re ge\u231?e ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Yr\u253?a boldy k\u246?p\u252?\u328? okan namazy,\par
Ta\u328?ry hi\u231? birinden bolmady razy,\par
Pygamber ornunda oturan kazy,\par
Para \u252?\u231?in elin a\u231?a ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
\u350?alarda galmady h\u246?kmi-adalat,\par
Bir pul \u252?\u231?in m\u252?fti berer rowa\u253?at,\par
Bil, bu i\u351?ler - ny\u351?ana\u253?y-ky\u253?amat,\par
Zalymlar bitoba \u246?te ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Dadhahlar turuban, \u253?\u252?z\u252?n sarardyp,\par
Kim t\u246?resin tapyp, re\u328?\u328?in gyzardyp,\par
Zalymlar mazluma syrtyn gabardyp,\par
Gam\u231?ysyndan ganlar sa\u231?a ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
M\u252?jtehid s\u246?z\u252?ne amal bolmady,\par
Mynapyklar \u221?aradany bilmedi,\par
Sopular pirinden taglym almady,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u252?\u231?in dinden ge\u231?e ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Bir para sopular \u171?sopy men\u187? di\u253?er,\par
Sorama\u253?, zalymlar tagamyn i\u253?er,\par
\u171?Bizi \u253?ag\u351?y ki\u351?i di\u253?sinler\u187? di\u253?er,\par
Her i\u351?ikde halka gura ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Garryga a\u253?landy biz g\u246?ren \u253?a\u351?lar,\par
A\u253?aga dolandy biz g\u246?ren ba\u351?lar,\par
Bimahal \u253?\u252?k baglap imdi garda\u351?lar,\par
Ahyret azmyna g\u246?\u231?e ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Akyl bolan gamda \u253?\u252?regin ezip,\par
Derdini\u328? dermanyn soraglap gezip,\par
Zamanany\u328? pisat bolanyn syzyp,\par
Panydan baky\u253?a g\u246?\u231?e ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Ne asyl begleri\u328? nobaty \u246?tdi,\par
Ga\u253?ta \u351?ugul-haramyga s\u246?z \u253?etdi,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de kim galyp, myrada \u253?etdi,\par
Muhabbet \u231?yragy \u246?\u231?e ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Kazy bolan bir jogapda durmady,\par
Gije m\u228?hnet tartyp, kitap g\u246?rmedi,\par
\u350?erigat s\u246?z\u252?nde dogry \u253?\u246?rmedi,\par
Nebs \u252?\u231?in imansyz \u246?te ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, barha \u253?ol tany,\par
B\u228?\u351? g\u252?n synamaga iberdi seni,\par
Senden burun \u246?ten jananlar hany?\par
Her kim nobatynda \u246?te ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
D\u214?K\u220?P BARADYR\par
Gam dumany basyp garyp k\u246?\u328?l\u252?mi,\par
G\u246?z \u253?a\u351?yn saklama\u253?, d\u246?k\u252?p baradyr.\par
Kimdir rehm e\u253?le\u253?en, sorap halymy,\par
Bozuk k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m g\u246?ren \u253?ykyp baradyr.\par
\par
Ger\u231?e ot \u253?aksalar a\u351?yk \u253?agyndan,\par
\u214?l\u252?m asan bolar dost pyragyndan,\par
Hijran meni kowdy sabyr dagyndan,\par
Pyrak bogun-bogun s\u246?k\u252?p baradyr.\par
\par
Owwal d\u246?wranymy \u231?arh bula\u351?dyrdy,\par
Gam janym guratdy, ot tuta\u351?dyrdy,\par
Y\u351?k meni \u253?andyrdy, hetden a\u351?dyrdy,\par
\u221?\u252?regim i\u231?imden \u231?ykyp baradyr.\par
\par
Parahat \u253?atyrdym nebsimi besl\u228?p,\par
Turdy k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m \u253?ar jemalyn h\u246?wesl\u228?p,\par
Hakdan hajat dil\u228?p, myradyn isl\u228?p,\par
G\u246?z\u252?m ol \u253?ollara bakyp baradyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, mejalym bar, s\u246?\u253?l\u228?\u253?in,\par
Dostlara derdimi a\u253?an e\u253?l\u228?\u253?in,\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, \u253?yglama\u253?yn ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in,\par
Y\u351?k meni \u253?andyryp, \u253?akyp baradyr.\par
\par
DA\u350? GALDY\par
Ne zowk-u sapalar \u253?igitlik bilen,\par
Bahar bolup ge\u231?di, bizden da\u351? galdy.\par
Garrylyk \u253?eti\u351?di m\u252?\u328? k\u252?lpet bilen,\par
Mizan \u246?tdi, hazan geldi, gy\u351? galdy.\par
\par
\u214?mr\u252?mi sarp etdim ha\u253? bile wa\u253?a,\par
Gulluk-tagat e\u253?lemedim Huda\u253?a,\par
Essiz \u253?igitligi \u246?t\u252?rdim za\u253?a,\par
Imdi ne g\u252?\u253?\u231?-kuwwat, ne bir jo\u351? galdy.\par
\par
\u214?mr\u252?mi\u328? galmady bir zerre \u351?ady,\par
Hi\u231? kimse e\u351?itmez ahy-per\u253?ady,\par
Jismim kebap etmi\u351? a\u253?ralyk ody,\par
\u221?\u252?rekler gan bolup, g\u246?zde \u253?a\u351? galdy.\par
\par
Her bir gula \u351?um a\u253?ralyk salyndy,\par
Jismim hazan urdy, g\u252?li solundy,\par
Gaznasy uruldy, \u246?\u253?i talandy,\par
Ne onda bir akyl, ne bir hu\u351? galdy.\par
\par
Go\u253?dy meni \u253?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? azara pyrkat,\par
Gij\u228?m uzyn boldy, da\u328? atmak \u8722? rykkat,\par
Gussa bilen g\u252?n ge\u231?irmek mu\u351?akgat,\par
Ne janda parahat, ne bir a\u253?\u351? galdy.\par
\par
A\u253?ralyk jan-jisme \u231?oh azar berdi,\par
Renj-u elem \u231?ekdim, tenim sargardy,\par
Gussa bilen sa\u231?-sakgalym agardy,\par
Ne ruhda \u351?at, ne k\u246?\u328?\u252?lde ho\u351? galdy.\par
\par
Magtymguly, i\u351?im kyl-u kal boldy,\par
\u350?um a\u253?ralyk bile aklym lal boldy,\par
Bilmedim, ne s\u246?wda, ni\u231?ik hal boldy,\par
Jan tenden a\u253?ryldy, gury l\u228?\u351? galdy.\par
\par
DEPE NEDIR, D\u220?Z NEDIR\par
\u221?edi \u253?a\u351?an arap aty\u328? \u351?anynda\par
M\u228?lim bolmaz, depe nedir, d\u252?z nedir.\par
\u221?\u252?\u328?i \u253?eten go\u231? \u253?igidi\u328? \u253?anynda\par
Elli nedir, altmy\u351? nedir, \u253?\u252?z nedir.\par
\par
Namart ogly gorky \u231?eker me\u253?dandan,\par
Aga\u231? adam bolup g\u246?rner her \u253?andan,\par
Muhannesler howply \u253?erde du\u351?mandan,\par
Se\u231?e bilmez, duman nedir, toz nedir.\par
\par
Sypah bolup, m\u252?ner atyn bilme\u253?en,\par
Aryp bolup, \u246?z yzzatyn bilme\u253?en,\par
S\u246?hbet i\u231?re s\u246?z lezzetin bilme\u253?en,\par
A\u328?a bilmez mejlis nedir, saz nedir.\par
\par
Garga \u253?iter baz, balaman je\u328?inde,\par
G\u246?rne bilmez ol me\u253?dany\u328? de\u328?inde,\par
A\u231? gary\u231?ga\u253?, algyr la\u231?yn \u246?\u328?\u252?nde,\par
M\u252?\u328? \u253?ygylsyn, \u246?rdek nedir, gaz nedir.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?z jo\u351? eder dili\u328?den,\par
Muhannese \u253?ol bermedi\u328? \u253?eli\u328?den,\par
Bu h\u252?n\u228?rler geler, gelmez eli\u328?den,\par
Dilden gelen bu j\u252?r\u253?etli s\u246?z nedir?!\par
\par
DON BOLSA\par
Ten \u253?apmaga k\u246?\u253?nek ist\u228?r \u253?ala\u328?a\u231?,\par
K\u246?\u253?nekli di\u253?r: wah, \u252?st\u252?nden don bolsa.\par
Ba\u351? saglyk di\u253?p, Hakdan dil\u228?r garny a\u231?,\par
B\u228?\u351?in tapsa, arzuw eder - on bolsa.\par
\par
Ol \u253?igit ki, \u231?eke-\u231?eke hasraty,\par
Saparlyk \u253?\u252?kl\u228?re bolsa d\u246?wleti,\par
\u221?any birle tapsa \u253?aragy-aty,\par
\u221?ene di\u253?r ki: mugt, t\u252?kenmez nan bolsa.\par
\par
K\u246?p nan tapyp, eger bolsa k\u246?\u328?li \u351?at,\par
Gyz-g\u246?zelden mahbup ist\u228?r hem \u246?wlat,\par
Bu d\u246?wleti pe\u253?da etse adamzat,\par
K\u246?\u328?li ist\u228?r, be\u253?ik \u351?\u228?hre han bolsa.\par
\par
Hem han bolsa, hem d\u252?n\u253?\u228?si ta\u253? bolsa,\par
Hem \u246?lmese, hem esbaby \u351?a\u253? bolsa,\par
Hem bermese, hem \u231?\u252?\u253?rimez ba\u253? bolsa,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y ady hem d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de dan bolsa.\par
\par
Magtymguly, g\u246?r\u252?p du\u351?man tagnasyn,\par
Mert oldur, \u351?at tuta gamdan synasyn,\par
\u221?er \u253?\u252?zi doldurmaz g\u246?z\u252?\u328? hanasyn,\par
Karun kimin gazna\u328? n\u228?\u231?e k\u228?n bolsa.\par
\par
DELALAT \u221?AG\u350?Y\par
Asla adamzada ajy s\u246?z urma\u328?,\par
Pakyra-misgine delalat \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
Bahyla ugrama\u328?, g\u252?ler \u253?\u252?z berm\u228?\u328?,\par
M\u246?h\u252?m bitirm\u228?ge kipa\u253?at \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
\u221?etimi g\u246?re\u328?de, g\u252?ler \u253?\u252?z bergil,\par
Goldan gelse, o\u328?a tagam-duz bergil,\par
Bir gamly g\u246?re\u328?de, \u351?irin s\u246?z bergil,\par
Ent\u228?ni goldara hema\u253?at \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
\u221?igit oldur - s\u246?ze e\u253?lese amal,\par
Goldan gelmez i\u351?e etmese jedel,\par
Allany\u328? emrine kylmagyl bedel,\par
Bege - berim, \u351?aha - adalat \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Garyplyk bir dertdir - adam \u246?ld\u252?rmez,\par
\u214?ld\u252?rmese, dirilikde g\u252?ld\u252?rmez,\par
It hem arryklygyn gurda bildirmez,\par
Elbetde, du\u351?mana sy\u253?asat \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u351?\u252?k\u252?r, \u351?irin til berdi,\par
\u350?ejerler g\u246?gerip, semer g\u252?l berdi,\par
G\u246?rogly Re\u253?hana ni\u231?ik \u253?albardy,\par
\u171?Amandyr\u187? di\u253?ene di\u253?anat \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
D\u214?KE BA\u350?LADY\par
G\u246?m\u252?ldi der\u253?alar, \u253?ykyldy daglar,\par
\u221?etimler g\u246?z\u253?a\u351?yn d\u246?ke ba\u351?lady.\par
Orramsydan bolan haramhor begler,\par
\u221?urdy bir \u253?anyndan \u253?yka ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Jemagatsyz azan bir gury sesdir,\par
Ni\u231?e molla\u328? okan ylmy hebesdir,\par
Kazylary\u328? k\u228?ri \u231?a\u253? bile nasdyr,\par
Bir bozuk ny\u351?ana tuta ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
I\u351?anlary her gapyda tapylar,\par
Mollalarna \u253?ok myjabat \u253?apylar,\par
\u214?wl\u252?\u253?\u228?lik satyp, ni\u231?e sopular,\par
Gygyryp, asmana b\u246?ke ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
\u199?ykar be\u253?ewana gyzy-gelini,\par
Ak \u253?\u252?z\u252?ne \u253?apar gara telini,\par
Kem\u231?inlik e\u253?le\u253?ip, \u253?ygan puluny,\par
D\u252?zedip \u246?z\u252?ne daka ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de s\u252?\u253?thory\u328? pul \u253?ygma derdi,\par
Ba\u253?lary\u328? mallary bizekat erdi,\par
Toba edi\u328?, g\u246?z\u252?m bir \u253?aman g\u246?rdi,\par
Big\u252?n\u228?, bir-birin \u253?aka ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ba\u351?a baglap selleler,\par
A\u231? b\u246?ri de\u253? \u253?ortup ni\u231?e mollalar,\par
Halaldan, haramdan \u253?ygnap gallalar,\par
Her ne tapsa, dynma\u253? dyka ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
DON TAPYLMASA\par
Dok doku\u351?ar sigse hylgat ge\u253?m\u228?ge,\par
Kilim g\u246?zel zatdyr don tapylmasa.\par
A\u231? dyry\u351?ar gaty nany i\u253?m\u228?ge,\par
M\u252?\u351?gildir bi\u351?ire un tapylmasa.\par
\par
Hasyl umydy bar ekin ekene,\par
Bu i\u351?ler m\u228?limdir m\u228?hnet \u231?ekene,\par
A\u253?ak \u253?ala\u328? basa bilmez tikene,\par
Ne\u253?lesin ge\u253?ere g\u246?n tapylmasa.\par
\par
Akylsyzlar i\u351? ahyryn garamaz,\par
Jolban \u231?igidinden harnup d\u246?remez,\par
Agyr mejlislere \u231?opan \u253?aramaz,\par
Ne\u253?lesin otyra jim tapylmasa.\par
\par
\u221?igitlikde her kim e\u351?retde \u253?a\u253?lar,\par
Ba\u351?yna \u253?a geler, gelmez bu k\u246?\u253?ler,\par
Di\u351?sizler nan tapsa \u231?\u228?resin e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
M\u252?\u351?gildir i\u253?ere nan tapylmasa.\par
\par
Magtymguly s\u246?\u253?mez jedeli, je\u328?i,\par
Ahyret azm etdi k\u246?p du\u351?y-de\u328?i,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de ne i\u351? bar - bolma\u253?yr so\u328?y,\par
Mu\u351?akgatdyr tende jan tapylmasa.\par
\par
\u214?Z\u220?\u327?DEN\par
M\u228?hnet bilen mal jem eden m\u228?k\u228?m ba\u253?,\par
Owwal ha\u253?ry\u328? bolsa, g\u246?nder \u246?z\u252?\u328?den!\par
\u221?ygyp, zekat berm\u228?nleri\u328? haly wa\u253?,\par
Ta\u328?la garny dolar tamug k\u246?z\u252?nden.\par
\par
Namut galdy\u328?, ger \u351?e\u253?tana \u253?ol berse\u328?,\par
\u350?e\u253?tan bo\u253?nun \u252?zd\u252?\u328? pire gol berse\u328?,\par
Yhlas bilen Alla \u252?\u231?in mal berse\u328?,\par
Sansyz sowap bolup barar yzy\u328?dan.\par
\par
\u214?wladyna abyra\u253?ly g\u252?n \u252?\u231?in,\par
\u221?igit e\u351?ret terkin e\u253?l\u228?r ten \u252?\u231?in,\par
Halal-haram mal \u253?ygarlar zen \u252?\u231?in,\par
\u214?lse\u328?, kany imdat ogul-gyzy\u328?dan.\par
\par
Ni\u231?eler bar - ha\u253?yr isl\u228?r, \u351?er tapar,\par
Ni\u231?eler bar - gum di\u253?p garbar, zer tapar,\par
Birew bardyr - \u253?aman e\u253?l\u228?r, \u253?er tapar,\par
Birew - ha\u253?yr g\u246?rmez beren duzundan.\par
\par
\u221?igit \u246?lse, hatyn galsa, \u228?r tapdy,\par
Ogul-gyz elinde maly\u328? \u253?er tapdy,\par
Zekatsyz mal mag\u351?ar g\u252?ni mar tapdy,\par
Yrak d\u252?\u351?d\u252?\u328? \u221?aradany\u328? g\u246?z\u252?nden.\par
\par
Dirilikde \u246?zi berse elinden,\par
Habar tutan \u221?aradany\u328? \u253?olundan,\par
Ha\u253?yr tapar \u8722? mal bi\u253?r eken malyndan,\par
Ol hem \u253?ag\u351?y \u253?at etseler yzyndan.\par
\par
Saglygy\u328?da el barmasa, berm\u228?ge,\par
Gy\u253?masalar galanlar gol germ\u228?ge,\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, azap g\u246?rm\u228?ge,\par
Ky\u253?amat garasy gitmez \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328?den.\par
\par
OTUR-TURU\u350?YN G\u214?R\u220?\u327?\par
Her \u253?igidi\u328? aslyn bile\u253? di\u253?se\u328?iz,\par
M\u228?rekede otur-turu\u351?yn g\u246?r\u252?\u328?.\par
Birew bilen a\u351?na bola\u253? di\u253?se\u328?iz,\par
Owwal ykrarynda duru\u351?yn g\u246?r\u252?\u328?.\par
\par
Uzak \u253?ola gidip geler bolsa\u328?yz,\par
Merdanalyk gyljyn \u231?alar bolsa\u328?yz,\par
Bir bedewi sa\u253?lap alar bolsa\u328?yz,\par
Synasyn, sagrysyn, geri\u351?in g\u246?r\u252?\u328?.\par
\par
Bir pul d\u252?\u351?se bir \u252?flasy\u328? goluna,\par
G\u246?ws\u252?n a\u231?yp gezer gy\u351?y\u328? \u253?eline,\par
Hyrydar bolsa\u328?yz gyza, geline,\par
Edebin, ekramyn, otur\u351?yn g\u246?r\u252?\u328?.\par
\par
Go\u231? \u253?igidi\u328? at-\u253?aragy \u351?a\u253? bolsa,\par
\u221?eti\u351?er her \u253?erde ha\u253?-da ha\u253? bolsa,\par
\u214?zi Hatam bolup, \u253?ene ba\u253? bolsa,\par
\u199?ar tarapdan myhman geli\u351?in g\u246?r\u252?\u328?.\par
\par
Bir ni\u231?\u228?ni kyldy\u328? maly-bis\u253?ary,\par
Bir ni\u231?\u228?ni kyldy\u328? bir pulu\u328? zary,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman, bar\u231?a adamy\u328? bary,\par
Nobat bile \u246?t\u252?p bary\u351?yn g\u246?r\u252?\u328?.\par
\par
Ta\u328?ry bizar erer zekatsyz ba\u253?dan,\par
Zynhar siz hem ga\u231?y\u328? ol gelen ja\u253?dan,\par
Merde her i\u351? d\u252?\u351?se, g\u246?rer Huda\u253?dan,\par
Namardy\u328? hemradan g\u246?r\u252?\u351?in g\u246?r\u252?\u328?.\par
\par
Namart \u253?\u246?rer mydam \u246?l\u252?mden ga\u231?yp,\par
\u214?\u253?\u252?ne gelende, z\u228?herin sa\u231?yp,\par
Mert \u253?igit \u246?l\u252?me synasyn a\u231?yp,\par
Namardy\u328? \u246?\u253?\u252?nden ga\u231?y\u351?yn g\u246?r\u252?\u328?.\par
\par
Zalymlar unudar zikri-Allany,\par
Arzan alyp, gymmat satar gallany,\par
S\u252?\u253?thor na\u253?ynsaplar halal tyllany,\par
Haram pe\u253?dasyna beri\u351?in g\u246?r\u252?\u328?.\par
\par
\u350?e\u253?tan melgun hergiz tagat etdirmez,\par
Haramdan ga\u253?tarmaz, halal \u253?uwtdurmaz,\par
Namaza u\u253?durmaz, roza tutdurmaz,\par
Lagnaty \u351?e\u253?tany\u328? tala\u351?yn g\u246?r\u252?\u328?.\par
\par
Go\u231? \u253?igidi\u328? i\u351?i s\u246?hbet-saz bolar,\par
K\u246?\u328?li gy\u351? bolma\u253?yn, da\u253?ym \u253?az bolar,\par
\u221?ag\u351?yny\u328? k\u246?\u328?l\u252?nde kine az bolar,\par
\u221?amany\u328? her g\u252?nde uru\u351?yn g\u246?r\u252?\u328?!\par
\par
Gadyrdan garda\u351?dan uzak, da\u351? bolup,\par
Gadyrsyz \u253?at bile garynda\u351? bolup,\par
Magtymguly n\u228?sazlara du\u351? bolup,\par
Hojany\u328?, se\u253?idi\u328? \u253?\u246?r\u252?\u351?in g\u246?r\u252?\u328?.\par
\par
N\u196?BILSIN\par
\u220?z umydy\u328? \u246?z\u252?n bilmez adamdan,\par
A\u328?lamaz ol, a:m-u hasy n\u228?bilsin.\par
Ne tama bar hamr i\u231?en gedemden,\par
Buzahor \u253?ag\u351?yny, \u253?asy n\u228?bilsin.\par
\par
\u221?amana \u253?ag\u351?y s\u246?z \u253?okmaz, ta\u351?lanar,\par
A\u328?lar \u228?ri\u328? a\u328?lamasy g\u252?\u253?\u231?lener,\par
It \u253?alyn topraga d\u246?kse\u328? ho\u351?lanar,\par
Topragy, tabagy, tasy n\u228?bilsin.\par
\par
Butparaz m\u252?\u328? kylsa roza-namazy,\par
O\u328?a nesip bolmaz behi\u351?di\u328? \u253?azy,\par
\u196?lemi g\u246?terse ebri\u328? owazy,\par
E\u351?itmez, ker pakyr sesi n\u228?bilsin.\par
\par
Di\u328?le s\u246?z\u252?m, ner zarbyny ner tanyr,\par
Har bakan har tanyr, m\u228?hek zer tanyr,\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, \u228?r \u253?igidi \u228?r tanyr,\par
Namartlar \u253?ag\u351?yny, pisi n\u228?bilsin.\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, s\u246?zlerim hakdyr,\par
Emma ki hak s\u246?ze ten beren \u253?okdur,\par
Bir g\u246?zli di\u253?mese, garadyr, akdyr,\par
K\u246?r pakyr k\u252?m\u252?\u351?i, misi n\u228?bilsin.\par
\par
N\u196?GE \u221?ATYP SEN\par
E\u253?, \u252?lkesi abat, m\u252?lk\u252?ne magrur,\par
M\u252?lk\u252?\u328? bakasy \u253?ok, n\u228?ge \u253?atyp sen?\par
E\u253? ykbaly bidar, d\u246?wlete mesrur,\par
D\u246?wlet wepasy \u253?ok, n\u228?ge \u253?atyp sen?\par
\par
\u350?irin jan ri\u351?tesi tende osaldyr,\par
Nebsi\u328? bir megesdir, mal bir asaldyr,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? aby-sildir, \u246?mr\u252?\u328? bir saldyr,\par
\u214?mre ygtybar \u253?ok, n\u228?ge \u253?atyp sen?\par
\par
Tagat bir derg\u228?he \u253?oldur basgan\u231?ak,\par
I\u351?i\u328? be\u253?le bolsa, durma sen anjak,\par
Ogul, gyz mal-u zen sa\u328?a asgynjak,\par
Go\u253?mazlar gezm\u228?ge, n\u228?ge \u253?atyp sen?\par
\par
Pelek sa\u328?sar da\u351?yn sa\u328?a atypdyr,\par
Zemin a\u382?darhasy pa\u253?y\u328? \u253?uwtupdyr,\par
Ajal tiz oragyn elde tutupdyr,\par
Binurbatdyr, bi\u231?er, n\u228?ge \u253?atyp sen?\par
\par
Magtymguly, i\u351?im ahy-zarydyr,\par
Bir m\u252?kemmel \u228?ri\u328? hyrydarydyr,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? ahyreti\u328? ke\u351?te k\u228?ridir,\par
Tohum sa\u231?ynawer, n\u228?ge \u253?atyp sen?\par
\par
ME\u221?DAN \u221?OLUKSA\par
Bedew \u246?lse, me\u253?dan galar armanly,\par
Hak y\u351?kyna at sal me\u253?dan \u253?oluksa,\par
\u196?r \u246?lejek, he\u328?\u328?am galar d\u246?wranly,\par
Wagty\u328?y ho\u351? ge\u231?ir, d\u246?wran \u253?oluksa.\par
\par
\u221?igit bardyr s\u246?z\u252?n tapmaz, surrudar,\par
\u221?igit bardyr demi da\u351?lar erider,\par
Ja\u253? \u253?erinde ga\u253?ra galsa garrydar,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igidi\u328? aty \u231?aman \u253?oluksa.\par
\par
I\u351?i d\u252?rs gelmez k\u246?\u328?\u252?l \u231?enine,\par
Dodagyny di\u351?l\u228?p, \u171?ah\u187? di\u253?r zenine,\par
\u221?ylan z\u228?hri bolup \u253?a\u253?ryr tenine,\par
\u221?igit garryr hatyn \u253?aman \u253?oluksa.\par
\par
\u221?\u252?z namart \u253?erini tutmaz bir merdi\u328?,\par
Mert \u231?eker t\u228?sibin ili\u328? - \u253?uwurdu\u328?,\par
Bitiren i\u351?in, g\u246?r, gedi namardy\u328? -\par
Je\u328?dir di\u253?ip ga\u231?ar duman \u253?oluksa.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u246?w\u252?t bergin s\u246?z bile,\par
E\u351?iden de\u328? bolmaz, g\u246?ren g\u246?z bile,\par
Mert \u231?ykar myhmana g\u252?ler \u253?\u252?z bile,\par
Namart \u246?z\u252?n gizl\u228?r myhman \u253?oluksa.\par
\par
MALA SERETMEZ\par
Owwal-a mal \u253?ag\u351?y, maldan ba\u351? \u253?ag\u351?y,\par
Ba\u351? d\u246?wletin tapan mala seretmez.\par
Dogmadyk oguldan dogan da\u351? \u253?ag\u351?y,\par
Nadan ogul atasyna seretmez.\par
\par
Atda a\u253?ak bolsa, ba\u351?ga syn bolmaz,\par
\u196?rde ga\u253?rat bolsa, i\u351?i kyn bolmaz,\par
S\u246?we\u351? g\u252?ni go\u231? \u253?igitde \u252?\u253?n bolmaz,\par
Gar\u351?y bakar, pe\u253?kam-\u253?a\u253?a seretmez.\par
\par
Alaman \u246?\u328?\u252?ni serdary ba\u351?lar,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igitler na\u253?za urar, gyly\u231?lar,\par
Kimse adam \u253?ykyp, kimse at u\u351?lar,\par
Abyra\u253? tapmasa, pa\u253?a seretmez.\par
\par
\u196?r dostdan ge\u231?erler adam a\u231? galsa,\par
\u221?ar \u253?ardan a\u253?rylyp, ara da\u351? galsa,\par
\u221?aman hatyn \u253?ag\u351?y \u228?re du\u351? bolsa,\par
Ba\u351?yny terk eder, da\u253?a seretmez.\par
\par
K\u246?ne d\u252?n\u253?\u228? muhannesi\u328? \u246?\u253?\u252?dir,\par
S\u252?\u253?thor bolan kesi\u328? dowzah ja\u253?ydyr,\par
Altyn-k\u252?m\u252?\u351? g\u246?zlerini\u328? ma\u253?ydyr,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igitler bozuk ja\u253?a seretmez.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? g\u246?rki n\u228?zeninler, ne janlar,\par
Nadana \u253?olukdy t\u252?rpe jenanlar,\par
\u221?ardan galan \u8213? \u228?ri \u246?len juwanlar,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igidi g\u246?zl\u228?r, ba\u253?a seretmez.\par
\par
Magtymguly garyp k\u246?\u328?l\u252?n ba\u253? edip,\par
Kanagat \u252?lkesin bende ja\u253? edip,\par
Her kim \u246?z \u253?aryny dogan A\u253? edip,\par
A\u253?yn g\u246?zl\u228?r, ba\u351?ga A\u253?a seretmez.\par
\par
M\u196?HRAP HA\u221?SY, BILMEDIM\par
Abdal ma\u328?a ebet jamyn sunaly,\par
Metjit ha\u253?sy, m\u228?hrap ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
Ol g\u252?dazda janym erip \u253?analy,\par
Abat ha\u253?sy, harap ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
\par
Bir tabe\u351?e tap etmedim, toz boldum,\par
Toprak boldum, ata\u351? boldum, suz boldum,\par
Da\u351?dan bi\u351?dim, i\u231?den k\u246?\u253?d\u252?m, k\u246?z boldum,\par
Ki nar ha\u253?sy, kebap ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
\par
G\u252?zer etdim bir mekansyz mekana,\par
Se\u253?ran etdim bir me\u253?dansyz me\u253?dana,\par
Ha\u253?ran galdym bir jahansyz jahana,\par
Be\u253?t ha\u253?sydyr hem bap ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
\par
Nebse u\u253?dum, \u246?z\u252?m bilme\u253?, hyrs boldum,\par
Akyl i\u351?in dogry sandym, ters bildim,\par
Her e\u351?\u253?adan \u253?ar sypatyn ders aldym,\par
Gurhan ha\u253?sy, kitap ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
\par
Magtymguly ol mekanda meks etdi,\par
\u350?yhlar turdy, \u253?igitler de\u253? raks etdi,\par
Her e\u351?\u253?adan \u253?ar jemaly eks etdi,\par
Ap ha\u253?sydyr, \u351?erap ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
\par
MAH-U SALLARA\par
Imdi, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m, bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni s\u246?\u253?megil,\par
Ynanmagyl, \u253?ag\u351?y mah-u sallara.\par
Akyl erse\u328?, her bir s\u246?ze u\u253?magyl,\par
S\u246?ze u\u253?an d\u252?\u351?er aldan-allara.\par
\par
\u221?ok eken d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? \u228?hti-wepasy,\par
Hany \u253?igitleri\u328? zowky-sapasy,\par
G\u252?n-g\u252?nden artadyr jebri-jepasy,\par
Bir g\u252?n salar sizi \u253?aman hallara.\par
\par
Bir g\u252?n du\u351?arsy\u328?yz dowasyz derde,\par
Jan a\u253?rylyp galar sargaryp murda,\par
\u221?olugar siz munda, onda, her \u253?erde,\par
Depdere \u253?azylan kyl-u kallara.\par
\par
Geler-ge\u231?er, munda hi\u231? kimse galmaz,\par
Bendiwandyr onda, baranlar gelmez,\par
\u214?tenden-ge\u231?enden habaryn bilmez,\par
Garyp \u252?lkesine giden illere.\par
\par
Jany\u328?y tartarlar bogazy\u328? gyssap,\par
\u350?ol dem gara\u328?kyrar A\u253? ile Aftap,\par
Ata-ogul, dost-\u253?aryndan dil ist\u228?p\par
Telmuryp bakar sen sag-u sollara.\par
\par
Nesip bolsa, ili\u328?-g\u252?n\u252?\u328? \u253?ygylar,\par
Hijran ody \u253?\u252?regi\u328?e dag salar,\par
Ogul-gyz, dost-\u253?ary\u328?, uzadyp galar,\par
A\u253?ralyga giden uzyn \u253?ollara.\par
\par
Jellat ajal bir g\u252?n gelse n\u228?der sen,\par
Alajy \u253?ok, na\u231?ar bolup gider sen,\par
Magtymguly, sen hem pu\u351?man eder sen,\par
............................................. billere.\par
\par
PE\u221?ANY BOLMAZ\par
Ge\u231? k\u246?\u328?\u252?l, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?den, e\u253?leme h\u246?wes,\par
Panydyr, hi\u231? kime pe\u253?any bolmaz.\par
Jan gu\u351?y bilbildir, teni\u328? bir kapas,\par
Bir g\u252?n u\u231?ar, da\u253?ym durany bolmaz.\par
\par
Bir ni\u231?\u228?ni \u351?alyk bile \u351?at edip,\par
\u171?\u350?\u228?hri\u253?ar\u187? di\u253?p, \u228?lem i\u231?re at edip,\par
Ajaly\u328? elinden bir g\u252?n dat edip,\par
Gitdiler barysy, \u253?\u246?reni bolmaz.\par
\par
Ynsa-jynsa \u351?alyk eden S\u252?le\u253?man;\par
Jem\u351?id-u Isgender, hany Now\u351?irwan?\par
Hany Hak habyby - ol Fahry-jahan?\par
Gitdi bary, hergiz g\u252?many bolmaz.\par
\par
Galmady Daraby\u328?, ne \u350?\u228?hri\u253?ary\u328?,\par
Hany ol G\u252?l\u231?ehre, simin-yzary\u328??\par
Hany \u351?asuwary\u328?, zerrin hysary\u328??\par
Hi\u231? birini\u328? nam-u ny\u351?any bolmaz.\par
\par
Ni\u231?e mursal ge\u231?di, ni\u231?e m\u252?\u328? nebi,\par
Ni\u231?e balyg ge\u231?di, ni\u231?e m\u252?\u328? saby,\par
Hasyl olma\u253?, hi\u231? birini\u328? matlaby,\par
Pany i\u231?re baky galany bolmaz.\par
\par
Kimi gany kyldy, kimleri galla\u231?,\par
\u221?oksuzy ba\u253?lara e\u253?ledi m\u228?t\u228?\u231?,\par
Gelse ajal bady, bolar n\u228?ala\u231?,\par
Gitgisidir, \u253?ag\u351?y-\u253?amany bolmaz.\par
\par
Maly-d\u252?n\u253?e berip ni\u231?e m\u252?\u328? gany,\par
Lagl-u j\u246?w\u228?hirden bolup mesgeni,\par
Gitdi go\u253?up kasry, k\u246?\u351?ki, e\u253?wany,\par
Barganydan ga\u253?dyp geleni bolmaz.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge geleni\u328? bary \u253?ok bolar,\par
Gapyl adam bilmezlikden aldanar,\par
\u221?ygnany\u328? barysy d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de galar,\par
Hi\u231? bir adam alyp barany bolmaz.\par
\par
Kamaty serwi dek n\u228?zik bedenler,\par
Sibi-zenehdanlar, gun\u231?a dahanlar,\par
G\u252?l \u253?\u252?zli periler, simin-zakanlar,\par
\u196?lemde \u351?at bolup g\u252?leni bolmaz.\par
\par
\u221?ok wepasy, dostlar, pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328?,\par
\u214?lin\u231?\u228?\u328? terk etme ha\u253?r-u yhsany\u328?,\par
Barandan, gelm\u228?ge \u253?okdur imkany\u328?,\par
Ynan, bu s\u246?zleri\u328? \u253?alany bolmaz.\par
\par
Akyl oldur, me\u253?l etmese d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge,\par
Sydk ile sygynsa Kadyr Allaga,\par
Magtymguly, her suraty-zybaga,\par
Bakmagyl, olary\u328? pa\u253?any bolmaz.\par
\par
MALYNA DEGMEZ\par
Ba\u253?lar bardyr, garyplara rehm e\u253?l\u228?r,\par
Bardyr ba\u253?lar, d\u252?n\u253?\u228? malyna degmez.\par
G\u246?zel bardyr, d\u252?n\u253?\u228? malyn har\u231? etse\u328?,\par
Bardyr g\u246?zel, i\u253?en nanyna degmez.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de bahyly\u328? \u253?\u252?z\u252?ni g\u246?rme,\par
A\u351? bile nany\u328?y aly\u351?yp berme,\par
Gul di\u253?ip, \u253?igidi\u328? aslyny sorma,\par
Hojasy bar, belki, guluna degmez!\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? malyn berse\u328?, e\u253?esi satmaz,\par
\u350?a istese, onu\u328? dilegi bitmez,\par
Bedew bar, pul berse\u328?, bahasy \u253?etmes,\par
Bardyr bedew, salan juluna degmez.\par
\par
Bedew gerek - \u228?re s\u246?we\u351?de serho\u351?,\par
\u221?at bilen bary\u351?sa\u328?, bolar garynda\u351?,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y ogul, \u253?ag\u351?y a\u253?al, gyz, garda\u351?, -\par
Bu d\u246?wlet her kimi\u328? eline degmez.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? e\u351?reti;\par
I\u253?mek, i\u231?mek, m\u252?nmek, gu\u231?mak, s\u246?hbeti,\par
Bir ni\u231?eler mydam kylar tagaty,\par
Ni\u231?\u228?ni\u328? sejde ja\u253? alyna degmez.\par
\par
L\u196?LE GETIRMI\u350?\par
Asmandan nur \u253?agsa, m\u252?newwer bolar,\par
Zemin \u253?a\u351?yl ge\u253?ip, l\u228?le getirmi\u351?\par
Huda bu\u253?rugyndan a\u253?rylan juwan -\par
O\u253?na\u351?yndan haram k\u246?le getirmi\u351?.\par
\par
Owwal akan \u253?erden akarmy\u351? aryk,\par
Men-menlik edeni\u328? tanapy \u231?\u252?\u253?r\u252?k,\par
Mertden a\u351?na tutsa\u328?, abra\u253?\u328?a \u351?\u228?rik,\par
Namart a\u351?nasyna hile getirmi\u351?.\par
\par
Her kim gezer bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de bir hile,\par
\u221?\u246?rg\u252?n ata-baba \u253?\u246?rigen \u253?ola,\par
Ba\u253?tal \u253?apagysyn \u231?ekermi\u351? \u231?\u246?le,\par
E\u351?ek k\u252?rresini k\u252?le getirmi\u351?.\par
\par
Her kim \u246?z adyna m\u246?h\u252?r gazdyrar,\par
\u221?azylan takdyry kimse bozdurar,\par
Ikini\u328? sylagy birin azdyrar,\par
Ta\u253?ak bir d\u228?lini \u253?ola getirmi\u351?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ger do\u253?ursa\u328? bir ajy,\par
M\u228?limdir, tapar sen bu \u253?erde hajy,\par
N\u228?ge mertlik etse adam biweji,\par
Her mejlisde \u253?\u252?z \u253?ol tile getirmi\u351?.\par
\par
KYL-U KAL BOLAR\par
Her ki\u351?ini\u328? iki bolsa a\u253?aly,\par
Gije-g\u252?ndiz i\u351?i kyl-u kal bolar.\par
Her birini\u328? bardyr \u253?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? hy\u253?aly,\par
Owkat s\u252?r\u252?p, g\u246?rejegi hal bolar.\par
\par
Birin s\u246?\u253?\u252?p, birin e\u253?lese na\u231?ar,\par
Ile ryswa bolup, \u246?z a\u253?byn a\u231?ar,\par
Akly ha\u253?ran bolup, baryndan ge\u231?er,\par
De\u328? tutmasa \u253?aryn, bikemal bolar.\par
\par
G\u228?hi bilbil kibi sa\u253?rar dilleri,\par
Toma\u351?adan h\u228?zir eder illeri,\par
G\u228?hi \u253?er \u253?umruklar, g\u228?hi-k\u252?lleri,\par
\u196?rin g\u246?re bilse, dilsiz lal bolar.\par
\par
Gahr e\u253?le\u253?ip, gelmez bolsa \u253?anyna,\par
S\u246?z a\u253?tmasa her birini\u328? \u351?anyna,\par
Be\u253?le \u228?r go\u351?ulmaz adam sanyna,\par
Iki hatyn, bir \u228?r - \u252?\u231? a\u253?al bolar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, kimse bilmez batyny,\par
\u214?\u253?lense\u328?iz, garap aly\u328? zatyny,\par
E\u253?\u228?m g\u246?rkezmesin \u253?aman hatyny,\par
Adam \u246?z\u252?n bilmez, ham hy\u253?al bolar.\par
\par
I\u350? BOLMAZ\par
Gel, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m, sydk ile \u253?albar Allaga,\par
\u221?aradandan hi\u231? \u253?a\u351?yryn i\u351? bolmaz.\par
Ryzk bir mukadderdir \u351?ah-u gedaga,\par
Galam birdir, munda \u253?azan bi\u351? bolmaz.\par
\par
Bir ni\u231?eler \u253?ortar gije \u253?atma\u253?yn,\par
Birew \u253?atyr, \u246?\u253?de m\u228?hnet tartma\u253?yn,\par
Takdyry-ezelden hergiz artma\u253?yn\par
Gezen artyk bolup, \u253?atan bo\u351? bolmaz.\par
\par
Bir go\u231? \u253?igit \u253?alan d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge gelse,\par
Gylgy gyly\u231?, \u231?\u246?rek, desterhan bolsa,\par
\u221?alan\u231?yda abra\u253? hem iman bolsa,\par
\u221?etmi\u351?, segsen, \u253?\u252?zden artyk \u253?a\u351? bolmaz.\par
\par
Kimseler d\u246?wletment, kimseler garyp,\par
Kimseler ha\u253?r edip, zekatyn berip,\par
Kimseler \u246?mr\u252?nde nan di\u253?ip \u253?\u246?rip,\par
Kimselerde \u253?assyk, d\u252?\u351?ek, a\u351? bolmaz.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu g\u252?n\u252?\u328?e \u351?\u252?kr e\u253?le,\par
Allany\u328? gudratyn g\u246?r\u252?p, pikr e\u253?le,\par
Ryzk \u252?\u231?in gam i\u253?me, Haka zikr e\u253?le,\par
Ezelde \u253?azylan senden da\u351? bolmaz.\par
\par
IGL\u196?RLER\par
Sag-salamat, sermest bolup gezen jan\par
D\u246?rt belany\u328? birisinden igl\u228?rler,\par
\u221?a sowukdan, \u253?a yssydan guryr gan,\par
Ten \u252?st\u252?nde tebipleri egl\u228?rler.\par
\par
Ryzk wekili geler ryzky\u328? \u253?ok edip,\par
G\u246?wr\u228?\u328?i guradyp, \u253?olu\u328? bek edip,\par
Demi\u328? peri\u351?desi demi\u328? t\u252?kedip,\par
Ili\u328?-g\u252?n\u252?\u328? \u246?zge \u253?urda \u231?aglarlar.\par
\par
Egsikleri\u328? sa\u231? \u253?a\u253?arlar, ba\u351? d\u246?k\u252?p,\par
\u221?ary-dostu\u328? \u253?ygla\u351?arlar \u253?a\u351? d\u246?k\u252?p,\par
Garda\u351?-dogan katlanarlar a\u351? d\u246?k\u252?p,\par
Gonsa, g\u246?\u231?mez \u8722? karar \u253?urda baglarlar.\par
\par
Habar d\u252?\u351?er: \u171?Pylan kimse \u246?tdi\u187? di\u253?p,\par
\u171?\u199?yragy s\u246?ndi\u187? di\u253?p, \u171?G\u252?ni batdy\u187? di\u253?p,\par
\u171?Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?den o d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge gitdi\u187? di\u253?p,\par
\u171?Alla rehmet etsin!\u187? di\u253?ip dargarlar.\par
\par
Kim bardyr ki, pelek bagryn ezmemi\u351?,\par
G\u246?wresin gy\u253?mamy\u351?, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?n bozmamy\u351?,\par
Magtymguly, dag-der\u253?alar d\u246?zmemi\u351?,\par
Bu dessurdyr, a\u253?ralyga aglarlar.\par
\par
IRNIP DURUPDYR\par
Gaflat \u253?assygynda go\u253?updyr ba\u351?y,\par
Gapyl adam mun\u231?a irnip durupdyr.\par
Ten kapasy i\u231?re wag\u351?y jan gu\u351?y,\par
Her dem perwaz e\u253?l\u228?p, urnup durupdyr.\par
\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328? \u246?tdi-gitdi kylmady\u328? perwa,\par
Menzili\u328? metjit kyl, d\u252?\u351?egi\u328? bor\u253?a,\par
Kylgany\u328? k\u252?p\u252?rdir, etgeni\u328? yr\u253?a,\par
Onda kaza \u253?a\u253?y gurlup durupdyr.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylardan bir nesihat alawer,\par
Gitdi kerwen, \u253?eke galdy\u328?, \u253?elewer,\par
Adam ogly, zynhar, h\u228?zir bolawer,\par
Nebsi-\u351?e\u253?tan sa\u328?a s\u252?rn\u252?p durupdyr.\par
\par
Elwan tagam i\u253?ip, al-\u253?a\u351?yl ge\u253?ip,\par
Parahat \u253?atyr sen, gorky\u328?y go\u253?up,\par
Ajal \u351?iri arlap, penjesin \u253?a\u253?yp,\par
Ba\u351?y\u328? ujun alyp, gernip durupdyr.\par
\par
O\u253?an, Magtymguly, gaflatda \u253?atma,\par
Mala magrur olup, m\u228?hnete batma,\par
\u214?ter d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u252?\u231?in \u246?mr\u252?\u328?i satma,\par
Bu nogsany\u328? d\u252?\u253?bi g\u246?rn\u252?p durupdyr.\par
\par
HALYMA MENI\u327?\par
Kerem e\u253?le, \u253?a Rep, gudratly Suhan,\par
Garyp, gamgyn ge\u231?en halyma meni\u328?.\par
Aklym ha\u253?randadyr, etmi\u351?em pu\u351?man,\par
Bilmezlikde ge\u231?en salyma meni\u328?.\par
\par
Mag\u351?ar g\u252?n bolmasa\u328? Sen ma\u328?a dalda,\par
\u221?a Rep, ni\u231?ik bolar i\u351?im \u351?o halda,\par
Imanym matagyn aparan \u253?olda,\par
Rehzenler go\u253?magyl \u253?oluma meni\u328?.\par
\par
Din gylyjyn ursam, tende zorum \u253?ok,\par
M\u228?t\u228?je nan bi\u253?re elde zerim \u253?ok,\par
Pakyr menem, Senden a\u253?ry \u253?erim \u253?ok,\par
Bir teselli bergil k\u246?\u328?l\u252?me meni\u328?.\par
\par
Istese de\u328?-du\u351?lar ba\u351?a altyn t\u228?\u231?,\par
Pakyrlyk m\u252?lk\u252?nden ma\u328?a bergin pa\u231?,\par
\u221?a, \u221?aradan, etme namarda m\u228?t\u228?\u231?,\par
Dilegim, du\u351? etme zalyma meni\u328?.\par
\par
Ejiz menem, Senden \u246?zge kimim bar,\par
\u214?z beren jany\u328?a jebr etme, Jepbar,\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, keremli Gapbar,\par
Bakma kyldygyma, p\u228?lime meni\u328?.\par
\par
HIJRAN HA\u221?SY, BILMEDIM\par
Pelek ma\u328?a gam badasyn bereli,\par
Wysal ha\u253?sy, hijran ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
Hak i\u351?ine ten bermi\u351?em, g\u246?reli,\par
Arzuw ha\u253?sy, arman ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
\par
Bende bolsa\u328?, g\u246?zle Haky\u328? ryzasyn,\par
Jebir e\u253?lese, \u231?ekewergil jezasyn,\par
Ajal atar bir g\u252?n tiri-kazasyn,\par
Kiri\u351? ha\u253?sy, keman ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
\par
Bir suratam, bakma\u328?, bu g\u252?n \u246?z\u252?me,\par
Aryp bolsa\u328?, gulak go\u253?gul s\u246?z\u252?me,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? d\u252?\u253?bi \u253?ok g\u246?r\u252?ner g\u246?z\u252?me,\par
D\u246?w\u252?r ha\u253?sy, d\u246?wran ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
\par
Az \u246?mr\u252?mi k\u246?p s\u246?wda\u253?a satyp men,\par
\u214?z\u252?m bilme\u253?, ol der\u253?a\u253?a atyp men,\par
Ne ummandyr, ne talapdyr, batyp men,\par
Zemin ha\u253?sy, zaman ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
\par
Her kim girse ol talaba-ummana,\par
Ba\u351?yn alyp \u231?yka bilmez bir \u253?ana,\par
Gadam go\u253?dum ol s\u228?hra\u253?a-me\u253?dana,\par
Jan ha\u253?sydyr, jahan ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
\par
Men d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni asmandaky re\u328? bildim,\par
Yssy-yssy asyly\u351?dym, so\u328? bildim,\par
Imdi onu\u328? baryn-\u253?ogun de\u328? bildim,\par
Sud ha\u253?sydyr, zy\u253?an ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?olu\u328? \u246?\u328?i, ardy bar,\par
\u199?eker \u253?\u252?k\u252?n, her ki\u351?ini\u328? merdi bar,\par
\u221?\u252?regimde pynhan y\u351?ky\u328? derdi bar,\par
Dert ha\u253?sydyr, derman ha\u253?sy, bilmedim.\par
\par
GALYP MEN\par
Jahyllygy\u328? jo\u351?y \u231?ykdy ba\u351?ymdan,\par
Men ol jo\u351?dan haly bolup galyp men.\par
Bir gama ula\u351?dym, gitdim hu\u351?umdan,\par
Bu dert ile doly bolup galyp men.\par
\par
Ba\u351?ym \u253?\u252?z h\u246?wesde, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m jo\u351?gunda,\par
Girdaba d\u252?\u351?\u252?p men d\u228?li da\u351?gynda,\par
Nejt dagynda gezen Mejnun y\u351?kynda,\par
\u221?anar otly Le\u253?li bolup galyp men.\par
\par
\u221?igitlik paslyny gy\u351?a \u253?etirdim,\par
K\u228?millik ki\u351?tisin der\u253?a batyrdym,\par
Be\u253?ik pikre galdym, aklym \u253?itirdim,\par
Il i\u231?inde d\u228?li bolup galyp men.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni g\u246?\u231?\u252?p baran g\u246?\u231? bildim,\par
I\u351?ini bet a\u328?dym, \u246?z\u252?n pu\u231? bildim,\par
\u214?\u328?\u252?n o\u253?un g\u246?rd\u252?m, so\u328?un hi\u231? bildim,\par
Tirik erken, \u246?li bolup galyp men.\par
\par
Magtymguly, pa\u351? e\u253?legil s\u246?z\u252?\u328?i,\par
Pelek mu\u351?ty-h\u228?k etme\u253?en g\u246?z\u252?\u328?i,\par
Bu wagta de\u328? \u253?a\u351? bilerdi\u328? \u246?z\u252?\u328?ni,\par
Imdi g\u246?r, bak, uly bolup galyp men.\par
\par
G\u214?ZLEME\u221?IN BOLARMY\par
Bir k\u228?kilik aldyrsa z\u252?rbe balasyn,\par
Sa\u253?ra\u253?-sa\u253?ra\u253?, g\u246?zleme\u253?in bolarmy?\par
Bir bilbil \u253?itirse gyzyl l\u228?lesin,\par
Hasratyndan s\u246?zleme\u253?in bolarmy?\par
\par
K\u252?rresi elinden gitse e\u351?egi\u328?,\par
Telmuryp t\u246?rt \u253?ana, bakar u\u351?agyn,\par
Akma\u253?a aldyrsa elden k\u246?\u351?egin,\par
Bagryn bozup, bozlama\u253?yn bolarmy?\par
\par
Bala sesin di\u328?l\u228?p, salar gulagyn,\par
D\u246?ke-d\u246?ke g\u246?z\u253?a\u351?yny\u328? bulagyn,\par
Bir jeren aldyrsa elden owlagyn,\par
M\u228?le\u253?-m\u228?le\u253?, yzlama\u253?yn bolarmy?\par
\par
Agsagy\u328? elinden alsa\u328? agajyn,\par
\u221?aman derde d\u252?\u351?er, tapmaz alajyn,\par
Bir g\u252?\u253?\u231?li du\u351?mana du\u351?sa mekejin,\par
Jojugyny gizleme\u253?in bolarmy?\par
\par
A\u253?ralyga adam ogly ne\u253?lesin?\par
Kim galar g\u246?rme\u253?in ajal hilesin,\par
Magtymguly ha\u253?wan bilse balasyn,\par
Ynsan bagryn duzlama\u253?yn bolarmy?\par
\par
\u220?SSESI BOLMAZ\par
Allany \u253?at edip, haky g\u246?zlese\u328?,\par
De\u328?me-de\u328? s\u246?wdany\u328? \u252?ssesi bolmaz,\par
Dawa kenarynda \u253?alan s\u246?zlese\u328?,\par
G\u252?mansyz \u253?anar sen, t\u252?ssesi bolmaz.\par
\par
Oka b\u228?\u351? wagty\u328?y, bolawer m\u252?fti\par
Eger bolajak sen resul ymmaty,\par
Zor bilen iberse\u328? go\u253?na bir iti,\par
Gurt gelende, go\u253?na yssysy bolmaz.\par
\par
Bu s\u246?zi di\u253?mesem, zybanym gij\u228?r,\par
\u214?z k\u246?\u328?l\u252?\u328? go\u253?masa\u328?, dost k\u246?\u328?li ynjar,\par
Bagdatda nar bi\u351?se, Tur\u351?i\u351?de injir,\par
Hyrat dek hi\u231? \u253?eri\u328? pissesi bolmaz.\par
\par
Bu s\u246?zi di\u253?meklik bizlere namys,\par
Bir mugjyzat g\u246?rd\u252?m, di\u253?dim: \u171?Elhepus!\u187?\par
Bagdatda gy\u351? bolmaz, Gyrgyzda tomus,\par
Bulgary\u328? \u351?\u228?hrini\u328? \u253?assysy bolmaz.\par
\par
Magtymguly, gel, go\u253?, bu belent \u253?oly,\par
Di\u253?se\u328? hem hi\u231? kimse ynanmaz h\u228?li,\par
Alsa\u328? bir sary di\u351? garry a\u253?aly,\par
O\u253?na\u351?a\u328?da, hi\u231? bir yssysy bolmaz.\par
\par
U\u199?A BILMEN NE\u221?L\u196?\u221?IN\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?m ist\u228?r, gezsem d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u228?lemi,\par
Ganatym \u253?ok, u\u231?a bilmen, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?!\par
Okar men, g\u246?rer men F\u246?wzi-Kelamy,\par
Manysyny sa\u231?a bilmen, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?!\par
\par
K\u246?pler onda guwwas bolup \u253?\u252?zerler,\par
Ma\u328?a zahyr, halkdan pynhan gezerler,\par
G\u252?l badada g\u252?lg\u252?n \u351?erap ezerler,\par
El uzadyp, i\u231?e bilmen, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?!\par
\par
\u214?\u253? da\u351?yndan \u351?erap ysyn no\u351? kyldym,\par
Gitdi aklym, \u246?z\u252?m bilme\u253?, jo\u351? kyldym,\par
Me\u253?-mest boldum, dersiz gapa du\u351? boldum,\par
Rugsat bolma\u253?, a\u231?a bilmen, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?!\par
\par
\u221?itdi \u253?olum, dag ha\u253?sydyr, d\u252?z ha\u253?sy,\par
A\u328?maz k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m many ha\u253?sy, s\u246?z ha\u253?sy,\par
P\u228?hm e\u253?lemen, \u253?ol ha\u253?sydyr, yz ha\u253?sy,\par
Umyt \u252?z\u252?p, ga\u231?a bilmen, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?!\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? hamusyn,\par
\u221?ygyp, d\u252?\u253?r\u252?p, \u253?ele berdim namysyn,\par
Pikir der\u253?asyna aklym g\u228?misin,\par
Batyrmy\u351?am, ge\u231?e bilmen, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?!\par
\par
G\u214?\u199?ER SEN\par
Magrur olma bu gondugy\u328? \u253?urdu\u328?a,\par
Bibakadyr, eglenmez sen, g\u246?\u231?er sen,\par
Saky ajal d\u246?w\u252?r-d\u246?w\u252?r sunular,\par
Sen hem baryp, bir d\u246?w\u252?rde i\u231?er sen.\par
\par
Bu rabatda bir di\u328?l\u228?n \u253?ok, okan \u253?ok,\par
Ba\u351?ly bazar, bir gurulgy d\u252?kan \u253?ok,\par
Gamhanadyr, belli menzil-mekan \u253?ok,\par
Bu mekana gelmi\u351? bolsa\u328?, ge\u231?er sen.\par
\par
A\u253?ralyk \u253?\u252?rekde derdi-dagy\u328?dyr,\par
Toba kyl Ta\u328?ryga, \u253?igit \u231?agy\u328?dyr,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328? \u351?ugla ursa, \u253?\u252?rek \u253?agy\u328?dyr,\par
\u221?ag t\u252?kener, pelt\u228?\u328? \u253?anar, \u246?\u231?er sen.\par
\par
La\u253? bolar sen, s\u246?\u253?\u252?nmegil g\u252?laba,\par
Lahap guma d\u246?ner, hana\u328? haraba,\par
S\u252?\u328?\u328?\u252?\u328? s\u252?rm\u228? d\u246?ner, teni\u328? - turaba,\par
Do\u253?maz-dolmaz \u253?er go\u253?nuny gu\u231?ar sen.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? durar, hi\u231? t\u252?kenmez bu galla,\par
\u214?m\u252?r baka berse, kyrkdyr bir pille,\par
Ajal otdur, ten myltykdyr, jan - g\u252?lle,\par
Ryzk d\u228?rige ata\u351? d\u252?\u351?se, g\u246?\u231?er sen.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y sagat, ajap wagtdyr, ho\u351? e\u253?\u253?am,\par
\u214?m\u252?r azdyr, akyl k\u252?teh, i\u351?i\u328? ham,\par
Jan bir gu\u351?dur, d\u252?n\u253?\u228? - d\u228?ne, pelek - dam,\par
Ha\u231?an mundan gutular sen, ga\u231?ar sen.\par
\par
Magtymguly s\u246?zl\u228?r, s\u246?z\u252?n so\u328?lamaz,\par
Bidert ki\u351?i dertli s\u246?z\u252?n di\u328?lemez,\par
Akmak s\u246?zden hezl e\u253?lemez, a\u328?lamaz,\par
Aryp bolsa\u328?, s\u246?z manysyn se\u231?er sen.\par
\par
TAPMAS SEN\par
Ni\u231?e i\u351?i akyl bilen jem etse\u328?,\par
Pelek \u231?a\u351?yr, bir g\u252?n hasap tapmas sen.\par
Bu jan saglygynda ha\u253?yr gazangyl,\par
\u221?er astyna girse\u328?, sowap tapmas sen.\par
\par
Munda ne i\u351? etse\u328?, onda soragly,\par
Sen hem \u253?ag\u351?ylardan alawer \u253?oly,\par
H\u228?li hem bir pille, e\u253?, adam ogly,\par
Alymlar kemelse, edep tapmas sen.\par
\par
\u221?igrimi \u253?a\u351?ynda \u228?ri\u328? ne gamy,\par
\u221?ykar dagy, da\u351?y erider demi,\par
Bir g\u252?n \u246?ter \u253?igitligi\u328? m\u246?ws\u252?mi,\par
\u221?yglap-\u253?yglap gelse\u328?, jogap tapmas sen.\par
\par
\u221?igit bolsa\u328?, gezgil \u253?ag\u351?y at bilen,\par
Bedew m\u252?n\u252?p, gezgil perizat bilen,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328?i \u246?t\u252?rgil jemagat bilen,\par
Metjidi \u253?ykylsa, m\u228?hrap tapmas sen.\par
\par
Magtymguly, a\u253?dar ajap jo\u351? etdi,\par
Erenler s\u246?hbetde bir g\u252?n du\u351? etdi,\par
Bir k\u228?se me\u253? berip g\u252?lg\u252?n, no\u351? etdi,\par
Her g\u252?n k\u228?se doly \u351?erap tapmas sen.\par
\par
BAKA-BAKA GIDER SEN\par
Panydan baky\u253?a g\u246?\u231?-h\u228? g\u246?\u231? bolsa,\par
Telmuryban, baka-baka gider sen.\par
Ajal jamyn berip, i\u231?-h\u228? i\u231? bolsa,\par
Jan ajygyn \u231?eke-\u231?eke gider sen.\par
\par
Oglanlary\u328? durar zary-gir\u253?ana,\par
Egsikler sa\u231? \u253?a\u253?ar, d\u252?\u351?er lerzana,\par
Maly\u328? kysmat bolup girer tala\u328?a,\par
Eli\u328? \u253?uwup, \u231?yka-\u231?yka gider sen.\par
\par
Mal \u252?\u231?in ynjydyp garda\u351?-dogany\u328?,\par
Az bildi\u328? tylladan satyp-sowany\u328?,\par
Pa\u253?la\u351?arlar halal-haram \u253?ygany\u328?,\par
Sen azabyn \u231?eke-\u231?eke gider sen.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?den barsa\u328?, ol d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, garda\u351?,\par
N\u228?ler g\u246?rejekdir bu \u351?um gara ba\u351?,\par
Ha\u253?yr gazan, bolar \u253?any\u328?a \u253?olda\u351?,\par
\u221?ogsa gabra \u253?eke-\u253?eke gider sen.\par
\par
Adam ogly \u253?ada salsa asylyn,\par
Kaza go\u253?mu\u351? ajal atly masylyn,\par
Akly\u328? bolsa ky\u253?amaty\u328? hasylyn,\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de eke-eke gider sen.\par
\par
Jahanda g\u246?rkezer gudrat i\u351?leri,\par
Ganaty\u328? kuwwaty galdyr gu\u351?lary,\par
\u221?igitligi\u328? zory syndyr da\u351?lary,\par
Kyrkdan a\u351?dy\u328?, \u231?\u246?ke-\u231?\u246?ke gider sen.\par
\par
Magtymguly, d\u252?\u351?d\u252?\u328? y\u351?ky\u328? g\u252?zerne,\par
Kim bar s\u246?zletm\u228?ge eltip nazarna,\par
Hi\u231? rowa\u231? tapmady\u328? s\u246?z\u252?\u328? bazarna,\par
Hyrydarsyz, d\u246?ke-d\u246?ke gider sen.\par
\par
BOLA-BOLA GIDER SEN\par
Gara ganlar \u253?uwdup, hasratlar \u231?ekip,\par
Mala me\u351?gul bola-bola gider sen.\par
Dodagy\u328? tebredip, \u253?\u252?regi\u328? \u253?akyp,\par
G\u252?many\u328? bar, alyp, bile gider sen.\par
\par
Mun\u231?a jepa \u8722? ogul, gyz-u zen \u252?\u231?in,\par
Mun\u231?a e\u351?ret \u8722? h\u228?k olajak ten \u252?\u231?in,\par
Gitmez garamaty iki g\u252?n \u252?\u231?in,\par
Ne\u231?\u252?n bo\u253?na ala-ala gider sen.\par
\par
Magrur olma senjaby\u328?a, samry\u328?a,\par
Ajal \u8722? Dawut elin \u231?ekmi\u351? demri\u328?e.\par
Gyl\u231?a jana bu b\u228?\u351? g\u252?nl\u252?k \u246?mr\u252?\u328?e,\par
Ne tet\u228?rik kyla-kyla gider sen.\par
\par
Malyny k\u252?\u253?seme berimsiz ba\u253?y\u328?,\par
Il gezdik\u231?e, g\u246?zi do\u253?maz geda\u253?y\u328?,\par
M\u246?min bolsa\u328?, kyl gullugyn Huda\u253?y\u328?,\par
B\u228?\u351? wagt \u253?ada sala-sala gider sen.\par
\par
Magtymguly, habar bergin ederi\u328?,\par
Her \u253?an barsa\u328?, ajal almy\u351? g\u252?zeri\u328?,\par
\u221?ashana di\u253?p, \u253?yglap ge\u231?di pederi\u328?,\par
Senmi mundan g\u252?le-g\u252?le gider sen?\par
\par
BOLAR SEN\par
Belent daglar, be\u253?iklig\u328?e bu\u253?sanma,\par
G\u252?dazda suw bolan zer dek bolar sen.\par
Tere\u328? der\u253?a, ha\u253?baty\u328?a guwanma,\par
Wagty\u328? \u253?etse, guryp, \u253?er dek bolar sen.\par
\par
Daglary\u328? arslany, babyr, pele\u328?i,\par
Mu\u351? bile de\u328? bolar pil, pe\u351?e je\u328?i,\par
Mejmegul-Bahre\u253?ni\u328?, Nili\u328? n\u228?he\u328?i,\par
Gulagyna urlan har dek bolar sen.\par
\par
Ky\u253?amatdan bir s\u246?z di\u253?dim ba\u253?akda,\par
Garaw bardyr \u253?ersiz urlan ta\u253?akda,\par
Zalymlar hor bolar, galar a\u253?akda,\par
Garyp, sen \u253?yglama, \u351?ir dek bolar sen.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y bedew m\u252?nen, hup mahbup gu\u231?an,\par
Bile eltipmidir baky\u253?a g\u246?\u231?en,\par
Hakykat namartdyr imansyz ge\u231?en,\par
Iman bile barsa\u328?, ner dek bolar sen.\par
\par
Ger\u231?e nesihatdyr illere s\u246?z\u252?\u328?,\par
Il almazdan owwal tutawer \u246?z\u252?\u328?,\par
Alymlara u\u253?sa\u328?, a\u231?ylar g\u246?z\u252?\u328?,\par
Jahyllara u\u253?sa\u328?, k\u246?r dek bolar sen.\par
\par
Lukman kibi dertli dermanyn berse\u328?,\par
R\u252?stem dek d\u246?wleri permana salsa\u328?,\par
Isgender dek \u253?eri\u328? \u253?\u252?z\u252?ni alsa\u328?,\par
\u221?ere \u253?egsan bolsa\u328?, \u253?er dek bolar sen.\par
\par
Magtymguly, garap s\u246?zle da\u351?y\u328?y,\par
Ja\u253?yn bilip sarp et bolsa a\u351?y\u328?y,\par
K\u228?mil tapsa\u328?, go\u253? \u253?olunda ba\u351?y\u328?y,\par
\u196?r ardynda gezse\u328?, \u228?r dek bolar sen.\par
\par
JO\u350?A D\u220?\u350?\u220?P SEN\par
Gel, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l, g\u246?zlegil \u228?lem-jahany,\par
S\u246?\u253?le, ne\u231?\u252?n be\u253?le jo\u351?a d\u252?\u351?\u252?p sen?\par
\u196?lemde seni\u328? dek \u253?okmy dahanly,\par
Syry\u328? dessan e\u253?l\u228?p, pa\u351?a d\u252?\u351?\u252?p sen.\par
\par
S\u246?kseler ne\u253?l\u228?r sen sen namyrada:\par
\u171?Seni\u328? kimin \u253?okmy?\u187? di\u253?ip - d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de,\par
\u221?a \u351?e\u253?le g\u252?\u253?\u231?l\u252?mi y\u351?ky\u328? zy\u253?ada,\par
Hetdi\u328? bilme\u253?, a\u351?a-a\u351?a d\u252?\u351?\u252?p sen.\par
\par
Gadam go\u253?sam, s\u228?hralara, \u231?\u246?llere,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l ga\u253?nar, s\u246?z jo\u351? eder dillere,\par
Iller sa\u328?a ha\u253?ran, sen hem illere,\par
\u221?a akly\u328? aldyryp, \u231?a\u351?a d\u252?\u351?\u252?p sen.\par
\par
Baka \u253?okdur s\u246?hbeti\u328?e, sazy\u328?a,\par
Ygtybar \u253?ok gy\u351? g\u252?n\u252?\u328?e, \u253?azy\u328?a,\par
Sen bu derdi \u253?ok etmese\u328? \u246?z\u252?\u328?e,\par
Ol k\u252?r\u228?, g\u252?daza ne\u253?\u351?e d\u252?\u351?\u252?p sen?\par
\par
Magtymguly, hamu \u253?ola ba\u351? urdu\u328?,\par
\u199?ohlar bilen gezdi\u328?, oturdy\u328?, turdu\u328?,\par
\u221?alan\u231?yda ne hezl etdi\u328?, ne g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?,\par
Imdi sen otuz d\u246?rt \u253?a\u351?a d\u252?\u351?\u252?p sen.\par
\par
\u221?ETER SEN\par
Gelen ge\u231?er, gonan g\u246?\u231?er, adamzat,\par
\u221?\u246?ri, sen hem bir menzile \u253?eter sen.\par
\u221?alan\u231?yda \u253?egdir galsa \u253?ag\u351?y at,\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge gelmi\u351? bolsa\u328?, \u246?ter sen.\par
\par
Gapyl adam \u253?ada salsa asylyn,\par
Pelek go\u253?mu\u351? ajal atly masylyn,\par
Gelen-ge\u231?se, eken-bi\u231?se hasylyn,\par
Orta \u253?erde sen ne i\u351?ler tutar sen.\par
\par
Jepa go\u253?ma, k\u228?\u253?itmegin bu jany\u328?,\par
Seri\u351?desi hi\u231? tutdurmaz jahany\u328?,\par
Terpendik\u231?e, derdi artar d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328?,\par
Gadam go\u253?sa\u328?, g\u246?wr\u228?\u328? birle batar sen.\par
\par
Jo\u351?gun geldi, hetdin \u253?ardy, s\u246?z a\u351?dy,\par
Bu \u253?ollardan dogry baran d\u252?z a\u351?dy,\par
Bihuda imesdir \u246?mr\u252?\u328? g\u252?ze\u351?ti,\par
Her \u231?\u228?\u351?ti\u328?e bir g\u252?n\u252?\u328?i satar sen.\par
\par
Aldamaga al kuma\u351?y\u328?, sim-zeri\u328?,\par
G\u252?zerg\u228?hin tutup durmu\u351? bu \u253?eri\u328?,\par
Germ e\u253?ledi\u328?, pelek, sen bu bazary\u328?,\par
M\u228?limdir ki, bu s\u246?wdada utar sen.\par
\par
Magrur olup bu d\u246?rt g\u252?n\u252?\u328? dirligne,\par
Ebet galma ky\u253?amaty\u328? horlugna,\par
Ynanmagyl bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? barlygna,\par
\u171?Bar, bar\u187? bilen, \u253?ok bolar sen, \u253?iter sen.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ba\u351?y\u328?da \u253?\u252?z k\u246?\u253? bardyr,\par
A\u253?ry menzil, a\u253?ry mekan, ja\u253? bardyr,\par
Lahat atly dar, d\u252?\u351?eksiz \u246?\u253? bardyr,\par
Ol \u246?\u253? i\u231?re t\u228? ky\u253?amat \u253?atar sen.\par
\par
PA\u350? BOLMAR SEN\par
Gel k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m, ge\u328?e\u351? edeli,\par
S\u246?zleme\u253?in pa\u351? bolmar sen!\par
Panydyr bu \u253?alan d\u252?n\u253?\u228?,\par
Bir g\u252?n ondan ho\u351? bolmar sen.\par
\par
Bir g\u252?ldir sen hem ho\u351?lar sen,\par
\u221?ene bir g\u252?n aga\u231?lar sen,\par
Hem da\u351?lar sen, hem di\u351?l\u228?r sen,\par
\u221?ene bizden da\u351? bolmar sen.\par
\par
Haky\u328? emridir, neter sen,\par
Sen bizim \u231?\u252?n bir g\u252?zer sen,\par
Geleni gar\u351?y \u253?uwtar sen,\par
Bir dem bizden bo\u351? bolmar sen.\par
\par
Owwal dost bolup g\u252?ldir sen,\par
Bir az yzy\u328?dan \u253?eldir sen,\par
Bir g\u252?n basalap \u246?ldir sen,\par
Baky garynda\u351? bolmar sen.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bilmi\u351? haly,\par
Sen bu \u253?urtda d\u228?l binaly,\par
Toba di\u253?p, Haka d\u246?neli,\par
Imdiden so\u328? \u253?a\u351? bolmar sen.\par
\par
\u196?DEJEK SEN\par
Adam ogly, \u246?z\u252?\u328? bilme\u253?,\par
Gedem-gedem \u228?dejek sen.\par
E\u253?\u228?ni\u328? emrini kylma\u253?,\par
\u214?z k\u246?\u328?l\u252?\u328?i g\u252?\u253?dejek sen.\par
\par
Ist\u228?r sen, \u228?lemi gapsa\u328?,\par
Karun bolup genje depse\u328?,\par
Halal, haram, her ne tapsa\u328?,\par
G\u246?z\u252?\u328? \u253?umup, \u253?uwdajak sen.\par
\par
Neden oldu\u328?, bilgil bary,\par
Unutdy\u328? Perwerdig\u228?ri,\par
K\u246?\u328?le gelen her ne k\u228?ri\par
Sangy etme\u253? edejek sen.\par
\par
Asly\u328? nedir, etgil nazar,\par
Tutan i\u351?i\u328?den kyl hezer,\par
Ajal sa\u328?a etse g\u252?zer,\par
Habary\u328? ber, n\u228?dejek sen?\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni gyzgyn tutmagyl,\par
I\u351?i\u328? g\u246?r, bik\u228?r \u253?atmagyl,\par
Magtymguly, unutmagyl,\par
Gidejek sen, gidejek sen.\par
\par
\u350?ASY GALANDAR\par
A\u351?yklar \u228?hlini\u328? hany, soltany,\par
Tejelli tagtyny\u328? \u351?asy galandar.\par
Gezerem \u253?ollary \u253?itirip ony,\par
Bilmenem, habar ber, ha\u253?sy, galandar.\par
\par
Men bu \u253?olda \u351?un\u231?a zille bolmu\u351?am,\par
Mande galyp, ejizligim bilmi\u351?em,\par
\u350?iblini, Mejnuny alyp gelmi\u351?em,\par
P\u228?hliwan Pir\u253?ary, We\u253?si, galandar.\par
\par
Habar aldym bagy-bossan, g\u252?l\u252?nden,\par
Re\u328?gi solmu\u351? bady-hazan \u253?elinden,\par
Gerdany ke\u231? gahba \u231?arhy\u328? elinden,\par
Menew\u351?e tutarmy\u351? \u253?asy, galandar.\par
\par
Ho\u351?lugym \u253?ok o\u253?namaga, g\u252?lm\u228?ge,\par
Rakyp go\u253?maz dogrulyban gelm\u228?ge,\par
Bir hylwatda \u253?ar habaryn almaga,\par
Sende bar a\u351?nalyk ysy, galandar.\par
\par
G\u252?ndizi\u328? pikirdir, o\u253?dur ag\u351?amy\u328?,\par
Bu resme ge\u231?irdim, wagtyn e\u253?\u253?amy\u328?,\par
\u221?a, Rep, kerem etse\u328? bize bir jamy\u328?,\par
Gymmatyn a\u253?t, ne bahasy, galandar?\par
\par
S\u246?\u253?se\u328? ol \u253?aradan Kadyr Suhany,\par
Men garyby \u351?at e\u253?legin pynhany,\par
G\u246?terdi \u228?lemi, tutdy jahany\par
A\u351?ygy\u328? nalasy, sesi, galandar.\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, ustuhan seni\u328?,\par
Ten seni\u328?dir, damar seni\u328?, gan seni\u328?,\par
Gymmat \u252?\u231?in akyl seni\u328?, jan seni\u328?,\par
Dodagyma tutgul tasy, galandar.\par
\par
\u350?AL TAPSA\par
E\u253?esine yhlas eden \u231?yn merdan,\par
Ebri\u351?\u252?m h\u246?wesin etmez, \u351?al tapsa.\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? maly, i\u351?i \u252?\u231?in sergerdan,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l guwan\u231? eder artyk mal tapsa.\par
\par
\u221?ol \u253?olda\u351?y \u253?olda\u351?yna s\u246?\u253?ener,\par
Howply \u253?erde \u253?atan tiz-tiz o\u253?anar,\par
Garak\u231?ylar kerwen g\u246?rse guwanar,\par
Ge\u231?it tapma\u253?anlar suwda sal tapsa.\par
\par
Ge\u231?irler her \u253?erde s\u246?z\u252?m takyga,\par
Garry arman \u231?eker \u253?igit \u231?akyga,\par
E\u351?ek monjugna bi\u253?r \u253?a-da akyga,\par
Bi\u231?\u228?re \u231?opanlar \u253?akut-lagl tapsa.\par
\par
Jan howpundan bolar akyly ha\u253?ran,\par
\u221?ylan ki\u351?mir g\u246?rse, \u252?telgi \u8722? ta\u253?ran,\par
\u350?ir sy\u253?agu\u351? g\u246?rse, pil hem kergerdan,\par
Agaja gurt d\u252?\u351?se, gawun hal tapsa.\par
\par
Mertden dileg eden namut \u246?wr\u252?lmez,\par
Namarda d\u252?\u351?en i\u351?, m\u228?lim, ga\u253?rylmaz,\par
Perwana ot g\u246?rse, jan bi\u253?r, a\u253?rylmaz,\par
Simap \u8722? gyzyl tapsa, meges \u8722? bal tapsa.\par
\par
E\u253?, terbi\u253?et ist\u228?n ki\u351?i ten \u252?\u231?in,\par
E\u351?ret dil\u228?n ogul-gyz-u zen \u252?\u231?in,\par
Ak puly saklarlar gara g\u252?n \u252?\u231?in,\par
Ho\u351? gezerler gyzyl, \u253?a\u351?yl, al tapsa.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? k\u246?\u253?ler, k\u246?\u231?eler,\par
A\u253?dadyrlar: \u171?D\u246?wran bizden ge\u231?eler\u187?,\par
Hak-n\u228?hakdan mal gazanyp ni\u231?eler,\par
Sarp edere ja\u253?yn tapmaz mal tapsa.\par
\par
\u350?A\u221?LAMA\u221?YNMY?\par
\u214?mre ygtybar \u253?ok, jana durum \u253?ok,\par
Ahyret esbabyn \u351?a\u253?lama\u253?ynmy?\par
Bende men, barara ga\u253?ry \u253?erim \u253?ok,\par
Istegim \u214?z\u252?nden e\u253?lem\u228?\u253?inmi?\par
\par
\u221?aranlar, \u253?etmek \u253?ok Suhan syryna,\par
A\u231?sa \u253?olum \u8722? \u253?etsem Dost eserine,\par
Ry\u253?azaty \u253?\u252?kl\u228?p nebsim \u351?\u252?t\u252?rne,\par
Yhlasa i\u253?tdirip, ha\u253?lama\u253?ynmy?\par
\par
\u221?okluga \u253?andyryp, menlikden sagyn,\par
E\u351?kimden suwarsam nistligi\u328? bagyn,\par
Ujb, ry\u253?a, kibr, hasat matagyn,\par
B\u246?l\u252?p, rahzenlere pa\u253?lama\u253?ynmy?\par
\par
Aby-towpyk \u253?uwup jesedim nawyn,\par
H\u252?mmet bile \u246?tsem ybadat zawyn,\par
Ruhum gu\u351?un besl\u228?p, nebsimi\u328? awun,\par
Pikir bi\u351?esinden awlama\u253?ynmy?\par
\par
Magtymguly, ne bar i\u231?mek, i\u253?mekden,\par
Jan jesetden gider, et hem s\u252?mekden,\par
G\u246?z g\u246?rmekden galar, dil hem di\u253?mekden,\par
Dilim teprenerk\u228?n, s\u246?\u253?lem\u228?\u253?inmi?\par
\par
SATA\u350?DYM\par
S\u228?her wagty se\u253?ran edip gezerk\u228?m,\par
Ajap menzil, ajap ja\u253?a sata\u351?dym,\par
Ugrum bilme\u253?, \u253?oldan-\u253?ola azarkam,\par
Hup mekana, hup sara\u253?a sata\u351?dym.\par
\par
Ussasyz i\u351?lenen, kir\u351?siz gatylan,\par
Gymmatsyz satylan, elsiz tutulan,\par
Gol degme\u253? \u231?ekilen, oksuz atylan,\par
\u199?illesiz gurulan \u253?a\u253?a sata\u351?dym.\par
\par
Ni\u231?e dostlar bilen se\u253?randa eken,\par
Hatardan aza\u351?dym, kerwende eken,\par
Jandan umyt \u252?z\u252?p, ha\u253?randa eken,\par
\u221?yldyzdan \u253?ol umdum, A\u253?a sata\u351?dym.\par
\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?m gitdi dostlar i\u231?en \u351?erbetde,\par
Olar \u253?\u252?z sapada, men m\u252?\u328? hasratda,\par
A\u253?rylyp, nalada, galdym gurbatda,\par
\u199?e\u351?meden suw isl\u228?p, \u231?a\u253?a sata\u351?dym.\par
\par
Ne tende kuwwat bar, ne i\u231?de jan bar,\par
Bu i\u351?de ne sud bar, bilmen, zy\u253?an bar,\par
Ne hasap, ne hesip, ne belli san bar,\par
Ki\u351?i bilmez, ne s\u246?wda\u253?a sata\u351?dym.\par
\par
Ba\u351?a baglap diwanalyk kemendin,\par
Segredip \u253?eti\u351?dim y\u351?ka semendim,\par
Al \u351?eraba el uzatdym, emendim,\par
Durusyn i\u231?mi\u351?ler, la\u253?a sata\u351?dym.\par
\par
Magtymguly di\u253?rler meni\u328? adymy,\par
\u196?lem elin \u231?o\u253?ar g\u246?rse odumy,\par
E\u253? \u253?aranlar, kime di\u253?em dadymy,\par
Ba\u351?ym \u231?ykmaz ne s\u246?wda\u253?a sata\u351?dym.\par
\par
SALAR GU\u350?UN A\u327?LAMAZ\par
Bedasyla beglik \u253?etse bir g\u252?nde,\par
Alar awun, salar gu\u351?un a\u328?lamaz,\par
\u221?arlygy \u253?\u246?rigen nurbatsyz begler,\par
Pukarany\u328? g\u246?zde \u253?a\u351?yn a\u328?lamaz.\par
\par
Belet ba\u351?lar dogry \u253?ola \u231?yn bile,\par
Akyl \u253?igit s\u246?z ba\u351?lamaz \u171?men\u187? bile,\par
Namart oldur - ge\u328?e\u351? e\u253?l\u228?r zen bile,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igitler zen ge\u328?e\u351?in a\u328?lamaz.\par
\par
Mertden dileg etse\u328? a\u253?dar: \u171?Hup bolar\u187?,\par
Bir bag\u351?a\u351?dan \u253?etmi\u351? bela dep bolar,\par
Muhannes ge\u328?e\u351?i \u246?\u253?de k\u246?p bolar,\par
Du\u351?man g\u246?rse, tutar i\u351?in a\u328?lamaz.\par
\par
Hak \u253?olunda her kim ha\u253?r-yhsan kylar,\par
Ky\u253?amat g\u252?n bir \u253?erine on geler,\par
Namart du\u351?man g\u246?rse, gussadan \u246?ler,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igitler d\u246?rd\u252?n, b\u228?\u351?in a\u328?lamaz.\par
\par
Magtymguly, beg \u253?anynda dil ba\u351?lar,\par
Gylyjy, ga\u253?raty bolan il ba\u351?lar,\par
Mertden dogan \u253?ygyn g\u246?rse, \u253?ol ba\u351?lar,\par
Namart ogly de\u328?in-du\u351?un a\u328?lamaz.\par
\par
S\u214?ZI GE\u199?ER JANY\u327?DAN\par
De\u328?siz bile de\u328? e\u253?lese\u328? \u246?z\u252?\u328?i,\par
Dert boluban, s\u246?zi ge\u231?er jany\u328?dan.\par
Yrak bolma gadry\u328? bilen garda\u351?dan,\par
Her i\u351? tutsa\u328?, ol guwanar \u253?any\u328?dan.\par
\par
Gahra m\u252?n\u252?p, galdyrmagyn \u351?e\u253?tany,\par
Nebse u\u253?up, unutmagyn Rahmany,\par
Kesse akly\u328? \u253?ag\u351?y bilen \u253?amany,\par
Her bir s\u246?ze dolup-da\u351?ma gany\u328?dan.\par
\par
Sabry\u328? bolsa, Suhan \u253?eter dady\u328?a,\par
Je\u328?\u328?i-jedel la\u253?yk d\u228?ldir ady\u328?a,\par
Alma \u253?aman s\u246?zi hergiz \u253?ady\u328?a,\par
Tiken bolup d\u252?rt\u252?p ge\u231?er donu\u328?dan.\par
\par
Bar\u231?a bolan i\u351?ler Haky\u328? i\u351?idir,\par
O\u328?a ten berme\u253?en - akmak ki\u351?idir,\par
Bir \u253?aman s\u246?z jana \u253?ylan di\u351?idir,\par
Soksa, z\u228?hri asan \u231?ykmaz ini\u328?den.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?alan\u231?ydyr bu jahan,\par
Mesde akyl bolmaz, g\u228?w\u252?rde \u8722? iman,\par
Ja\u253?yn tapsa, garynja de\u253? pes du\u351?man,\par
Arslan bolup, el g\u246?termez \u351?any\u328?dan.\par
\par
S\u214?HBET \u221?AG\u350?YDYR\par
Adam bolsa\u328?, gulak go\u253?gul \u246?w\u252?de,\par
Alymlar \u253?anynda s\u246?hbet \u253?ag\u351?ydyr.\par
Atarman-\u231?aparman algyr \u253?igide,\par
\u221?eri gelse aman-nurbat \u253?ag\u351?ydyr.\par
\par
Hemra bolup oturmagyl pis bile,\par
Poha degse\u328?, be\u253?ni\u328? dolar ys bile,\par
G\u246?wher da\u351?yn \u253?\u252?z\u252?k etse\u328? mis bile,\par
Gymmaty egsilmez, hormat \u253?ag\u351?ydyr.\par
\par
Zynhar, kast etmegil i\u253?digi\u328? nana,\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?\u328? ha\u253?ra bagla, sydky\u328? - imana,\par
Hi\u231? azar bermegil bir musulmana,\par
Ogry \u228?rden, bir dogry it \u253?ag\u351?ydyr.\par
\par
K\u228?\u351?ki adam bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge gelmese,\par
Gelenden so\u328? \u246?m\u252?r s\u252?rse - \u246?lmese,\par
Elden gelen \u253?ag\u351?y i\u351?i\u328? bolmasa,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l i\u231?re \u253?ag\u351?y ni\u253?et \u253?ag\u351?ydyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ni\u231?ik ge\u231?se rozyg\u228?r,\par
Haka \u351?\u252?kr et, barma namarda zynhar,\par
\u221?ok d\u246?wletden \u253?egdir, bolsa bir h\u252?n\u228?r,\par
M\u252?\u328? h\u252?n\u228?rden zerre d\u246?wlet \u253?ag\u351?ydyr.\par
\par
SIR GIDER\par
K\u246?p namarda mal berip sen, dun d\u252?n\u253?\u228?,\par
G\u246?zi g\u246?kde, ga\u253?gysy \u253?ok, sir gider.\par
Hany akly\u328?, oda d\u252?\u351?\u252?p \u253?an, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?,\par
Ne mertler bar, \u253?oksullykda hor gider.\par
\par
Az \u246?mr\u252?\u328?i s\u252?rse\u328? elwan a\u351?ratda,\par
So\u328? \u351?irin jan galar uzyn hasratda,\par
Akmaklar bu \u253?erde galar gaflatda,\par
Akyl bolan \u246?z gamyny i\u253?r gider.\par
\par
Ne dogry gelene m\u228?hri\u328? inderdi\u328?,\par
Ne gelm\u228?ne sowgat-salam g\u246?nderdi\u328?,\par
Hi\u231? parhy \u253?ok sende merdi\u328?, namardy\u328?,\par
Arslan \u246?ter, tilki ge\u231?er, \u351?ir gider.\par
\par
Pe\u253?da dil\u228?p gelen d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u351?\u228?hrinden,\par
Janyn berip, guryp galdy gahryndan,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? mardyr, ol \u253?ylany\u328? z\u228?hrinden,\par
T\u252?\u253? d\u246?k\u252?ler, ganat gyrlar, per gider.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? zendir, k\u246?p o\u253?na\u351?ly, \u228?ri bir,\par
Bir \u246?p\u252?\u351?de eti\u328?, gany\u328? sorubi\u253?r,\par
\u214?lenden so\u328?, \u351?ah-u geda bary bir,\par
Munda her kim boldujagyn go\u253?r gider.\par
\par
Adam ogly \u253?alan\u231?yny\u328? \u253?alanyn,\par
\u199?yn sanypdyr egri bakyp g\u252?lenin,\par
Gam \u231?ekme, e\u253? d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, her kim alanyn -\par
Karz maly\u328?dyr, \u253?ene ga\u253?dyp bi\u253?r gider.\par
\par
Magtymguly, g\u252?\u253?\u231?li bile dala\u351?ma\u328?,\par
Ha\u253?ry go\u253?up, \u351?er i\u351?lere ula\u351?ma\u328?,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman s\u246?z\u252?m k\u246?pd\u252?r, galy\u351?ma\u328?,\par
Ne\u231?\u252?n, her kim bildijegin di\u253?r gider.\par
\par
SALY, D\u220?N\u221?\u196?, HE\u221?\par
Suw \u253?\u252?z\u252?nde gezen ni\u231?e g\u228?mini,\par
Bir g\u252?n agdarar sen, saly, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, he\u253?.\par
Adam ogly barmaz bolsa yzy\u328?dan,\par
Munda di\u253?p aldar sen maly, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, he\u253?.\par
\par
Bilermi sen, ha\u231?an t\u252?kener demi\u328?,\par
Gabyr bolar bir g\u252?n basan gadamy\u328?,\par
D\u246?wran gerdi\u351?inde gapyl adamy\u328?,\par
\u220?st\u252?nden salar sen \u253?oly, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, he\u253?.\par
\par
Aramy\u328? \u253?ok, karary\u328? \u253?ok, dynmaz sen,\par
Gije-g\u252?ndiz gan i\u231?er sen, ganmaz sen,\par
Ahyr ne bela\u328? bar, so\u328?un sanmaz sen,\par
Aklyny aldyran d\u228?li, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, he\u253?.\par
\par
Habarsyz geler sen, \u253?aka tutar sen,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y e\u253?l\u228?p, \u253?aman e\u253?l\u228?p \u246?ter sen,\par
Bir g\u252?n a\u351?ymyza awy gatar sen,\par
Owwal aldap bi\u253?r sen baly, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, he\u253?.\par
\par
A\u253?lanar, gy\u351? ge\u231?er, \u253?az, tomus, g\u252?\u253?z hem,\par
Onu\u328?-le \u253?ag\u351?ydyr, dag, de\u328?iz, d\u252?z hem,\par
Ahyry \u246?termiz \u252?st\u252?\u328?den biz hem,\par
Gugaryp galar sen, haly, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, he\u253?.\par
\par
K\u246?pleri \u253?ok etdi\u328?, k\u228?ni \u253?uwutdy\u328?,\par
Muhammet - Hak resul jany \u253?uwutdy\u328?,\par
Harun, Karun, S\u252?le\u253?many \u253?uwutdy\u328?,\par
Budur seni\u328? i\u351?i\u328?, beli, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, he\u253?.\par
\par
Adam oglun saldy\u328? t\u252?kenmez gama,\par
\u221?a\u351?-garry - \u253?olu\u328?da sergezdan heme,\par
Bir mada e\u351?ek sen gelip sen deme,\par
Gasygy gam bilen doly, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, he\u253?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, d\u252?n\u253?\u228? syryn du\u253?maz sen,\par
Bu g\u252?n g\u246?rd\u252?gimiz ert\u228? go\u253?maz sen.\par
Ni\u231?e wagtdan b\u228?ri i\u253?er, do\u253?maz sen,\par
\u221?ykylgyn, \u253?umrulgyn, loly d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, he\u253?.\par
\par
SIL GALMAZ\par
Altmy\u351? ba\u351?ly, ala garly daglardan,\par
Duman g\u246?\u231?er, \u253?agmyr ge\u231?er, sil galmaz.\par
\u350?e\u253?da bilbil mesgen tutan baglardan,\par
Hazan urar, \u253?aprak ga\u231?ar, g\u252?l galmaz.\par
\par
Her kim i\u231?se ol \u351?erapdan, ol jamdan,\par
\u221?\u252?rek jo\u351?ar, her s\u246?z geler zybandan,\par
Gelen ge\u231?er bu \u253?alan\u231?y jahandan,\par
Hoja, se\u253?it, beg, paty\u351?a, gul galmaz.\par
\par
Jana degse garrylygy\u328? z\u228?heri,\par
Bozuk bolar k\u246?\u328?\u252?l-g\u246?wre \u351?\u228?heri,\par
Elden gitse \u253?igitligi\u328? bahary,\par
Kuwwat ga\u231?ar, dyz egiler, bil galmaz.\par
\par
Bir namardy\u328? k\u246?p minnetli a\u351?yndan,\par
El uzatma, \u246?wr\u252?lewer da\u351?yndan,\par
Ilsiz galan belent daglar ba\u351?yndan,\par
Aga\u231? biter, jadde \u253?iter, \u253?ol galmaz.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu jahanda kim bolar,\par
Ol mekana giden gelmez, g\u252?m bolar,\par
G\u246?rer g\u246?z\u252?\u328?, g\u246?rkli g\u246?wr\u228?\u328? gum bolar,\par
Dahan gider, dendan d\u252?\u351?er, dil galmaz.\par
\par
PARA-PARADYR\par
\u221?aranlar, gerdi\u351?i-\u231?arhy\u328? elinden,\par
Bu meni\u328? \u253?\u252?regim para-paradyr.\par
Syzzylda\u351?ar tenim E\u253?\u253?up teni dek,\par
Ki\u351?i bilmez, bir agyzsyz \u253?aradyr.\par
\par
Gije-g\u252?ndiz i\u351?im-g\u252?\u253?j\u252?mdir ha\u253?-wa\u253?,\par
Telmuryp \u253?yglar men g\u246?zlenip her ta\u253?,\par
U\u231?ra\u351?yp k\u246?l\u252?ge: \u171?Gark oldum - di\u253?r - Ha\u253?,\par
\u196?rler-pirler, sizden medet-hara\u253?dyr\u187?.\par
\par
Garyp eger garyp \u253?erde \u253?\u246?rijek,\par
G\u246?zlerinden ganly \u253?a\u351?lar \u253?\u246?rijek,\par
A\u351?yk eger mag\u351?ugyny g\u246?rijek,\par
G\u252?l-g\u252?li a\u231?ylar, k\u246?\u328?li para\u253?dyr.\par
\par
Tohum sal, orar sen, geldi\u328? bu ja\u253?a,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328?i ge\u231?irme bihuda-za\u253?a,\par
Nazar e\u253?l\u228?r sizler u\u351?bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?\u253?e,\par
Gelen ge\u231?er, durmaz, k\u246?ne sara\u253?dyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly kylmy\u351? jigerin bir\u253?an,\par
\u221?\u252?rege gan dolmu\u351?, bu \u231?e\u351?mi-gir\u253?an,\par
\u350?e\u253?le ejiz galmy\u351?, \u253?albaryp her \u253?an,\par
Rehm eden bolmady, bagtym garadyr.\par
\par
PYGAN EGLENMEZ\par
Bilbil h\u252?j\u252?m e\u253?l\u228?n howaly baglar,\par
Bilbil senden gider, pygan eglenmez.\par
\u221?agy\u351?ly, \u253?agmyrly, \u252?m\u252?rli daglar,\par
Siller senden gider, duman eglenmez.\par
\par
Adam \u253?aradylmy\u351? belentli, pesli,\par
Akylly-pikirli, d\u228?lili, usly,\par
\u221?igitlik bir g\u246?\u253?\u228? bahary\u328? pasly,\par
Bahar senden gider, zaman eglenmez.\par
\par
Gelene gar\u351?y \u231?yk, bolsa mejaly\u328?,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y tutawergil ni\u253?eti\u328?-p\u228?li\u328?,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? d\u246?wranynda a\u231?yk tut eli\u328?,\par
D\u246?w\u252?r senden gider, d\u246?wran eglenmez.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? gowgadyr, bir galmagaldyr,\par
Kimi ber-h\u228?-berdir, kim al-ha-aldyr,\par
\u221?igitler, bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u351?u\u328?a mysaldyr,\par
Bark urar asmanda, baran eglenmez.\par
\par
Bir menzildir, \u252?\u231? g\u252?n i\u253?ip-i\u231?enso\u328?,\par
Orna\u351?yp, gi\u328?renip, bili\u328? a\u231?anso\u328?,\par
\u220?ze\u328?\u328?i\u328? \u231?ekerler d\u246?rt g\u252?n ge\u231?enso\u328?,\par
B\u228?\u351? g\u252?nden \u253?okary myhman eglenmez.\par
\par
Go\u253?nun a\u231?ar bir g\u252?n, \u253?er seni gizl\u228?r,\par
Gara gumdan dolar bu n\u228?zik g\u246?zler,\par
Ady\u328?a bu\u253?sanma, \u231?emenli d\u252?zler,\par
\u199?emen senden gider, se\u253?ran eglenmez.\par
\par
Magtymguly, a\u253?dar aryp dostuna,\par
Kim galar d\u252?\u351?me\u253?en ajal destine,\par
Pelek bir g\u252?n salar \u253?eri\u328? astyna,\par
Agyz dilden galar, zyban eglenmez.\par
\par
P\u196?LI BEND\u196?NI\u327?\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, haram i\u351?e ula\u351?maz,\par
Eger d\u252?r\u252?st bolsa p\u228?li bend\u228?ni\u328?.\par
Harama ula\u351?maz, pise bula\u351?maz,\par
Haka dogry bolsa \u253?oly bend\u228?ni\u328?.\par
\par
T\u228?ze \u246?mr\u252?\u328? solar ajal badyndan,\par
Ahyr nogsan geler d\u252?n\u253?\u228? sudundan,\par
Bo\u253?ny azat bola tamug odundan,\par
Haky \u253?at e\u253?lese dili bend\u228?ni\u328?.\par
\par
Gabry\u328?a salmazlar d\u252?n\u253?\u228? malyndan,\par
\u221?\u252?zi garar, jogap gelmez dilinden,\par
Ky\u253?amat g\u252?n \u351?ikat eder elinden,\par
Zekatsyz \u253?ygylan maly bend\u228?ni\u328?.\par
\par
Nebs hy\u253?alda, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l d\u252?n\u253?\u228? k\u252?\u253?\u252?nde,\par
\u221?ol yrakdyr, agyr \u253?\u252?k hem bo\u253?unda,\par
A\u253?agy talapda, eli o\u253?unda,\par
Ajal agzyndadyr bili bend\u228?ni\u328?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, her kim i\u351?in sap etmez,\par
M\u228?limdir ki ahyretden howp etmez,\par
Eziz teni \u246?tg\u252?r oda tap etmez,\par
\u221?a, Rep, ni\u231?ik bolga\u253? haly bend\u228?ni\u328?.\par
\par
\u221?ETI\u350?SE\par
E\u253?, Huda\u253?-a, bize bir towpyk berse\u328?,\par
Synamyza y\u351?kdan bir dag \u253?eti\u351?se.\par
Sydk ilen dillerme toba iberse\u328?,\par
S\u228?her didelerim o\u253?ag \u253?eti\u351?se.\par
\par
S\u228?her turup y\u351?ky\u328? kitabyn a\u231?sam,\par
Okap-okap, d\u252?rri-manylar sa\u231?sam,\par
Kyrklar-le jem bolup, py\u253?ala i\u231?sem,\par
K\u252?nji me\u253?hanada a\u253?ag \u253?eti\u351?se.\par
\par
Bir m\u252?r\u351?it etegin tutsam, aglasam,\par
Y\u351?k oduna jany-jismim daglasam,\par
Sydky-dilden Haka k\u246?\u328?\u252?l baglasam,\par
Ky\u253?amat za\u253?yrdan bir sag \u253?eti\u351?se.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylar yzynda \u253?\u246?rsem dowamat,\par
Parz-u wajyp, terk etmesem hem s\u252?nnet,\par
Erenler \u253?olunda tartyp mu\u351?akgat,\par
\u171?\u350?ypa ber, Resul!\u187? di\u253?p, sedag \u253?eti\u351?se.\par
\par
Ylmy-kal, ylmy-hal baryn jem etsem,\par
\u350?erigat \u253?olunda da\u253?ym g\u246?z etsem,\par
Nebsi-\u351?e\u253?tan - d\u252?n\u253?\u228? hyrsyn terk etsem,\par
\u350?eraban tehuran bulag \u253?eti\u351?se.\par
\par
Ni\u231?e \u253?yllar \u253?\u246?rd\u252?m ha\u253?-u h\u246?wesde,\par
Bar\u231?a kylan i\u351?im boldy ebesde,\par
Gark olup d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge, galdym kapasda,\par
Toty kimin terki-duzag \u253?eti\u351?se.\par
\par
Kadyr E\u253?\u228?m bu gamlardan gutaryp,\par
Hatarlyk ja\u253?lardan aman \u246?t\u252?rip,\par
Pazly bilen bar\u231?a i\u351?im bitirip,\par
H\u252?\u253?r-u gulman i\u231?re pyrag \u253?eti\u351?se.\par
\par
Ysrapyl sur urup, halklar dirilse,\par
\u196?hli \u228?lem arasata s\u252?r\u252?lse,\par
\u350?epagathah Resul m\u252?n\u228?di kylsa,\par
Magtymguly di\u253?ip sorag \u253?eti\u351?se.\par
\par
N\u196?ME SEN?\par
Asla Seni g\u246?rmemi\u351?em, dildarym.\par
Gumrumy Sen, bilbilmi Sen, n\u228?me Sen?\par
Gamgyn k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m hy\u253?aly\u328?da aldaram,\par
Bag i\u231?inde g\u252?lg\u252?lmi Sen, n\u228?me Sen?\par
\par
Gara\u231?ymy\u328?, \u253?a se\u253?itmi\u328?, hojamy\u328?,\par
\u221?a sakymy\u328?, \u253?a \u351?erapmy\u328?, \u253?a jammy\u328?,\par
\u221?a \u253?ylmy Sen, \u253?a g\u252?ndizmi\u328?, gijemi\u328?,\par
\u221?a A\u253?my Sen, \u253?a G\u252?nmi Sen, n\u228?me Sen?\par
\par
\u221?a m\u252?\u351?kmi Sen, \u253?a kokunar anbarmy\u328?,\par
A\u253?da bilmen, \u253?a \u231?arhmy Sen, \u231?enbermi\u328?,\par
\u221?a der\u253?amy\u328?, \u253?a m\u246?w\u231?mi Sen, lenbermi\u328?,\par
\u221?a girdapmy\u328?, \u253?a burgunmy\u328?, n\u228?me Sen?\par
\par
Altynmy Sen, k\u252?m\u252?\u351?mi Sen, zermi Sen,\par
\u221?a Ar\u351?my Sen, \u253?a K\u252?rsmi Sen, \u221?ermi Sen,\par
\u221?a \u253?akutmy\u328?, \u253?a merjenmi\u328?, d\u252?rmi Sen,\par
\u221?a \u231?yragmy\u328?, \u253?a r\u246?w\u351?enmi\u328?, n\u228?me Sen?\par
\par
Magtymguly, ge\u231? namysdan, ary\u328?dan,\par
El g\u246?tergil bu wepasyz k\u228?ri\u328?den,\par
Jahan doly, sen gapyl sen \u253?ary\u328?dan,\par
Me\u253?-mestmi sen, \u253?a \u351?e\u253?damy\u328?, n\u228?me sen?\par
\par
\u199?YKARDYM \u199?ENDEN\par
Jelil-e\u253?, Jepbar-e\u253?, \u214?z\u252?\u328? biler Sen,\par
Jahan i\u231?re j\u252?rm\u252?m \u231?ykardym \u231?enden.\par
Bende men, ne kylsa\u328?, \u214?z\u252?\u328? kylar Sen,\par
G\u252?n\u228?him g\u252?\u253?\u231? alyp, basdy g\u252?n-g\u252?nden.\par
\par
Derg\u228?hi\u328?den derman dilene\u253? ni\u231?e,\par
Uzyn \u246?mr\u252?m sag\u253?yn sarp etdim hije,\par
\u221?\u252?k agyr, \u253?ol yrak, gara\u328?ky gije,\par
Jan hem j\u246?wlan urar \u231?ykmaga tenden.\par
\par
Rah r\u246?wd\u252?m, mande bolup oturdym,\par
Keremi\u328?e sygnyp, pena getirdim,\par
\u221?olda\u351?ym \u253?ok etdim, \u253?olum \u253?itirdim,\par
Nebs ynsapdan etdi, \u351?um \u351?e\u253?tan \u8722? dinden.\par
\par
Hasylym us\u253?andyr gendeligimden,\par
\u214?l\u252?m asan erer zindeligimden,\par
Hyjalata galdym bendeligimden,\par
Sa\u328?a la\u253?yk amal gelmedi menden.\par
\par
Hasrat bile ge\u231?dim, ha\u253?randa galdym,\par
Derg\u228?hi\u328? daldadyr, sygynyp geldim,\par
Nebs ile \u351?e\u253?tany\u328? pa\u253?maly boldum,\par
E\u253?\u228?m, Sen lutp edip, gutargyl ondan.\par
\par
Yhlasym ary kyl, \u253?alanym \u253?ok et,\par
Tilimi deraz kyl, \u253?\u252?z\u252?mi ak et,\par
Hatardan hyfz e\u253?le, haramdan p\u228?k et,\par
Towpygy\u328? \u253?ar e\u253?l\u228?p, toba ber \u231?yndan.\par
\par
Magtymguly, a\u351?nalyk ber y\u351?k ile,\par
Synama - syr bile, \u231?e\u351?me - e\u351?k ile,\par
Agmalym a\u328?lasam, galdym m\u252?\u351?gile,\par
\u221?erim \u253?ok a\u253?rylyp barara Senden.\par
\par
MAL \u221?AG\u350?Y\par
Adam gadryn bilm\u228?n \u253?\u246?ren adamdan,\par
Ondan \u253?ene otlap \u253?\u246?ren mal \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
S\u246?z manysyn bilm\u228?n s\u246?zl\u228?n adamdan,\par
Ondan \u253?ene s\u246?zleme\u253?en lal \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Huda\u253?ym saklasyn \u351?erden, gahardan,\par
Minnetli a\u351? ajy bolar z\u228?herden,\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, bir bazarsyz \u351?\u228?herden,\par
Ondan ki bir g\u252?wl\u228?p \u253?atan \u231?\u246?l \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Her kimi\u328? \u246?z\u252?ne M\u252?s\u252?rdir ja\u253?y,\par
\u221?adyndan \u231?ykma\u253?yr ba\u253?ramy-to\u253?y,\par
Jan saglygy\u328? bolmaz hi\u231? de\u328?i-ta\u253?y,\par
Ag\u351?am \u253?atyp, ertir \u351?\u252?kr\u252?n kyl \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Bihuda k\u246?p \u253?ara g\u252?l\u252?p s\u246?zleme,\par
Y\u351?k oduna \u253?\u252?rek-bagry\u328? duzlama,\par
M\u228?rek\u228? barganda bija\u253? s\u246?zleme,\par
S\u246?z s\u246?zlese\u328? s\u246?z ja\u253?yna sal \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? di\u253?geni\u328? k\u246?ne sara\u253?dyr,\par
Owwaly to\u253?-ba\u253?ram, ahyry wa\u253?dyr,\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de hemme b\u228?\u351? g\u252?n myhmandyr,\par
Bir-biregi\u328? gadryn \u253?ene bil \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Bir biwepa \u253?ara g\u252?l\u252?p bakandan,\par
\u350?irin jany y\u351?k oduna \u253?akandan,\par
\u221?at illerde mysapyrlyk \u231?ekenden,\par
Ursa, s\u246?kse, horlasa-da il \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?zlegil sen her bapdan,\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228? tutdurmaz, \u231?\u252?\u253?r\u252?kdir d\u252?\u253?pden.\par
A\u328?yrsy gelme\u253?en gury, bat gepden -\par
Ondan ki bir \u351?uwlap \u246?ten \u253?el \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
PA\u350? EDER SENI\par
I\u231?ki syry\u328? a\u253?tma her bir namarda,\par
Syry\u328? ile \u253?a\u253?yp, pa\u351? eder seni.\par
Ogry-kezzap bilen obada\u351? bolma,\par
Maly\u328?dan a\u253?yryp, a\u231? eder seni.\par
\par
Sam-sam adam bilen oturma, turma,\par
Zynhar, namart bilen sen s\u246?hbet gurma,\par
Gadyrdan dostu\u328?dan \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328? \u246?w\u252?rme,\par
Barsa\u328?, depesine t\u228?\u231? eder seni.\par
\par
Bir go\u231? \u253?igit n\u228?zenine \u253?ar bolsa,\par
Jemalyny bir g\u246?rm\u228?ge zar bolsa,\par
Aralykda bir \u351?um rakyp bar bolsa,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y dostu\u328? bilen \u246?\u231? eder seni.\par
\par
Sopular \u253?a\u328?ylyp a\u253?tmaz senany,\par
S\u228?her tursa\u328?, ge\u231?ge\u253? bar\u231?a g\u252?n\u228?ni,\par
A\u253?tmawer gybat s\u246?z, etme zynany,\par
Dowzahy\u328? oduna du\u351? eder seni.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ile \u253?a\u253?dy\u328? nesihat,\par
Zynhar, \u253?aman bilen bolmagyn \u252?lpet,\par
Huda berse sagadatly bir perzent,\par
Garrygan \u231?agy\u328?da \u253?a\u351? eder seni.\par
\par
\u221?EK\u196?NI\u327?\par
Agalar, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? pe\u253?any bolmaz,\par
I\u351? ba\u351?a d\u252?\u351?ende, dogany gelmez.\par
M\u228?rekede o\u253?nap, hi\u231? g\u246?wni galmaz,\par
Arman bilen ge\u231?er saly \u253?ek\u228?ni\u328?.\par
\par
Bir \u253?eke \u253?igidi\u328? bilinmez i\u351?i,\par
Elinde mal bolmaz, g\u246?wn\u252?nde ho\u351?y,\par
\u221?assyk \u231?ekip \u253?atsa - agyrsa ba\u351?y,\par
G\u246?z\u252?nde ganly \u253?a\u351? doly \u253?ek\u228?ni\u328?.\par
\par
\u221?eke-\u253?etim ga\u253?gy-gamdan gutulmaz,\par
Me\u253?lisler gurulsa, ady tutulmaz,\par
Onu\u328? \u252?\u231?in hi\u231? alada edilmez,\par
Ga\u253?gydyr-k\u252?lpetdir haly \u253?ek\u228?ni\u328?.\par
\par
Barly \u246?lse, uly ile \u253?a\u253?randyr,\par
Garyp \u246?lse, onu\u328? yzy we\u253?randyr,\par
Bu i\u351?lere akyl-hu\u351?u\u328? ha\u253?randyr,\par
G\u246?m\u252?lipdir \u351?e\u253?le \u253?oly \u253?ek\u228?ni\u328?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?alan-\u253?a\u351?ryk s\u246?zleme,\par
Nogsany\u328? i\u231?inden ha\u253?yr g\u246?zleme,\par
Egisgin derdi\u328?i di\u253?gin, gizleme,\par
Il-ulusdyr dosty-\u253?ary \u253?ek\u228?ni\u328?.\par
\par
\u221?A\u221?LAHLARY BAR\par
Sapar edip barsak Now\u351?ah m\u252?lk\u252?ne,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l isl\u228?ni dek \u253?a\u253?lahlary bar.\par
Se\u253?ran etsek gun\u231?asyna, g\u252?l\u252?ne,\par
Bakjasynda bilbil o\u253?nahlary bar.\par
\par
\u221?eri sazdyr, hassa bolan sagalar,\par
Arryk, m\u252?flis, garyp bolan o\u328?alar,\par
Ser\u231?emen agajy bile de\u328?eler,\par
Ajap gu\u351? salmaly awlahlary bar.\par
\par
Me\u253?dany doludyr \u351?eker gamy\u351?dan,\par
Dileg etmez hergiz garda\u351? garda\u351?dan,\par
\u220?sti \u253?apyglydyr k\u252?m\u252?\u351? kerpi\u231?den,\par
Her kimi\u328? \u246?zi \u231?\u252?n suwlahlary bar.\par
\par
Ba\u351? go\u351?mandyr arryk, agsak \u351?a bile,\par
Atdyryp dogan-le, baz-le gapyla,\par
\u350?irwan galasydyr, ony kim bile,\par
Her bur\u231?unda altyn ba\u253?dahlary bar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, sazdyr, s\u246?hbetdir i\u351?i\u328?\par
Ajaldan, ga\u253?rydan bolmaz te\u351?w\u252?\u351?i\u328?,\par
Ba\u253?lary\u328?, pakyry\u328?, \u228?hli derw\u252?\u351?i\u328?\par
\u221?urdy bolar \u253?aly parsahlary bar.\par
\par
\u221?AT BOLAR\par
Muhammet ymmaty malsyz bolmasyn,\par
Malsyz bolsa, dogan-garda\u351? \u253?at bolar.\par
Ga\u231?ar aga\u328?, ini\u328? bolmaz hatyra\u328?,\par
Guwanar du\u351?many\u328?, dostu\u328? mat bolar.\par
\par
Garyp a\u253?ak \u253?ala\u328?, kendir gu\u351?akdyr,\par
Bir m\u228?rek\u228? barsa, orny a\u351?akdyr,\par
Garyplar at m\u252?n\u252?p, depse - e\u351?ekdir,\par
D\u246?wletliler e\u351?ek m\u252?nse, at bolar.\par
\par
Bir dileg dilese\u328?, m\u246?h\u252?mi\u328? bitmez,\par
Dostu\u328? yhlas bilen m\u252?rewwet etmez,\par
M\u228?rekede a\u253?dan s\u246?z\u252?\u328? ja\u253? tutmaz,\par
Di\u328?lemezler, a\u253?dan, s\u246?z\u252?\u328? bat bolar.\par
\par
G\u246?re\u351? bir abra\u253?dyr, uru\u351? bir destdir,\par
Ki\u351?ini kemsiden - \u246?zi n\u228?kesdir,\par
Bir m\u246?mine gybat etmek hebesdir,\par
Gybatke\u351?i\u328? gazanany ot bolar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u351?\u252?kr e\u253?legil Hudaga,\par
\u214?l\u252?m barabardyr \u351?ah-u gedaga,\par
Bisabyr gul tiz \u253?olugar belaga,\par
Sabyrly gul dura-bara \u351?at bolar.\par
\par
\u221?ARA\u350?MAZ\par
Ho\u351? t\u228?mizli beg ogluny\u328? n\u228?\u351?tesin,\par
Sygyr \u253?atagynda kylmak \u253?ara\u351?maz.\par
Go\u351?un serenjamyn, il seri\u351?desin,\par
Padyman ogluna bilmek \u253?ara\u351?maz.\par
\par
Eger habar alsa\u328? gepi\u328? te\u253?inden,\par
Di\u328?lese\u328? di\u253?e\u253?in janym \u246?\u253?\u252?nden,\par
Aryplar \u253?anynda d\u252?n\u253?\u228? pe\u253?inden,\par
Awaralyk e\u253?l\u228?p bilmek \u253?ara\u351?maz.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?ydan \u253?aman i\u351? \u231?yksa bolar ge\u328?,\par
Akly, g\u246?rki Alla ga\u253?yrmamy\u351? de\u328?,\par
Tow\u351?an der\u253?a d\u246?zmez, \u351?or suwa \u8722? har\u231?e\u328?,\par
Humsu\u328? \u252?lkesine d\u252?lmek \u253?ara\u351?maz.\par
\par
Her s\u246?z\u252?m bir d\u252?rd\u252?r gadryn bilene,\par
Doga etmek delalatdyr \u246?lene,\par
U\u231?arda, ga\u231?arda - garga, gulana,\par
\u221?edi \u253?\u252?z \u253?a\u351?aman \u246?lmek \u253?ara\u351?maz.\par
\par
Her kimi\u328? ne mukdar bolsa yhlasy,\par
Ol mukdar a\u231?ykdyr Haky\u328? dergahy,\par
Bir \u253?erde jem bolsa jahan der\u253?asy\par
G\u252?m-g\u252?m\u252?\u328? rigine dolmak \u253?ara\u351?maz.\par
\par
Her kime el bermez d\u252?rri-galtany,\par
A\u351? barka dost gazan, at bar - \u253?ol tany,\par
Rumu\u328? tagtyna \u8722? Hebe\u351? soltany,\par
K\u228?be metjidine galmyk \u253?ara\u351?maz.\par
\par
Magtymguly, k\u246?\u253?di bagrym ot bolup,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? gelen gidejekdir mat bolup,\par
\u214?z\u252?n bilme\u253?, o\u253?un edip, \u351?at bolup,\par
\u221?ashana \u253?erinde g\u252?lmek \u253?ara\u351?maz.\par
\par
\u221?\u220?Z URSA\u327?\par
Doga kylsam, derg\u228?he du\u351? gelermi,\par
S\u228?her turup, Biribara \u253?\u252?z ursa\u328?.\par
\u221?a, Rep, berhak dosty ho\u351?wagt bolarmy,\par
Bir k\u246?\u328?\u252?l \u231?\u252?n \u253?\u252?z h\u252?n\u228?re \u253?\u252?z ursa\u328?.\par
\par
S\u228?her turup, naly\u351? kylsa\u328? Huda\u253?a,\par
G\u252?ne gol g\u246?terip, \u253?albarsa\u328? A\u253?a,\par
D\u246?wlet \u252?\u231?in baksa\u328? d\u246?wlet huma\u253?a,\par
Gen\u231? \u252?\u231?in syhr okap, mara \u253?\u252?z ursa\u328?.\par
\par
Gark olsa\u328? der\u253?aga, du\u351? gelse\u328? derde,\par
Tama \u252?\u231?in a\u231?ma \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328?den perde,\par
Katlan, dileg etme gedi namarda,\par
I\u351?i\u328? d\u252?\u351?\u252?p, dosta-\u253?ara \u253?\u252?z ursa\u328?.\par
\par
Namarda \u253?\u252?z ursa\u328?, i\u351?i\u328? ga\u253?yrmaz,\par
Itden s\u252?mek isl\u228?n bir zat a\u253?yrmaz,\par
Tilki \u246?z\u252?n g\u252?nde bir hem do\u253?urmaz,\par
\u221?egdir, a\u231? hem bolsa, \u351?ire \u253?\u252?z ursa\u328?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, ger\u231?e bagty\u328? \u351?or bolar,\par
M\u246?wlam nazar salsa, d\u246?wlet \u253?ar olar,\par
Gam senden sowular, derdi\u328? du:r olar,\par
Kemal han owgan dek \u228?re \u253?\u252?z ursa\u328?.\par
\par
\u221?AKAN\u199?A BOLMAZ\par
Her sepile sa\u231?ma derdi\u328?, s\u246?z\u252?\u328?i,\par
Hasrat ody jismi\u328? \u253?akan\u231?a bolmaz.\par
Gussa bile d\u228?ne-d\u228?ne g\u246?z\u252?\u328?den,\par
E\u351?ki-nedamaty\u328? akan\u231?a bolmaz.\par
\par
Kanyg bolup, yzzatda tut \u246?z\u252?\u328?i,\par
Tama kylyp, sargartmagyn \u253?\u252?z\u252?\u328?i,\par
Her namarda ha\u253?p e\u253?leme s\u246?z\u252?\u328?i,\par
S\u246?z\u252?\u328?ni\u328? binasyn \u253?ykan\u231?a bolmaz.\par
\par
Magrur olup gezme \u246?mr\u252?\u328? g\u252?l\u252?ne,\par
Sowrular sen bir g\u252?n hazan \u253?eline,\par
\u221?\u252?z \u253?a\u351?a\u253?yp d\u252?\u351?se\u328? ajal eline,\par
Sagy\u328?dan solu\u328?a bakan\u231?a bolmaz.\par
\par
S\u252?le\u253?mandan artyk bolsa \u351?\u246?wketi\u328?,\par
Lerzana getirse g\u246?gi ha\u253?baty\u328?,\par
G\u246?ws\u252?\u328? \u252?zre g\u252?rzi \u252?zer ri\u253?eti\u328?,\par
Ajaly\u328? jellady kakan\u231?a bolmaz.\par
\par
K\u246?\u328?li gara bilen bolma\u328?lar \u252?lpet,\par
\u221?okar ondan d\u252?rli-d\u252?rli kesapat,\par
Her\u231?ent ki k\u246?m\u252?re e\u253?lese\u328? yzzat,\par
Alny\u328?a garasy \u253?okan\u231?a bolmaz.\par
\par
Magtymguly hergiz tapmady aman,\par
Dil \u253?amany tygdan, teberden \u253?aman,\par
\u221?aman dil \u253?anynda z\u228?hri \u231?oh \u253?ylan,\par
\u199?aksa-da bir \u231?ybyn \u231?akan\u231?a bolmaz.\par
\par
\u221?ELDIM TUT\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? g\u246?rme\u253?, tutgun galsa\u328? bir k\u252?n\u231?de,\par
Bady-pa\u253? dek \u253?er \u253?\u252?z\u252?ne \u253?eldim tut.\par
\u199?yn-Ma\u231?ynda, Rumda, Hindde, Hebe\u351?de\par
Bolan-bolmu\u351? h\u252?n\u228?rleri bildim tut.\par
\par
A\u231? hem bolsa\u328?, barma ile dilege,\par
Di\u253?: \u171?K\u246?\u351?kde men, ba\u351?ym barmy\u351? pelege\u187?,\par
\u199?\u246?lde galsa\u328? hi\u231? tapma\u253?an k\u246?lege,\par
Erem bagy i\u231?re sa\u253?a buldum tut.\par
\par
A\u351? g\u246?re\u328?de, \u246?z\u252?\u328? atma tullanyp,\par
Ger\u231?e a\u231? hem bolsa\u328?, halka bellenip,\par
Zer d\u246?k\u252?b\u228?n, \u231?yn gullary goldanyp,\par
Tiz hem \u246?lse\u328?, Nuh \u253?a\u351?yna geldim tut.\par
\par
M\u228?t\u228?\u231?ligi\u328? Hakdan \u246?zge bilmese,\par
Ol rozyg\u228?r besdir, a\u231?dan \u246?lmese,\par
Hindi kimin egin-\u246?rti\u328? bolmasa,\par
Paty\u351?alyk pu\u351?e\u351? \u231?igne saldym tut.\par
\par
Suwa, \u253?ele h\u246?kmi ge\u231?en S\u252?le\u253?man,\par
Bak, olardan ne nam galdy, ne ny\u351?an,\par
Te\u351?ne galyp, ja\u253?y\u328? bolsa \u231?\u246?l\u252?stan,\par
Der\u253?a i\u231?re men Isgender boldum tut.\par
\par
\u221?olda\u351? bolsa\u328? dile d\u252?\u351?mez mur bile,\par
Fer\u351? tapma\u253?yn, bile \u253?atsa\u328? mar bile,\par
\u221?igrim alty keret, \u253?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? \u228?r bile,\par
Karun hazynasyn gola aldym tut.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u231?ekse\u328? jepa, jebir, bil -\par
Hudaga ho\u351? geler, \u351?\u252?k\u252?r-sabyr bil,\par
Gyl\u231?a jana gyzyl teni gabyr bil,\par
Gyzyl dili\u328? s\u246?zl\u228?r eken, \u246?ld\u252?m tut.\par
\par
\u221?AR E\u221?L\u196?R\par
Akly\u328? bolsa, \u253?ag\u351?ylarga hemdem bol,\par
Akmak \u246?z\u252?n nadan bile \u253?ar e\u253?l\u228?r.\par
Hak a\u351?yklar n\u228?zli \u253?ary\u328? jemalyn,\par
Bir g\u246?rsem di\u253?p, gije-g\u252?ndiz zar e\u253?l\u228?r.\par
\par
N\u228?ge syrym bolsa, a\u253?dar men merde,\par
Kerwen \u253?ata bilmez gorkuly \u253?erde,\par
Uly namyslarda \u253?aramaz derde,\par
Namart \u246?\u253?de s\u228?hel i\u351?i ar e\u253?l\u228?r.\par
\par
Namart k\u252?lpetinden galyp men derde,\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?m ja\u253? tapma\u253?yr bir pynhan \u253?erde,\par
Maly k\u246?p di\u253?p, myhman bolma namarda,\par
Jomart her\u231?ent galla\u231? bolsa, bar e\u253?l\u228?r.\par
\par
Namart \u246?z \u246?\u253?\u252?nde merde s\u246?z a\u253?dar,\par
Hak o\u328?a k\u228?r etmez, tanapyn dartar,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igit mal tapsa, h\u252?mmeti artar,\par
Namart ba\u253?adyk\u231?a, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?n dar e\u253?l\u228?r.\par
\par
Magtymguly, imdi \u246?z\u252?\u328?i g\u246?zle,\par
Ha\u253?yr i\u351?i\u328? artdyr, \u253?amany d\u252?zle,\par
Akly\u328? bolsa, m\u228?rekede az s\u246?zle,\par
K\u246?p s\u246?z seni il i\u231?inde har e\u253?l\u228?r.\par
\par
\u221?ETME\u221?IN GALMAZ\par
Yhlas bile bir k\u228?mile gol beren,\par
\u221?eter bir menzile, \u253?etme\u253?in galmaz.\par
Der\u253?a i\u231?re \u253?\u252?zen, \u231?\u246?llerde \u253?\u246?ren,\par
Dem hasabyn t\u252?kel etme\u253?in galmaz.\par
\par
\u199?\u252?nki geldi\u328? bu \u253?alan\u231?y jahana,\par
A\u253?agy\u328? garama\u253?, bakdy\u328? asmana,\par
Pelek bazarynda i\u253?digi\u328? nana,\par
Adam ogly \u246?mr\u252?n satma\u253?yn galmaz.\par
\par
Hemrazym \u253?ok, baryp syrym a\u231?ara,\par
Derdim togta\u351?ara, odum \u246?\u231?ire,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? bir menzildir gelip-ge\u231?ere,\par
Bu menzile gelen, gitme\u253?in galmaz.\par
\par
Pelek toma\u351?ak\u228?r asmana \u231?ykyp,\par
Adamzat mal \u252?\u231?in \u253?\u252?regin \u253?akyp,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? a\u382?darhasy dem bile \u231?ekip,\par
J\u252?mle-jandar tohmun \u253?uwtma\u253?yn galmaz.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? d\u246?wletin,\par
Gelen g\u246?rer-\u231?eker \u246?l\u252?m m\u228?hnetin,\par
Mydam \u253?\u246?r\u252?derler ajal \u351?erbetin,\par
Bu \u351?erbetden hi\u231? kim datma\u253?yn galmaz\par
\par
\u221?EL BILE\par
G\u246?z, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l, dil, akyl \u8722? galdy bu d\u246?rdi,\par
Jan watan arzuwlap, turdy \u253?el bile.\par
Terhosym bar, gel, terk etme bu \u253?urdy,\par
E\u351?ret s\u252?rg\u252?n, s\u246?hbet gurgun g\u252?l bile.\par
\par
Bir ajap menzildir, umydy\u328? \u252?zme,\par
G\u246?wn\u252?\u328?i sowutma, watan di\u253?p gyzma,\par
D\u252?kany\u328? dagytma, bazary\u328? bozma,\par
Ten m\u252?lk\u252?nde birni\u231?e g\u252?n gal bile.\par
\par
Myhman boldu\u328? bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? \u246?\u253?\u252?ne,\par
K\u246?\u328?\u252?l berip gitme onu\u328? k\u252?\u253?\u252?ne,\par
Ba\u351?y\u328? baglap, me\u351?gul eder o\u253?una,\par
Gitse\u328? bermez, aldap gezer dil bile.\par
\par
Munda gul bol, bar ol jahan seni\u328?dir,\par
Elwan nygmat, t\u228?ze bir\u253?an seni\u328?dir,\par
Behi\u351?t, Byrag, h\u252?\u253?ri-ryzwan seni\u328?dir,\par
Asy adam, dogry gelse\u328? \u253?ol bile.\par
\par
Pelek go\u253?maz, bu gezdigi\u328? sara\u253?da,\par
Gurt bile ko\u253? mydar etmez bir o\u253?da,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? doly gazna \u253?ygsa\u328? ne pe\u253?da,\par
\u199?yn mal oldur - ja\u253?na berse\u328? el bile.\par
\par
G\u246?gi b\u252?k\u252?p, \u253?azsa \u253?eri\u328? \u253?\u252?z\u252?ni,\par
Gurt ga\u328?rylyp, gapa bilmez guzyny,\par
M\u252?b\u228?rizler tuta bilmez \u246?z\u252?ni,\par
Pil hem durar baglasalar gyl bile.\par
\par
Magtymguly Hak gullugyn bitirse,\par
\u196?r ol bolar - emrin berja\u253? getirse,\par
M\u246?wlam \u214?zi diwan \u252?\u231?in otursa,\par
Pe\u351?e turup, dawa urar pil bile.\par
\par
YHSAN HA\u221?SY, BILINMEZ\par
Derdim k\u246?pd\u252?r di\u253?arymdan, d\u246?wr\u252?mden,\par
Ha\u253?yr ha\u253?sy, yhsan ha\u253?sy, bilinmez.\par
Zalymlary\u328? jepasyndan, jebrinden\par
Yslam ha\u253?sy, iman ha\u253?sy, bilinmez.\par
\par
S\u246?hbetinde Hak Kelamyn s\u246?\u253?l\u228?n \u253?ok,\par
Mejlisinde bir nesihat e\u253?l\u228?n \u253?ok,\par
Halal ha\u253?sy, haram ha\u253?sy, sa\u253?lan \u253?ok,\par
Sud ha\u253?sydyr, zy\u253?an ha\u253?sy, bilinmez\par
\par
Hala\u253?ykda g\u246?relde \u253?ok, g\u246?r\u252?m \u253?ok,\par
Ba\u253?larynda sahawat \u253?ok, berim \u253?ok,\par
A\u253?allarda u\u253?at, gyzda \u351?erim \u253?ok,\par
Edep ha\u253?sy, erkan ha\u253?sy bilinmez.\par
\par
Ki\u351?ini\u328? malyna g\u246?z\u252?n aldyrlar,\par
T\u228?sip edip, k\u246?\u328?le kine doldyrlar,\par
Bir-birini n\u228?hak \u253?ere \u246?ldirler,\par
Nurbat ha\u253?sy, aman ha\u253?sy, bilinmez.\par
\par
Magtymguly, jan myhmandyr, g\u246?wre \u8722? l\u228?\u351?,\par
\u221?ag\u351?a dost k\u246?p, \u253?aman bolsa\u328?, \u253?ok garda\u351?,\par
Bu e\u253?\u253?amda ba\u351? a\u253?akdyr, a\u253?ak \u8722? ba\u351?,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y ha\u253?sy, \u253?aman ha\u253?sy bilinmez.\par
\par
YKBAL BOLMADY\par
K\u246?p \u253?igitler gelip, ge\u231?di jahandan,\par
Ni\u253?etine g\u246?r\u228? ykbal bolmady.\par
Gerdi\u351?i ke\u231? gahba pelek elinden,\par
Ertiri \u351?at bolan \u246?\u253?l\u228?n g\u252?lmedi.\par
\par
G\u252?nde kepen bi\u231?er bu ajal \u8722? ha\u253?\u253?at,\par
Bir beladyr, hi\u231? gutarmaz bu sa\u253?\u253?at,\par
Pelle-pelle a\u351?ak d\u252?\u351?er adamzat,\par
Bu g\u252?n g\u246?rd\u252?gimiz ert\u228? galmady.\par
\par
Nesihatym di\u328?le, e\u351?it bu s\u246?zi,\par
Bir degi\u351?hanadyr d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? \u253?\u252?zi,\par
Ajal \u253?etip, adam \u253?umulsa g\u246?zi,\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? bu jahana geldi, gelmedi.\par
\par
Huma\u253?un gorganyn saldyran Harun,\par
Hany d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni d\u246?rt b\u246?len Feridun,\par
Kyrk \u351?\u228?hri gyzyldan dolduran Karun,\par
G\u246?zi gumdan doldy puldan dolmady.\par
\par
Magtymguly ha\u253?ran, her \u253?ana bakar,\par
Bu ne gudrat i\u351?dir, suwdan ot \u231?ykar?!\par
\u221?ag\u351?y oguldan rehmet arygy akar,\par
N\u228?letkerde ogul dogdy dogmady.\par
\par
JANAN BOLARMY?\par
D\u228?li k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m, bir nesihat di\u253?e\u253?in,\par
Jan di\u253?megil, be\u253?le janan bolarmy?\par
Bir s\u246?z\u252?\u328? ornunda s\u246?\u253?le\u253? bilme\u253?en, -\par
Adam di\u253?en be\u253?le ynsan bolarmy?\par
\par
Mutyg bolup, Huda emrin tutma\u253?an,\par
G\u246?wher alyp, bazarynda satma\u253?an,\par
Atadan, babadan beglik etme\u253?en,\par
Il gadyryn bilen soltan bolarmy?\par
\par
Adam bardyr adamlary bozduran,\par
\u350?e\u253?tan bolup, dogry \u253?oldan azdyran,\par
Hatyn s\u246?z\u252?n \u246?\u253? arada gezdiren -\par
Olary\u328? go\u253?nunda iman bolarmy?\par
\par
Magtymguly di\u253?er, bu s\u246?z\u252?m \u231?ohdur,\par
Men ibham eder men, hi\u231? a\u253?by \u253?okdur,\par
Kitap g\u246?ren gullar magnydan dokdur,\par
Olary\u328? kalbynda \u351?e\u253?tan bolarmy?\par
\par
\u221?AT \u221?AG\u350?Y\par
Ho\u351? g\u252?n\u252?\u328?de, ho\u351?tapla\u351?yp gezm\u228?ge,\par
Bary\u351?maga, geli\u351?m\u228?ge \u253?at \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
Gamly g\u252?n\u252?\u328?, galmagaly\u328? \u252?st\u252?nde\par
Garda\u351? \u253?ag\u351?y, dogan \u253?ag\u351?y, zat \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Halal i\u351?le \u8722? ahyretden wehmi\u328? bar,\par
Pakyry ynjytma \u8722? k\u246?\u328?\u252?l rehmi\u328? bar,\par
A\u351?yk a\u253?dar, azda-k\u246?pde p\u228?hmi\u328? bar,\par
Akyl bolsa\u328?, s\u246?ze gulak tut \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
\u221?\u252?rek da\u253?anjydyr ogul z\u252?r\u253?aty,\par
\u350?irin mahbup erer s\u252?\u328?\u328?\u252?\u328? kuwwaty,\par
\u221?igidi\u328? d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de \u252?\u231?d\u252?r myrady,\par
Mahbup gerek, \u253?arag gerek, at \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Mollalar ahyret s\u246?z\u252?n s\u246?\u253?l\u228?rler,\par
M\u252?\u328?k\u252?r olma, ger\u231?ek i\u351?dir, e\u253?l\u228?rler,\par
Kim biler ki, ahyretde ne\u253?l\u228?rler,\par
I\u253?ip-i\u231?ip, m\u252?n\u252?p-gu\u231?up \u246?t \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Ta\u328?ry gi\u328? e\u253?lese bende k\u246?\u328?l\u252?ni,\par
Ryzk agzyna girer \u8722? tutsa\u328? elini,\par
D\u246?wlet g\u252?zer etse, tapar \u253?oluny, -\par
Geler bolsa, gider bolsa, \u253?at \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Nep alma\u253?an ki\u351?i s\u246?zden, \u246?w\u252?tden,\par
Ena\u253?lygy bolmaz gury s\u246?w\u252?tden,\par
De\u328?-du\u351? bilmez, many a\u328?maz \u253?igitden,\par
Agyly\u328?da yssy beren it \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Magtymguly, dostdan syry\u328? gizleme,\par
Biwepadyr n\u228?m\u228?hremi g\u246?zleme,\par
\u220?ms\u252?m otur, halk i\u231?inde s\u246?zleme,\par
S\u246?zl\u228?r bolsa\u328?, s\u246?z aslyna \u253?et \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
GY\u350? GO\u221?AR\par
\u221?igit men di\u253?ip, \u253?az pasly\u328?a guwanma,\par
\u221?azy\u328? alar, \u253?az ornuna gy\u351? go\u253?ar.\par
\u214?l\u252?m bardyr, dirilig\u328?e da\u253?anma,\par
Jany\u328? alar, jesedi\u328?i bo\u351? go\u253?ar.\par
\par
S\u252?le\u253?many\u328? h\u246?kmi bar bolsa sende,\par
Yns-u jyns salama gelse her g\u252?nde,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328? ahyrynda, \u253?eri\u328? d\u252?\u253?b\u252?nde,\par
Adamzat ejizdir, \u253?al\u328?yz ba\u351? go\u253?ar.\par
\par
Gulluk hasyl bolmaz re\u328?\u328?i\u328? solmasa,\par
\u214?zi \u246?lmezinden owwal \u246?lmese,\par
Haka gulluk etse\u328?, hi\u231? kim bilmese,\par
Bihabardyr, \u253?ol \u252?st\u252?nde go\u351? go\u253?ar.\par
\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? lezzetinden el g\u246?ter,\par
Sen ondan \u246?tmese\u328? ol senden \u246?ter,\par
Bahyl i\u253?mez, i\u231?mez, nanyn bek tutar,\par
Jomart ogly a\u351? \u252?st\u252?ne a\u351? go\u253?ar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, haram i\u351?e ba\u351? go\u253?sa\u328?\par
M\u252?\u328? g\u252?n a\u231? bolar sen bir g\u252?ni do\u253?sa\u328?\par
Nebsi\u328?i yzzatlap, \u351?e\u253?tana u\u253?sa\u328?\par
Iman bilen abyra\u253?dan da\u351? go\u253?ar.\par
\par
BILI BOLMASA\par
Her kim suluw men di\u253?r, olmaz ygtybar,\par
S\u252?nb\u252?l sa\u231?y, gyl\u231?a bili bolmasa.\par
\u221?\u252?rekleri at ba\u351?y dek batyrlar,\par
Hatyn\u231?a \u253?ok, at-\u253?aragy bolmasa.\par
\par
N\u228?leri g\u246?rjekdir bu \u351?um k\u246?\u328?\u252?ller,\par
Hazan ursa, solar a\u231?ylan g\u252?ller,\par
Bag i\u231?re sa\u253?ra\u351?an \u351?e\u253?da bilbiller,\par
Torga\u253?\u231?a \u253?ok, gonar g\u252?li bolmasa.\par
\par
S\u246?zlese, her \u253?ana jo\u351?ardy diller,\par
Arkadan \u253?el \u246?sse, jo\u351?ardy siller,\par
G\u246?kde garkylda\u351?an \u253?a\u351?ylba\u351? gu\u351?lar,\par
Haly harap d\u252?\u351?er k\u246?li bolmasa.\par
\par
Ahyr bir g\u252?n bolar ahyrzamany,\par
Ysrapyl sur \u231?alsa, bolarlar pany,\par
Gyrgy g\u246?ren gu\u351?lar almaz awuny,\par
Gu\u351? ganaty, t\u252?\u253?, gu\u253?rugy bolmasa.\par
\par
Gu\u351?lar u\u231?a bilmez gu\u253?ruk-ganatsyz,\par
A\u351?yk \u253?ara \u253?etmez dady-per\u253?atsyz,\par
Bir bedew hanazat bolar sy\u253?aksyz,\par
Gu\u253?rugy, k\u228?kili, \u253?aly bolmasa.\par
\par
Ahyrzaman bolsa, \u351?yhdan p\u228?l ga\u231?ar,\par
Kelamy\u328? \u253?\u252?z\u252?nden hat galma\u253? \u246?\u231?er,\par
\u221?abandaky suwsuz aryga og\u351?ar,\par
Her kimi\u328? sahawat-ha\u253?ry bolmasa.\par
\par
Ba\u351?y\u328? go\u351?ma gadyr bilmez betzada,\par
Go\u351?sa\u328? go\u351?gul ba\u351?y\u328? bir asylzada,\par
Bir \u253?agmazak bulda me\u328?z\u228?r howada,\par
Her ki\u351?ini\u328? h\u252?mmet, ha\u253?ry bolmasa.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bildi\u328?, mundag zamandyr,\par
H\u228?l\u228? sudy bolsa, so\u328?ra zy\u253?andyr,\par
\u196?r \u253?igidi\u328? i\u231?i doly armandyr,\par
Gara g\u246?z, in\u231?e bil \u253?ary bolmasa.\par
\par
BILE MYHMANDYR\par
Adam ogly, \u246?mre bolmagyl ma\u253?yl,\par
\u221?igitligi\u328? dyza, bile myhmandyr.\par
\u221?ene Hak \u253?olunda bolmagyl k\u228?hil,\par
Basan gadamlary\u328? \u253?ola myhmandyr.\par
\par
Mekany\u328?dyr h\u228?ki-zemin gu\u231?ar sen,\par
Bir kerwen sen - di\u253?ary\u328?a g\u246?\u231?er sen,\par
M\u246?ws\u252?m g\u252?li solar, guryr \u246?\u231?er sen,\par
Owazy\u328? sem bolar, tile myhmandyr.\par
\par
Kimseler Hak di\u253?er, kimse saz bile,\par
Kimse humar bile, kimse baz bile,\par
Garkylda\u351?yp gezen ho\u351? owaz bile,\par
\u221?a\u351?ylba\u351? sonalar k\u246?le myhmandyr.\par
\par
G\u246?r\u252?\u328?, dostlar, bu s\u246?z\u252?mde \u253?alan \u253?ok,\par
Bir garybam, nesihatym alan \u253?ok,\par
Magtymguly, meni\u328? derdim bilen \u253?ok,\par
Derdimi\u328? dermany dile myhmandyr.\par
\par
BEGLER\par
Mert bilen namardy\u328? o\u253?ny de\u328? gelmez,\par
Namartlar s\u246?we\u351?de zy\u253?andyr, begler.\par
Namart go\u231? \u253?igidi\u328? gadryny bilmez,\par
Namardy\u328? her i\u351?i we\u253?randyr, begler.\par
\par
K\u228?mil go\u231? \u253?igitler haky\u328?y i\u253?mez,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? malyn berse\u328?, namartlar do\u253?maz,\par
Namart maslahata, ge\u328?e\u351?e u\u253?maz,\par
Namardy\u328? her i\u351?i a\u253?andyr, begler.\par
\par
Bir atada alty atany\u328? so\u253?y bar,\par
Bir nadany\u328? \u253?\u252?z hy\u253?allyk o\u253?y bar.\par
Go\u231? \u253?igitler kanda barsa \u246?\u253?i bar,\par
Namardy\u328? \u246?z \u246?\u253?i zyndandyr, begler.\par
\par
D\u246?wlet ba\u351?a gelse, dost-\u253?aryn g\u246?rmez,\par
Kaza gelse, bagryn \u253?erden g\u246?termez,\par
Hakdan di\u253?ip, hergiz iman getirmez,\par
Magtymguly, \u351?e\u253?le zamandyr, begler.\par
\par
S\u214?\u221?MEK BIL\u196?NI\par
Y\u351?ky\u328? ody hyru\u231? alyp batlanar,\par
Hi\u231? s\u246?nme\u253?ir, \u253?arym, s\u246?\u253?mek bil\u228?ni.\par
Ga\u253?ta ba\u351?dan dert atyna atlanar,\par
Hi\u231? gitmez gapymdan kowmak bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Bedasylda akyl bolmaz, dert bolmaz,\par
M\u252?\u328? tilki \u253?ygylsa, \u253?eke gurt bolmaz,\par
Namart ki\u351?i t\u228? \u246?lgen\u231?e mert bolmaz,\par
Taryp e\u253?l\u228?p, ony \u246?wmek bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y \u253?igit gadryn \u246?z ili bilmez,\par
Ba\u351?yna i\u351? d\u252?\u351?se, \u253?anyna gelmez,\par
Ol mert \u253?igit zarlar, derdi egsilmez,\par
Dat e\u253?l\u228?p, \u253?a, ilim, di\u253?mek bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
Balyk\u231?ylar a\u253?dar: \u171?Saldan do\u253?um \u253?ok\u187?,\par
Namart myhman g\u246?rse di\u253?er: \u171?\u214?\u253?\u252?m \u253?ok\u187?,\par
Bil, ynsan ogluna maldan do\u253?um \u253?ok,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y ge\u253?ip, \u253?ene i\u253?mek bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
A\u253?dy\u328? dostlar, zemin ha\u231?an ganarmy\u351?,\par
\u221?aman ni\u253?et bilen p\u228?lden d\u246?nermi\u351?,\par
Adam ogly \u253?eke onda dynarmy\u351?,\par
Ol amanat janyn bermek bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?, aklym \u253?etmez, be\u253?le \u253?eser sen,\par
Golsuz tutar sen-de, \u253?\u252?ps\u252?z asar sen,\par
Pyragy, dili\u328? \u253?yg, dili\u328? keser sen,\par
Ak don ge\u253?ip, \u253?ere girmek bil\u228?ni.\par
\par
GARA DA\u350?DAN A\u221?RYLSA\par
Gara da\u351?ly, seri duman bu daglar\par
Toprak bolar, gara da\u351?dan a\u253?rylsa.\par
Sil bolar, agdarlyp akar bulaglar\par
\u199?ille dolup, garlar gy\u351?dan a\u253?rylsa.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?de bir gowga uzakdan bolar,\par
G\u246?z gowasy gandan, bak \u253?a\u351?dan dolar,\par
Gurhan g\u246?rme\u253? gezen pirler a\u231? galar,\par
Ili undyp, seri pe\u351?den a\u253?rylsa.\par
\par
\u199?oh di\u253?er men: d\u252?n\u253?\u228? galdy \u253?amana,\par
Rehim etmez boldy, g\u246?r, musulmana,\par
La\u231?ynlar pel-pell\u228?p galar asmana,\par
Haram \u246?len porsy l\u228?\u351?den a\u253?rylsa.\par
\par
Zynahor sylamaz ilin-\u253?urduny,\par
Ga\u253?ra teser, g\u246?rse \u228?ri\u328? merdini,\par
Adam ogly di\u253?e bilmez derdini\par
\u221?\u252?rek \u253?anyp, \u231?e\u351?mi \u253?a\u351?dan a\u253?rylsa.\par
\par
Namart juwanparaz haly zebundyr,\par
Merdi g\u246?rse \u253?yglar, g\u246?zleri hundur,\par
Dosty garyp d\u252?\u351?se, mertler mejnundyr,\par
Namart dost istemez a\u351?dan a\u253?rylsa.\par
\par
\u221?urt derdine gider ilde merdanlar,\par
Namart ga\u231?yp barar, baky\u328?, \u253?aranlar,\par
Mal di\u253?ip \u253?urt gezer bahyl-nadanlar,\par
Gussa batar g\u246?zel d\u252?\u253?\u351?den a\u253?rylsa.\par
\par
Namart-zenan gepde hi\u231? durky bolmaz,\par
Wezirler nadandyr, bir erki bolmaz,\par
G\u252?ler \u253?\u252?zli \u253?ary\u328? hi\u231? g\u246?rki bolmaz\par
Sy\u253?a z\u252?lp, gara g\u246?z, ga\u351?dan a\u253?rylsa.\par
\par
Bezirgenler mydam \u253?ola bil baglar,\par
Nadan \u246?tse yrak giden il \u231?aglar\par
Magtymguly, Haky \u253?atlar, gan aglar\par
\u350?a, gedalar akyl-hu\u351?dan a\u253?rylsa.\par
\par
BA\u350? \u221?AG\u350?Y\par
A\u253?ak, golsuz galyp, ma\u253?yp bolandan,\par
G\u252?lle degip, alyp giden ba\u351? \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
K\u228?rsizlikden gam \u246?\u253?\u252?nde bi\u351?enden,\par
\u199?enden agdyk sere d\u252?\u351?en i\u351? \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Kelle go\u253?up saldyk hany\u328? galasyn,\par
E\u351?itdik ahy-zar, misgin nalasyn,\par
Golda saklap bolmaz jeren balasyn,\par
Hemra kylmak \u252?\u231?in toty gu\u351? \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Nakyl bardyr: \u171?Ganar bolmaz \u253?arydan\u187?,\par
Adamzat \u253?ag\u351?ydyr gulman, periden,\par
\u199?oh i\u351?leri ba\u351?dan salan garrydan,\par
S\u246?zle\u351?m\u228?ge, i\u351? kylmaga \u253?a\u351? \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Ulag bardyr uzak \u253?ollar ge\u231?m\u228?ge,\par
\u350?erap g\u246?zel me\u253?-mest bolup i\u231?m\u228?ge,\par
Rahat seredip, g\u246?w\u252?n a\u231?maga,\par
Da\u328? s\u228?herde bir g\u246?r\u252?len d\u252?\u253?\u351? \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
E\u351?ek g\u246?wni ho\u351?dur \u231?oh bolsa saman,\par
Gy\u351? paslynda daglar b\u252?rener duman,\par
Gulaksyz, g\u246?zs\u252?zlik, dilsizlik \u253?aman,\par
A\u351? i\u253?m\u228?ge bar\u231?asyndan di\u351? \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Ylym-alym, baryp sora\u328? arapdan,\par
Hywa hany suw \u253?uwudar Lebapdan,\par
Tagamsyz lukmadan, arak-\u351?erapdan,\par
G\u246?w\u252?n iste\u253?ip bir i\u253?ilen a\u351? \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
Pyragy - d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de galan ma\u253?ypdyr,\par
\u220?\u231? \u253?\u252?z altmy\u351? eren - bary ga\u253?ypdyr,\par
Go\u231? \u253?igide \u253?ekelik-de a\u253?ypdyr,\par
Mert garda\u351?y \u252?\u231?den, d\u246?rtden, b\u228?\u351? \u253?ag\u351?y.\par
\par
DU\u350?MANYM PELEK\par
Meni ata-ene, garda\u351?, oguldan,\par
A\u253?ra saldy\u328?, zalym, du\u351?manym pelek.\par
Ilimden-g\u252?n\u252?mden, erkim, malymdan\par
A\u253?ra saldy\u328? meni, du\u351?manym pelek.\par
\par
Misginlikden golum uzatsam, \u253?etmez,\par
\u221?\u252?regim armany a\u253?rylmaz, gitmez.\par
Haka g\u252?nde \u253?albarsam-da, egsilmez,\par
A\u253?ra saldy\u328? meni, du\u351?manym pelek.\par
\par
Bor\u231? e\u253?ledim, agyr g\u252?nd\u252?r ba\u351?ymda,\par
Bilmen, ne belalar bardyr da\u351?ymda,\par
Ne akyl, ne pikir galdy hu\u351?umda,\par
A\u253?ra saldy\u328? meni, du\u351?manym pelek.\par
\par
Ne \u253?amanlyk kyldym seni\u328? k\u228?ri\u328?e,\par
Gel-de otur, pelek, deslap \u253?eri\u328?e,\par
Salma indi Pyragyny seri\u328?e,\par
A\u253?ra saldy\u328? meni, du\u351?manym pelek.\par
\par
SALDY DI\u221?DILER\par
\u196?hli-kuhy-Kapdan Dehistan \u252?zre,\par
Bir mekan le\u351?gerin saldy di\u253?diler,\par
Byragyn galgadyp, inip g\u252?zere,\par
Bir damja suw go\u253?man sordy di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Bejan harap bolmu\u351? ahy-zar bilen,\par
T\u252?rk\u252?stan s\u246?we\u351?ip en\u231?e mar bilen,\par
Isa ga\u231?yp gitmi\u351? \u253?eke har bilen,\par
Owazy \u228?lemge doldy di\u253?diler.\par
\par
D\u246?k\u252?lip galdylar zarlap be\u253?tinler,\par
\u199?ykypdyr janlarmyz, bo\u351? galyp tenler,\par
\u350?\u246?hlesizdir Mahlar, tutulyp G\u252?nler,\par
Asmandan bir bela geldi di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Ba\u351?y bo\u351? galypdyr bolan juwanlar,\par
Tagtyn unudyp \u351?a, \u246?t\u252?pdir hanlar,\par
Titre\u351?ip gara gan olup p\u228?lwanlar,\par
G\u252?l \u253?\u252?zi sargaryp soldy di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Hywa gark bolupdyr gamy\u328? siline,\par
Tagma basypdyrlar t\u252?rkmen diline,\par
E\u253?ran jebir edipdir g\u246?zel iline,\par
Barysy ga\u231?y\u351?yp geldi di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Gudratyndan d\u252?\u351?\u252?p k\u246?p uly pirler,\par
Daglar \u253?ykylypdyr j\u252?nb\u252?\u351?l\u228?p \u253?erler,\par
Akyllar u\u231?updyr bo\u351? galyp serler,\par
Bir gudrat g\u246?terip \u231?aldy di\u253?diler.\par
\par
\u214?z\u252?n yrak ta\u351?lap sarwansyz mallar,\par
S\u246?k\u252?p gidipdirler k\u246?p uzak \u253?ollar,\par
Ummanda gark bol\u351?up e\u253?esiz sallar,\par
Gol serip, agla\u253?yp galdy di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Budur seni\u328? jebri\u328?, e\u253? zalym pelek,\par
G\u246?r, ne g\u246?zel janlar e\u253?ledi\u328? hel\u228?k,\par
Pyragy, pi\u351?eler barysy telek,\par
Alla nazaryny saldy di\u253?diler.\par
\par
\u221?A\u350?LAR I\u199?INDE\par
Daglar goja galsa, der\u253?alar - silsiz,\par
\u221?a, Repbim di\u253?erler, \u253?a\u351?lar i\u231?inde.\par
Dahan \u253?al\u328?yz d\u252?\u351?se, bir barmak dilsiz,\par
Ne \u231?\u228?re e\u253?lesin di\u351?ler i\u231?inde.\par
\par
Garry g\u252?\u253?\u231?den galar, \u253?igitler hu\u351?dan,\par
Sa\u253?\u253?at awdan galar, la\u231?ynlar gu\u351?dan,\par
\u350?ada akyl bolmaz, akmaklar ba\u351?dan,\par
K\u246?p hy\u253?al kylarlar d\u252?\u253?\u351?ler i\u231?inde.\par
\par
Dokuz kelam okan ili\u328? sopusy,\par
Ja\u253?y belli imes, kanda gapysy,\par
Iki g\u246?ws arasy - juwan sapasy,\par
Garagu\u351? mekany l\u228?\u351?ler i\u231?inde.\par
\par
Toka\u253?lar bir zaman pele\u328?siz bolmaz,\par
Hindi jandan \u246?ter, pilinden galmaz,\par
Gazak ge\u231?i s\u246?\u253?er, go\u231?, g\u228?wmi\u351? almaz,\par
Mekany bolarmy\u351? g\u246?\u231?ler i\u231?inde.\par
\par
Magtymguly, sakla uzyn dili\u328?i,\par
\u221?erin tana, m\u228?k\u228?m bagla bili\u328?i,\par
Bahar pasly \u246?w\u252?sdirme \u253?eli\u328?i,\par
\u221?el mekany bolar gy\u351?lar i\u231?inde.\par
\par
KERWEN \u199?YKAR\par
Bizem d\u252?\u351?d\u252?k indi kerwensara\u253?a,\par
Go\u351?un baglap \u253?ola bu kerwen \u231?ykar.\par
Kimse geler zary e\u253?l\u228?p hara\u253?a,\par
Idegin \u253?itirip, bir sarwan \u231?ykar.\par
\par
Gezse\u328? bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de \u231?oh h\u246?wes e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Dostlar bilen her dem bir me\u253?lis e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Bir g\u252?n dem gutarar, be\u253?tin \u253?as e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Salam berip, \u246?\u328?den bir zemin \u231?ykar.\par
\par
\u221?asy\u328?y tutarlar \u252?\u253?\u351?\u252?p k\u246?p bende,\par
Hi\u231? kesi\u328? umydy bolma\u253?ar sende,\par
Ak don ge\u253?ip, molla geler her g\u252?nde,\par
Tekrar e\u253?l\u228?p, sa\u328?a ol Gurhan \u231?ykar.\par
\par
Repbi\u328?i sora\u253?yr sorag\u231?y gelip,\par
Sen gidersi\u328? bu panydan a\u253?rylyp,\par
Garda\u351?-dogan, hemme galar zar bolup,\par
Aga-ini, na\u231?arlardan hun \u231?ykar.\par
\par
Pyragy, \u351?\u252?kr edip, k\u246?p dessan \u253?azgyn,\par
Haka galan borju\u328? deprenme\u253? \u252?zg\u252?n,\par
Byradarym, b\u228?\u351? g\u252?n mest bolup gezgin,\par
Bir g\u252?n dem gutarar, tenden jan \u231?ykar.\par
\par
\u221?YL BILE\par
Ba\u351?y\u328?a gelendir garrylyk gy\u351?y,\par
Hi\u231? a\u253?rylmaz a\u253?lar bile, \u253?yl bile.\par
D\u246?k\u252?ldi dahandan Hak beren di\u351?i,\par
\u221?okdur ho\u351?um s\u252?\u253?ji s\u246?zli dil bile.\par
\par
\u221?agty jahan g\u246?zlerime zyndandyr,\par
Gije-g\u252?ndiz ganly \u253?a\u351?ym rowandyr,\par
\u221?\u252?regim takatsyz, kalbym armandyr,\par
H\u246?wesim \u253?ok, dostlar, gyzyl g\u252?l bile.\par
\par
\u214?tdi menden ol \u253?igitlik ga\u253?raty,\par
Garrady, a\u253?ryldy gu\u253?rukdan aty,\par
Pelek ba\u351?a saldy \u231?ykmaz apaty,\par
Dyzda kuwwat \u253?okdur, egri bil bile.\par
\par
Dolandy da\u351?yma baky gerdi\u351?i,\par
\u221?atsam-tursam \u231?ykmaz d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? i\u351?i,\par
Dat e\u253?l\u228?p \u231?ekerem en\u231?e k\u228?\u253?i\u351?i,\par
\u214?mr\u252?m ge\u231?ip barar altmy\u351? sal bile.\par
\par
Essimden \u231?ykardym gu\u351?um, awlagym,\par
Burnun \u253?ele tutup ga\u231?dy owlagym,\par
Ner-ma\u253?a \u231?yrpynan otly \u253?a\u253?lagym\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228?ki d\u252?\u253?\u351? boldy, gitdi \u231?\u246?l bile.\par
\par
Pyragy di\u253?r, \u253?ok d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de h\u246?wesim,\par
\u221?eke dinde bolup galdy yhlasym,\par
Zar epl\u228?p aglasam, di\u328?lenmez sesim,\par
Arzuwym galmady g\u246?zel il bile.\par
\par
TUTA BA\u350?LADY\par
S\u252?le\u253?man tagtyna e\u253?e bolanlar,\par
Tagtyn l\u228?mekanda tuta ba\u351?lady.\par
Il i\u231?inde p\u228?lwan bolup galanlar,\par
\u214?\u253?den \u231?ykman, her dem \u253?ata ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Namart gezdi, mala \u246?z\u252?n \u253?ar e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Myhman alabilmez, baryn bar e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Mert \u253?igidi\u328? g\u246?wni da\u253?ym zar e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Ykbaly, g\u246?r, la\u253?a bata ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Ne aja\u253?yp g\u252?nler, \u246?ten d\u246?wranlar,\par
Barysy \u253?at boldy, a\u253?landy ganlar,\par
Ata \u231?ykyp, jelep-loly zenanlar,\par
\u221?igitler de\u328?inden \u246?te ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Gudratyndan d\u252?\u351?di pirler-i\u351?anlar,\par
\u199?\u228?resiz, azarly galdy bu janlar,\par
Molla boldy her \u246?\u328? \u253?eten nadanlar,\par
Igi-guly hoja \u231?ata ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Daglar ba\u351?yn egdi, d\u246?kdi g\u246?z\u253?a\u351?yn,\par
Siller akyp, gu\u351?ap aldylar da\u351?yn,\par
Unutdy k\u246?p iller s\u246?wer garda\u351?yn,\par
Mal ist\u228?p, zenanyn sata ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Nebisden galmady azan a\u253?danlar,\par
Hajy bolup Medineden ga\u253?danlar,\par
Suwa girdi \u246?m\u252?r k\u228?ri la\u253?danlar,\par
Ilatdan mallaryn tarta ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
Magtymguly, gorkym k\u246?pd\u252?r \u253?anymdan,\par
Habar sorar iller \u253?a\u328?y donumdan.\par
....................................................... \par
Ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in, kararym gide ba\u351?lady.\par
\par
AMANA GELER\par
Mert bolar men di\u253?se\u328?, merde hemra bol,\par
Namart merdi g\u246?rse, amana geler.\par
Zar kylar men di\u253?se\u328?, aha gulak sal,\par
Ba\u253?gu\u351? uzak u\u231?maz, we\u253?rana geler.\par
\par
R\u252?stem Zal d\u228?lmidi d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni alan?\par
Merdana-mert bolup, d\u246?w\u252?\u351?ler kylan.\par
Rafyk d\u228?lmi s\u246?wer hemrasy bolan?\par
Namyssyz \u253?igitler g\u252?mana geler.\par
\par
Nakyl bardyr: \u171?Ten agyrsa, jan syzar\u187?,\par
Kim g\u246?r\u252?pdir, u\u231?an gu\u351?dan p\u228?l ozar?\par
Jojuk dogan g\u252?ni penasyn gazar,\par
So\u328?ra gu\u253?ruk bulap, me\u253?dana geler.\par
\par
At ala\u328?da s\u252?r\u252?p alsa\u328? \u231?amany,\par
G\u246?wn\u252?\u328?de go\u253?maz ol zerre g\u252?many,\par
Hemra kylma g\u246?wni gara, \u253?amany,\par
Syry\u328?y pa\u351? e\u253?l\u228?p, diwana geler.\par
\par
Hana hemra bolma, p\u228?li\u328? azmasa,\par
\u350?a gyzyny alma, Huda \u253?azmasa.\par
Her dem \u253?\u246?rg\u252?l, birew \u253?olu\u328? bozmasa,\par
Egri \u253?oldan gitse\u328?, \u253?amana geler.\par
\par
Misgin bolsun mydam seni\u328? syrda\u351?y\u328?,\par
Oldur \u253?\u252?rekde\u351?i\u328? hem-de garda\u351?y\u328?,\par
\u221?owuz g\u252?ne d\u252?\u351?se bu ejiz ba\u351?y\u328?,\par
Oda bile \u253?anar, dermana geler.\par
\par
Kazylar betp\u228?ldir, uzyndyr dili,\par
Bir lakgy \u231?a\u351?yrar ol k\u252?ren ili,\par
Aksakgal ba\u253?lary\u328? azanda p\u228?li,\par
Bir ge\u328?e\u351? kylmaga Karuna geler.\par
\par
Me\u253? mest bolup, gelen g\u252?n\u252?m \u246?t\u252?rsem,\par
Hana arzym a\u253?dyp, golum \u253?etirsem,\par
G\u246?w\u252?nde islegim gola getirsem,\par
Gamda galan g\u246?wn\u252?m d\u246?wrana geler.\par
\par
Daglar gojalandyr, dumany gitmez,\par
\u350?uny anyk bili\u328?, namartlar \u246?tmez,\par
Mert \u253?igidi\u328? goly d\u246?wlete \u253?etmez,\par
Ga\u253?ta ba\u351?dan hy\u253?al armana geler.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu ne hy\u253?al, ne p\u228?ldir?\par
Bu ne nesihatdyr, ne uzyn dildir?\par
G\u246?w\u252?n bir a\u231?ylan gyrmyzy g\u252?ld\u252?r,\par
Bu g\u252?n \u351?atdyr, erte pygana geler.\par
\par
TUTUP BARADYR\par
Pelek bu jahana torun \u253?azypdyr,\par
Yns-jyns di\u253?m\u228?n, tutup baradyr.\par
En\u231?e \u252?flas tutup, le\u351?ger d\u252?z\u252?pdir,\par
Dagy-d\u252?zde baryn s\u252?r\u252?p baradyr.\par
\par
Ga\u231?yp gutulmar sen, kowup \u253?eterler,\par
Azm urup, \u231?alyp, \u253?aka tutarlar,\par
Bir daban zemine l\u228?\u351?i\u328? atarlar,\par
Gara \u253?ere teni\u328? garyp baradyr.\par
\par
Ne j\u252?re zamandyr, nedir hy\u253?aly,\par
Jan \u351?\u228?hrine salar mydam ol \u253?oly,\par
Adam ogly \u231?\u246?ker la\u253?a ykbaly,\par
\u220?st\u252?nden tokmaklap urup baradyr.\par
\par
Magtymguly, g\u246?zi bagly elenip,\par
Har galypdyr lahat i\u231?re towlanyp,\par
\u221?alan d\u252?n\u253?\u228? d\u246?rt bur\u231?uny a\u253?lanyp,\par
Bar\u231?any bu pelek sorup baradyr.\par
\par
DUMAN G\u214?TERLER\par
Serin duman tutan bu belent daglar,\par
Gojalyp, serinden duman g\u246?terler.\par
Bilbiller sa\u253?ra\u253?an howaly baglar,\par
Hazan urup, serwi-re\u253?han g\u246?terler.\par
\par
Uly jemagatlar, uly ge\u328?e\u351?ler,\par
G\u246?w\u252?nde\u351? syrda\u351?lar, na\u231?ar, garda\u351?lar,\par
Gam tagtynda ge\u328?e\u351? guran te\u351?w\u252?\u351?ler,\par
Tagty synyp, h\u246?kmi rowan g\u246?terler.\par
\par
Bulanyp \u253?\u246?re\u253?en ne ajap siller,\par
Alnynda bent gurar, \u246?sd\u252?rmez \u253?eller,\par
Kesmez akyl, s\u246?z s\u246?zle\u351?mez bu diller,\par
Pelek urup, g\u246?zel suhan g\u246?terler.\par
\par
Hany, ol Isgender, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni alan,\par
R\u252?stem-u Zal \u246?tdi \u8722? gylyjyn \u231?alan,\par
Hezret Aly atasyna zor salan,\par
Mertler wepat boldy, p\u228?lwan g\u246?terler.\par
\par
Karuny \u253?uwutdy bu gara zemin,\par
Ajal gowgasyndan dynmady Emin,\par
Ol uly S\u252?le\u253?man almady demin,\par
Der\u253?alar gurady, umman g\u246?terler.\par
\par
\u214?tenin sanadym, aklym \u231?a\u351?ypdyr,\par
Hesibim gutardy, \u231?akdan a\u351?ypdyr,\par
Magtymguly, a\u253?ym-g\u252?n\u252?m \u253?a\u351?ypdyr,\par
Sahypkyran, g\u246?zel iman g\u246?terler.\par
\par
G\u214?ZDEN AKAN \u221?A\u350?YMA\par
Zemin j\u252?nb\u252?\u351? e\u253?l\u228?p, asman lerzandyr,\par
E\u253?-\u228?, dostlar, g\u246?zden akan \u253?a\u351?yma.\par
Behi\u351?t g\u252?li, dowzah, ata\u351?-suzandyr,\par
E\u253?-\u228?, dostlar, g\u246?zden akan \u253?a\u351?yma.\par
\par
Azazyl go\u351?uny saldy kastyma,\par
Nardan d\u252?\u351?ek go\u253?dy, ne\u253?le\u253?, astyma,\par
Peri\u351?deler perwaz urdy \u252?st\u252?me,\par
E\u253?-\u228?, dostlar, g\u246?zden akan \u253?a\u351?yma.\par
\par
Harte\u231?jal ot sa\u231?yp, \u231?\u246?zdi goluny,\par
Urdy dowzah ody, tutdy \u253?oluny,\par
Nuh \u231?ykaryp umman i\u231?re salyny,\par
Terpendirme\u253? durdy g\u246?zde \u253?a\u351?yma.\par
\par
Eminler ne derman, ne \u231?\u228?re tapar,\par
Rehim e\u253?l\u228?n bolmaz, kim \u252?st\u252?n \u253?apar,\par
Pa\u253? astyna salyp kylarlar sapar,\par
Bezirgenler s\u252?r\u252?p g\u246?zde \u253?a\u351?yma.\par
\par
Magtymguly, bu pelekden zar e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Lukmany g\u246?rmedi ol azar e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Du\u231?ar boldy \u253?\u252?regimde nar e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Gider boldy durman g\u246?zde \u253?a\u351?yma.\par
\par
S\u220?RDI-DE BARDY\par
Pelek golun serdi d\u252?n\u253?\u228? malyna,\par
E\u253?esiz e\u253?ledi, s\u252?rdi-de bardy.\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman d\u252?\u351?er bolsa \u253?oluna,\par
So\u328?un sanman, baryn urdy-da bardy.\par
\par
Daga azy salyp, da\u351?yn goparyp,\par
Der\u253?any guradyp, suwun aparyp,\par
Ata \u231?ykyp, ynsy-jynsy \u253?apyryp,\par
Bir ujundan \u8722? baryn gyrdy-da bardy.\par
\par
\u220?\u253?tgetdi en\u231?\u228?ni\u328? aja\u253?yp ke\u351?bin,\par
\u220?flasa ge\u253?dirip, pirleri\u328? pe\u351?in,\par
Bir s\u252?ri g\u252?sbende gurdu\u328? s\u246?we\u351?in,\par
Dahan a\u231?yp, baryn \u253?ardy-da bardy.\par
\par
Magtymguly, d\u246?k\u252?p ganly \u253?a\u351?lary,\par
Zakgun e\u253?l\u228?p, g\u246?w\u252?n isl\u228?n a\u351?lary,\par
\u350?ehit kyldy en\u231?e g\u246?zel ba\u351?lary,\par
Pikr etme\u253?en, baryn serdi-de bardy.\par
\par
ZAR I\u199?INDE TELMURYP\par
Namys-arsyz pelek, garda\u351? e\u253?ledim,\par
Tora d\u252?\u351?\u252?p, zar i\u231?inde telmuryp.\par
Tany bilm\u228?n namart syrda\u351? e\u253?ledim,\par
\u221?al\u328?yzlykda har i\u231?inde telmuryp.\par
\par
Pelegi\u328? \u231?arhynda golum syndyrdym,\par
Gan i\u231?inde galyp, g\u246?z\u252?m gandyrdym,\par
Janym, ykbal imanymy \u253?andyrdym,\par
Bu jahanda nar i\u231?inde telmuryp.\par
\par
\u221?\u252?regim tolgunyp, hetden a\u351?ypdyr,\par
Zyndanda galypdyr, g\u252?ni \u253?a\u351?ypdyr,\par
Desterhany\u328? \u171?merdi\u187? \u228?re og\u351?apdyr,\par
\u199?\u228?resiz ol zor i\u231?inde telmuryp.\par
\par
Gel g\u246?w\u252?n, ukudan g\u246?tergil seri\u328?,\par
Emma ki gola\u253?dyr ajal eseri\u328?,\par
Magtymguly, g\u246?zden u\u231?updyr nuru\u328?,\par
Ol behi\u351?di\u328? nur i\u231?inde telmuryp.\par
\par
MALLAR DARGADY\par
E\u253?-\u228?, dostlar, pelek zulum e\u253?le\u253?ip,\par
Bazarymdan zerrin mallar dargady.\par
Pelek gazap kylyp, ba\u351?ym a\u253?la\u253?yp,\par
G\u246?w\u252?n i\u231?re bar hy\u253?allar dargady.\par
\par
Gezer boldum, il i\u231?inde san bolup,\par
Gymmatdan d\u252?\u351?\u252?p men, derdi-hun bolup,\par
Bid\u246?wlet, buzahor ile han bolup,\par
Jebir kyldy, g\u246?zel iller dargady.\par
\par
Gaflat ukusynda bendidir g\u246?zler,\par
U\u253?alar il-g\u252?nden gymmatsyz s\u246?zler,\par
Gy\u351?da nowruz geldi, gy\u351? boldy \u253?azlar,\par
Dehistandan gelen \u253?eller dargady.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?\u252?regimde dert galdy,\par
Dert \u252?st\u252?nden pelek nazaryn saldy,\par
Ykbal \u253?atdy, g\u246?wn g\u228?misi gark boldy,\par
Onu\u328? bilen bar\u231?a sallar dargady.\par
\par
\u221?OLLARA SARY\par
S\u246?wdeg\u228?r, bezirgen, jahanke\u351?deler,\par
Karardan a\u253?rylar \u253?ollara sary.\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni e\u253?el\u228?p ol \u246?ten Karun,\par
G\u246?z\u252?n \u253?umup di\u253?er: \u171?Mallara sary\u187?.\par
\par
Pelegi\u328? \u252?st\u252?nden h\u246?km\u252?n \u253?\u246?reden,\par
Gudrat bilen yns-jynsy d\u246?reden,\par
Demin urup, dagy-da\u351?y ereden\par
Dahan a\u231?yp barmy\u351? dillere sary.\par
\par
\u221?edi g\u252?n agla\u253?yp, g\u246?z\u252?nden galan,\par
Kyrk ineri tirk\u228?p, rowana bolan,\par
Lagl g\u246?zl\u228?p, tylla, misden u\u253?alan\par
Ussa Jebpar a\u253?dar: \u171?Illere sary.\u187?\par
\par
G\u252?n\u228?siz bendeler Haky\u328? \u253?anynda,\par
Azazyl galta\u351?ar mag\u351?ar g\u252?n\u252?nde,\par
Bir n\u228?rse go\u253?an dek adam janynda,\par
Ezra\u253?yl ugramy\u351? illere sary.\par
\par
Abady az bolan d\u252?n\u253?\u228? we\u253?rany,\par
Dargatdy bazaryn, \u253?apdy d\u252?kany,\par
\u196?lem intizardyr arap zybany,\par
Her kes ist\u228?p di\u253?er dillere sary.\par
\par
We\u253?rana d\u246?n\u252?pdir ne g\u246?zel iller,\par
Solup zagpyran dek lam-elip biller,\par
Andalypsyz bagda \u253?eti\u351?en g\u252?ller,\par
Go\u253?nuny a\u231?army\u351? \u253?ellere sary.\par
\par
Daglar kemerinden turan dumanym,\par
Egsildi\u328?, g\u246?teri\u328? meni\u328? pyganym,\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, dostum-\u253?aranym,\par
D\u228?li g\u246?w\u252?n di\u253?er \u231?\u246?llere sary.\par
\par
M\u196?REK\u196? BARMAZ\par
Utanmaz adamdan namart \u253?ag\u351?ydyr,\par
Howatyr e\u253?le\u253?ir, m\u228?rek\u228? barmaz.\par
Dendan \u8213? pena, zyban \u8213? dahan nag\u351?ydyr,\par
Leb bilen g\u252?w\u351? hi\u231? zybana \u253?aramaz.\par
\par
Akylly az g\u252?rl\u228?r, gorkar dilinden,\par
Namart a\u253?yp g\u246?zl\u228?r dogan ilinden,\par
Bilbil jyda d\u252?\u351?se now\u231?a g\u252?l\u252?nden,\par
G\u252?l\u252?n arzuw e\u253?l\u228?r, asala gonmaz.\par
\par
G\u246?r\u252?\u328?, bu pelegi\u328? ma\u253?sa or\u351?uny,\par
\u221?ygna\u253?ar ol \u231?arhy\u328? sowar harjyny,\par
Mert \u253?igitler atar, salar gyljyny,\par
M\u252?\u328? namart bolsa-da, bir merde sanmaz.\par
\par
Pelek s\u246?wdatalap, jana hyrydar,\par
\u199?arhyn terse a\u253?lar, \u228?lem bikarar,\par
Magtymguly, \u253?\u252?regimde bir ot bar,\par
Bir a\u351?ykda munu\u328? kibi ot \u253?anmaz.\par
\par
G\u214?RER G\u214?Z\u220?\u327? - ILI\u327?I\par
Gel, g\u246?w\u252?n, men sa\u328?a \u246?w\u252?t bere\u253?in,\par
Yrak kylma g\u246?rer g\u246?z\u252?\u328? \u8213? ili\u328?i.\par
Gymmatyn ga\u231?yrma, \u253?erinde s\u246?zle,\par
Uzatmagyl her n\u228?kese dili\u328?i.\par
\par
Doga e\u253?le, bir s\u246?z di\u253?se\u328? a\u351?agyn,\par
Hormatlagyl g\u246?zel ili\u328? u\u351?agyn,\par
\u221?azdyrmagyl, m\u228?k\u228?m e\u253?le gu\u351?agyn,\par
\u221?eri bardyr, ajap sakla bili\u328?i.\par
\par
\u199?agyrylmaz ja\u253?da g\u246?r\u252?nme, barma,\par
Ba\u351?arsa\u328?, sopyny\u328? \u253?\u252?z\u252?ni g\u246?rme,\par
Pikir-zikri\u328? d\u252?n\u253?\u228? malyna berme,\par
Karuna og\u351?atma, tutgun p\u228?li\u328?i.\par
\par
S\u246?z\u252?ne ber jogap, her kes sorasa,\par
\u214?z\u252?\u328? yrak e\u253?le, namart \u253?\u246?rese,\par
Bir misgin telmuryp, \u253?yglap garasa,\par
Baha urma, mugt bergin maly\u328?y.\par
\par
Gorkma namartlary\u328? k\u246?p di\u253?p sanyndan,\par
Gara g\u246?rse, bary ge\u231?er janyndan,\par
Ugrun tapsa\u328?, \u246?tm\u228?wergil \u253?anyndan,\par
Bahyllardan yrak e\u253?le \u253?olu\u328?y.\par
\par
Akylly ba\u351? k\u246?pd\u252?r, akyl kesen azdyr,\par
Datma \u351?erap, uzak i\u231?se\u328?, ol azdyr,\par
Mert g\u246?wn\u252?nde da\u253?ym bahardyr-\u253?azdyr,\par
Mejnun umman i\u231?re salma saly\u328?y.\par
\par
Magtymguly, akyl ba\u351?ymdan u\u231?dy,\par
Ykbalym \u253?atypdyr, d\u246?wletim g\u246?\u231?di,\par
Pir-kazylar para ist\u228?p, gol a\u231?dy,\par
Haram e\u253?le, emma berme pulu\u328?y.\par
\par
NE\u221?LESIN\par
Dowzah ata\u351?na \u253?anyp, perwana jan ne\u253?lesin,\par
D\u252?\u351?di \u231?ille gahryna misgin ur\u253?an ne\u253?lesin?\par
De\u351?t i\u231?inde galdy\u328? \u253?al\u328?yz, dagy-umman ne\u253?lesin,\par
Sen kibi bi\u231?\u228?r\u228?ni dowzah-suzan ne\u253?lesin?\par
\par
H\u252?mmeti\u328?den a\u253?rylyp, terhos bilen \u253?yglar sen,\par
\u214?tdi \u246?mr\u252?\u328?, ne akmak, \u246?ten pasly \u231?aglar sen,\par
Bihuda a\u351?yk bolup, jan-jigeri\u328? daglar sen,\par
Seni\u328? kibi gojalary Perhat, Mejnun ne\u253?lesin.?\par
\par
Wasp e\u253?le\u253?ip \u253?ar suratyn sahawaty\u328? babynda,\par
G\u246?r\u252?pmi sen misginleri da\u253?ym eski tabynda,\par
Gazlar heman a\u253?lanyp, u\u231?ar K\u246?wser abynda,\par
Pany jahan gyrgydyr, jan-natuwan ne\u253?lesin.?\par
\par
Magtymguly, sen \u252?telgi sa\u253?\u253?at golun zar kylyp,\par
Te\u351?w\u252?\u351? bilen g\u246?zel \u246?mr\u252?\u328? \u246?t\u252?rip sen har kylyp,\par
Biwepaga g\u246?w\u252?n berip, bir mynasyp \u253?ar kylyp,\par
Akla inip aglar sen, indi pu\u351?man ne\u253?lesin.?\par
\par
P\u196?L GALMAZ\par
S\u246?z\u252?me gulak tut, pany myhmany,\par
G\u246?ws\u252?\u328? \u253?ele tutma, sende p\u228?l galmaz.\par
Behi\u351?t h\u252?\u253?ri, jan \u351?\u228?hrini\u328? gulmany,\par
Ne g\u252?ler \u253?\u252?z, ajap jugra hal galmaz.\par
\par
Akylsyz di\u253?erler uzak \u253?a\u351?ana,\par
Umydyg\u228?r iller b\u246?wr\u252?n ga\u351?ana,\par
Nesip tartyp du\u231?ar bolar \u231?a\u351?ana,\par
Barysy \u246?\u253?lener, ne gul, dul galmaz.\par
\par
G\u246?w\u252?nde islegi\u328? golu\u328?a gelmez,\par
He Hak a\u328?ar, ne-de erenler bilmez,\par
Tartar baryn zemin \u253?uwdar, u\u253?almaz,\par
Ne dagda gar, j\u252?lgesinde g\u252?l galmaz.\par
\par
Pelek golun go\u351?ar d\u252?n\u253?\u228? baryna,\par
Bagyrtlar, du\u351? geler adam zoruna,\par
G\u246?r, Isgender, Jem\u351?it d\u252?\u351?di toruna,\par
S\u252?le\u253?man wepatdyr, R\u252?stem Zal galmaz.\par
\par
Aklym pana \u253?etmez, halym zebundyr,\par
Naly\u351? \u8722? lukmam, al \u351?erabym hut hundyr,\par
Umman Je\u253?hun y\u351?ka \u253?anan Mejnundyr,\par
Ne Ne\u382?d dagy, ne Le\u253?lisi, sal galmaz.\par
\par
Magtymguly, di\u253?di\u328? herne bileni\u328?,\par
