So\u328?un sanap gutarmady\u328? \u246?leni\u328?,\par
\u221?oda \u253?iter, \u351?ol \u253?\u246?relen \u253?ol galmaz.\par
\par
HANY GEREKDIR\par
Namys-arly, berkararly illeri\u328?,\par
Bir d\u246?wletli merdan hany gerekdir.\par
Bir z\u252?nnarda gymmaty \u253?ok billeri\u328?,\par
Ajap humar-gyrmyz dony gerekdir.\par
\par
Gymmatly hy\u253?aly\u328?, taban didary\u328?,\par
Daglary\u328? dumany, \u253?eli Hazary\u328?,\par
Namysly, d\u246?wletli bir ger\u231?ek \u228?ri\u328?,\par
\u214?tg\u252?r gyljy, zor \u231?amany gerekdir.\par
\par
Magtymguly, halyn sorma \u351?ul gamy\u328?,\par
Jepasy k\u246?p, sapasy \u253?ok e\u253?\u253?amy\u328?,\par
Iki d\u252?n\u253?\u228? byradary adamy\u328?,\par
G\u246?z-guwanjy ar-imany gerekdir.\par
\par
G\u214?ZEL \u221?ARYM G\u214?R\u220?NMEZ\par
Turgul, Jebra\u253?yldan habar sora\u253?yn,\par
Ne seb\u228?pdir, g\u246?zel \u253?arym g\u246?r\u252?nmez?\par
Telmuryp gapy\u328?a g\u252?nde bara\u253?yn,\par
\u196?hti-pe\u253?man \u8722? ol ykrarym g\u246?r\u252?nmez.\par
\par
Pelek asy\u253?asyn bikarar kylmy\u351?,\par
Namysdan da\u351? d\u252?\u351?\u252?p, Hakdan u\u253?almy\u351?,\par
\u221?igitler gojalyp, goja \u253?igt bolmu\u351?,\par
\u199?yragym \u246?\u231?\u252?pdir, narym g\u246?r\u252?nmez.\par
\par
Bahyllar mert bolup, geda \u351?a bolup,\par
Mertler namart bolup, pir dinden galyp,\par
Azanlar kesilip, metjit \u253?apylyp,\par
Hakdan \u246?zge bir azarym g\u246?r\u252?nmez.\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, bu ne heka\u253?at,\par
Il bary \u171?alymdyr\u187?, tutmaz nesihat,\par
Asmandan inipdir zemine apat,\par
Isa, M\u228?ti, M\u228?lik A\u382?dar g\u246?r\u252?nmez.\par
\par
\u214?L INDI\par
Sap tutu\u351?yp, ha\u253?bat atar tilkiler,\par
Arly pele\u328?, \u246?ler bolsa\u328?, \u246?l indi.\par
Aryp bolup, mest bolupdyr telkiler,\par
Dana molla, biler bolsa\u328?, bil indi.\par
\par
\u221?ala\u328?a\u231? ge\u253?inip, a\u231?lar do\u253?updyr,\par
Karun toba e\u253?l\u228?p, p\u228?lin go\u253?updyr,\par
Nadan: \u171?Gurhan \u351?uny di\u253?er\u187?... di\u253?ipdir.\par
Gurhan, s\u246?we\u351? salar bolsa\u328?, sal indi.\par
\par
Bir s\u246?z bilen k\u246?\u253?en bagrym \u253?andyrdy\u328?,\par
Jigerden a\u253?yrdy\u328?, ba\u351?dan dyndardy\u328?,\par
\u221?\u252?z g\u246?rkezm\u228?n, ho\u351? s\u246?z bilen gandyrdy\u328?,\par
N\u228?zli \u253?arym, geler bolsa\u328?, gel indi.\par
\par
Magtymguly \u231?a\u351?yp, lala d\u246?n\u252?pdir,\par
\u221?andy teni-jany, k\u252?le d\u246?n\u252?pdir.\par
Ady il i\u231?inde gula d\u246?n\u252?pdir,\par
Hoja, se\u253?it, biler bolsa\u328?, bil indi.\par
\par
K\u214?P BOLSA\par
Akylsyzlar akyl g\u246?zl\u228?r, ze\u253?rener,\par
Akly bolan di\u253?er: \u171?Aklym k\u246?p bolsa\u187?.\par
Mert \u253?igitler gylyjyna da\u253?anar,\par
Namart tutabilmez, golda \u231?\u246?p bolsa.\par
\par
Aryp gadryn bilmez duzsuz-nadanlar,\par
M\u252?\u351?gildir a\u253?rylyp d\u252?\u351?se dendanlar,\par
Biakyl, gezegen, nadan zenanlar\par
I\u351?den jyda d\u252?\u351?er, ilde gep bolsa.\par
\par
San bardyr, hasapsyz bolan pidalar,\par
Her g\u252?n\u252?n pikir e\u253?l\u228?r \u253?\u246?ren gedalar,\par
Haznasyn dolduran berkarar \u351?alar\par
G\u252?nde bir \u246?\u253?lener, ke\u253?pi k\u246?k bolsa.\par
\par
Ni\u231?e akdy, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, sen di\u253?ip derler,\par
Barysy pu\u231? boldy, bo\u351? galdy serler,\par
\u221?\u252?z\u252?n sowup, gep aly\u351?maz \u231?yn \u228?rler,\par
Bir s\u246?\u253? bilen \u253?ag\u351?y dosty \u231?ep bolsa.\par
\par
Keramatly medrese\u253?i-agzamlar\par
\u221?apdy gapysyny, g\u246?\u231?di makamlar,\par
\u221?ara\u351?yga geler d\u252?rli tagamlar,\par
Da\u351?dan d\u246?r\u228?n ajap g\u246?rkli gap bolsa.\par
\par
Namart gorkar go\u231? \u253?igidi\u328? adyndan,\par
\u214?\u253?\u252?nde telmurar merdi\u328? badyndan,\par
Dertli gullar \u246?m\u252?r salmaz \u253?adyndan\par
Lukmanyny, kylan emi nep bolsa.\par
\par
Dert zy\u253?at bolmasa, dertli samramaz,\par
\u221?etse akly biakyllar \u253?a\u328?ramaz,\par
Misgin d\u252?\u351?en Magtymguly e\u328?remez,\par
\u221?\u252?reginden gam-gussalar dep bolsa.\par
\par
DERT NEDIR\par
Akyl, g\u246?z hem ykbal, iman d\u246?rd\u252?si,\par
Jyda galsa, derman nedir, dert nedir.\par
\u196?r \u253?igidi\u328? bolmaz \u253?\u252?zde perdesi,\par
Ykbal \u253?atsa, namart nedir, mert nedir.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y derde d\u252?\u351?er, aglar \u253?amana,\par
Namart gara g\u246?rse, geler amana,\par
Nesip e\u253?l\u228?p, m\u252?nse \u253?\u246?rg\u252?r \u231?amana,\par
Tana bilmez, ba\u351?y nedir, art nedir.\par
\par
Namart \u231?a\u351?yr, k\u252?ren ile ba\u351? bolsa,\par
A\u253?byn a\u231?ar, \u246?z ilinden da\u351? galsa,\par
Serho\u351? bolan go\u231? \u253?igide du\u351? bolsa,\par
Salar gyljyn, \u252?\u231?i nedir, d\u246?rt nedir.\par
\par
R\u252?stem Zal at aldy, atlanyp atyn,\par
Ne zy\u253?at i\u351? etdi, di\u253?i\u328?, ga\u253?ratyn,\par
Pele\u328? gazaplanyp ursa ha\u253?batyn,\par
Dura bilmez, bars nedir, gurt nedir.\par
\par
Magtymguly, a\u253?la, pelegi\u328? \u231?arhy,\par
Tanar sen \u351?ol zaman du\u351? gelen nyrhy,\par
Namardy\u328? \u253?anynda \u253?ok ili\u328? parhy,\par
P\u228?lin g\u246?zl\u228?r, mekan nedir, \u253?urt nedir.\par
\par
GAM \u214?\u221?\u220?NDE GALYP MEN\par
\u221?igitligi\u328? zory gidip dyzymdan,\par
Goja bolup, gam \u246?\u253?\u252?nde galyp men.\par
Y\u351?ky\u328? ody irip \u231?ykyp g\u246?z\u252?mden,\par
K\u252?li bilen doly bolup galyp men.\par
\par
Ba\u351?ym gamda galdy, hu\u351?um dargady,\par
Ne\u382?d dagyna \u231?ykdym, Mejnun gargady,\par
Diriler-mal, \u246?l\u252?ler-jan sargady,\par
Ba\u351?ym \u231?ykmaz sargyt alyp galyp men.\par
\par
Tapanym har\u231? etdim, so\u328?un sanmadym,\par
Y\u351?k me\u253?inden doly i\u231?dim, ganmadym,\par
Gamdan galyp, bir pygandan dynmadym,\par
Hazan uran g\u252?l dek solup galyp men.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u228?r \u253?ag\u351?ysyn il tanar,\par
A\u351?y \u8722? dahan, s\u246?z \u253?ag\u351?ysyn dil tanar,\par
Dony \u8722? g\u246?wre, \u253?eg z\u252?nnary bil tanar,\par
Aklym kesme\u253? \u8213? tana bolup galyp men.\par
\par
GALSA NE\u221?LESIN\par
Ykbal la\u253?a batyp, d\u246?wlet sowulyp,\par
Ba\u253?lar misgin bolup galsa ne\u253?lesin.\par
Pelek torna d\u252?\u351?\u252?p, \u246?m\u252?r bogulyp,\par
Gowasyn \u351?um ajal \u253?olsa ne\u253?lesin.\par
\par
\u220?m\u252?r gitse, ne gymmat bar daglarda,\par
Bir gowga tapylar \u253?ag\u351?y \u231?aglarda,\par
Gy\u351? gargy\u351?y \u253?agsa gara baglarda,\par
Bilbil pakyr g\u252?li solsa ne\u253?lesin.\par
\par
Namart gargy\u351? eder merdi\u328? \u253?a\u351?yna,\par
G\u246?rse merdi gowga geler ba\u351?yna,\par
\u196?r \u253?igidi\u328? nadan gelip ga\u351?yna,\par
Ga\u253?ta ba\u351?dan hemra bolsa ne\u253?lesin.\par
\par
\u199?\u246?lde howalanar mydam dag a\u351?an,\par
\u214?w\u252?ner, gep a\u231?ar saly garta\u351?an,\par
Zar e\u253?le\u253?ip, mag\u351?ugyna sata\u351?an,\par
N\u228?zirgenip, \u253?ar dolansa ne\u253?lesin.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?ykdy\u328? g\u246?w\u252?n \u351?\u228?hrini,\par
Tolgunyp ol \u351?amar sokdy z\u228?hrini,\par
T\u228?le\u253?i\u328?e pelek tutmaz m\u228?hrini,\par
Erse ga\u253?gy-gamdan dolsa ne\u253?lesin.\par
\par
\u221?OLUN A\u327?LAMAZ\par
Hindi jyda d\u252?\u351?se hemrasy pilden,\par
\u214?ten g\u252?n\u252?n, baran \u253?olun a\u328?lamaz.\par
Karun a\u253?ra d\u252?\u351?se garda\u351?y p\u228?lden,\par
G\u246?zi do\u253?maz, d\u252?n\u253?\u228? malyn a\u328?lamaz.\par
\par
Agsak a\u253?ra d\u252?\u351?se, aga\u231?syz galsa,\par
\u221?ol a\u328?lamaz, garry hemrasyz bolsa,\par
Mert \u253?ananda, daga azysyn salsa,\par
Gara da\u351?yn, duman, silin a\u328?lamaz.\par
\par
Gutarmaz \u246?\u328?\u252?nden ajal eseri,\par
A\u328?lamaz pa\u253?-desti, du\u351? gelse seri,\par
\u221?anar-k\u246?\u253?er adam ogly, digeri,\par
Ne \u351?e\u253?tan, ne eren p\u228?lin a\u328?lamaz.\par
\par
\u199?\u228?resiz a\u351?ykdyr, mag\u351?uk da\u351? galsa,\par
\u221?\u252?rek \u253?anyp, sokur g\u246?zden \u253?a\u351? gelse,\par
Mert \u253?ananda, Jem\u351?it o\u328?a du\u351? gelse,\par
Isgenderi, R\u252?stem Zalyn a\u328?lamaz.\par
\par
Ykbal \u253?atsa, iki dide gapylar,\par
Ha\u253?yr di\u253?p ugran \u253?oly \u253?apylar,\par
Mert g\u246?wn\u252?nde birje kemlik tapylar,\par
Salar gyljyn, sagy-solun a\u328?lamaz.\par
\par
Magtymguly, dile dessan getirdim,\par
Hesret bilen g\u252?n\u252?m-a\u253?ym \u246?t\u252?rd\u252?m,\par
Arzy-halym arzymana \u253?etirdim,\par
\u214?ter gider, a\u253?y-\u253?ylyn a\u328?lamaz.\par
\par
GALDY, NE\u221?L\u196?\u221?IN\par
Bazarym sowuldy, harydym galdy,\par
D\u252?kanym e\u253?esiz galdy, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?\par
Penasyn dargytdy, garak\u231?y doldy,\par
Bar\u231?asyn d\u252?\u253?rle\u253?ip aldy, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?\par
\par
Mertler namart boldy, namart mert boldy,\par
Gurtlar pe\u351?e boldy, pe\u351?e gurt boldy,\par
\u221?urtlar we\u253?ran boldy, zyndan \u253?urt boldy,\par
\u350?um pelek le\u351?gerin saldy, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?\par
\par
A\u351?yklardan \u246?tdi y\u351?ky\u328? h\u246?wesi,\par
Tartyldy, \u253?azyldy dowzah perdesi,\par
Dagdan a\u351?yp gyzylba\u351?y\u328? ordasy,\par
G\u246?zel ilim we\u253?ran kyldy, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?\par
\par
\u221?ar-\u253?ardan a\u253?yrdy, merdi ilinden,\par
Der\u253?any guratdy, dagy silinden,\par
Bagy \u8722? serwisinden, bilbil \u8722? g\u252?l\u252?nden,\par
Gan \u253?ygla\u253?yp, jyda boldy, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?\par
\par
Mahrum kyldy g\u246?zel g\u246?rk\u252?\u328? h\u252?n\u228?rin,\par
Ata-en\u228?\u328? aldy g\u246?w\u252?n kararyn.\par
Her g\u252?n a\u231?dy gul-gyrnagy\u328? bazaryn,\par
Namysym bazara saldy, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?\par
\par
Magtymguly, goly bagly, peri\u351?an,\par
Ajap dessanymdan go\u253?mady ny\u351?an,\par
Zyndanda oturdy pirlerimiz, i\u351?an,\par
Idegim kerwenden \u253?oldy, ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in?\par
\par
\u221?ARY\u327? \u221?AG\u350?YSYN\par
Gawuny\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn \u351?agal i\u253?r bolsa,\par
Namarda du\u351? etdi\u328?, \u253?ary\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
Hak her kime ga\u253?ry d\u246?wlet bi\u253?r bolsa,\par
Paty\u351?a bag\u351? etdi\u328? zeri\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
\par
Binamysy dertden aman e\u253?ledi\u328?,\par
Baran ja\u253?yn me\u253?lis-mekan e\u253?ledi\u328?,\par
Durna, gaz mesgenin umman e\u253?ledi\u328?,\par
Hindige bag\u351? e\u253?l\u228?p \u253?eri\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
\par
Akyl keser, g\u246?w\u252?n galkar her bapda,\par
Bars-g\u246?wheri bent e\u253?ledi\u328? mahtapda,\par
Bedewi \u8722? parsyda, dili\u328? \u8722? arapda,\par
Bagy\u351? kyldy\u328? bady-\u351?\u252?tr\u252?\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
\par
Periler o\u253?na\u253?an ajap \u231?aglarda,\par
G\u252?l, bilbil bendidir Erem baglarda,\par
Gara da\u351?ly, gudraty k\u246?p daglarda,\par
Mekan e\u253?l\u228?p go\u253?du\u328? gary\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn.\par
\par
\u350?alar aglar boldy, bagryn ba\u351? etdi\u328?,\par
Aklyn aldy\u328?, k\u246?r e\u253?ledi\u328?, l\u228?\u351? etdi\u328?,\par
Magtymguly, di\u253?, ne ajap i\u351? etdi\u328?,\par
\u221?amana du\u351? kylyp \u228?ri\u328? \u253?ag\u351?ysyn?.\par
\par
SEN DEK NAMARDY\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni ke\u351?t edip, pelek, gezip men,\par
Bir \u253?erde g\u246?rmedim sen dek namardy.\par
Der\u253?a-ummanlara d\u252?\u351?\u252?p \u253?\u252?z\u252?p men,\par
Suwlarda g\u246?rmedim sen dek namardy.\par
\par
Wepa berip, g\u246?z g\u252?ld\u252?rip durmaz sen,\par
En\u231?e k\u228?ni\u328? bardyr, birin bermez sen,\par
Adam oglun hemra kylyp \u253?\u246?rmez sen,\par
Bir \u253?urtda g\u246?rmedim sen dek namardy.\par
\par
\u214?mr\u252?m pajyn aldy\u328? bazar barma\u253?an,\par
Kimse \u246?t\u252?p gitdi hyra\u231? berme\u253?en,\par
\u214?m\u252?r ahyr bir kararda durma\u253?an\par
Panyda g\u246?rmedim sen dek namardy.\par
\par
Ba\u351?ymda bir hijran, gelge\u253? sen indi,\par
\u221?asymda o\u253?na\u253?yp, g\u252?lge\u253? sen indi,\par
Magtymguly di\u253?er, bilge\u253? sen indi,\par
Hi\u231? \u253?erde g\u246?rmedim sen dek namardy.\par
\par
SOWRUP GIDIPDIR\par
Bu pany d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de kim bina e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Golunda baryny sowrup gidipdir.\par
En\u231?elere pelek, g\u246?r, g\u252?n\u228? e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Janyn jeset bilen gowrup gidipdir.\par
\par
Ni\u231?eleri\u328? \u246?mr\u252?n ol per\u253?at e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Ni\u231?eleri\u328?, g\u246?r\u252?\u328?, \u246?mr\u252?n mat e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Ni\u231?eleri pany jahan \u351?at e\u253?l\u228?p,\par
Ni\u231?e \u351?irin jany urup gidipdir.\par
\par
Kimler d\u246?wlet bilen saldy minara,\par
Minara \u252?st\u252?nde d\u252?\u351?\u252?pdir nara,\par
Kimi\u328? g\u246?zi hums boldy bir hara,\par
Kimlere, g\u246?r, bedew berip gidipdir.\par
\par
Kimseleri\u328? z\u228?her e\u253?l\u228?p naharyn,\par
En\u231?eleri\u328? sy\u253?a kylypdyr aryn,\par
Kimse g\u246?r\u252?p gelipmi\u351?in ahyryn,\par
Emma zemin jeset sorup gidipdir.\par
\par
Kimse g\u252?lse, kimler \u253?a\u351?lar g\u246?zlerin,\par
Kimler misgin, kim han e\u253?l\u228?r \u246?zlerin,\par
Magtymguly, bahyl bolman, s\u246?zlerin,\par
Tara\u351?lap, her kanda urup gidipdir.\par
\par
ELIP KADDY\u327? DAL OLAR\par
Adam ogly, bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de gezer sen,\par
Bir g\u252?n seni\u328? elip kaddy\u328? dal olar.\par
Gapyl bolma, dogry \u253?oldan azar sen,\par
Bilbil kibi sa\u253?ran dili\u328? lal olar.\par
\par
Ahyrzaman olsa, pitneler tursa,\par
Zalymlar \u253?amanlyk mejlisin gursa,\par
Paty\u351?alar ri\u351?wet di\u253?ip dem ursa,\par
Pakyrlara g\u252?n-nafaga hal olar.\par
\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman, yzzat kylar ba\u253?lara,\par
Pakyr-u binowa galar wa\u253?lara,\par
Her \u253?igit kim, garyp d\u252?\u351?se ja\u253?lara,\par
Hesret \u231?eker, her bir mahy sal olar.\par
\par
Her kimse \u351?erigat \u253?olun bilmese,\par
Alymlary\u328? s\u246?z\u252?n g\u246?ze almasa,\par
Kyrk \u253?a\u351?ynda ki\u351?i toba kylmasa,\par
Onu\u328? i\u351?i hile, mekir, al olar.\par
\par
Her \u253?igit kim, garyp d\u252?\u351?se watandan,\par
Habar sorar her bir \u253?oldan \u246?tenden,\par
Telmuryban hajat dil\u228?r \u253?etenden,\par
Hajaty bitmese, kyl-u kal olar.\par
\par
Gel, e\u253?, dostum, \u231?ekme ga\u253?gy-gamy sen,\par
Akdyrmagyl g\u246?zleri\u328?den nemi sen,\par
Bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de ganymat bil demi sen,\par
Ga\u253?gy \u231?ekse, \u253?igit ki\u351?i \u231?al olar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, nesihatlar d\u252?zer sen,\par
Hala\u253?ygy\u328? \u253?\u252?rek bagryn ezer sen,\par
Lekin, \u246?z\u252?\u328? dogry \u253?oldan azar sen,\par
R\u252?stem olan bir g\u252?n piri-Zal olar.\par
\par
IL GE\u199?ER\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, pany-jahan i\u231?inde,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y \u246?ner, \u253?aman \u246?ner, il ge\u231?er.\par
Ajap s\u246?zl\u228?p, pena dahan i\u231?inde,\par
Dendan d\u252?\u351?er, gymmat d\u252?\u351?er, dil ge\u231?er.\par
\par
Biz gezen me\u253?danlar, aja\u253?yp ja\u253?lar,\par
Binasy tutulan uly sara\u253?lar,\par
D\u246?wr a\u253?lanyp, gelip-gider g\u252?n-a\u253?lar,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman, nowruz, gy\u351?y \u253?yl ge\u231?er.\par
\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? gelip, bar g\u246?rd\u252?gi\u328? pygandyr,\par
Bu g\u252?n \u8213? diri, erte bolsa g\u252?mandyr,\par
Hazana gurulan pany-jahandyr,\par
\u221?igitler gojalyp, \u246?mri-sal ge\u231?er.\par
\par
Pelek pygany\u328?y g\u246?z\u252?ne almaz,\par
Ol derdi\u328?e Lukman dermany bolmaz,\par
\u221?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman, geda-\u351?ahy sylamaz,\par
Gara g\u246?z, galam ga\u351?, in\u231?e bil ge\u231?er.\par
\par
Kimse tutup gola saldy jahany,\par
G\u246?r, bent edip go\u253?dy ol S\u252?le\u253?many,\par
Bagy hazan urar, solar re\u253?hany,\par
Bilbil \u253?esir d\u252?\u351?er, serwi, g\u252?l ge\u231?er.\par
\par
Pelek, sen hem bir dem aman e\u253?legil,\par
Biz nadan \u253?esire d\u246?wran e\u253?legil,\par
Magtymguly, arma, dessan e\u253?legil,\par
Akyl-hu\u351? da\u351? d\u252?\u351?er, senden dil ge\u231?er.\par
\par
MERT KYLDY\u327?\par
\u221?a, \u221?aradan, arzym bardyr alny\u328?a,\par
Merdi-namart, namartlary mert kyldy\u328?.\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? ykbalyny tutup golu\u328?a,\par
Her tilkiden gapla\u328? kyldy\u328?, gurt kyldy\u328?.\par
\par
Kimse bazar tutup girdi d\u252?kana,\par
Kims\u228?ni getirmez pany jahana,\par
Bag i\u231?inde kimi go\u253?du\u328? erkana?\par
Dag i\u231?inde men misgine \u253?urt kyldy\u328?.\par
\par
Kim namaz okamaz, kim roza tutmaz,\par
Kimse p\u228?lin agtar, gijesi \u253?atmaz,\par
Kimse s\u246?zi adam janyna batmaz,\par
Kimseleri\u328? s\u246?z\u252?n kesapat kyldy\u328?.\par
\par
Adam ogly \u253?yglar, \u253?\u252?rekde ahy,\par
Di\u328?lemez garda\u351?y, Kadyr Hudahy,\par
Kimselere watan kyldy\u328? dowzahy,\par
Kimselere behi\u351?t m\u252?rewwet kyldy\u328?.\par
\par
Magtymguly di\u253?er derdi\u328? halyny,\par
Soran bolmaz meni\u328? bu ahwalymy,\par
Kimseleri\u328? toprak kylyp malyny,\par
En\u231?eler topragyn zeberjet kyldy\u328?.\par
\par
GALMAZ-A\par
G\u246?rsem, e\u253?, dilber, jemaly\u328?, ygty\u253?arym galmaz-a,\par
G\u246?rmez ersem bir zaman, sabr-u kararym galmaz-a.\par
Wasly\u328? umydyna bir dem ygtybarym galmaz-a,\par
Bolmasa umydy-wasly\u328?, hi\u231? mydarym galmaz-a.\par
\par
Ger ena\u253?at bolmasa Senden, a\u231?ylmaz \u253?olumyz,\par
Tutgun olar da\u253?yma, bolmaz k\u252?\u351?at ykbalymyz,\par
Ejz ile bimar olup, a\u351?ufta bolgan halymyz,\par
Rehm edip, Sen sormasa\u328?, bir a\u253?ry \u253?arym galmaz-a.\par
\par
Hasrat i\u231?re galmy\u351?am, ejiz boluban mande men,\par
Parh ede bilmen \u246?z\u252?m e\u253?wanda \u253?a we\u253?randa men.\par
Kimse p\u228?hm etmez bu derdim, bolmu\u351?am dermende men,\par
Sanyram \u246?lmezden owwal tende janym galmaz-a.\par
\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? ki be\u253?tul-hazan men, \u351?at gelen gamn\u228?k ola,\par
T\u228? ha\u253?aty-pany\u253?am, synam Seni\u328? \u231?\u252?n \u231?\u228?k ola,\par
Suratym nis\u253?andadyr, ustuhanym h\u228?k ola,\par
T\u228? olyn\u231?a rozy-mag\u351?ar, ahy-zarym galmaz-a.\par
\par
Ger\u231?e bu Magtymgulydyr ma\u253?yly-nebsi-howa,\par
Hak erer Sen birligi\u328?, \u231?\u252?n hajatym kylgyl rowa,\par
Hajatym Senden rowa bolmas erse ger, muddaga,\par
Be\u253?le m\u228?limdir ki, hi\u231? bir gamgusarym galmaz-a.\par
\par
\u350?ALYK BILE\par
De\u328? bolar di\u253?p sa\u253?magyl, i\u351?i\u328? bet efgallyk bile,\par
Hi\u231? ha\u231?an de\u328? bolmaga\u253? e\u351?ek bedew \u351?alyk bile.\par
Garda\u351? olma hyz-haramy, pitne-ryswalyk bile,\par
Ba\u351?y\u328?y gowga\u253?a salma maly-d\u252?n\u253?\u228?lik bile,\par
Tur, s\u228?her \u253?at e\u253?le Haky, \u253?ygla tenhalyk bile.\par
\par
Bardy Turu\u328? dagyna, Hak birle boldy ol Kelim,\par
\u214?tdi anlar, galdy d\u252?n\u253?\u228?, ge\u231?di e\u253?\u253?amul-kadym,\par
\u221?atsa \u253?er boldy d\u252?\u351?ek, \u246?rt\u252?njesi par\u231?a kilim,\par
Bakdy go\u253?nun \u350?uga\u253?by\u328? \u253?edi \u253?yl Musa Kelim,\par
\u199?\u246?lde gezdi da\u253?yma raz a\u253?dy\u351?yp Halyk bile.\par
\par
E\u253?, aty \u253?\u252?wr\u252?k \u253?igit, \u246?zi go\u231?ak, g\u252?lg\u252?n kaba,\par
Munda jebr eden ki\u351?i, ol g\u252?nde bolga\u253? rusy\u253?a,\par
Her ki\u351?i zor e\u253?le\u253?ip, alsa bu g\u252?n, berge\u253? saba,\par
Ol weliler serweri Soltan We\u253?is dek \u246?wl\u252?\u253?\u228?,\par
D\u252?\u351?egi, \u246?rt\u252?njesi boldy gara halyk bile.\par
\par
\u221?akup ogly ol \u221?usuby\u328? k\u228?kilinden tutdular,\par
Urdular, aglatdylar \u171?Gurt i\u253?di\u187? di\u253?ip satdylar,\par
Ni\u231?e \u253?yl E\u253?\u253?up pygamber tenni gurt i\u253?p \u253?atdylar,\par
El-a\u253?agyn bagla\u253?yp, \u221?unusy der\u253?a atdylar,\par
Ni\u231?e wagt tagat \u231?ekip, \u171?Huw!\u187? di\u253?di bir balyk bile.\par
\par
Sen ni\u231?ik, Magtymguly, \u253?amanlygy\u328? unutmady\u328?,\par
G\u228?hi-g\u228?hi zalym oldu\u328?, g\u246?rgeni\u328?den ga\u253?tmady\u328?,\par
G\u228?hi-g\u228?hi sopy boldu\u328?, hi\u231? haramdan datmady\u328?,\par
Bilmedim, sen ha\u253?sy boldu\u328?, belli bir i\u351? tutmady\u328?,\par
Ne sypag\u228?rlik bile boldu\u328?, ne mollalyk bile.\par
\par
GALMAGALY NE\u221?LEREM\par
\u196?hli-Hak bolsam, di\u253?er men: \u171?\u214?zge haly ne\u253?lerem\u187?,\par
Bu sowulmaz derdi, sansyz galmagaly ne\u253?lerem.\par
Owwaly zowky-surur, hasratly maly ne\u253?lerem,\par
Ahyry m\u246?wt-u gubur, bu bo\u351? hy\u253?aly ne\u253?lerem,\par
Bolmu\u351?am men zowk \u228?hli, esbap-melaly ne\u253?lerem.\par
\par
D\u252?\u351?di y\u351?ky\u328? ata\u351?yga, gyl\u231?a janym k\u246?\u253?di, \u253?ar,\par
Gury jismim odun e\u253?l\u228?p oda \u253?akmakda ne bar,\par
Gamda k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m bikarardyr, ba\u351?da derdim set hezar,\par
Onu\u328? \u252?\u231?in d\u228?hr era bir k\u246?\u351?e kyldym ygty\u253?ar,\par
Ygty\u253?arym \u253?ok turur, je\u328?\u328?i-jedeli ne\u253?lerem.\par
\par
G\u246?rn\u252?\u351?i\u328? e\u351?retnema, g\u246?rk\u252?\u328? \u252?\u231?in k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m g\u252?daz,\par
Gysga \u8722? ykbalym goly, dost, dameni-wasly\u328? \u8722? deraz,\par
P\u252?r hatar, ol \u253?ol yrak, y\u351?ky\u328? geran, kuwwatym az,\par
D\u252?\u351?m\u252?\u351?em bir m\u252?\u351?gile, sen-sen bu i\u351?e \u231?\u228?resaz,\par
Iltifaty\u328? imdi kyl, \u246?tgen mahaly ne\u253?lerem.\par
\par
Her zaman, Magtymguly, halk i\u231?re gezme lap edip,\par
Sakla gybatdan dili\u328?, ugrunda gez ynsap edip,\par
El uzatma k\u246?p pisada, \u253?\u246?r Hudadan howp edip,\par
Sopulyk esbaby ho\u351?dur, ge\u253? i\u231?i\u328?i sap edip,\par
Bolsa m\u246?\u253?-m\u246?jek i\u231?im, bu eski \u351?aly ne\u253?lerem.\par
\par
D\u214?NDI D\u214?W\u220?R \u221?AMANA\par
E\u253?, a\u351?yklar, aglar men, geldi, ge\u231?di zamana,\par
\u221?ag\u351?a gadyr bolma\u253?yn, d\u246?ndi d\u246?w\u252?r \u253?amana.\par
\u221?aman aldy jahany, d\u246?nmez dili imana,\par
K\u246?p pakyrlar agla\u351?yp, geler ondan amana,\par
Ist\u228?ri bar az wagtdan derhem bola zamana.\par
\par
Ne sapaly g\u252?nm\u252?\u351?dik, de\u328?-du\u351? bile ba\u351? go\u351?man,\par
Ba\u351?y\u328? aldy\u328? garyldy\u328?, ne dost bildi\u328?, ne du\u351?man,\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, sud etmez imdi etse\u328? m\u252?\u328? pu\u351?man,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?sine dola\u351?man, ogul-gyza bula\u351?man,\par
Ne h\u246?zirli g\u252?nm\u252?\u351?dik bolup gitsek diwana.\par
\par
D\u252?\u351?megin ham hy\u253?ala - d\u252?n\u253?\u228? gelen \u246?lmezler,\par
Gelen ge\u231?er d\u252?n\u253?\u228?den, biri aman galmazlar,\par
Janlar \u231?ekip \u231?agyrsam, dogry \u253?ola gelmezler,\par
Her ne bolsa \u253?uwdarlar, halal, haram bilmezler,\par
Di\u253?rler: Hakdyr Muhammet, u\u253?updyrmyz Gurhana!.\par
\par
D\u246?wran, ni\u231?ik d\u246?wran sen, garyp aglar, il dynmaz,\par
Zulmy artar zalymy\u328?, hi\u231? k\u246?\u328?l\u252?ne rehm inmez.\par
Jahany \u253?akdy gitdi, \u253?amany\u328? ody s\u246?nmez,\par
Bir Muhammet hatyrna \u253?er \u253?arylmaz, g\u246?k inmez,\par
\u199?arh guwanyr bu i\u351?e, bolmaz ahyrzamana.\par
\par
Gapyl galdym, \u253?aranlar, \u246?z-\u246?z\u252?mden ri\u351?tim \u253?ok,\par
Hakdan ga\u253?ry hi\u231? \u253?erde penahym \u253?ok, pu\u351?tum \u253?ok,\par
Pikir bahryna girdim, \u253?elkenim \u253?ok, ki\u351?tim \u253?ok,\par
Magtymguly, men mundan \u231?ykar \u253?a\u328?lyg de\u351?tim \u253?ok.\par
Elim bersem tutan \u253?ok, d\u252?\u351?d\u252?m d\u252?\u253?ps\u252?z ummana.\par
\par
\u214?LMESDEN BURUN\par
Saglygy\u328? gadryny bilgil, hassa bolmasdan burun,\par
Hassalyk \u351?\u252?kr\u252?ni kylgyl, t\u228?ki \u246?lmesden burun.\par
D\u252?z \u253?eri\u328? gadryny bilgil, der\u253?a dolmasdan burun,\par
G\u228?mide h\u252?\u351?g\u228?r oturgyl, girdaba gelmesden burun,\par
\u221?a\u351?lygy\u328? gadryny bilgil, t\u228? ulalmasdan burun.\par
\par
Ulaldy\u328? - k\u246?\u328?l\u252?\u328?dedir \u253?alan jahany\u328? s\u246?\u253?g\u252?si,\par
G\u246?zleri\u328? g\u246?zel g\u246?r\u252?p, seni g\u252?n\u228?he go\u253?gusy,\par
Dilleri\u328? gybat kesip, lap-\u253?alan s\u246?zler a\u253?gysy,\par
Hatyry\u328? \u253?\u252?z-m\u252?\u328? peri\u351?an, kethudalyk ga\u253?gysy,\par
Ne ajap ho\u351? hal idi\u328?, \u246?z\u252?\u328?i bilmesden burun.\par
\par
\u221?aradan \u253?ady\u328?dadyr, ba\u351?y\u328? \u253?owuz halda eken,\par
\u214?tse \u253?\u252?z \u253?yl, \u253?ada d\u252?\u351?mez, belli ho\u351? halda eken,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328?i bihuda tutma, pursaty\u328? elde eken,\par
Degse bir bady-hazan, soldyr seni g\u252?lde eken,\par
G\u252?lni \u253?ady\u328?dan \u231?ykarma, t\u228?ki solmasdan burun.\par
\par
Akly-hu\u351?u\u328?a \u253?eti\u351?di\u328?, e\u253?ledi\u328? se\u253?rany sen,\par
Ist\u228?r idi\u328? jem edem, bu k\u252?ll\u252?h\u252?m E\u253?rany sen,\par
I\u253?medi\u328? bir dem parahat Ta\u328?ry beren nany sen,\par
He\u253?, habary\u328? barmydyr, bu jahany\u328? myhmany sen,\par
Azygy\u328? ta\u253?\u253?ary kyl, kerwen \u231?ekilmesden burun.\par
\par
Galmamy\u351? bu k\u246?ne d\u252?n\u253?\u228? R\u252?stem ile Zaly\u328?a,\par
Garra bolma iki g\u252?nl\u252?k i\u253?gu-i\u231?gu, maly\u328?a,\par
Hakykat arypy g\u246?r, atlasy berdi \u351?aly\u328?a,\par
Tur s\u228?her, Magtymguly, \u253?ygla bu g\u252?n \u246?z haly\u328?a,\par
Ta\u328?la, ol mag\u351?ar g\u252?ni derl\u228?p u\u253?almasdan burun.\par
\par
S\u220?LE\u221?MAN NE\u221?LESIN\par
Jan \u351?\u228?hrine d\u252?\u351?di tala\u328?, bu \u253?owuz jan ne\u253?lesin,\par
\u214?tdi \u246?mri bipermandyr, ol S\u252?le\u253?man ne\u253?lesin.\par
Haky\u328? beren bu derdine, di\u253?i\u328?, Lukman ne\u253?lesin,\par
\u214?t\u252?p baran \u246?mr\u252?me agy-gir\u253?an ne\u253?lesin,\par
Y\u351?k odundan k\u252?l bolup men, dowzah-suzan ne\u253?lesin.\par
\par
Sa\u253?\u253?at bolup girdi pelek, ka\u253?da jan pynhan kyla\u253?,\par
Kimlere derdimi a\u253?dyp, kimlere hemra bola\u253?,\par
Kimler bilen d\u246?w\u252?\u351? kylyp, kimlere gyly\u231? sala\u253?,\par
Derdim \u228?\u351?g\u228?r kyla bilm\u228?n, il-g\u252?n\u252?mden u\u253?ala\u253?,\par
Meni\u328? kibi bir awara pelek \u8722? zyndan ne\u253?lesin.\par
\par
Ga\u253?ybana a\u351?yk bolup, y\u351?ky bilen \u253?anaram,\par
Di\u253?erler d\u246?wlet murgy men hijrana gonaram,\par
Le\u253?li \u253?arym bolmasa hem, \u246?z\u252?m Mejnun sanaram,\par
G\u252?nde bir wagt naly\u351? e\u253?l\u228?p, y\u351?ky-me\u253?den ganaram,\par
Meni\u328? kibi bir serho\u351?y uly Suhan ne\u253?lesin.\par
\par
\u350?anyna dessan d\u252?z\u252?p men y\u351?kyny\u328? mekanyda,\par
K\u252?lli a\u351?yk sergerdandyr ol ata\u351? ha\u253?ranyda,\par
Men kibi bir Mejnuny g\u246?rmez pany e\u253?wanyda,\par
Men kibi bir misgin geda \u253?okdur Nuh zamanyda,\par
Y\u351?k ata\u351?yna geda men, d\u246?wleti k\u228?n ne\u253?lesin.\par
\par
A\u253?dadyr Magtymguly, a\u253?yp g\u246?rm\u228?\u328?, illerim,\par
G\u246?wn\u252?m ra\u253?yna garaman, \u253?a\u328?ra\u253?ypdyr dillerim,\par
Gojalygy\u328? pasly bilen nuna d\u246?nm\u252?\u351? billerim,\par
Bilbilleri \u253?esir kylmy\u351? bag i\u231?inde g\u252?llerim,\par
Ger ki halas e\u253?lemesem, pakyr bagban ne\u253?lesin.\par
\par
BILMEZMI\u327?\par
Galam alyp, namany g\u246?nderdigim bilmezmi\u328??\par
Efsun urup, h\u252?th\u252?ti inderdigim bilmezmi\u328??\par
Ar\u351? \u252?st\u252?ne galdyryp, m\u252?nd\u252?rdigim bilmezmi\u328??\par
D\u246?rt gije, \u252?\u231? g\u252?n aglap, di\u328?dirdigim bilmezmi\u328??\par
E\u351?ek m\u252?n\u252?p Isa dek, \u253?eldirdigim bilmezmi\u328??\par
\par
Mejnun kibi s\u228?hrada \u253?ygla\u253?-\u253?ygla\u253? gezdigim,\par
Warka kimin Gul\u351?adan \u246?l\u252?p, umyt \u252?zd\u252?gim,\par
Jo\u351?gun berip y\u351?k ody, ga\u253?nap-ga\u253?nap gyzdygym,\par
G\u246?z\u252?m \u253?a\u351?yn merjen de\u253? d\u252?z\u252?m-d\u252?z\u252?m d\u252?zd\u252?gim,\par
\u350?ibli kimin bir dagy \u253?andyrdygym bilmezmi\u328??\par
\par
H\u252?th\u252?t kimin Pere\u328?den \u199?yn-Ma\u231?yna bardygym,\par
Bag i\u231?inde Bylkysy\u328? sa\u231?yn a\u231?yp g\u246?rd\u252?gim,\par
S\u252?le\u253?many\u328? tagtyndan s\u246?zl\u228?p habar berdigim,\par
Gu\u351? gonsun di\u253?p ba\u351?yma bilbil he\u328?in gurdugym,\par
\u199?ar\u351?enbe g\u252?n \u231?\u228?\u351?t wagty gondurdygym bilmezmi\u328??\par
\par
Surahy\u328? arkasynda Mejnun gurdy jadyny,\par
\u171?Bismilla\u187? di\u253?p ba\u351?lady, \u231?agyrdy ussadyny.\par
Hakdan ga\u253?ry bir kimse e\u351?itmedi dadyny,\par
Kyrk a\u351?yk nagra \u231?ekip, \u351?ugla urdy oduny,\par
G\u246?z\u253?a\u351?ymdan suw alyp, s\u246?nd\u252?rdigim bilmezmi\u328??\par
\par
\u350?irwan hany\u328? s\u246?wdasy ne aja\u253?yp s\u246?wdadyr,\par
Gyldan bu \u253?an agdyrsa, ky\u253?amat g\u252?n ryswadyr,\par
\u221?\u252?z \u253?igrimi sap gurlup, her sapda m\u252?\u328? gowgadyr,\par
A\u351?yklyk bir jo\u351?gunlyk, akmaz u\u253?gun der\u253?adyr,\par
Bir jurgadan kyrk a\u351?yk gandyrdygym bilmezmi\u328??\par
\par
\u221?etilmemi\u351? \u351?unkarym, gamy\u351? ganat ak t\u252?rpek,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228? meni ta\u253?dyrdy, bir \u253?anym etdi gurpak,\par
Pelek alba\u253?yn bular, tartar, gan go\u253?maz torpak,\par
Her tikenden \u253?\u252?z gussa, her kyrk g\u252?lden bir \u253?arpak,\par
Dagy-da\u351?y elenip, \u246?nd\u252?rdigim bilmezmi\u328??\par
\par
Magtymguly, a\u253?yd\u253?ar, dokuz pelek Z\u246?hresi,\par
\u221?edi \u253?yldyz garda\u351?y, A\u253?y\u328?, G\u252?n\u252?\u328? parasy,\par
Nury-did\u228?m \u253?agtysy ak g\u246?z\u252?mi\u328? garasy,\par
Aby-Zemzem \u231?e\u351?mesi, Safa, Merwe arasy,\par
S\u252?le\u253?man dek \u228?hdimi syndyrdygym bilmezmi\u328??\par
\par
K\u214?\u327?L\u220?M\par
O\u253?an haby-gaflatdan, ajalsyz \u246?len k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m,\par
Umyt \u252?z\u252?p \u228?lemden, dergahdan dilen, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m.\par
Mert gerekdir almaga bu garyp galan, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m,\par
D\u252?\u253?ps\u252?z der\u253?a\u253?a d\u252?\u351?di g\u246?renne g\u252?len k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m,\par
Jan pany, jahan pany, kepene \u231?olan, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m,\par
S\u246?z bilen i\u231?in egser, gabz olup, dolan k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m.\par
\par
Alymlar s\u246?z\u252?n di\u328?le, nesihatyn al-g\u246?ter,\par
Tur, Haky\u328? dergahyna mynajat kyl, gol g\u246?ter,\par
Ry\u253?azaty\u328? \u253?\u252?k\u252?ni arkan \u253?\u252?p\u252?n sal g\u246?ter,\par
Bu i\u351? merdi\u328? i\u351?idir, merdana dur, gal, g\u246?ter,\par
K\u228?mil a\u253?agna ba\u351? go\u253?, \u253?alan\u231?ydan el g\u246?ter,\par
Toba kylyp, bir piri\u328? topragna bulan, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m.\par
\par
Y\u351?kym bardyr Mejnundan altmy\u351? esse zy\u253?ada,\par
Kyrk \u253?yl kuwwatym bardyr ders a\u253?dara Perhada\par
\u221?\u252?regim \u253?akyp oda, Hojama barsam dada,\par
Kerem der\u253?asy jo\u351?up, \u253?etirge\u253?mi myrada,\par
Galsa k\u246?\u328?\u252?l tapylmaz, \u231?yksa bu jan d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de.\par
Mert gerekdir almaga bu garyp galan k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m.\par
\par
S\u228?her turup, doga kyl, \u171?\u196?min!\u187? di\u253?sin peri\u351?de,\par
Ne bardyr gapyl \u253?atyp, bihuda otury\u351?da,\par
M\u252?lki-jahan tutdurmaz e\u253?lese\u328? m\u252?\u328? seri\u351?de,\par
Abdal \u246?rt\u252?sin ge\u253?ip, git diwana gary\u351?-da,\par
\u221?ogsa galar sen tenha serge\u351?te-\u253?u gamge\u351?de,\par
A\u253?gan s\u246?z\u252?\u328?e pygly\u328? bolmasyn \u253?alan, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m.\par
\par
Magtymguly, no\u351? etdim gam badasyn iki tas,\par
\u220?\u231? i\u231?ere ragbat \u253?ok, \u231?\u252?n jandan boldum halas,\par
Serimde sansyz s\u246?wda, i\u231?de waswasul-hannas,\par
Geli\u328?, bir tedbir e\u253?l\u228?\u328?, bu derde e\u253?\u253?\u252?hannas,\par
Dyz \u231?\u246?k\u252?p dem ursalar Isa, Hydyr hem Yl\u253?as,\par
Galynmaz, zinde bolmaz, hut murda bolan k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m.\par
\par
DUMAN PE\u221?DA\par
Gelse nowruz \u228?leme, re\u328? kylar jahan pe\u253?da,\par
Ebrler owaz urup, dag kylar duman pe\u253?da.\par
Bijanlar jana gelip, a\u231?arlar dahan pe\u253?da,\par
G\u246?germedik gy\u253?alar, g\u246?gerip rowan pe\u253?da,\par
Ederler ha\u253?wanata hem sud-u zy\u253?an pe\u253?da,\par
\u221?er \u253?\u252?z\u252?nde \u253?a\u253?ylyp, \u253?\u246?rirler nahan pe\u253?da,\par
Wabeste dahan gu\u351?lar kylarlar zyban pe\u253?da.\par
\par
\u199?\u246?l tarapyn berk edip, der a\u231?ar suwa har\u231?e\u328?,\par
Zemin sebzewar olup, teninden a\u253?rylar ze\u328?,\par
J\u252?nbendeler mest olup, g\u246?\u253?\u228? i\u231?mi\u351? arak, be\u328?,\par
Her e\u351?\u253?any\u328? \u246?z\u252?ne \u246?z owazy bolar ge\u328?,\par
Sebze i\u231?re sandywa\u231? \u253?\u252?z dilde kylar \u228?he\u328?,\par
Zemin hazarpu\u351? olup, g\u252?l bitirmi\u351? re\u328?be-re\u328?,\par
Hyruja gelip \u228?lem, kylarlar pygan pe\u253?da.\par
\par
Surud-u seda birle, jahan \u253?\u252?zi abatdyr,\par
Olma suruda magrur, pa\u253?anasy bibatdyr,\par
Hak y\u351?kynda zinde jan, bili\u328?, baky ha\u253?atdyr,\par
Her tende y\u351?k olmasa, rozy-ezel mematdyr,\par
\u221?az \u246?tin\u231?\u228? \u253?er-u g\u246?k, g\u252?nden-g\u252?ne zy\u253?atdyr,\par
Bir ha\u351?ry-ky\u253?amatdyr, bir \u253?owmy-arasatdyr,\par
D\u228?hr i\u231?re bolar her dem, jahan i\u231?re jan pe\u253?da.\par
\par
Zerbaba zowkun olma, baka \u253?okdur d\u246?wletde,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328?i bada berme, sen bu daryl-m\u228?hnetde,\par
\u221?eter sa\u328?a ir-u gi\u231?, ne \u253?azylsa kysmatda,\par
Jany\u328?a jepa e\u253?l\u228?p, mun\u231?a gezme hasratda,\par
Sowap \u253?ag\u351?y amalda \u253?a jud \u253?ag\u351?y ni\u253?etde,\par
\u196?lem bar\u231?a hyzmatda, adam \u253?atyp gaflatda,\par
Hasyly\u328? ata\u351? bolga\u253?, e\u253?lese\u328? \u253?aman pe\u253?da.\par
\par
Magtymguly, \u253?yglar men bu bagty-sy\u253?ahymdan,\par
Gorkaram jan apaty, el-a\u253?ak g\u252?w\u228?himden,\par
Umydym hasyl olmaz, bu \u246?mri-tebahymdan,\par
Jan k\u246?\u253?di jeset i\u231?re bu ata\u351?y-ahymdan,\par
Golum sunup, dil\u228?r men hajatym Allahymdan,\par
Bende men, umydym k\u246?p ol keremli \u350?ahymdan,\par
E\u253?lege\u253? arasatda g\u252?l kibi iman pe\u253?da.\par
\par
NAZAR E\u221?LE\par
Ten kapasna giriftar, gel, jana nazar e\u253?le,\par
Bak, k\u246?\u328?\u252?l g\u246?zg\u252?sine, janana nazar e\u253?le.\par
Ybrat g\u246?z\u252?ni a\u231?yp, jahana nazar e\u253?le,\par
Iki g\u228?mi tutmagyn, bir \u253?ana nazar e\u253?le,\par
Hi\u231? kime baka bermez, d\u246?wrana nazar e\u253?le,\par
D\u246?wranyna da\u253?anan ynsana nazar e\u253?le,\par
Bu gonup-g\u246?\u231?\u252?p baran kerwana nazar e\u253?le.\par
\par
Bu d\u246?wran i\u231?re k\u246?\u328?\u252?l gu\u351?lary e\u253?l\u228?r perwaz,\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? murgy-s\u228?herdir, \u351?eb suhan e\u253?l\u228?r agaz,\par
Bag i\u231?re bilbil olup, okar nagma hezar saz,\par
Huda\u253?a toba e\u253?l\u228?p, derg\u228?hi\u328?e d\u246?nd\u252?m baz,\par
\u214?m\u252?r az, d\u246?wran deraz, ne roza bar, ne namaz,\par
O\u253?an haby-gaflatdan, ha\u351?ra me\u328?z\u228?r pasly-\u253?az,\par
\u196?lem ne tesbih okar, her \u253?ana nazar e\u253?le.\par
\par
\u214?lmes men di\u253?p d\u252?\u351?mesin, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?\u328? bu g\u252?man i\u231?re,\par
\u214?mre \u253?okdur ygtybar, \u246?teg\u231?i zaman i\u231?re,\par
Ajal go\u253?mu\u351? ok-kezin, kiri\u351?e keman i\u231?re,\par
Bend\u228?ge ne armandyr, jan berse iman i\u231?re,\par
S\u246?zle, s\u246?z\u252?\u328? \u253?a\u253?ylsyn bu \u253?ag\u351?y-\u253?aman i\u231?re,\par
Az \u246?mre agyr i\u351?ler gurup sen jahan i\u231?re,\par
Mukym i\u351?ini tutan myhmana nazar e\u253?le.\par
\par
Ne ho\u351? g\u252?nd\u252?r a\u351?yga hylwat \u253?ara ula\u351?mak,\par
Hal-ahwalyn sora\u351?yp, gol bo\u253?una saly\u351?mak,\par
Mag\u351?ary\u328? ne\u351?ri \u253?a\u328?lyg ten, jan kimin bulu\u351?mak,\par
Bir-bire derdin d\u246?k\u252?p, serg\u252?ze\u351?tin kyly\u351?mak,\par
Tow berilen ri\u351?te de\u253? \u231?yrma\u351?yban-\u231?ola\u351?mak,\par
Dostlar ne m\u252?\u351?gil i\u351?dir, gowu\u351?yp, a\u253?ryly\u351?mak,\par
Wysala magrur olma, hijrana nazar e\u253?le.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?zleme\u253? go\u253?maz durmaga derdi\u328?,\par
\u221?alan\u231?yda \u253?a\u253?lanyp, altmy\u351? \u253?ana el gerdi\u328?,\par
Panyny baky bildi\u328?, \u253?eldi\u328? \u8722? \u246?sd\u252?\u328?, \u253?\u252?w\u252?rdi\u328?,\par
Dostu\u328?a azar berdi\u328?, du\u351?mana \u253?\u252?z \u246?w\u252?rdi\u328?,\par
Bildi\u328? ki biwepadyr, bahasy \u253?ok bu \u253?urdu\u328?,\par
Otuz d\u246?rt \u253?a\u351?a geldi\u328?, bu jahanda ne g\u246?rd\u252?\u328?,\par
Gurhana gulak go\u253?up, permana nazar e\u253?le.\par
\par
SEDA BOLDUM\par
Sandywajy-sermestem, bergimden jyda boldum,\par
Bergimi hazan \u231?aldy, bisowt-u seda boldum.\par
Bir g\u252?l\u231?ehre \u253?olunda bihuda pida boldum,\par
Bet i\u351?lere ba\u253? boldum, ha\u253?r i\u351?e geda boldum,\par
Pyrkat, waslat, her ne ki - aslyn ez Huda bildim,\par
Bar\u231?any bidar g\u246?rd\u252?m, \u246?z\u252?m u\u253?kuda bildim,\par
D\u252?n\u253?\u228?ge dura gelen, eglenme\u253? gid\u228? bildim,\par
I\u253?enim awy sandym, ge\u253?enim reda bildim,\par
K\u246?\u253?d\u252?m, bi\u351?dim, \u253?ar-dostlar, \u246?rtendim, eda boldum.\par
\par
\u221?aranlar, \u253?olda\u351? boldum nebsi-howa zalyma,\par
Ke\u253?ik de\u253? ga\u231?ar, barmaz, nesihatg\u246?\u253? alyma,\par
Serke\u351?ligin Suhana me\u351?hur etdi \u228?leme,\par
Men n\u228?te\u253?in, \u253?a, dostlar, ugursyz ykbalyma,\par
Go\u253?mady \u246?z halyma, \u253?\u246?rirge mejalyma,\par
Ne gazanja guwanjym, ne ho\u351?wagtlyk malyma,\par
J\u246?w mukdaryna ge\u231?mez bu jahan hy\u253?alyma,\par
Bilmen, \u228?lem ne k\u246?\u253?de, men ha\u253?ran \u246?z halyma,\par
K\u246?\u253?d\u252?m, bi\u351?dim, \u253?ar-dostlar, \u246?rtendim, eda boldum.\par
\par
J\u228?hl i\u351?ine \u231?apyk men, Alla emrine suster,\par
Garky-zalalat boldum, hida\u253?aty Sen g\u246?ster,\par
Ne derw\u252?\u351? men, ne molla, ne sopy \u228?hli-dester,\par
Garda\u351?lar gulak berse, a\u253?tsam s\u246?z\u252?mi raster,\par
Pikir e\u253?l\u228?\u328?, kim bardyr E\u253?\u228?mden \u246?zge doster,\par
Bendelikde bolmasa\u328?, bolgany\u328? \u253?ag\u351?y nister,\par
G\u246?rmedim G\u252?n astynda hergiz \u246?z\u252?mden pester,\par
Ata\u351?a la\u253?yk bolmaz eda bolan h\u228?kister,\par
K\u246?\u253?d\u252?m, bi\u351?dim, \u253?ar-dostlar, \u246?rtendim, eda boldum.\par
\par
S\u228?hrasyna S\u252?le\u253?man ger s\u252?rse set sy\u253?asat,\par
Gelse peri paty\u351?ahy-Aktemir-u Janpolat,\par
\u221?\u252?z-m\u252?\u328? d\u246?we ba\u351? bolan d\u246?w t\u246?resi Demirbat,\par
Meges \u351?asy Turtarus hemralyk etse, he\u253?hat,\par
Mur m\u228?ligi M\u252?nzere gelse bihet, bega\u253?at,\par
Musa nur golun a\u231?yp, Isa okyp \u253?\u252?z a\u253?at,\par
Hydyr doga e\u253?le\u253?ip, Yl\u253?as etse mynajat,\par
Mundag murda jesede muhaldyr tapmak nejat,\par
\par
K\u246?\u253?d\u252?m, bi\u351?dim, \u253?ar-dostlar, \u246?rtendim, eda boldum.\par
Magtymguly, misginem, k\u246?\u328?l\u252?m \u246?\u253?i n\u228?magmur,\par
S\u246?ze \u253?akyn bende men, ha\u253?rym kem-u \u351?erim zor,\par
\u214?z\u252?m halka n\u228?kabyl, ykbalym ke\u231?, bagtym \u351?or,\par
N\u228?\u351?a\u253?este agmalym, g\u246?\u253?\u228? gadam urar k\u246?r,\par
Meger E\u253?\u228?m istese, bolga\u253? nuran ala nur,\par
\u221?eter tarfatyl-a\u253?nda mehjur bolup d\u252?\u351?en dur,\par
Betgylyk birle boldum jahan i\u231?inde me\u351?hur,\par
Degirmen de\u253? ba\u328?gir men, semender de\u253? ata\u351?hur,\par
\u221?andym, bi\u351?dim, \u253?ar-dostlar, \u246?rtendim, eda boldum.\par
\par
\u199?ILIMKE\u350?\par
Hak seni ra\u253?y\u328?a go\u253?mu\u351? jahanda,\par
Ede bileni\u328? et munda, \u231?ilimke\u351?.\par
Diwan gurlan g\u252?ni hasap ja\u253?ynda,\par
Jowaby\u328? n\u228?medir onda, \u231?ilimke\u351?.\par
\par
Kuwwaty\u328? kemelder, g\u252?\u253?j\u252?\u328? \u252?zd\u252?rer,\par
Ke\u253?pi kell\u228? gelse, akly\u328? azdyrar,\par
S\u252?\u328?\u328?\u252?\u328?i syzdyrar, eti\u328? gyzdyrar,\par
Bir ny\u351?ana budur sende, \u231?ilimke\u351?.\par
\par
El g\u246?tergin be\u253?le n\u228?hak tala\u351?dan,\par
Pulu\u328? k\u246?\u253?er, jany\u328? \u253?anar bu i\u351?den,\par
Erte garny\u328? doldurarlar ata\u351?dan,\par
Z\u228?hmi \u231?ykmaz, galar janda \u231?ilimke\u351?.\par
\par
Iki d\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u253?ag\u351?ylyk \u253?ok egri\u253?e,\par
Ki\u351?i bolsa\u328?, gadam go\u253?gul dogru\u253?a,\par
Binamaza, gybatke\u351?e, ogru\u253?a,\par
\u221?olda\u351? bolar \u253?owuz g\u252?nde \u231?ilimke\u351?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, M\u246?wlam jandan \u253?akyndyr,\par
\u199?ilim bir \u351?or suwdur, ten bir zemindir,\par
Iman bir tilkidir, g\u246?wre bir hindir,\par
Tilki t\u252?ss\u228? d\u246?zmez hinde, \u231?ilimke\u351?.\par
\par
BIRNI\u199?E MYSAL\par
Ugradym Yl\u253?asa, du\u351?dum Hydyra,\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?m i\u231?re geldi birni\u231?e mysal.\par
\par
Gol g\u246?terdim, durdum ny\u253?aza, nezre,\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?Rugsat bolsa, a\u253?da\u253?yn sowal\u187?.\par
\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?Nedir bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni\u328? dirligi?\u187?,\par
Di\u253?di: \u171?\u221?atsa\u328? d\u252?\u253?\u351?d\u252?r, tura\u328?da \u8722? hy\u253?al\u187?.\par
\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?\u221?a, Rep, d\u252?n\u253?\u228? n\u228?ge me\u328?ze\u253?dir?\u187?\par
Di\u253?di: \u171?Garry zendir, \u253?\u252?z\u252?nde \u253?\u252?z hal\u187?.\par
\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?Nedir m\u252?lki-jahan s\u246?\u253?g\u252?si?\u187?\par
Di\u253?di: \u171?Derdeserdir, \u253?a bo\u253?na webal\u187?.\par
\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?D\u252?n\u253?\u228? \u252?\u231?in nedir bahsy-je\u328??\u187?\par
\u171?Bihuda bogaz \u253?yrtmak, \u253?ersiz galmagal\u187?.\par
\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?\u196?hli-zaman n\u228?ge bent olmu\u351??\u187?\par
\u171?Ogul, gyz s\u246?\u253?g\u252?si, jem etm\u228?ge mal\u187?.\par
\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?Bu s\u246?\u253?g\u252?den, maldan ne hasyl?\u187?\par
\u171?\u221?ygmagy ga\u253?gydyr, gitmegi melal\u187?.\par
\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?\u196?hli-zalym ne ta\u253?pa durur?\u187?\par
Di\u253?di: \u171?Gurtdur, itdir, pi\u351?ikdir, \u351?agal\u187?.\par
\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?Ondan nefsim ni\u231?e ram olur?\u187?\par
Di\u253?di ki: \u171?Pir olan ile g\u252?w\u351?mal\u187?.\par
\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?Bende j\u228?hdi ba\u351?a bararmy?\u187?\par
Di\u253?di: \u171?Barmaz, istemese Z\u252?ljelal\u187?.\par
\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?\u221?a, Rep, kethudalyk ni\u231?edir?\u187?\par
Di\u253?di: \u171?Hepde \u8722? e\u351?ret, ga\u253?gy \u8722? galan sal\u187?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?zi d\u252?rdir bilene,\par
Ba\u351?da hu\u351?u\u328? bolsa, s\u246?ze gulak sal.\par
\par
BOLDUM GIR\u221?ANA\par
\u221?azygym \u253?at edip, \u253?\u252?z\u252?m h\u228?k edip,\par
S\u228?her naly\u351? bilen boldum gir\u253?ana.\par
Dideden \u253?a\u351? d\u246?k\u252?p, synam \u231?\u228?k edip,\par
Telbe dek \u246?z\u252?mi urdum her \u253?ana.\par
\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?mi ge\u231?irdim j\u252?mle-jahandan,\par
Ne jahandan, belki, el \u252?zd\u252?m jandan,\par
Hydyrdan, Isadan, \u350?ahymerdandan,\par
H\u252?mmet ist\u228?p bakdym su\u253?y-asmana.\par
\par
Asmany\u328? \u253?\u252?z\u252?nden kehke\u351?an \u246?\u231?di,\par
N\u228?gehan \u252?\u231? \u228?re nazarym d\u252?\u351?di,\par
Iki \u253?a\u351?yl ge\u253?mi\u351?, bir sefit pu\u351?dy,\par
G\u246?z\u252?m g\u246?rdi, tilim gelmez permana.\par
\par
Biri gelip, elin g\u246?gs\u252?me urdy,\par
Biri bir tyg bilen \u253?\u252?regim \u253?ardy,\par
Agzyma agzyn go\u253?up, biri dem urdy,\par
Di\u253?rler: \u171?Arzy\u328? di\u253?gil \u350?ahymerdana!\u187?\par
\par
Bular be\u253?le di\u253?ge\u231?, dilim a\u231?yldy,\par
Gana-gana me\u253?-muhabbet i\u231?ildi,\par
K\u246?\u328?l\u252?me \u253?edi t\u246?wr sowal ge\u231?ildi,\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?Rugsat bolsa, gelsin zybana\u187?.\par
\par
Iki uzyn \u228?rdir, bir gysga kaddyr,\par
Di\u253?diler: \u171?Ho\u351?wagtdyr, \u253?ag\u351?y pursatdyr,\par
S\u246?z\u252?\u328? bolsa, sora - di\u253?rler - rugsatdyr,\par
K\u246?\u328?le gelen s\u246?z\u252?\u328? getir be\u253?ana!\u187?\par
\par
Di\u253?dim: \u171?G\u246?kden agyr, \u253?erden mert nedir?\par
Der\u253?adan ba\u253? nedir, da\u351?dan saht nedir?\par
Otdan \u253?akyjy n\u228?, buzdan sert nedir?\par
Z\u228?herden ajyrak nedir bu jana?\u187?\par
\par
Di\u253?rler: \u171?\u221?aman t\u246?hmet agyr asmandan,\par
Gaharsyz, \u253?ag\u351?y s\u246?z gi\u328?dir jahandan,\par
Mynapygy\u328? k\u246?\u328?li saht se\u328?istandan,\par
\u196?hli-kanyg me\u328?z\u228?r bahry-ummana,\par
\par
Jebr etg\u252?ji soltan \u253?akyjy k\u246?zden,\par
Bahyldan dilemek, sowukdyr buzdan,\par
Jepa\u253?a jan etmek \u8213? z\u228?her jansuzdan,\par
\u214?w\u252?tdir bu s\u246?zler, bizden ny\u351?ana\u187?.\par
\par
Bular be\u253?le di\u253?ge\u231?, \u253?erimden turdum,\par
Gadam urdum, el etegne \u253?etirdim,\par
Mest boldum, sust boldum, \u246?z\u252?m \u253?itirdim,\par
Gep-kelam tapmadym, galdym ha\u253?rana.\par
\par
Di\u253?diler: \u171?\u220?\u231? ki\u351?i bolduk ussady\u328?,\par
Da\u253?ym dessan bolar \u228?lemde ady\u328?,\par
Magtymguly, wagtdyr, iste myrady\u328?...\u187?,\par
Bu syry akmak a\u231?ar, \u253?a bir diwana.\par
\par
U\u199?DUM, \u221?ARANLAR\par
Bir juma gijesi g\u246?rd\u252?m d\u252?\u253?\u351?\u252?mde,\par
Bal urup, g\u246?klere u\u231?dum, \u253?aranlar.\par
Perwaz e\u253?l\u228?p, se\u253?ran etdim d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni,\par
Bir abadan ja\u253?a d\u252?\u351?d\u252?m, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Kehke\u351?ana \u231?ykyp d\u252?rli semerler,\par
M\u252?\u328? d\u252?rli miweler, horram \u351?ejerler,\par
Narynjy, turunjy, le\u253?mun, almalar,\par
Bir abadan baga du\u351?dum \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
A\u231?ylmy\u351?dyr onda re\u328?be-re\u328? g\u252?ller,\par
\u350?ure\u351?-u efganda \u351?e\u253?da bilbiller,\par
Mermerden howuzly, k\u246?wser dek suwlar,\par
Taha\u253?\u253?ur e\u253?le\u253?ip, \u231?a\u351?dym, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Ol gara baglykda g\u246?rd\u252?m bir \u231?emen,\par
Aja\u253?yp mejlisin g\u246?rd\u252?m enj\u252?men.\par
D\u246?wre girip, g\u246?rd\u252?m, oturmy\u351? \u231?ilten,\par
Salam berip, golun gu\u231?dum, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Hemme owaz e\u253?l\u228?p, \u171?Ale\u253?k!\u187? a\u253?dylar,\par
Y\u351?arat e\u253?le\u253?ip: \u171?\u214?tg\u252?l\u187? di\u253?diler,\par
D\u246?wre gurap, jama \u351?erap gu\u253?dular,\par
Ma\u328?a \u253?etge\u231?, golum a\u231?dym, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Bilmedim, k\u246?pmi \u253?a ma\u328?a az berdi,\par
\u214?zge \u228?lem, ba\u351?ga bir owaz berdi,\par
Y\u351?k aldy k\u246?\u328?l\u252?mi, dile s\u246?z berdi,\par
A\u253?akdan-a\u253?aga d\u252?\u351?d\u252?m, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Magtymguly, h\u252?\u351?\u253?ar oldum, o\u253?andym,\par
O\u253?andym, \u246?rtendim, tuta\u351?dym, \u253?andym,\par
Many bazarynda ha\u253?\u253?ata d\u246?nd\u252?m,\par
\u350?irin gazal donun bi\u231?dim \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
O\u221?AN DI\u221?DILER\par
\u221?atyp erdim gamda, geldi erenler,\par
\u171?Turgul-ha \u253?eri\u328?den, o\u253?an!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
G\u246?z\u252?m a\u231?yp g\u246?rd\u252?m j\u252?mle-jahany,\par
\u171?\u350?ol durany \u350?ahymerdan!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Erenler jem bolup, bazar etdiler,\par
Mynapyklar turup, hezer etdiler,\par
Aly babam bize nazar etdiler,\par
Bir k\u228?se me\u253? berip: \u171?I\u231?, gan!\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
O\u253?anyp gaflatdan, a\u231?dym g\u246?z\u252?mi,\par
Erenler pa\u253?yna s\u252?rtd\u252?m \u253?\u252?z\u252?mi,\par
Okatdylar, hak s\u246?zledim s\u246?z\u252?mi,\par
\u171?Segsen m\u252?\u328? kelamy be\u253?an\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Erenler jem bolup, mundan g\u246?\u231?d\u252?ler,\par
Syrat k\u246?pr\u252?sinden bir-bir ge\u231?diler,\par
Ol howzy-K\u246?wserden \u351?erap i\u231?diler,\par
I\u231?en \u351?ahbazlary \u171?Soltan\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?zle bu \u351?irin dilde,\par
Umydym k\u246?p durur \u351?ol duran \u253?olda,\par
B\u228?\u351? wagt namazy\u328?y oka her g\u252?nde,\par
\u171?Ahyret \u253?olda\u351?y\u328? - iman\u187? di\u253?diler.\par
\par
DIWANA GELDI\par
Bir gije \u253?atyrdym, \u351?a Nagy\u351?bendi \u8722?\par
Bahaweddin atly diwana geldi.\par
Hasasyn s\u252?\u253?re\u253?ip gelmi\u351? Buhardan,\par
Hak y\u351?kyna mest-u mestana geldi.\par
\par
Birni\u231?esi \u253?ar-u \u253?aran durdular,\par
Mejlisler uzandy, halka gurdular.\par
Nagralar \u231?ekdiler, semag urdular,\par
Sedalar d\u252?z\u252?ldi, jan-jana geldi.\par
\par
Gowga gopdy, rehmet bo\u253?andy d\u252?zler,\par
Sa\u231?yldy gan \u253?a\u351?lar, a\u231?yldy g\u246?zler,\par
\u221?ygyldy derw\u252?\u351?ler, d\u246?k\u252?ldi pa\u253?zlar,\par
G\u246?\u253?\u228? di\u253?r sen ahyrzamana geldi.\par
\par
Okar bolsa, ylmy-ledun a\u231?ygly,\par
Hem diwana, hem be\u328?\u328?i, hem i\u231?igli,\par
Golunda k\u228?sesi ba\u351?dan ge\u231?igli,\par
Synamda go\u253?dular, bir \u351?ana geldi.\par
\par
Magtymguly a\u253?dar, Gurhana u\u253?dum,\par
Gybaty ta\u351?ladym, haramy go\u253?dum,\par
Sygryna bilmedim, syrymy di\u253?dim,\par
Saklana bilmedim, zybana geldi.\par
\par
BIR NAN GETIRDI\par
Bir gije \u253?atyrdym, \u351?a Nagy\u351?bendi\par
Keremi jo\u351? e\u253?l\u228?p, bir nan getirdi,\par
Sag elinde g\u252?lg\u252?n bada \u351?eraby,\par
Sol elinde t\u228?ze bir\u253?an getirdi.\par
\par
O\u253?andym ukudan, galdym d\u252?\u253?\u351?\u252?mden,\par
Ha\u253?ran galdym Diwanany\u328? i\u351?inden,\par
Badasyn no\u351? e\u253?l\u228?p, gitdim hu\u351?umdan,\par
Gam dideden e\u351?ki-gir\u253?an getirdi.\par
\par
Jan hyru\u351?a geldi ga\u253?nap-jo\u351?madan,\par
\u221?\u252?regim m\u246?w\u231? urdy dolup-da\u351?madan,\par
Bir y\u351?arat boldy o\u328?a d\u252?\u351?medim,\par
P\u228?hm etmedim, janda arman getirdi.\par
\par
A\u328?lamadym, boldum y\u351?ka hyrydar,\par
Bilmedim, istedim Dilberden didar,\par
Y\u351?k derdine d\u252?\u351?d\u252?m, galdym giriftar,\par
Kimse bu dert \u252?\u231?in derman getirdi?.\par
\par
Magtymguly, turdum togap etm\u228?ge,\par
Til perman bermedi jowap etm\u228?ge,\par
Y\u351?k \u228?hlini\u328? halyn harap etm\u228?ge,\par
Aklyn alyp, mesti-ha\u253?ran getirdi.\par
\par
K\u220?LAHLY GELDI\par
Bir gije \u253?atyrdym, bir ahwal g\u246?rd\u252?m,\par
Bir b\u246?lek ba\u351?lary k\u252?lahly geldi.\par
Tisginip o\u253?andym, \u253?erimden turdum,\par
Gollary tylladan hasaly geldi.\par
\par
Bir b\u246?lek erenler degr\u228?mi a\u253?lap,\par
Al-u \u253?a\u351?yl ge\u253?ip, esbabyn \u351?a\u253?lap,\par
Tutdum birisini baryndan sa\u253?lap,\par
Lebleri \u351?ekerden mazaly geldi.\par
\par
Bir peri sallanyp, se\u253?le \u231?ykypdyr,\par
Gamza birle galam ga\u351?yn kakypdyr,\par
Meni\u328? janym y\u351?k oduna \u253?akypdyr,\par
Ba\u351?lary tylladan jygaly geldi.\par
\par
Jepalar \u231?ekipdir \u253?ar di\u253?arynda,\par
Bagda biten alma bile narynda,\par
Magtymguly, bir perini\u328? zarynda\par
Hemmesini\u328? dili senaly geldi.\par
\par
E\u221?\u221?AMY G\u214?RD\u220?M\par
\u350?\u252?k\u252?r Haka, biz hem bu \u253?ola d\u252?\u351?d\u252?k,\par
Ge\u231?irdim, birni\u231?e e\u253?\u253?amy g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
Magrypeti\u328? der\u253?asyna ula\u351?dyk,\par
Aryplar s\u252?rerler, \u253?\u252?z g\u228?mi g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
\par
Hydyr se\u253?ran eder gudrat \u228?lemin,\par
Musa okar hakykaty\u328? kelamyn,\par
\u221?edi g\u252?n almamy\u351? Ta\u328?ry salamyn,\par
Kutbul-Aktap atly betnamy g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
\par
T\u228?ze taban olan \u246?mr\u252?m \u231?yragy,\par
Gy\u351? hazany degse, g\u246?germez bagy,\par
G\u246?z e\u253?l\u228?p gar\u351?yda birni\u231?e saky,\par
Her biri o\u253?nadar, \u253?\u252?z jamy g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
\par
Agladym, \u253?ykyldym, tutdum elini,\par
D\u246?rt pi\u351?wasy bilen Hezret Alyny,\par
Sanjar han, Selim \u351?a, \u253?edi welini,\par
Bir Z\u228?hra, on iki ymamy g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
\par
S\u252?le\u253?many g\u246?rd\u252?m, \u253?atyr e\u253?wanda,\par
Birni\u231?e ga\u253?yplar jem olmu\u351? onda,\par
Gulzum der\u253?asynda, d\u252?\u253?ps\u252?z ummanda\par
Aly, Hatam salan lejamy g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
\par
Karun bu d\u252?n\u253?\u228?ni aldy mal bilen,\par
Iblis asy boldy, gelmez \u253?ol bilen,\par
Semengan \u351?\u228?hrinde batyr Zal bilen,\par
D\u246?w bilen je\u328? salan R\u252?stemi g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
\par
Magtymguly, perman boldy Alladan,\par
\u221?ere inip geldi ar\u351?y-agladan,\par
Jebra\u253?yl getirmi\u351? ulug dergahdan,\par
Muhammede inen Kelamy g\u246?rd\u252?m.\par
\par
\u221?AR \u199?EKER\par
Ta\u328?ry s\u246?\u253?en Muhammedi\u328? ymmaty,\par
\u171?Bismilla\u187? di\u253?p, owal Haky \u253?ar \u231?eker.\par
Biimanlar hergiz g\u246?rmez jenneti,\par
Dowzah i\u231?re k\u246?p azaby-nar \u231?eker.\par
\par
Gam \u231?ekip ahyret \u246?\u253?\u252?n gazanlar,\par
Hakykaty, \u351?erigaty d\u252?zenler,\par
Jepa \u231?ekip Hak \u253?olunda gezenler,\par
S\u228?her turup tagatlaryn ir \u231?eker.\par
\par
Adam ogly ky\u253?amat g\u252?n bolanda,\par
M\u246?mini\u328? g\u252?n\u228?si galmaz teninde,\par
Pul-Syrat \u252?st\u252?nden, he\u253?hat g\u252?n\u252?nde,\par
Sopulary keramatly pir \u231?eker.\par
\par
Ter a\u231?ylan gyzyl g\u252?ller solanda,\par
Ezra\u253?yl adamy\u328? janyn alanda,\par
Ky\u253?amat ahyry mag\u351?ar bolanda,\par
S\u252?\u253?thor bile \u231?ilimke\u351?ler nar \u231?eker.\par
\par
Saparke\u351?ler uzak \u253?oldan ga\u253?danda\par
Agyr \u253?\u252?kli \u351?\u252?t\u252?rlerni ha\u253?danda\par
G\u246?hert \u231?\u246?k\u252?p \u253?\u252?ki galsa me\u253?danda\par
Mazlamasyn hatardaky ner \u231?eker.\par
\par
Me\u253?dan era sap-sap uru\u351? gurulsa,\par
Tasap-tasap arap atlar urulsa,\par
Bir go\u231? \u253?igit galsa bo\u253?ny burulsa,\par
Onu\u328? aryn alp \u253?\u252?rekli \u351?ir \u231?eker.\par
\par
Kimse gezer Biribara \u253?albaryp,\par
Kimse gezer hakykatdan \u253?ol g\u246?r\u252?p,\par
Bir bi\u231?\u228?re \u253?at \u253?oluksa telmuryp\par
Onu\u328? i\u351?in ga\u253?et ger\u231?ek \u228?r \u231?eker.\par
\par
Magtymguly i\u351?i\u328? d\u252?\u351?se mert bile,\par
Namart batyr bolmaz, jedel-\u351?ert bile,\par
Du\u351? gelende hemra bolsa\u328? gurt bile,\par
Her \u231?ent bolsa at \u252?s\u252?nde ar \u231?eker.\par
\par
LEWADA BELLI\par
Nury-mahwe\u351?, ku\u253?a\u351? gutlug habybym,\par
Ady\u328? ser depderde, lewada belli.\par
\u221?edi asman, dokuz pelek \u252?st\u252?nde,\par
Be\u351?er resulynda zy\u253?ada belli.\par
\par
Mahlary\u328? t\u228?ji sen, g\u246?zler \u231?yragy,\par
G\u246?kde melek, \u253?erde be\u351?er \u253?egr\u228?gi,\par
Zemini\u328? rafygy, g\u246?g\u252?\u328? diregi,\par
Lowhy-mahfuzda hem semada belli.\par
\par
\u350?afygyl-m\u252?znibin mag\u351?ar g\u252?n\u252?nde\par
Makamy-agla sen Haky\u328? \u253?olunda\par
\u350?am-u s\u228?her ymmatlary\u328? dilinde\par
M\u246?min dileginde dogada belli\par
\par
Melekler gymmaty\u328? bilm\u228?n gapylar,\par
Az bahaga satdy nice sabylar,\par
Arzuw edip ge\u231?mi\u351? \u246?\u328?ki nebiler,\par
Jelil rehmeti sen, senada belli.\par
\par
Muhabbeti\u328? tende, \u253?\u252?rekde, janda,\par
Ne bir janda, belki j\u252?mle jahanda,\par
H\u252?\u253?ri-ryzwan okar jennet mekanda,\par
\u171?Taha\u187?, \u171?\u221?asin\u187?, bar\u231?a s\u252?rede belli.\par
\par
Gelsin di\u253?ip habar gelge\u231? habypdan\par
Byrag m\u252?n\u252?p \u231?ykdy\u328? arzy-\u351?eripden\par
\u350?epagaty\u328? daryg etme garypdan\par
Mag\u351?ar g\u252?n \u253?etirgin myrada belli\par
\par
Aklymy unutdy y\u351?ky\u328? howasy\par
\u221?\u252?z jan bolsa bir g\u246?rn\u252?\u351?i\u328? pidasy\par
Magtymguly di\u253?rler, \u351?ermende, asy\par
Atasy s\u228?hra\u253?y-Azada belli.\par
\par
USSADA BELLI\par
E\u253?, agalar, bir g\u252?n bolar, pa\u253? alar,\par
Gulluk edip gezen ussada, belli.\par
Huda \u246?zi kime dogry g\u246?zlese,\par
\u221?eti\u351?er myrada, maksada, belli.\par
\par
\u214?wr\u252?le-\u246?wr\u252?le \u351?erbet i\u231?er sen,\par
Dolana dolana, peri gu\u231?ar sen,\par
Ol e\u253?wany g\u246?rse\u328?, mundan ge\u231?er sen,\par
\u214?mr\u252?\u328? \u253?ele berme, d\u252?n\u253?\u228?de belli.\par
\par
Jo\u351?ar sen, her s\u246?zi pe\u253?da eder sen,\par
Jan bilbili sa\u253?rar \u8213? \u351?e\u253?da eder sen,\par
Pelek bir bakgaldyr, s\u246?wda eder sen,\par
Owwal-ahyr utar s\u246?wdada, belli.\par
\par
Mest olar sen, jahyllykda jo\u351?ar sen,\par
Bilmez sen, her i\u351?e ba\u351?y\u328? go\u351?ar sen,\par
Bir g\u252?n bolar, bir zulmata d\u252?\u351?er sen,\par
Ba\u351?y\u328? bilmez, ge\u231?er gowgada, belli.\par
\par
Haram urup, ganlar d\u246?kd\u252?\u328? ellikde,\par
Gel, ne i\u351? bitirdi\u328? segsen \u253?yllykda,\par
Ga\u253?dyp \u253?aman \u253?oldan, gezgin gullukda,\par
Jennet di\u253?ip \u253?\u246?rg\u252?l tamada, belli.\par
\par
Ajal - der\u253?a bo\u253?lar, ba\u351?y\u328?dan a\u351?ar,\par
Seri\u351?d\u228?\u328? suw bolar, akyly\u328? \u231?a\u351?ar,\par
Kyrk g\u252?n owwalyndan \u253?apragy\u328? d\u252?\u351?er,\par
\u171?\u214?li\u187? di\u253?p at bi\u253?rler semada, belli.\par
\par
Keramul-k\u228?tibe\u253?n sag-u solu\u328?a,\par
\u221?azyp, nama\u328? tab\u351?yr mag\u351?ar, golu\u328?a,\par
\u199?arhy-pelek duzak gurmu\u351? \u253?olu\u328?a,\par
Sen \u252?\u231?in oturmy\u351? sa\u253?\u253?ada belli.\par
\par
Kimseden alar sen, kimine bi\u253?r sen,\par
Halal parh etme\u253?in, haramy i\u253?r sen,\par
Bir \u351?a\u253?ydan \u246?tri sowaby\u328? bi\u253?r sen,\par
D\u252?\u351?er sen ondan so\u328? zulmata, belli.\par
\par
\u199?ara\u253?na bagla\u253?yp, ge\u253?en sowutlar,\par
\u221?er go\u253?nuna girdi m\u252?n\u252?p tabytlar,\par
Magtymguly, a\u253?dar, de\u328?-du\u351? \u253?igitler,\par
Garda\u351?lar, \u253?at edi\u328? dogada, belli!\par
\par
ZOR BOLAR\par
\u221?ag\u351?ylykda ile \u246?z\u252?n tanydan -\par
Alky\u351? alyp, derejesi zor bolar,\par
\u221?aman bolup, \u253?ag\u351?ylygy unudan -\par
\u214?z yzzatyn gidir, itden hor bolar.\par
\par
Melul bolar myradyna \u253?etmedik,\par
M\u252?\u253?nli bolar Hak emrini tutmadyk,\par
\u214?z ryzkyna hi\u231? kanagat etmedik,\par
G\u246?z\u252?n diker, ki\u351?i a\u351?yna zar bolar.\par
\par
Her kim \u253?amanlasa de\u328?i-du\u351?uny,\par
\u214?zi m\u252?\u351?gil eder asan i\u351?ini,\par
Kim dargatsa akyl bilen hu\u351?uny,\par
Eder i\u351?in bilmez, \u351?ermisar bolar.\par
\par
Zehini ke\u231? bolar bady \u253?a\u328?ylan,\par
Biygty\u253?ar bolar goly da\u328?ylan,\par
G\u246?re\u351?de \u253?ykylan, je\u328?de \u253?e\u328?ilen,\par
I\u231?i doly namys bilen ar bolar.\par
\par
Ga\u253?raty kem bolar gahary azy\u328?,\par
Depgini pes bolar matamda sazy\u328?,\par
\u214?\u253?\u252?ne barsa\u328?yz, bir biny\u253?azy\u328?,\par
G\u246?wresi gysylar, k\u246?\u328?li dar bolar.\par
\par
Kim belany satyn alsa ba\u351?yna,\par
Re\u351?k edip, rakyplar ge\u231?er da\u351?yna,\par
Toku\u351? etse kim ba\u351?armaz i\u351?ine,\par
S\u246?wdasyndan gele bilse, \u228?r bolar.\par
\par
So\u328?un toba etmez \u253?a\u328?ylyp-\u253?azan,\par
Ot \u253?aksa\u328? ga\u253?namaz bir gury gazan,\par
P\u228?hm edi\u328?, her \u253?erde bir p\u228?li azan,\par
\u221?owuz musallata sezewar bolar.\par
\par
Hazana d\u246?n\u252?pdir \u246?mr\u252?m ter g\u252?li,\par
Nazaryn pes tutar ilden, bergili,\par
Biykbal, \u253?azykly, \u253?aman g\u246?rg\u252?li,\par
U\u231?ra\u351? gelse, bir \u253?amana \u253?ar bolar.\par
\par
\u214?\u328?de, yzda g\u246?rse\u328? her kes gulamyn,\par
Ondan a\u253?amagyn Ta\u328?ry salamyn,\par
Kim okap unutsa Haky\u328? Kelamyn,\par
Ky\u253?amat g\u252?n iki g\u246?zi k\u246?r bolar.\par
\par
Haly m\u252?\u351?gil bolar k\u246?\u253?\u252?p-\u253?anany\u328?,\par
Imany \u351?ikest tapar haram i\u253?eni\u328?,\par
Kastdan roza, namazyny go\u253?any\u328?,\par
\u214?zi kapyr, bili\u328?, ja\u253?y dar bolar,\par
\par
Magtymguly, s\u246?zle her ne bileni\u328?,\par
\u214?z\u252?\u328?e kemlik bil a\u253?tman \u246?leni\u328?,\par
Tara\u351?lap, \u351?aglatgyl k\u246?\u328?le geleni\u328?,\par
Senden so\u328?kulara \u253?adyg\u228?r bolar.\par
\par
SE\u221?RAN I\u199?INDE\par
E\u253?, \u253?aranlar, musulmanlar,\par
Bir gije se\u253?ran i\u231?inde;\par
Otuz iki ki\u351?i g\u246?rd\u252?m\par
Ol \u350?ahymerdan i\u231?inde.\par
\par
Olara berdim salamy,\par
Sordular saglyk kelamy,\par
\u350?yhys-se\u253?it \u8722? M\u246?wla Jamy,\par
Ol \u253?edi soltan i\u231?inde.\par
\par
Soltan We\u253?is p\u228?hliwany,\par
Hekim Ata \u8213? S\u252?le\u253?many,\par
Hoja \u221?usup Hemedany\par
\u350?ol \u351?ahy-Kengan i\u231?inde.\par
\par
T\u252?rk\u252?stan e\u253?esi serwer,\par
Ymam K\u228?zim, ymam Jafar,\par
\u221?ah\u253?a bilen Nuh pygamber,\par
Ba\u253?ezit soltan i\u231?inde.\par
\par
G\u246?zel pirler - g\u246?zel \u253?arlar,\par
\u199?ekdiler bu \u253?olda zarlar,\par
Ymam Ryza \u8722? \u351?ahy-pirler,\par
Ni\u231?e g\u246?zel jan i\u231?inde.\par
\par
Magtymguly, syrym \u231?ohdur,\par
Men ne\u253?l\u228?\u253?in, a\u231?an \u253?okdur,\par
\u214?lmek - hak, direlmek hakdyr,\par
Okadym Gurhan i\u231?inde.\par
\par
ATLY, \u221?ARANLAR\par
Depderler i\u231?inde bir kitap g\u246?rd\u252?m,\par
\u171?Kasasyl-enbi\u253?a\u187? atly, \u253?aranlar.\par
Hezreti \u221?usuby be\u253?an e\u253?l\u228?li,\par
Kyssasy \u351?ekerden datly, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Renji azym, rahaty k\u246?p, \u351?e\u253?le bil,\par
S\u246?zleri hadysdyr, a\u253?aty-delil,\par
Beni Ishak ibni Ybra\u253?ym Halyl,\par
\u221?alawa\u231? urugy zatly, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
On iki ogly bar, altysy hatyn,\par
Habar sorsa\u328?, budur bu asylzatyn,\par
Illalla Ta\u328?ryny\u328? ol mugjyzatyn,\par
\u221?akuby k\u246?r basr etdi, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
\u221?edi \u253?a\u351?da \u221?usup g\u246?rdi bu d\u252?\u253?\u351?i,\par
\u221?aranlar tagajjup Allany\u328? i\u351?i,\par
\u350?emgun, Rubil atly ondur garda\u351?y,\par
\u221?usuby bir \u231?aha atdy, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
\u171?\u221?usup jany b\u246?ri i\u253?di\u187? di\u253?diler,\par
Bir b\u246?rini tutup baglap geldiler,\par
Hezreti \u221?akup bir doga kyldylar,\par
B\u246?ri \u246?z halyny a\u253?tdy, \u253?aranlar:\par
\par
\u171?Bir balam bar, \u253?itirip men \u253?anymdan,\par
\u220?\u231? g\u252?n boldy, ist\u228?p tapman \u253?abandan,\par
Dilegi\u328? kabuldyr seni\u328? Suhandan,\par
Doga kyl\u187? di\u253?p, umyt etdi, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
\u221?usuby saldylar tehi-zemine,\par
Onu\u328? dagly k\u246?\u328?li boldy kemine,\par
Hak emr etdi ol Jebra\u253?yl emine,\par
Bir demde \u221?usuby n\u228?tdi, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
\u199?ah i\u231?inde \u253?atdy \u252?\u231? gije-g\u252?ndiz,\par
Hezreti Jebra\u253?yl saklady t\u228?miz,\par
Bir a\u253? bile bir g\u252?n ol on bir \u253?yldyz\par
\u221?usuba k\u246?p tagzym etdi, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Bir kerwen gele\u253?di M\u252?s\u252?rden \u350?ama,\par
N\u228?gehan geldiler u\u351?bu makama,\par
Be\u351?ir, Be\u351?er atly iki gulama,\par
Birgip gowalaryn tartdy, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Gowalaryn \u231?ykardylar da\u351?yna,\par
\u221?usup \u231?ykdy a\u253? dek bolup ny\u351?ana,\par
\u221?\u252?z m\u252?\u328? \u351?\u252?k\u252?r kyldy ol dem Suhana\par
Gullara iman arz etdi \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Allany\u328? emrine sunup bo\u253?nuny,\par
Begler g\u246?r\u252?\u328?, bu \u351?um pelek o\u253?nuny,\par
Hezreti \u221?akuby\u328? nury-a\u253?nyny,\par
Gullar hojasyga a\u253?tdy \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
M\u228?lik Dinar alyp bardy Kengana,\par
Habar tapdy baky on t\u246?rt diwana,\par
\u221?usup Syddyk \u171?Gul men\u187? di\u253?di merdana,\par
On sekiz \u253?armakga satdy \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Paty\u351?any\u328? ady M\u228?lik Ry\u253?\u253?andy,\par
Wezirini\u328? ady Eziz Gerendi,\par
Olar boldy \u8722? Z\u252?le\u253?haga derekli,\par
M\u228?lik Dinar o\u328?a satdy, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Dellallar \u253?ygnalyp, baha go\u253?dular,\par
\u171?Bo\u253?y de\u328?i altyn-k\u252?m\u252?\u351?\u187? di\u253?diler,\par
Lagly j\u246?wahyrdan an\u231?a o\u253?dular,\par
\u171?H\u228?lem bolsa arzan!\u187? a\u253?tdy \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
\u350?\u228?her ortasynda bir tagt gurdular,\par
\u221?usup Syddyk: \u171?Gul men\u187? di\u253?ip durdular,\par
Gymmat go\u253?up, Z\u252?le\u253?haga berdiler,\par
Ahyr myradyna \u253?etdi, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
A\u351?yk oldy \u228?r \u221?usuby\u328? g\u246?rk\u252?ne,\par
Saldylar \u253?edi gat \u253?eri\u328? berkine,\par
Alty hatyn go\u253?madylar erkine,\par
\u221?usup hem olara n\u228?tdi, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Hatynlar mekrinden ga\u231?dy, gutuldy,\par
Etegin kesdiler, da\u351?da tutuldy,\par
Ni\u231?e \u253?yllar zyndan i\u231?re \u253?atyldy,\par
\u221?usup hem tamamyn \u246?tdi, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
\u221?usup Syddyk \u253?atyr zyndan i\u231?inde,\par
Paty\u351?a bir waka g\u246?rdi d\u252?\u253?\u351?\u252?nde,\par
M\u252?ne\u231?jimler bes bar idi ga\u351?ynda,\par
Her ka\u253?sy bir tagbyr a\u253?tdy, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Elkyssa, bu tagbyr \u221?usuba \u253?etdi,\par
\u221?usup hem ol d\u252?\u253?\u351?\u252?\u328? be\u253?anyn etdi,\par
Ybrat alyp, pat\u351?a ra\u253?yndan ga\u253?tdy,\par
Tamamyn musulman etdi, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
\u221?usup tagta m\u252?n\u252?p, pat\u351?a boldular,\par
Tamam M\u252?s\u252?r halkyn satyn aldylar,\par
Agalary gelip, tagzym kyldylar,\par
K\u252?lli g\u252?n\u228?lerin \u246?tdi, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
Magtymguly s\u246?zl\u228?r Haky\u328? sungatyn,\par
Bende sen, hatyby\u328? emrine k\u246?\u253?g\u252?n,\par
Kime b\u228?\u351? g\u252?n berer, kims\u228?ge on g\u252?n,\par
S\u252?reweri\u328?, d\u246?wran \u246?tdi, \u253?aranlar.\par
\par
ARAP TILLI, S\u214?WD\u220?GIM\par
Bo\u253?adylar k\u246?\u253?negi\u328?i gan bile,\par
Ady belli, arap tilli s\u246?wd\u252?gim.\par
